NK119(he)001:1: // rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i lam gyi cha lag
NK119(he)001:2: sdom gsum rnam par nges pa'i 'grel pa rnam grol
NK119(he)001:3: lam bzang zhes bya ba bzhugs so //
NK119(he)001:4: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i lam gyi cha lag
NK119(he)001:5: sdom pa gsum rnam par nges pa'i 'grel pa rnam
NK119(he)001:6: grol lam bzang zhes bya ba /
NK119(he)001:8: chos kun stong nyid rang bzhin zla mdzes gzhon nu'i mkha' dbyings khyon yangs par //
NK119(he)001:9: so sor rtogs pa'i ye shes gsal ba'i dkyil 'khor ngag dbang rta bdun rgyas //
NK119(he)001:10: mkhyen dang brtse ba'i 'od kyis srid zhi'i khams kun 'gengs la bsnyengs pa bral //
NK119(he)001:11: stangs dpyal gnyis med yang ye bdag blo'i dbyings bzhugs brtsam legs mthar phyin stsol //
NK119(he)001:12: grangs med so thar ltar dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK119(he)001:13: bskal par tshogs gnyis chu gter bsrubs las spang rtogs
NK119(he)001:14: phun tshogs yon tan lhun po thub dbang sprul pa'i
NK119(he)001:15: sku // chos can chos nyid 'gog dang lam bden
NK119(he)001:16: sprin chen chags dang bral ba'i rgyun zegs rab 'thul
NK119(he)001:18: rigs bdun spang dang bsgrub pa'i pad tshal ldan grol
NK119(he)001:19: dri bsung mthar khyab zhugs dang zhugs 'bras sbrang rtsi'i
NK119(he)001:20: 'byung gnas mchog / sangs rgyas gser gyi phung po
NK119(he)001:21: dam chos bdud rtsi'i dpal 'byor 'chal pa'i 'dam gyis
NK119(he)001:22: rab dben chos gsum zhabs la bdud //
NK119(he)001:23: dpag byang sems ltar dkon mchog gsum med sngon nas
NK119(he)001:24: mngon par byang chub chos sku'i dbyings las srid pa
NK119(he)001:25: ji srid 'gro ba'i khur chen bzhes mdzad dam pa
NK119(he)001:26: sku gnyis bdag / sde snod rab 'byams lung gi
NK119(he)001:27: rkang 'thung sa rab dga' ba'i dpal las rtogs pa'i
NK119(he)001:28: 'bras smin legs gsung dam pa'i chos khams dge //
NK119(he)001:29: sgrib pa'i mun bral gzhan don 'od dkar mthar khyab
NK119(he)001:30: sa lam cha shas rdzogs pa'i byang sems 'phags pa'i
NK119(he)001:31: dge 'dun mchog / mkhyen brtse'i dbang phyug skye dgu'i
NK119(he)001:32: rten ma lung rtogs dpag bsam ljon pa rgyal sras
NK119(he)001:33: kun+da'i bshes gyur bla med mchog gsum zhabs la 'dud
NK119(he)001:34: dge 'dun mchog / // gdod gsang sngags ltar dkon mchog gsum /
NK119(he)001:35: ma'i gzhi dbyings sbubs su mngon par mthar phyin sgyu
NK119(he)001:36: 'phrul dra ba sku lnga'i 'od zer mu mtha' med
NK119(he)001:37: pa'i bdag / stong phrag du ma'i rgyud sde rgya
NK119(he)001:38: mtsho zab dang rgya che bskyed rdzogs grub pa'i dgongs
NK119(he)001:39: don yid bzhin dbyig gi mdzod //
NK119(he)001:40: thabs mang tshegs bral 'bad med rtsal rdzogs grub pa'i
NK119(he)001:41: dbang phyug brgyad ldan rig 'dzin rnam bzhi'i gangs ri'i
NK119(he)001:42: rtser gnon pa // khyab bdag rigs kun nyi ma
NK119(he)001:43: mtshon bya byed pa'i rgyud sde'i chu gter dbang thob
NK119(he)001:44: rig 'dzin stobs ldan mchog gsum bla mar 'dud //
NK119(he)001:45: gsum ldan bla ma dkon mchog gsum dngos snang srid
NK119(he)001:46: dag mnyam ye grol dbang dang dam tshig lhun grub
NK119(he)001:47: sku lnga'i khyab bdag mkha' ltar dag pa'i thugs /
NK119(he)001:48: mdo rgyud rab 'byams rgya mtsho'i sprin chen spang thob
NK119(he)001:49: rlabs chen byang sems bslab bya'i bdud rtsis yongs gang
NK119(he)001:50: gsung // rnam dkar bzang po'i mdzad phrin brtul zhugs
NK119(he)001:51: bzang po'i 'dul khrims phun tshogs rnam grol sgra brgya'i
NK119(he)001:52: gsung // dbyangs ldan sku // mchod do gsum ldan
NK119(he)001:53: rdo rje 'dzin rgyal sgo gsum mchog gsum rang bzhin
NK119(he)001:54: dkon mchog bzhi pa bla ma'i zhabs //
NK119(he)001:55: pad 'byung slar yang dpal ldan rtsa ba'i bla ma la /
NK119(he)001:56: thugs rje'i 'od dkar nya gang la //
NK119(he)001:57: skal bzang rlan 'dzin 'pho ba'i zlos gar can //
NK119(he)001:58: mi g.yo kun khyab bdag blo'i gtsug rgyan mchog /
NK119(he)001:59: ma ra dzi tam badz+ra des 'dir skyongs //
NK119(he)001:61: rnam grol mchog gi rtsal rdzogs ri dwags rgyal po
NK119(he)001:62: yongs kyis 'khra sa hi ma la ya'i gnas dag
NK119(he)001:63: las // sdom gsum bka' dang bstan bcos sprin zegs
NK119(he)001:64: du ma'i tshogs kyang thos bsam sgom pa'i rnam dpyod
NK119(he)001:66: legs bzhus tshig gi lam las 'chos skyobs gnyis ldan
NK119(he)001:67: phu chu'i rgyun 'bab lhag bsam dbu phreng dkar po
NK119(he)001:68: g.yo ba can // gang zhig nges legs bdud rtsis
NK119(he)001:69: phongs pa'i srid lam mya ngan dgon par 'khyams kun
NK119(he)001:71: de la gang gi tshe dpal kun tu bzang po
NK119(he)001:72: khyab bdag rdo rje 'chang chen po de nyid gdod
NK119(he)001:73: ma'i gzhi la mngon par byang chub ste sku gsum
NK119(he)001:74: 'du 'bral med pa'i rang bzhin sku gsung thugs mi
NK119(he)001:75: 'dzad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i bdag nyid du bzhugs
NK119(he)001:76: so // de'i tshe sgyu ma'i grong khyer rigs drug
NK119(he)001:77: gi khams la'ang bde gshegs snying pos ma khyab pa
NK119(he)001:78: so // med kyang / rang ngo ma shes te
NK119(he)001:79: gzung 'dzin las dang nyon mongs pa mthu brtas pa
NK119(he)001:80: so // med kyang / las / srid pa'i gdung bas kun nas nyon mongs par gyur pa lags /
NK119(he)001:81: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rnam par rol ba bsam gyis
NK119(he)001:82: mi khyab pas 'jig rten gyi 'dren par sgrun du
NK119(he)001:83: med pa'i mnga' dbang bsgyur ba las /
NK119(he)001:84: de yang ston pa sangs rgyas 'jig rten du byung zhing /
NK119(he)001:85: des bstan pa'i gsung rab dam pa'i chos rnams kyang
NK119(he)001:86: skyes bu dam pa rnams kyi bka' drin las gnas
NK119(he)001:87: pa dang / de dag kyang bslab pa gsum ste
NK119(he)001:88: sdom pa gsum gyi mdzod 'dzin cing rigs can gsum
NK119(he)001:89: gyi 'gro ba rnams bla na med pa'i sar 'god
NK119(he)001:90: pa'i phrin las la snyems pa dang bral ba 'ba'
NK119(he)001:91: pa dang / zhig go // de lta bas na /
NK119(he)001:92: rang nyid kyi dal 'byor gyi mi lus rin po
NK119(he)001:93: che thob pa'i dus 'dir 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal gyi
NK119(he)001:94: rgya mtsho chen po las rang dang gzhan gyi 'gro
NK119(he)001:95: ba rnams yongs su sgrol ba'i phyir /
NK119(he)001:96: sngon gyi lam ldan chen po dag gi tshul la dkri bar bya ba las gzhan ma yin zhing /
NK119(he)001:97: de yang sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa'i gzhi ma 'dul ba'i khrims dang /
NK119(he)001:98: bstan pa'i gzhung lam byang chub tu sems bskyed pa'i bslab bya /
NK119(he)001:99: bstan pa'i snying po gsang sngags kyi dam tshig ste /
NK119(he)001:100: sdom pa gsum po de dag gya tshoms su mi 'dor bar /
NK119(he)001:102: gsum ldan du gang zag gis nyams su len pa'i
NK119(he)001:103: tshul rnam par nges pa'i bstan bcos sdom gsum rnam
NK119(he)001:104: nges zhes bya ba 'di nyid ni 'chad par bya
NK119(he)001:105: ba'i chos so // de yang 'di skad thos te /
NK119(he)001:107: gzugs brnyan rang bzhin yon tan ldan pa me long nang dag na //
NK119(he)001:108: mthong ba'i dbang gis mi rnams rab tu dga' ba'i mchog bskyed pa //
NK119(he)001:109: de bzhin legs gsungs rtag tu rang bzhin yon tan ldan pa yi //
NK119(he)001:110: chos kyang don rnams phye bas mkhas rnams 'di na dga' mchog bskyed //
NK119(he)001:112: byams pa seng ge'i sgras zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK119(he)001:113: stong gsum 'jig rten khams 'dir gser dag gis //
NK119(he)001:114: bkang ste gzhan la sbyin pa byin pa bas //
NK119(he)001:115: tshig bzhi tshigs su bcad pa gcig ston pas //
NK119(he)001:116: ci ltar phan 'dogs de ltar gyur ma yin //
NK119(he)001:121: dbye ba don 'grel grub mtha' gsang 'grel te tshul bzhi dang /
NK119(he)001:125: rgya cher 'grel la sogs 'dod pa mtha' yas kyang /
NK119(he)001:126: 'dir don 'grel 'ba' zhig gi dbang du bshad par bya'o //
NK119(he)001:128: mtshan smos pas bstan bcos ngos bzung ba dang /
NK119(he)001:129: de nyid rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK119(he)001:131: de yang bstan bcos kyi rang bzhin ni /
NK119(he)001:132: ston pa sangs rgyas kyi bka'i dgongs 'grel du brtsam
NK119(he)001:133: pa 'chos skyob kyi yon tan gnyis dang ldan pa
NK119(he)001:134: ste / rnam bshad rig pa las /
NK119(he)001:135: nyon mongs dgra rnams ma lus 'chos pa dang //
NK119(he)001:136: ngan 'gro'i srid las skyob pa gang yin pa //
NK119(he)001:137: 'chos skyob yon tan phyir na bstan bcos te //
NK119(he)001:138: gnyis po 'di dag gzhan gyi lugs la med //
NK119(he)001:140: dbye na ltar snang ba'i bstan bcos drug dang /
NK119(he)001:141: yang dag pa'i bstan bcos gsum ste /
NK119(he)001:142: thos pa las byung ba'i sa rnam par gtan la dbab pa las /
NK119(he)001:143: don med don log don dang ldan //
NK119(he)001:144: thos rtsod sgrub pa lhur len dang //
NK119(he)001:145: ngan g.yo brtse bral sdug bsngal 'byin //
NK119(he)001:146: bstan bcos drug bral gsum du 'dod //
NK119(he)001:148: 'dir ni gnas skabs bde zhing mthar thug grol ba thob pa'i don dang ldan pa dang /
NK119(he)001:150: 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal 'byin pa'i tshul yang dag pa gsum dang ldan pa'i bstan bcos so //
NK119(he)001:151: de yang tshul khrims ting 'dzin shes rab kyi bslab
NK119(he)001:152: pa gsum gyi dbang du mdzad nas sde snod gsum
NK119(he)001:153: gyi rnam par mdzad pa ste /
NK119(he)001:155: ltung dang 'byung dang ldang pa dang //
NK119(he)001:156: nges par 'byung dang gang zag dang //
NK119(he)001:157: bcas pa dang ni rab dbye dang //
NK119(he)001:158: rnam par nges phyir 'dul ba'i don //
NK119(he)001:159: gnas rnams dang ni mtshan nyid dang //
NK119(he)001:160: chos don smos phyir mdo yin no //
NK119(he)001:161: mngon du'i phyir dang yang dang yang //
NK119(he)001:162: zil gnon rtogs phyir mngon pa'i chos //
NK119(he)001:164: de yang rtsis 'go yan lag lngas 'chad de /
NK119(he)001:165: mdzad pa po gang gis mdzad ce na /
NK119(he)001:166: bstan bcos rtsom pa po rab chos nyid kyi bden pa mthong ba /
NK119(he)001:167: 'bring yi dam lhas gnang ba thob pa /
NK119(he)001:168: tha ma'ang rig pa'i gnas lnga la mkhas shing brgyud
NK119(he)001:169: pa'i man ngag yod pa zhig dgos par gsungs pa
NK119(he)001:170: las / 'dir rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po bya
NK119(he)001:171: rtsol dang bral ba'i chos nyid mngon du gyur cing
NK119(he)001:172: las / / yi dam gyi lha du mas byin gyis brlabs shing /
NK119(he)001:173: khyad par rig 'dzin chen po pad+ma 'byung gnas kyis rjes su bzung bas /
NK119(he)001:174: zab mo'i gter rig 'dzin yongs 'dus dang /
NK119(he)001:176: gu ru drag po yang gsang rdo rje 'bar ba
NK119(he)001:177: la sogs pa gter kha ji snyed pa'i mdzod 'dzin
NK119(he)001:178: pa / gangs can gyi ljongs na mang du thos
NK119(he)001:179: pa rnams kyi khyu mchog tu gyur pa mnga' ris
NK119(he)001:180: pa gter ston chen po pad ma dbang gi rgyal
NK119(he)001:181: po de nyid kyis mdzad pa'o //
NK119(he)001:182: ji skad du rgyud bla ma las /
NK119(he)001:183: gang zhig ston pa rgyal ba 'ba' zhig gis //
NK119(he)001:184: dbang byas rnam g.yeng med yid can gyis sbyar //
NK119(he)001:185: thar pa thob pa'i lam dang rjes mthun pa //
NK119(he)001:186: de yang drang srong bka' bzhin spyi bos blang //
NK119(he)001:188: lung gang nas btus zhe na 'dul ba /
NK119(he)001:190: mngon pa ste sde snod gsum dang /
NK119(he)001:191: gsang sngags phyi nang kun las btus pa'o //
NK119(he)001:192: phyogs gang du gtogs zhe na /
NK119(he)001:193: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen por gtogs te de'i lam gyi cha lag yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK119(he)001:194: don ched su'i don du mdzad ce na /
NK119(he)001:195: phyi rabs kyi gang zag rim gyis pa dang gcig
NK119(he)001:196: char ba thams cad skyel so mthun par byas pa'o
NK119(he)001:197: // dbu nas zhabs su bsdus pa'i don gang yin zhe na /
NK119(he)001:198: dbu mtshan smos pas dbu zhabs don khong chud /
NK119(he)001:199: gsung bas 'dir mtshan smos pas don shes pas sla ba ste /
NK119(he)001:201: ming du gdags par ma mdzad na //
NK119(he)001:203: de bas rmongs pa bsal ba'i phyir //
NK119(he)001:204: ston pas ming du gdags par mdzad //
NK119(he)001:206: de yang gsung rab la ming gdags pa'i tshul yang /
NK119(he)001:207: dpe la mtshan du gsol ba dkon mchog ta la la'i mdo lta bu /
NK119(he)001:208: don la mtshan du gsol ba gsang ba 'dus pa lta bu /
NK119(he)001:209: sho lo ka la mtshan du gsol ba stong phrag brgya ba lta bu /
NK119(he)001:210: yul las mtshan du gsol ba lang kar gshegs pa lta bu dang /
NK119(he)001:211: zhu ba po las mtshan du gsol ba byams pas zhus pa lta bu las /
NK119(he)001:213: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i lam gyi cha lag sdom pa gsum rnam par nges pa //
NK119(he)001:215: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i dbang dang bsgrub pa'i
NK119(he)001:216: dus su thob cing khas blangs bas na de'i lam
NK119(he)001:218: cha lag mkho byar gyur pas na /
NK119(he)001:221: dam tshig ste sdom pa gsum mo //
NK119(he)001:226: so thar gyi sdom pas gzhan gnod gzhi dang bcas pa spang ba dang /
NK119(he)001:227: byang sems kyi sdom pas de'i steng du gzhan phan gyi dge ba bsgrub pa dang /
NK119(he)001:228: de'i steng du sngags sdom gyis rang sems yongs su grol bar byed pa ste /
NK119(he)001:229: sdig pa ci yang mi bya zhing //
NK119(he)001:230: dge ba phun sum tshogs par spyad //
NK119(he)001:231: rang gi sems ni yongs su gdul //
NK119(he)001:232: 'di ni sangs rgyas bstan pa yin //
NK119(he)001:234: de yang thog mar sdom gsum spyi'i gnas lugs bstan nas /
NK119(he)001:235: bye brag de dag so sor bshad /
NK119(he)001:236: 'gag gang zag gcig gis nyams su ji ltar blang ba'i thabs bshad pa ste /
NK119(he)001:238: gnyis pa de nyid rgyas par bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK119(he)001:239: bstan bcos la 'jug pa klad kyi don dang /
NK119(he)001:240: brjod par bstan pa gzhung gi don dang /
NK119(he)001:241: mthar phyin pa gzhug gi don no //
NK119(he)001:246: dpal ldan tshogs gnyis chu gter bsrubs pa las //
NK119(he)001:247: mkhyen brtse'i 'od dkar nges gsang gru char 'bebs //
NK119(he)001:248: gangs can mkhas grub yongs kyi gtsug rgyan mchog /
NK119(he)001:249: mtsho skyes rdo rje 'gro ba'i bla mar 'dud //
NK119(he)001:250: ces bya ba dag smos te /
NK119(he)001:251: gang zhig tshig dang don gyi skal ba bzang pos snyan par bstod pa ni /
NK119(he)001:256: de dag kyang mdzes par byed pa'i rgyan gyi rnam grangs sum cu rtsa lnga yod de /
NK119(he)001:258: slob dpon dan+da'i snyan ngag me long rol mtsho las /
NK119(he)001:259: rang bzhin brjod dang dpe dang ni //
NK119(he)001:260: gzugs can gsal byed bskor ba can //
NK119(he)001:261: 'gog dang don gzhan bkod pa dang //
NK119(he)001:262: zlog pa can dang srid pa can //
NK119(he)001:263: sdus dang phul byung rab brtag dang //
NK119(he)001:264: rgyu dang phra mo cha dang rim //
NK119(he)001:265: dga' dang nyams ldan gzi brjid can //
NK119(he)001:266: rnam grangs brjod pa kun phan dang //
NK119(he)001:267: rgya che bsnyon dor sbyar ba dang //
NK119(he)001:268: khyad par brjod dang mtshungs par sbyar //
NK119(he)001:269: 'gal dang skabs min bstod pa dang //
NK119(he)001:270: zol bstod nges par bstan pa dang //
NK119(he)001:271: lhan cig brjod dang yongs barjesa shis //
NK119(he)001:272: rab spel de nas dgongs pa can //
NK119(he)001:273: de dag tshig rnams dag gi ni //
NK119(he)001:274: rgyan du sngon gyi mkhas rnams bzhed //
NK119(he)001:277: tshogs gnyis mthu brtas pa'i sku gnyis kyi dpal gyi
NK119(he)001:278: char rgyun gyis yongs su gang ba'i sprin chen chu'i
NK119(he)001:279: rgyun du ma'i gter 'dzin pa kun nas g.yos shing
NK119(he)001:280: bsrubs pa las byung ba'i chu shel gyi dwangs ma
NK119(he)001:281: / chos nyid ji lta ba mkhyen pa dang /
NK119(he)001:282: chos can ji snyed pa mkhyen pa'i ye shes gnyis
NK119(he)001:283: dang thugs rje chen po'i 'od dkar kun nas bsil
NK119(he)001:284: ba ga bur gyi rgyun ltar 'phro zhing /
NK119(he)001:285: theg pa thams cad dang khyad par gsang sngags kyi
NK119(he)001:286: ston pa'i rnam par 'phrul pa gdul bya'i chu snod
NK119(he)001:287: ji snyed pa de snyed du gru char 'bebs pa'i
NK119(he)001:289: bod yul gyi snga phyir gshegs shing byon pa'i mkhas
NK119(he)001:290: pa dang grub pa brnyes pa thams cad kyi gtsug
NK119(he)001:291: phud kyi rgyan du kun nas thal ler mdzes pa
NK119(he)001:292: ni / d+ha na ko sha'i mtsho gling du rang
NK119(he)001:293: byung pad ma'i snying po las rang byon pa'i sangs
NK119(he)001:294: rgyas kun dngos pad+ma 'byung gnas de nyid /
NK119(he)001:295: de yang zla ba ni chu'i khams kyi dwangs ma
NK119(he)001:296: las byung ba'i 'og gzhi chu shel las grub phyir
NK119(he)001:297: mtsho skyes zhes pa dang dpe don mnyam par gnas
NK119(he)001:298: pa ste / de ni gzugs can gyi rgyan du gnas pa'o //
NK119(he)001:299: 'o na bod gangs can pa'i bla ma las gzhan gyis ma yin nam zhe na /
NK119(he)001:300: de ni gangs ri'i rgyal po la zla ba'i zer
NK119(he)001:301: gyis sbags pas dkar la 'tsher ba'i tshad sgrun du
NK119(he)001:303: don bdag cag bod kyi yul 'dir thub pa bcom
NK119(he)001:304: ldan 'das la sogs pas zhabs kyis ma bcags zhing
NK119(he)001:305: / pad+ma 'byung gnas ni gcig tu bdag cag bod
NK119(he)001:306: kyi 'dren pa 'ba' zhig tu gyur pas bka' drin
NK119(he)001:307: dran pa'i ched du yin zhing /
NK119(he)001:309: ces pas 'gro drug thams cad kyi skyabs gnas yin par des ston pa ste /
NK119(he)001:310: de nyid la gus pas phyag 'tshal ba'o //
NK119(he)001:311: de yang dpal ldan tshogs gnyis ni /
NK119(he)001:312: dpal zhes pa ye shes kyi tshogs mthar phyin pas /
NK119(he)001:313: chos sku'i dbyings las mi g.yo ba rang gi dpal dang /
NK119(he)001:314: bsod nams kyi tshogs mthar phyin pas gzugs sku'i rnam
NK119(he)001:315: par rol ba gzhan gyi dpal gnyis dang ldan pa
NK119(he)001:316: ste / glang chen rab 'bog gi rgyud las /
NK119(he)001:317: chos kyi sku las ma g.yos bzhin //
NK119(he)001:318: gzugs kyi sku lnga lhun gyis grub //
NK119(he)001:319: de las don gnyis yongs rdzogs phyir //
NK119(he)001:320: dpal ni lhun rdzogs gcig tu rol //
NK119(he)001:323: gzugs kyi sku ni mdor bsdus na //
NK119(he)001:324: bsod nams tshogs las 'khrungs pa ste //
NK119(he)001:325: chos kyi sku ni mdor bsdus na //
NK119(he)001:326: rgyal po ye shes tshogs las 'khrungs //
NK119(he)001:328: tshogs gnyis rang gi ngo bo ni /
NK119(he)001:329: phar phyir drug gis bsdus pa'i dge ba'i rtsa ba rnams te /
NK119(he)001:331: sbyin dang tshul khrims bsod nams kyi //
NK119(he)001:332: tshogs yin shes rab ye shes kyi //
NK119(he)001:333: gsum ni gnyis char la yang gtogs //
NK119(he)001:335: de ltar phyag 'tshal ba'i phan yon ni /
NK119(he)001:336: rang dang gzhan dang gnyis kas thob pa nyid las /
NK119(he)001:337: dang po rang gis thob pa'ang /
NK119(he)001:338: yul mchog tu gyur pa la bstod pas rang nyid
NK119(he)001:339: dam par rtogs shing dam pa'i spyod pa la zhugs
NK119(he)001:340: pas brtsam pa mthar phyin pa'i dgos pa yod de
NK119(he)001:341: / brgyad stong 'grel chen las gzhan don brtse ba can rnams srog phyir yang /
NK119(he)001:342: rang gi brtson pa lhod par mi 'gyur te //
NK119(he)001:343: skyes bu dam pa khur lci khur ba dag /
NK119(he)001:344: nyams nga'i gnas su nam yang 'dor mi byed //
NK119(he)001:347: ston pa dang bstan bcos la dam par rtogs nas 'dun pa ste /
NK119(he)001:348: klu sgrub kyi zhal snga nas /
NK119(he)001:349: bstan bcos byed pas ston pa la //
NK119(he)001:350: mchod par brjod pa 'bras med min //
NK119(he)001:351: ston pa dang ni bstan bcos la //
NK119(he)001:352: dad 'dun bskyed par bya phyir ro //
NK119(he)001:355: tshogs rdzogs pas smon pa'i don 'grub pa ste /
NK119(he)001:357: bsod nams ldan pa'i mi yis bsam pa rnams kyang 'grub //
NK119(he)001:359: gnyis pa brtsam par dam bca' ba ni /
NK119(he)001:360: de ltar phyag 'tshal nas ci bya zhe na /
NK119(he)001:361: 'gro blo'i dri ma 'khrud mkhas drang srong gis //
NK119(he)001:362: blo gros chu gter bum bzang rab thogs nas //
NK119(he)001:363: legs bshad sdom gsum bdud rtsi'i chu sbyin gyi //
NK119(he)001:364: don gnyer skye bo'i tshogs rnams 'dir 'dus shig /
NK119(he)001:365: de yang 'gro ba'i khams la de bzhin gshegs pa'i
NK119(he)001:366: snying pos til la mar gyis khyab pa ltar gnas
NK119(he)001:367: pa nyid / sgyu 'phrul rgyas pa las /
NK119(he)001:368: rgya che ba dang yangs pa dang //
NK119(he)001:369: ye shes gzugs brnyan 'dzin pa'i phyir //
NK119(he)001:370: dbyings ni dag pa'i rgya mtsho 'dra //
NK119(he)001:371: ma rig gzung 'dzin rlung dag gis //
NK119(he)001:372: dkrug pas rnyog pa can du byas //
NK119(he)001:375: sangs rgyas pad ngan sbrang ma sbrang rtsi sogs //
NK119(he)001:376: dpe dgus ye shes sgrib par gsungs te //
NK119(he)001:377: glo bur nyon mongs dri mas bsgribs pa yi //
NK119(he)001:378: sems can rnams la de bzhin khams 'di gnas //
NK119(he)001:379: ces sgrib pa'i dri ma de dag bkru ba'i phyir //
NK119(he)001:380: 'gro ba'i bla ma sngon gyi drang srong chen po
NK119(he)001:381: ston pa sangs rgyas sku gsum gyi bdag nyid des
NK119(he)001:383: bstan bcos kyi chu gtsang gis thos bsam sgom pa'i
NK119(he)001:384: blo gros kyi bum bzang legs par bkang ba de
NK119(he)001:385: nyid bdag gi lhag bsam gyi lag tu thogs nas
NK119(he)001:388: tshig dang don legs par bshad pa'i bdud rtsi sdom pa gsum gyi chu gtsang 'di sbyin gyi /
NK119(he)001:389: thar pa dang thams cad mkhyen pa don du gnyer ba'i skye bo'i tshogs /
NK119(he)001:390: las dang nyon mongs pas gdung ba sgo gsum sgrib
NK119(he)001:391: pa'i dri mas sbags pa kun 'dir 'dus la ci
NK119(he)001:392: dgar longs spyod cig ces pa ste gzugs can gyi
NK119(he)001:393: rgyan no // de yang rgya mtsho dang mnyam pa rnyog pa med pa'i rgyud las /
NK119(he)001:394: rba rlabs med pa'i mnyam nyid mtsho //
NK119(he)001:395: rnyog pa med pa dri med chu //
NK119(he)001:396: gdod nas dag pa'i bdud rtsi 'dis //
NK119(he)001:399: 'di dag bshad kyi dam pa'i chos nyan phyir ni 'dir 'dus shig /
NK119(he)001:401: des bstan bcos la 'jug pa'i phyogs dang po bstan zin to //
NK119(he)001:402: don gnyis pa brjod bya bstan pa gzhung gi don la rim par phye ba lnga ste /
NK119(he)001:404: bye brag 'dul ba so thar gyi tshul khrims byang chub sems bskyed kyi bslab bya /
NK119(he)001:406: sdom pa gsum gang zag gcig gis nyams su blang tshul lo //
NK119(he)001:408: chos thams cad kyi mthar thug pa ngos bzung ba /
NK119(he)001:409: bye brag theg pa'i dbye ba bstan pa /
NK119(he)001:410: sdom pa gsum gyi 'gag bsdu ba gsum las /
NK119(he)001:413: rdzogs pa chen po ye shes spyi yi gzugs //
NK119(he)001:414: yongs su dag sku rdo rje 'chang chen po //
NK119(he)001:415: 'bras bu'i mthar thug sangs rgyas nyag gcig ste //
NK119(he)001:416: zab rgyas chos kyi sgo 'phar bsgrangs yas kyang //
NK119(he)001:417: gsang chen smin grol lam la ma brten par //
NK119(he)001:418: thob pa min zhes rdzogs sangs rgyas des gsungs //
NK119(he)001:419: de yang nyan thos dang rang sangs rgyas nas bzung
NK119(he)001:420: ste zab pa rgya che ba'i chos tshul bsam gyis
NK119(he)001:421: mi khyab pa zhig yod kyang mthar thug 'bras bu'i
NK119(he)001:422: grol sa chen po rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po
NK119(he)001:423: sku dang ye shes 'du 'bral med pa'i dgongs pa
NK119(he)001:424: mngon du bya ba la ni /
NK119(he)001:425: smin byed dbang bzhi'i rim pa dang /
NK119(he)001:426: grol byed gdams pa'i rim pa gnyis la ma brten par thob pa min te /
NK119(he)001:427: chos dbyings rin po che'i mdzod las /
NK119(he)001:428: rgyu 'bras theg pa'i chos kyi sgo dbye bas //
NK119(he)001:429: skal ldan 'gro ba byang chub gsum du 'dren //
NK119(he)001:430: kun kyang mthar thug rdo rje snying po'i don //
NK119(he)001:431: gsang chen rmad du byung 'dir 'jug dgos pas //
NK119(he)001:433: rgyud kun byed rgyal po las /
NK119(he)001:434: bstan pa'i rang bzhin theg pa dgu po yang //
NK119(he)001:435: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen por bsgrod pa'i lam //
NK119(he)001:438: 'di ma mthong ba'i sangs rgyas ni //
NK119(he)001:439: gcig kyang 'byung ba snga phyi med //
NK119(he)001:441: de yang rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa ni gsang ba zab mo la rmongs shing /
NK119(he)001:442: sngags phyi rgyud gsum yang smin byed kyi skabs su dbang bzhi yongs rdzogs mi bskur zhing /
NK119(he)001:443: grol byed bskyed pa'i rim pa dang rdzogs pa'i rim pa'ang /
NK119(he)001:444: dgongs pa tsam las mtshan nyid dang ldan pa med cing /
NK119(he)001:445: 'dir dbang bzhi rdzogs dang grol lam bskyed rdzogs rnam
NK119(he)001:446: par dag pa la brten pas theg pa 'og ma
NK119(he)001:447: las 'das pa'i rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po ye
NK119(he)001:448: shes spyi'i khyab bdag chen po mngon du byed pa'o
NK119(he)001:449: // de yang theg pa ni gang du 'degs pa'i khyogs lta bu ste /
NK119(he)001:450: rdzogs pa chen po ni theg par smos kyang ye shes kyi spyi gzugs zhes bya ste /
NK119(he)001:451: sa skya pan chen gyi zhal snga nas /
NK119(he)001:452: rdzogs pa chen po'i lta ba ni //
NK119(he)001:453: ye shes yin gyi theg pa min //
NK119(he)001:455: gnyis pa bye brag theg pa'i dbye ba bstan pa la'ang /
NK119(he)001:457: bye brag tu bshad pa gnyis las /
NK119(he)001:459: ji srid sems kyi 'jug pa ma zad bar //
NK119(he)001:460: bsam yas theg pa'i mtha' la thug pa med //
NK119(he)001:461: bsgrod gcig lam la dkri ba'i ngal stegs te //
NK119(he)001:462: rang rang rjes mthun 'bras bu bla dang bcas //
NK119(he)001:463: thob kyang theg pa so so'i nges 'byung las //
NK119(he)001:464: theg gcig lam la ma zhugs 'bras thob ci //
NK119(he)001:466: ston pa thabs la mkhas shing thugs rje che ba
NK119(he)001:467: rnams kyi gdul bya'i nyon mongs pa ji snyed 'dul
NK119(he)001:468: ba'i phyir de snyed kyi chos ston pas theg pa'i
NK119(he)001:469: rnam grangs 'di kho na'o zhes grangs su chad pa
NK119(he)001:472: sems can rnams ni yongs drongs phyir //
NK119(he)001:473: theg pa mtha' dag ngas bshad de //
NK119(he)001:474: 'di zhes dmigs su yod ma yin //
NK119(he)001:476: gdul bya 'gro ba'i bloo rtog ma zad kyi bar
NK119(he)001:477: la 'dul byed kyi theg pa'ang thug pa med de
NK119(he)001:479: ji srid sems ni 'jug pa'i bar //
NK119(he)001:480: theg pa'i mtha' la thug pa med //
NK119(he)001:482: de yang re zhig rdzas su bsdu na /
NK119(he)001:483: theg pa che chung gnyis su'ang 'dus te /
NK119(he)001:485: 'od srung theg pa ni gnyis te /
NK119(he)001:488: rgyu dang 'bras bu la dgongs nas gnyis su'ang gsungs te /
NK119(he)001:489: dpal 'byung bzhi zad pa'i rgyud las //
NK119(he)001:490: rgyu chos rnams dang 'bras bu'i phyir //
NK119(he)001:491: theg pa de'ang rnam pa gnyis //
NK119(he)001:493: yang nyan rang byang sems gsum du'ang bshad de /
NK119(he)001:495: sbyor ba dang ni tshor dag dang //
NK119(he)001:496: bsam pa dang ni bshad nyid dang //
NK119(he)001:497: sgrub pa'i rab tu dbye ba yis //
NK119(he)001:498: theg pa rnam pa gsum du 'dod //
NK119(he)001:501: gsang ba thig le nor bu'i rgyud las //
NK119(he)001:502: phyi nang gsang ba'i theg pa gsum //
NK119(he)001:503: dam pa'i chos kyang rab tu bzung //
NK119(he)001:505: rgyu'i theg pa gsum 'bras bu'i theg pa dang bzhir yang bshad de sgyu 'phrul las /
NK119(he)001:506: theg pa gsum gyi nges 'byung las //
NK119(he)001:507: theg pa gcig gi 'bras bur gnas //
NK119(he)001:509: lngar yang bshad de lang kar gshegs pa las //
NK119(he)001:510: lha yi theg dang tshongs pa'i theg /
NK119(he)001:511: de bzhin du yang nyan thos dang //
NK119(he)001:512: rang sangs rgyas kyi theg pa dang //
NK119(he)001:513: theg pa chen po zhes bya ba'i //
NK119(he)001:514: theg pa mtha' dag ngas bshad do //
NK119(he)001:518: nges pa thob pa'i theg pa drug /
NK119(he)001:522: lha dang mi dang nyan thos dang //
NK119(he)001:523: rang sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems //
NK119(he)001:524: gsang ba phyi dang nang gnyis te //
NK119(he)001:525: de ltar theg pa bdun du bshad //
NK119(he)001:529: ma rtogs pa dang log par rtogs //
NK119(he)001:530: phyogs rtogs yang dag nyid ma rtogs //
NK119(he)001:531: 'dul ba dgongs pa gsang ba dang //
NK119(he)001:532: rang bzhin gnas pa'i don nyid de //
NK119(he)001:534: de ltar rnam grangs mtha' yas pa dag kyang rang
NK119(he)001:535: bzhin rdzogs pa chen po sangs rgyas kyi sa gcig
NK119(he)001:536: pu la dkri ba'i ngal stegs te /
NK119(he)001:537: dam chos pad ma dkar po las /
NK119(he)001:538: nga yis bstan pa'i theg pa dgu po dag /
NK119(he)001:539: sems can dag gi mthu dang mos par bstan //
NK119(he)001:540: 'di ltar thabs kyi ye shes mchog chen la //
NK119(he)001:541: rab tu gzud pa'i phyir na ngas bshad do //
NK119(he)001:543: 'o na theg pa gzhan la 'bras bu med dam zhe na /
NK119(he)001:544: rang rang gi rgyu mthun gyi 'bras bu re yod de /
NK119(he)001:546: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa ni //
NK119(he)001:547: mya ngan las 'da' ba'i phyir nye bar gnas te //
NK119(he)001:548: nyan thos kyi sa la mya ngan las 'da' bar
NK119(he)001:549: 'dod na'ang shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa
NK119(he)001:551: zhes sogs gsungs pas de dag kyang theg pa so so'i nges 'byung yin te /
NK119(he)001:552: theg pa gsum gyis nges 'byung la //
NK119(he)001:553: theg pa gcig gi 'bras bur gnas //
NK119(he)001:555: zhi byed chu klung rol pa'i rgyud las /
NK119(he)001:556: snang srid 'khor 'das chos rnams thams cad la //
NK119(he)001:557: rang dgar spyod pa skye bo 'khrul ba'i ngo //
NK119(he)001:558: yod med brtag spyod mu stegs 'khrul ba'i blo //
NK119(he)001:559: dngos por 'dzin pa nyan thos dman pa'i rigs //
NK119(he)001:560: gnyis 'dzin rang rgyal sa mi zin pa ste //
NK119(he)001:561: bden 'dod rdzun 'dod sems tsam 'dod pas bcings //
NK119(he)001:562: sgyu mas khas len dbu mas skyon mi spangs //
NK119(he)001:563: khas len med pa'i thal 'gyur rtog ge ba //
NK119(he)001:564: lha ru 'dzin pa 'dre yi lta ba yin //
NK119(he)001:565: gsal bar 'dod pas gti mug chen po yin //
NK119(he)001:566: nyon mongs bde bar 'dod pas sdug bsngal rgyu //
NK119(he)001:567: snying po'i don la tshig gi lta ba med //
NK119(he)001:568: brjod bral lhan gcig skyes pa'i ye shes 'di //
NK119(he)001:569: tshogs bsags sgrib pa dag pa'i lag rjes dang //
NK119(he)001:570: rtogs ldan bla ma'i byin rlabs kho na las //
NK119(he)001:571: thabs gzhan bsten na rmongs par shes par bya //
NK119(he)001:573: des na mthar thug gi theg pa ni sangs rgyas kyi sa kho na ste /
NK119(he)001:574: pad+ma dkar po las theg pa gcig ste gnyis su yod ma yin /
NK119(he)001:577: rab 'byor theg pa ni gcig kho na ste //
NK119(he)001:578: bla na med pa sangs rgyas kyi theg pa'o //
NK119(he)001:580: de yang theg pa'i spros pa las 'das pa rang
NK119(he)001:581: bzhin rdzogs pa chen po bya btsal las 'das pa'i
NK119(he)001:582: ye shes de nyid mthar thug gi 'bras bu yin
NK119(he)001:584: sems ni nam zhig gyur pa na //
NK119(he)001:585: theg pa med cing 'gro ba'ang med //
NK119(he)001:587: ye shes yin gyi theg pa min zhes pa'i don no //
NK119(he)001:588: gnyis pa bye brag tu bshad pa ni /
NK119(he)001:589: theg pa'i dbye ba dang 'dod tshul mang na'ang //
NK119(he)001:590: 'dir ni rdzogs pa chen po'i ring lugs ltar //
NK119(he)001:591: nyan thos rang rgyal byang chub sems dpa' la //
NK119(he)001:592: mtshan nyid rgyu yi theg pa gsum zhes gsungs //
NK119(he)001:593: kri ya u pa yo ga phyi pa gsum //
NK119(he)001:594: bla med pha rgyud ma h+aa yo ga dang //
NK119(he)001:595: ma rgyud a nu yo gar grags pa dang //
NK119(he)001:596: gnyis med rgyud sde a ti yo ga la //
NK119(he)001:597: nang rgyud gsum zhes theg pa rim dgur bsdu //
NK119(he)001:598: de ltar dgu yod pa las /
NK119(he)001:599: dang po nyan thos kyi theg pa bshad pa la'ang /
NK119(he)001:600: phyi rol pa las 'phags tshul dang /
NK119(he)001:601: theg pa dngos bshad pa gnyis las /
NK119(he)001:603: tri sin du a pa ta ri'i rgyud las /
NK119(he)001:604: bstan dang ston dang lta spyod tshul bltas dang //
NK119(he)001:605: chos rtag bzhi dang bshad pa khyad par che //
NK119(he)001:607: ston pa sku gsum 'dzin pa nang pa /
NK119(he)001:608: dbang phyug khyab 'jug la sogs 'dzin pa phyi pa /
NK119(he)001:609: ston pa sangs rgyas ni nang pa /
NK119(he)001:610: mu stegs drug sogs phyi ba /
NK119(he)001:611: lta ba spros bral du 'dod pa nang pa /
NK119(he)001:612: rtag chad du lta ba phyi ba /
NK119(he)001:613: spyod pa dge bcur spyad pa nang pa /
NK119(he)001:614: me lnga sogs bsten pa phyi pa /
NK119(he)001:615: chos rtags kyi phyag rgya bzhi khas len pa nang pa /
NK119(he)001:616: gtsang rtag bde bdag bzhi 'dod pa phyi'o //
NK119(he)001:618: 'dus byas thams cad mi rtag pa /
NK119(he)001:619: zag pa dang bcas pa sdug bsngal ba /
NK119(he)001:620: chos thams cad stong zhing bdag med pa /
NK119(he)001:621: mya ngan las 'das pa zhi ba'o //
NK119(he)001:625: 'gog pa'i nyan thos gsum du 'dod kyang /
NK119(he)001:626: 'dir rang rang gi grub mtha' mdor bstan pa la /
NK119(he)001:630: nyan thos pa dag phyi gzung ba chos kyi bdag med ma rtogs la /
NK119(he)001:631: nang 'dzin pa gang zag gi bdag med rtogs pa ste /
NK119(he)001:632: lam dmigs yul bden pa bzhis bsdus pa'i chos la blang dor du byed pas 'jug ste /
NK119(he)001:633: de'ang sdug bsngal gyi bden pa nad dang 'dra ba
NK119(he)001:634: lus ngag yid gsum 'khor ba'i dus kyi nyer len
NK119(he)001:635: gyi phung po lnga dang bcas pa spang ba'i phyir
NK119(he)001:636: rang bzhin shes par bya ba dang /
NK119(he)001:637: kun 'byung ni nad kyi rgyu dang 'dra ste dug
NK119(he)001:638: gsum la sogs 'du byed kyi las spang bar bya
NK119(he)001:639: ba dang / 'gog pa'i bden pa ni nang las grol ba'i bde ba dang 'dra ste /
NK119(he)001:640: srid pa'i gzeb las grol ba'i dga' ba thob par bya ba dang /
NK119(he)001:641: lam bden ni sman dang 'dra ste sdug bsngal gyi
NK119(he)001:642: nad las grol bar bya ba'i phyir mngon du bya
NK119(he)001:645: nad ni shes bya nad kyi rgyu ni spang bya la //
NK119(he)001:646: bde gnas thob par bya phyir sman dag bsten bya bzhin //
NK119(he)001:647: sdug bsngal rgyu dang de 'gog pa dang lam bden pa //
NK119(he)001:648: shes bya spang bya rig par bya zhing brten par bya //
NK119(he)001:654: de yang phyi gzung ba chos kyi bdag ma brtag
NK119(he)001:655: pa'i ngor snang ba ri la sogs 'di dag g.yag
NK119(he)001:656: rnga ne'u seng ltar 'tshogs pa gcig tu snang yang
NK119(he)001:657: / don dam par rdul phran cha ldan sil bur 'dod la /
NK119(he)001:658: nang 'dzin pa gang zag gi bdag phung po khams
NK119(he)001:659: dang skye mched dus gsum du snang ba'i blo yang
NK119(he)001:660: skad cig cha shas med par khas blangs te /
NK119(he)001:662: gang la bcom dang blo yis gzhan //
NK119(he)001:663: bsal na de blo mi 'jug pa //
NK119(he)001:664: bum chu bzhin du kun rdzob tu //
NK119(he)001:665: yod de don dam yod gzhan no //
NK119(he)001:667: de yang gzung ba chos kyi bdag ni rdul phran dang skad cig yod par 'dod pa'o //
NK119(he)001:668: gnyis pa mdo sde pa ni /
NK119(he)001:669: gang zag gi bdag med sngar dang 'dra la /
NK119(he)001:670: de'i steng du chos kyi bdag med phyogs gcig gis 'phags te /
NK119(he)001:671: de'ang cha dang bcas pa'i rdul phran shes bya'i gzhi lnga gtso bas khegs la /
NK119(he)001:672: cha med kyi rdul phran tsam ma khegs te /
NK119(he)001:673: chos kyi bdag gi phyed gzung yul rags snang gi
NK119(he)001:674: rdul phran reg la ma 'byar ba tsam de yang
NK119(he)001:675: cha med du rtogs pas 'phags te /
NK119(he)001:676: don gyi ltar med pas rdul phran khas ma blang pa dang 'dra'o //
NK119(he)001:677: de dag gis don sgom pa'i tshul yang /
NK119(he)001:679: tshul gnas thos dang bsam ldan pas //
NK119(he)001:680: bsgom pa la ni rab tu sbyor //
NK119(he)001:681: zhes pa ltar so thar rigs bdun gyi sgor zhugs nas dge sbyong gi chos bzhi dang /
NK119(he)001:682: sbyang ba'i yon tan bcu gnyis la sogs pa dang ldan pas thos bsam bsten pa dang /
NK119(he)001:683: dug gsum gnyen pos bcom pa dang /
NK119(he)001:684: dkar po rnam par mthong ba la sogs pa brgyad
NK119(he)001:685: bsgrod de mthong spang dang sgom spang gis phra rgyas
NK119(he)001:686: spangs nas / dgra bcom pa rgyan can dang rgyan med kyi 'bras bu mngon du byed pa'o //
NK119(he)001:687: theg pa'i rnam dbye 'di dag shin tu gal che na'ang /
NK119(he)001:688: 'di'i brjod bya'i skabs phyogs tsam las ma spros pas gzhan du rtogs par bya'o //
NK119(he)001:689: gnyis pa rang sangs rgyas kyi theg pa ni /
NK119(he)001:690: nyan thos ltar gang zag gi bdag med rtogs pa'i steng du /
NK119(he)001:691: gzung ba chos kyi bdag phyed rtogs pas 'phags te /
NK119(he)001:693: nyan thos dang de'i phyogs su klan pa rang sangs
NK119(he)001:694: rgyas te mngon par rtogs pa gcig gis 'phags pa
NK119(he)001:696: de yang dmigs yul bden bzhis bsdus pa'i chos la
NK119(he)001:697: rten 'brel bcu gnyis lugs 'byung dang lugs ldog tu
NK119(he)001:698: bsgoms pas khams gsum pa'i phra rgyas spang bar 'dod
NK119(he)001:699: de / gang zag gi bdag med sngar ltar las /
NK119(he)001:700: chos kyi bdag phyed phyi gzung ba rdul phran cha bcas dang cha med gnyis ka med par /
NK119(he)001:701: gzugs brnyan ltar rang bzhin gyi ngo bo nyid med cing ma skyes par rtogs la /
NK119(he)001:702: nang yul snang 'dzin mkhan gyi shes pa skad cig ma don dam pa'i ngo bor 'dod de /
NK119(he)001:704: gzung don rtog pa spangs phyir dang //
NK119(he)001:705: 'dzin pa mi spang phyir dang ni //
NK119(he)001:706: rten gyi bse ru lta bu'i lam //
NK119(he)001:707: yang dag bsdus par shes par bya //
NK119(he)001:709: dbye na bse ru ltar gcig pur gnas par tshogs spyod chung ba dang /
NK119(he)001:710: ne tsho ltar khyur lding pa tshogs spyod che ba dang /
NK119(he)001:713: bse ru bskal pa brgya yis rgyus //
NK119(he)001:714: zhes pas bskal ba brgyar tshogs bsags shing lam bsgrod tshul phal cher nyan thos dang mthun la /
NK119(he)001:715: 'bras bu yid bzhin bde ba mchog gi sa zhes dgra bcom pa mngon du byed pa'o //
NK119(he)001:716: gsum pa byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa la'ang /
NK119(he)001:718: theg pa dngos bshad pa gnyis las /
NK119(he)001:720: 'gro ba'i don du dmigs pa che ba la sogs /
NK119(he)001:721: stong nyid snying rje'i ngo bo yin pas theg pa chen po zhes bya ste /
NK119(he)001:723: theg pa 'di ni mkha' 'dra gzhal med khang chen po /
NK119(he)001:724: dga' skyid bde ba mngon par sgrub byed theg pa mchog /
NK119(he)001:725: de gang zhon nas sems can thams cad mya ngan bzlo /
NK119(he)001:726: rgyu des theg pa chen po zhes brjod do //
NK119(he)001:730: dmigs pa che ba nyid dang ni //
NK119(he)001:731: de bzhin sgrub pa gnyis dag dang //
NK119(he)001:732: ye shes brtson 'grus brtsam pa dang //
NK119(he)001:733: thabs la mkhas pa gang yin dang //
NK119(he)001:734: yang dag grub pa chen po dang //
NK119(he)001:735: sangs rgyas phrin las chen po ste //
NK119(he)001:736: chen po bdun dang ldan pa'i phyir //
NK119(he)001:737: theg pa che zhes nges par brjod //
NK119(he)001:739: gzhan yang lang kar gshegs pa las //
NK119(he)001:740: chos lnga dag dang rang bzhin gsum //
NK119(he)001:741: rnam par shes pa brgyad nyid dang //
NK119(he)001:742: bdag med gnyis kyi nang du ni //
NK119(he)001:743: theg pa chen po mtha' dag 'dus //
NK119(he)001:755: rnam par shes pa brgyad ni /
NK119(he)001:758: kun gzhi'i rnam shes te brgyad do //
NK119(he)001:759: bdag med gnyis ni gzung ba chos dang /
NK119(he)001:760: 'dzin pa gang zag gi bdag med do //
NK119(he)001:763: grub mtha' so sor bshad pa gnyis las /
NK119(he)001:765: gzhi bden gnyis kyi rang bzhin shes par bya ba dang /
NK119(he)001:766: de nyams su blang ba dang /
NK119(he)001:769: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad bden pa gnyis su 'dus te /
NK119(he)001:771: sangs rgyas rnams kyi chos bstan pa //
NK119(he)001:772: bden pa gnyis su yang dag 'dus //
NK119(he)001:773: 'jig rten kun rdzob bden pa dang //
NK119(he)001:774: dam pa'i don gyi bden pa'o //
NK119(he)001:776: de la yang chos can mtshan mar snang ba'i blo
NK119(he)001:777: yul du snang ba rnams kun rdzob kyi bden pa
NK119(he)001:779: snang la don byed mi nus pa skra shad dang
NK119(he)001:780: zla gnyis kyi snang ba la sogs pa ni log
NK119(he)001:785: mthun par snang ba ste mtshan nyid bzhi dang ldan pa ni /
NK119(he)001:788: snang du 'dra yang don byed dag /
NK119(he)001:789: nus pa'i phyir dang mi nus phyir //
NK119(he)001:790: yang dag yang dag ma yin pa'i //
NK119(he)001:791: kun rdzob kyi ni dbye ba'ang byas //
NK119(he)001:793: chos nyid rang bzhin gyis stong pa dang /
NK119(he)001:794: rjes su 'jal bas spros pa zhi ba'i rnam pa can ni /
NK119(he)001:795: don dam gyi bden pa ste /
NK119(he)001:797: rigs pas gzhal na skye ba la sogs ma grub
NK119(he)001:798: pa'i chos nyid gshis dang mthun par skyes pa rnam
NK119(he)001:800: gdod nas spros pa las 'das pa'i dbyings rang bzhin
NK119(he)001:801: gyi rnam par dag pa rnam grangs ma yin pa'i
NK119(he)001:802: don dam ste / de nyid las /
NK119(he)001:803: skye ba la sogs bkag pa yang //
NK119(he)001:804: yang dag pa dang mthun nyid bzhed //
NK119(he)001:805: skye med spros kun zhi ba la //
NK119(he)001:806: don dam zhes pa'i brdar mdzad do //
NK119(he)001:809: theg chen so thar gyi sdom pa gang rung gi steng du byang chub tu sems bskyed nas /
NK119(he)001:810: lam lnga sa bcu mngon du byed pa'o //
NK119(he)001:812: bcu gcig kun tu 'od kyi sa la rang don chos sku dang /
NK119(he)001:813: gzhan don gzugs sku dam pa gnyis thob nas //
NK119(he)001:814: mkhyen pa gnyis kyis sems can gyi don mdzad pa ste /
NK119(he)001:816: zhi sku dpag bsam shing ltar gsal gyur la //
NK119(he)001:817: yid bzhin nor bu lta bur rnam mi rtog /'gro
NK119(he)001:818: grol bar du 'jig rten 'byor slad rtag /'di ni
NK119(he)001:819: spros dang bral la snang ba yin //
NK119(he)001:821: gnyis pa grub pa'i mtha' so sor bshad pa la'ang /
NK119(he)001:822: sems tsam pa dang dbu ma pa gnyis las /
NK119(he)001:824: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad sems kho na tsam las gzhan med de /
NK119(he)001:825: de yang gzung 'dzin gnyis med kyi shes pa rang rig rang gsal don dam du 'dod de /
NK119(he)001:827: blo yis nyams myong bya gzhan med //
NK119(he)001:828: de yi myong pa'ang gzhan yod min //
NK119(he)001:829: gzung dang 'dzin pa gnyis med phyir //
NK119(he)001:830: de ni de ltar rang nyid gsal //
NK119(he)001:833: yid bzhin rin po che'i mdzod las /
NK119(he)001:834: don snang shes par 'dod dang mi 'dod las //
NK119(he)001:835: rnam pa bden rdzun gnyis su grags pa ste //
NK119(he)001:836: zhes pas phyi rol sna tshogs su snang ba rang
NK119(he)001:837: gi shes pa don gzhan du snang bar 'dod pa
NK119(he)001:839: shes pa ma yin te shes pa rdzun pas na bag chags brtas pa'i snang ba der snang ba'o //
NK119(he)001:842: snang srid 'khor 'das gnyis bsdus kyi chos thams cad
NK119(he)001:843: spros mtha' dang bral zhing dbus la'ang mi gnas pa
NK119(he)001:845: rtag dang mi rtag 'di yang mtha' yin te //
NK119(he)001:846: yod dang med ces bya ba gnyis ka mtha' //
NK119(he)001:847: de phyir gnyis ka'i mtha' ni rab spangs te //
NK119(he)001:848: mkhas pas dbus la'ang gnas par mi bya'o //
NK119(he)001:851: dbu ma rang rgyud pa ni chos thams cad kun rdzob tu snang la /
NK119(he)001:852: de yang brtags na don dam par rang bzhin med par 'dod de /
NK119(he)001:855: rigs pas brtag na 'ga' mi rnyed //
NK119(he)001:856: ma rnyed pa ni don dam ste //
NK119(he)001:857: ye nas gnas pa'i chos nyid do //
NK119(he)001:860: dpyad rung ma dpyad rung dus gtan du spros pa
NK119(he)001:861: thams cad nye bar zhi ba khas len thams cad
NK119(he)001:864: ji ltar khyod kyis gzhan dbang dngos 'dod ltar //
NK119(he)001:865: kun rdzob kyang ni bdag gis khas ma blangs //
NK119(he)001:868: gal te ngas dam bcas 'ga' yod //
NK119(he)001:869: de tshe nga la skyon 'di yod //
NK119(he)001:870: ngal la khas len med pas na //
NK119(he)001:871: nga ni skyon med kho na yin //
NK119(he)001:873: de dag ni gang zag dbang po chung ngu'i rab 'bring tha gsum la dgongs pa ste /
NK119(he)001:874: rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa bstan zin to //
NK119(he)001:875: bzhi pa 'bras bu gsang sngags kyi theg pa bshad pa la /
NK119(he)001:876: dkyus ltar rgyud sde drug po bshad pa dang /
NK119(he)001:877: zhar la sngags gsar ma'i bzhed pa 'phros pa dang gnyis las /
NK119(he)001:882: mthar thug gi gnyer bya kun 'dod pa mtshungs na'ang /
NK119(he)001:883: gsang sngags ni lam sgrub pa'i tshul la ma rmongs pa dang /
NK119(he)001:886: dbang po rnon po'i khyad par gyi chos yin te /
NK119(he)001:888: don gcig na'ang ma rmongs dang //
NK119(he)001:889: thabs mang dka' ba med pa dang //
NK119(he)001:890: dbang po rnon po'i dbang byas nas //
NK119(he)001:891: sngags kyi theg pa khyad par 'phags //
NK119(he)001:894: ra li bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i rgyud las /
NK119(he)001:895: nyan thos la sogs theg dman la //
NK119(he)001:896: man ngag yod pa ma yin te //
NK119(he)001:897: lta ba spyod pa sems bzung dang //
NK119(he)001:898: rgyud dang lam dang 'bras bu dang //
NK119(he)001:899: dus dang longs spyod rnal 'byor dang //
NK119(he)001:900: bdag gzhan don dang dgongs pa dang //
NK119(he)001:901: ngal dub mtha' spangs tshegs chung dang //
NK119(he)001:902: tshogs bsags pa yi khyad par dang //
NK119(he)001:903: khyad par rnam pa bco lnga yis //
NK119(he)001:906: dkyus ltar rgyud sde drug tu bshad pa la /
NK119(he)001:908: nang pa thabs kyi rgyud sde gsum dang drug las /
NK119(he)001:909: don bzhi pa kri ya ste bya ba'i rgyud ni /
NK119(he)001:910: lus ngag gi dag pa gtsor byas te /
NK119(he)001:911: yid kyi lha ye shes sems dpa' dang /
NK119(he)001:912: bdag dam tshig sems dpa' rje 'bangs kyi tshul du blta bas dngos grub sgrub pa ste /
NK119(he)001:913: ye shes rol pa'i rgyud las /
NK119(he)001:914: don dam spros bral stong pa'i ngang nyid las //
NK119(he)001:915: kun rdzob sgyu ma lta bu'i skur snang la //
NK119(he)001:916: rje 'bangs tshul du dang pas rab bsgom na //
NK119(he)001:917: dngos grub dam pa sangs rgyas thob par 'gyur //
NK119(he)001:920: ye shes rdo rje kun las btus par /
NK119(he)001:921: bdag nyid lha yi snyems pa med pa dang //
NK119(he)001:922: zhes pas bdag bskyed med par bzhed kyang /
NK119(he)001:923: rnying ma'i rgyud dang sgrub thabs rnams su yo ga'i rgyud ltar du bkral nas bdag bskyed gsungs so //
NK119(he)001:924: lnga pa u pa ya ste spyod pa'i rgyud ni /
NK119(he)001:925: spyod pa kri ya ltar spyod cing /
NK119(he)001:926: lta ba yo ga ltar blta bas bdag dang lha grogs po lta bus dngos grub 'dod pa ste /
NK119(he)001:927: blo gros rgya mtsho'i rgyud las /
NK119(he)001:928: don dam rnam dag ye shes chen po las //
NK119(he)001:929: sgyu ma'i tshul ston grogs po lta bur bsgom //
NK119(he)001:930: mchod bstod sngags bzlas sangs rgyas nyid du 'gyur //
NK119(he)001:932: lnga pa yo ga ste rnal 'byor gyi rgyud ni /
NK119(he)001:933: lus ngag gtso bor mi ston cing //
NK119(he)001:934: sems kyi bya ba gtso bor ston pas mngon byang
NK119(he)001:935: lnga'i sgo nas lha dang bdag gnyis dbyer med bsre
NK119(he)001:937: ye shes rgya mtsho'i rgyud las /
NK119(he)001:938: bdag mdun gnyis po lhar bskyed nas //
NK119(he)001:939: mchod bstod bzlas pa tshar ba dang //
NK119(he)001:940: ye shes pa gshegs mgron lta bu //
NK119(he)001:941: bsgom pas sangs rgyas nyid du 'gyur //
NK119(he)001:943: 'di dag gi shan 'byed rgyud sde'i rnam grangs sogs mtha' yas kyang 'dir yi ges 'jigs so //
NK119(he)001:944: de dag ni dbang po 'bring po gsum la dgongs pa'o //
NK119(he)001:945: nang pa thabs kyi rgyud gsum bshad pa la'ang /
NK119(he)001:946: gsang sngags phyi nang gi khyad par dang /
NK119(he)001:947: bye brag so sor bshad pa gnyis las //
NK119(he)001:949: kun mkhyen klong chen rab 'byams kyis mdzad pa'i /
NK119(he)001:950: yid bzhin mdzod kyi 'grel chen pad ma dkar por gsang sngags phyi nang gnyis kyi khyad par ram /
NK119(he)001:953: rig pa'i dbang lnga dang bum dbang gtso che ba gsang sngags phyi pa /
NK119(he)001:954: dbang bzhi rdzogs par bskur ba nang pa /
NK119(he)001:955: lam bskyed rim res 'jog gi rdzogs rim sgom pa phyi pa /
NK119(he)001:956: bskyed rdzogs zung 'jug sgom pa nang pa /
NK119(he)001:957: spyod pa gtsang sbra la spyod pa phyi pa /
NK119(he)001:958: gnyis med du spyod pa nang pa /
NK119(he)001:959: longs spyod dkar gsum mngar gsum gtso che ba phyi pa /
NK119(he)001:960: sha lnga bdud rtsi lnga bsten pa nang ba /
NK119(he)001:961: gos ras sogs gtsang ma gtso che ba phyi pa /
NK119(he)001:962: zhing chen nam gos med gtso che ba nang pa /
NK119(he)001:963: bya ba khrus dang gtsang sbra gtso che ba phyi pa /
NK119(he)001:964: 'bag pa dang ma dag pas mi gnod pa nang pa /
NK119(he)001:965: 'bras bu tshe bcu drug la sogs na 'dod pa phyi pa /
NK119(he)001:966: tshe 'adi'am bar dor 'grub pa nang pa /
NK119(he)001:967: lha zhal sbyor du mi bsgom pa phyi pa sgom pa nang pa /
NK119(he)001:968: rgyan dar dang rin po che gtso che ba phyi pa /
NK119(he)001:969: dur khrod kyi chas rol ba nang pa /
NK119(he)001:970: gnas ri rab kyi steng la sogs dben par gnas pa phyi pa /
NK119(he)001:971: o rgyan dang dur khrod la sogs par sgom pa nang pa /
NK119(he)001:972: snod rin po che'am pad ma'i gzhong pa ni phyi pa /
NK119(he)001:973: ka p+aa la gtso che ba nang pa /
NK119(he)001:974: las zhi rgyas gtso cher ston pa phyi pa /
NK119(he)001:975: dbang drag gtso cher ston pa gsang sngags nang par gsungs so //
NK119(he)001:976: bye brag tu pha rgyud ma h+aa yo ga dang /
NK119(he)001:977: ma rgyud a nu yo ga gnyis la'ang khyad par bdun gsungs te /
NK119(he)001:978: de kho na nyid kyi khyad par la'ang /
NK119(he)001:979: dbang dang sbyin sreg la sogs cho ga mang po rgya che ba gtsor ston na pha rgyud /
NK119(he)001:980: bskyed rim dang rdzogs rim sogs zab pa gtsor ston na ma rgyud /
NK119(he)001:982: lha gtso bo 'pho zhing gtso mo mi 'pho na pha rgyud /
NK119(he)001:983: gtso mo 'pho zhing gtso bo mi 'pho na ma rgyud /
NK119(he)001:985: gang du lha pho'i rnam pa mang zhing dar dang rin po ches brgyan pa pha rgyud /
NK119(he)001:986: lha mo'i rnam pa mang zhing rus rgyan dang ro gdan yod pa ma rgyud /
NK119(he)001:987: phyogs kyang mngon rtogs la sogs pa'i tshe /
NK119(he)001:988: g.yas bskor byed pa pha rgyud /
NK119(he)001:989: g.yon du bskor ba ma rgyud /
NK119(he)001:991: gtso bor skyes pas mtshon cing /
NK119(he)001:992: dus nyin mo dang yar ngo gtso che ba pha rgyud /
NK119(he)001:993: de las bzlog pas ma rgyud /
NK119(he)001:994: rdzogs rim yang rtsa thig bde ba gtsor byed pa pha rgyud /
NK119(he)001:995: rlung dang gsal ba lam du byed pa ma rgyud /
NK119(he)001:996: rnam dag kyang phung khams dag pa lha dang lha mor byed pa pha rgyud /
NK119(he)001:997: rtsa khams dag pa dpa' bo dang rnal 'byor mar
NK119(he)001:998: ston pa ma rgyud du grub mtha' mdzod las gsungs
NK119(he)001:999: so // drug pa pha rgyud ma h+aa yo ga ni /
NK119(he)001:1000: snang srid lha dang gzhal yas khang du gsal zhing /
NK119(he)001:1001: phung khams skye mched dag pa lhar gsal bas rlung
NK119(he)001:1002: gtso bor gyur pa'i lam bsgom pas tshe 'dir grol
NK119(he)001:1003: bar 'dod de / ye shes rol pa'i rgyud las /
NK119(he)001:1004: bskyed dang rdzogs pa'i rim pa las //
NK119(he)001:1005: ye shes rlung gi las byed cing //
NK119(he)001:1006: nam mkha'i 'jo ba rab rdzogs pas //
NK119(he)001:1007: tshe gcig gis ni rab grol lo //
NK119(he)001:1009: dbye na gzhi lam 'bras bu gtso ba dang /
NK119(he)001:1010: thabs lam sgrub pa gtso ba dang /
NK119(he)001:1011: sna tshogs lam 'gyur du 'dod pa gsum /
NK119(he)001:1012: sna tshogs lam 'gyur la'ang rgyud dang no pi ka gnyis /
NK119(he)001:1013: no pi ka la'ang sa t+wa no pi ka dang /
NK119(he)001:1014: man+dala no pi ka gnyis yod la /
NK119(he)001:1015: nges byed kyi rgyud sde'ang mtha' yas pa'o //
NK119(he)001:1016: bdun pa ma rgyud a nu yo ga ni /
NK119(he)001:1017: snod bcud lha'i rang bzhin du dbyings nas sangs rgyas
NK119(he)001:1018: pa tsam du rtogs pa'i ngang nas bskyed rim lus
NK119(he)001:1019: rtsa rlung dag pa lha dang gzhal yas khang du
NK119(he)001:1020: shes pas / rdzogs rim rlung sems bde gsal mi
NK119(he)001:1021: rtog pa'i ye shes mngon du byed pas tshe 'dir
NK119(he)001:1022: shes pas / grol ba ste / thig le mchog gi rgyud las /
NK119(he)001:1023: 'od gsal ba yi sems nyid ni //
NK119(he)001:1024: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis med par //
NK119(he)001:1025: bde ba ched du sus bsgom pa //
NK119(he)001:1028: dbye na lung dang mdo gnyis te rgyud sde'i rnam grangs gzhan nas shes so //
NK119(he)001:1029: brgyad pa gnyis med a ti yo ga la'ang /
NK119(he)001:1031: gong du bshad pa ltar theg pa 'og ma rnams
NK119(he)001:1032: ni yid dpyod du 'dzin pa'i lta ba la zhen
NK119(he)001:1033: pas lam 'di'i stegs su gnas pa tsam ste /
NK119(he)001:1035: des thob pa yi theg pa drug /
NK119(he)001:1036: rdzogs pa chen po'i gol sa bstan //
NK119(he)001:1038: a ti bkod pa chen po las /
NK119(he)001:1039: theg brgyad a ti blo 'das khyad //
NK119(he)001:1041: de la a ti yo ga'i ngo bo ni /
NK119(he)001:1042: spros bral rang byung gi ye shes rgya chad phyogs
NK119(he)001:1043: lhung med pa theg pa kun gyi don thams cad
NK119(he)001:1044: yongs su rdzogs pas rtse mor gyur pa ste /
NK119(he)001:1046: gcig rdzogs gnyis rdzogs sems la rdzogs //
NK119(he)001:1047: gcig rdzogs sems kyis byas par rdzogs //
NK119(he)001:1048: gnyis rdzogs phun sum tshogs par rdzogs //
NK119(he)001:1049: kun rdzob byang chub sems su rdzogs //
NK119(he)001:1052: rang sems las gzhan pa'i chos logs su med pas sems sde dang /
NK119(he)001:1053: chos nyid kun tu bzang mo'i klong las gzhan du 'gro sa med pas klong sde dang /
NK119(he)001:1054: yin lugs gnad thog tu phebs pas man ngag gi sde dang gsum yod la /
NK119(he)001:1055: man ngag gi sde la'ang phyi skor nang skor gsang skor gsum /
NK119(he)001:1056: de dag thams cad las mchog tu 'phags pa gsang
NK119(he)001:1057: ba bla na med pa 'od gsal rdo rje snying
NK119(he)001:1058: po'i mngon sum snying thig gi skor ro //
NK119(he)001:1059: de dag ni dbang po rab gsum la dgongs pa ste /
NK119(he)001:1060: gsang sngags phyi nang gnyis la gsum gsum ste /
NK119(he)001:1061: rgyud sde drug tu bzhed de /
NK119(he)001:1064: rgyu la gsum dang 'bras la gnyis //
NK119(he)001:1065: gnyis pa las phye drug tu 'gyur //
NK119(he)001:1067: gnyis pa zhar la gsang sngags gsar ma'i bzhed pa 'phros su bshad de /
NK119(he)001:1074: sku dang gsung dang thugs kyi mchog /
NK119(he)001:1075: de bzhin gshegs pa kun gyi gsang //
NK119(he)001:1076: byang chub sems ni bla na med //
NK119(he)001:1077: snying po bcom ldan bshad du gsol //
NK119(he)001:1080: ting nge 'dzin gyi khyad par gong na med pa ston pas rnal 'byor bla med dang bzhi ste /
NK119(he)001:1081: rdo rje snying po bkod pa'i rgyud las /
NK119(he)001:1082: bde bar gshegs pa'i dgongs pa'i rgyud //
NK119(he)001:1083: rnam pa bzhi ru yang dag bshad //
NK119(he)001:1084: bya spyod rnal 'byor bla med do //
NK119(he)001:1091: phyin ci log gi lha bzhi 'dul ba la dgongs nas kyang bzhir bzhag go //
NK119(he)001:1093: slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang bas //
NK119(he)001:1094: rnal 'byor spyod dang bya dbye bas //
NK119(he)001:1095: rgyud sde rnam pa gsum du 'dod //
NK119(he)001:1097: rnal 'byor bla med mar rnal 'byor gyi khog tu brgyab pas rgyud sde gsum du 'dod pa'o //
NK119(he)001:1098: yang rtogs pa dum bu'i rgyud /
NK119(he)001:1099: bya spyod rnal 'byor bla med de lngar 'dod pa'ang /
NK119(he)001:1100: ye shes rdo rje kun las btus pa las /
NK119(he)001:1101: 'dod mchog las byung ba'i byang chub kyi sems ston pa'i phyir /
NK119(he)001:1102: btsun mo'i 'khor gyis dbus su b+ha ga la bzhugs te /
NK119(he)001:1103: 'jig rten pa dang mi 'gal ba'i spyod pa dang /
NK119(he)001:1104: mtha' drug gi spyod pa ston pa ni rnal 'byor gyi rgyud la bzhugs so //
NK119(he)001:1105: rig pa dang lha mo'i dkyil 'khor la bkod de /
NK119(he)001:1106: de la phrin las bsgrub pa de kho na nyid ston pa gnyis ka'i rgyud la bzhugs so //
NK119(he)001:1107: las kyi bya ba phyag rgya chen po sgrub par byed par spyod pa'i rgyud la bzhugs so //
NK119(he)001:1108: 'jig rten la dmigs te gtsang sbra dang /
NK119(he)001:1109: ye shes sems dpa'i bde ba med pa dang /
NK119(he)001:1110: rmad du byung ba'i skyon gyi rgyu'i rtogs pa bya ba'i rgyud la bzhugs so //
NK119(he)001:1114: rkang mgyogs la sogs pa dngos grub brgyad spyod pas
NK119(he)001:1115: 'grub par byed pa rtogs pa dum bu'i rgyud la
NK119(he)001:1116: bzhugs so // zhes pa ltar ro //
NK119(he)001:1117: yang brtag pa gnyis pa las /
NK119(he)001:1118: blta dang dgod dang lag bcangs dang //
NK119(he)001:1119: 'khyud dang de bzhin gnyis gnyis te //
NK119(he)001:1120: rgyud kyang rnam pa bzhi rnams kyi //
NK119(he)001:1121: sbas pa'i skad kyis ma bsgrags pa //
NK119(he)001:1122: bcom ldan nges par gsung du gsol //
NK119(he)001:1123: zhes bzhir ma gsungs pa'i shugs las //
NK119(he)001:1124: lnga pa zhes 'byung ba la dpag nas //
NK119(he)001:1125: slob dpon b+ha ba b+ha tra la sogs pas rnal
NK119(he)001:1126: 'byor bla med la gnyis su dbye bas lngar 'dod
NK119(he)001:1127: do // yang bde mchog bsdus rgyud las /
NK119(he)001:1128: ji srid mdo bya spyod pa dang //
NK119(he)001:1129: rnal 'byor gsang matha'i dbye ba las //
NK119(he)001:1130: sems can mos pa sna tshogs pas //
NK119(he)001:1131: de dang de la dga' ba yin //
NK119(he)001:1132: zhes gsungs pa'i rjes su 'brangs nas /
NK119(he)001:1133: slob dpon rgyal ba'i sras lwa ba pa'i na bza' can la sogs pas /
NK119(he)001:1134: mdo sde rdo rje sa 'og la sogs rtogs pa'i rgyud /
NK119(he)001:1139: rnal 'byor bde mchog la sogs gsang matha'i rgyud dang drug tu 'dod pa'o //
NK119(he)001:1140: gsum pa sdom pa gsum gyi 'gag bsdam pa la'ang /
NK119(he)001:1141: sdom pa gsum gyi mtshan nyid mdor bstan pa dang /
NK119(he)001:1142: dbang po'i rim pas gsum du bshad pa /
NK119(he)001:1143: rang lugs nges pas gtan la dbab pa gsum las /
NK119(he)001:1144: dang po ni rgyud las sdom pa gsum po gnas 'gyur ba'am /
NK119(he)001:1145: ngo bo gcig par gser 'gyur gyi dpes bstan pa yang /
NK119(he)001:1146: nyan rang byang sems rigs can so so la //
NK119(he)001:1147: rdo rje 'dzin pa'i lam zhugs yod do zhes //
NK119(he)001:1148: 'bum lnga'i rgyud kyi lung las gsal bar grub //
NK119(he)001:1150: kyee rdo rje'i rgyud 'bum phrag lnga ba las /
NK119(he)001:1151: rdo yis rigs kyi bye brag bzhus //
NK119(he)001:1152: lcags dang zangs dang dngul du 'byung //
NK119(he)001:1153: gser 'gyur rtsi yi dngos po yis //
NK119(he)001:1154: kun kyang gser du bsgyur ba bzhin //
NK119(he)001:1155: de nyid sems kyi bye brag gis //
NK119(he)001:1156: rigs can gsum gyi sdom pa yang //
NK119(he)001:1160: dpe de'i rdo ni phal pa yin la //
NK119(he)001:1161: lcags ni nyan thos kyi bslab par bya ba dang /
NK119(he)001:1162: zangs ni rang rgyal gyis bslab par bya ba /
NK119(he)001:1163: dngul ni byang chub sems dpa'i bslab par bya ba
NK119(he)001:1164: yin cing gser 'gyur rtsi ni rdo rje theg pa'i
NK119(he)001:1165: bslab par bya ba yin par mngon no //
NK119(he)001:1166: gzhan gang zag tha dad pa'i /
NK119(he)001:1167: bsam pa'i dbye bas sngags la 'jug pa'i tshul /
NK119(he)001:1168: chos sgo mang yang de dag spro bya min /
NK119(he)001:1169: rim gyis dang gcig char du 'jug tshul la sogs mtha' yas pa yod kyang /
NK119(he)001:1170: de dag 'dir ched du gnyer nas bshad par bya ba ma yin pas mi spro'o //
NK119(he)001:1172: 'dir ni dbang po rab 'bring tha gsum las /
NK119(he)001:1173: rab mchog sbyangs pa mthar son skal ldan de //
NK119(he)001:1174: dbang bskur thob pas sdom gsum cig car skyes //
NK119(he)001:1175: rtogs grol dus mnyam in+d+ra b+h+au ti bzhin //
NK119(he)001:1176: de yang o rgyan gyi rgyal po in+d+ra b+h+au ti
NK119(he)001:1177: snga ma de nyid kyis bcom ldan 'das 'khor dang
NK119(he)001:1179: 'dod yon spangs pa'i thar ba ni /
NK119(he)001:1180: bcom ldan nam yang mi 'tshal lo zhes zhus pas /
NK119(he)001:1181: de nyid du bcom ldan 'das 'khor dang bcas pa
NK119(he)001:1182: dpal gsang ba 'dus pa'i dkyil 'khor lha tshogs su
NK119(he)001:1183: bzhengs te / dbang bskur zhing rgyud bstan pas sdom
NK119(he)001:1184: pa gsum cho ga tha dad ma dgos par gcig
NK119(he)001:1185: car du rgyud la skyes te rtogs grol dus mnyam
NK119(he)001:1186: bzhengs te / pa ltar / gang zag dbang po yang rab kyis /
NK119(he)001:1187: sngon du sdom pa 'og ma gnyis ma ma nos kyang dbang bskur thob pa'i tshe /
NK119(he)001:1188: skyabs su song ba na so thar dang /
NK119(he)001:1190: dbang rdzogs pa na dam tshig ste gsum ldan du gcig char skye ba yin te /
NK119(he)001:1192: dang po chu yis kyang ni dge bsnyen nyid du
NK119(he)001:1193: 'gyur la bum pa yis ni dge tshul nyid du
NK119(he)001:1194: 'gyur / dge slong gsang ba'i dbang bskur dag gis
NK119(he)001:1195: 'gyur la gnas brtan zhes bya bar 'gyur gong ma'i
NK119(he)001:1197: dbang po 'bring ni sdom gsum so so'i cho ga la /
NK119(he)001:1198: brten nas rim thob n+aa gardzu na ltar /
NK119(he)001:1199: de yang klu sgrub snying po ni /
NK119(he)001:1200: thog mar n+aa lan+dara bram ze sgra gcan 'dzin bzang po las rab tu byung /
NK119(he)001:1202: bsnyen par rdzogs nas dge slong dpal ldan zhes btags /
NK119(he)001:1203: de nas 'phags pa 'jam dpal gyis rjes su bzung /
NK119(he)001:1205: de nas mkha' 'gro dang grub pa can dag las dam tshig mnos pa ltar /
NK119(he)001:1206: gang zag dbang po 'bring gis sdom gsum rim gyis blang bas thob pa'o //
NK119(he)001:1207: dbang po tha ma skal dman shin tu 'dul dka' ste /
NK119(he)001:1208: gso sbyong bslab pa'i gnas bcu grub mtha' bzhi /
NK119(he)001:1209: bya spyod rnal 'byor rgyud kun rim shes nas /
NK119(he)001:1210: bla med 'jug par brtag pa gnyis par gsungs /
NK119(he)001:1211: de yang skal dman rim 'jug gi lam gyi rim
NK119(he)001:1212: pas bsnyen gnas nas mthar gyis slob dgos par yang
NK119(he)001:1213: / kyee rdo rje'i rtsa rgyud brtag gnyis las /
NK119(he)001:1214: dang por gso sbyong sbyin par bya //
NK119(he)001:1215: de rjes bslab pa'i gnas bcu nyid //
NK119(he)001:1216: de la bye brag smra ba bstan //
NK119(he)001:1217: mdo sde pa yang de bzhin no //
NK119(he)001:1218: de nas rnal 'byor spyod pa nyid //
NK119(he)001:1219: de yi rjes su dbu ma bstan //
NK119(he)001:1220: sngags kyi rim pa kun shes nas //
NK119(he)001:1221: de rjes kye yi rdo rje bstan //
NK119(he)001:1224: mnga' ris pa tshul khrims 'od zer la sogs gsar
NK119(he)001:1225: ma ba kha cig mi dge bcu spang ba la
NK119(he)001:1226: 'dod pa dang / kha cig dge tshul gyi rags ldog bcur 'dod la /
NK119(he)001:1227: rnying ma'i rgyud kun 'dus rig pa las /
NK119(he)001:1228: rnal 'byor rig pa'i mtha' bcu chub par 'dod pas kyang lam 'di la bslab par bya ste /
NK119(he)001:1230: gzhi dam tshig gis bzung bar bslab pa dang /
NK119(he)001:1231: rgyud thos pas grol bar bslab pa dang /
NK119(he)001:1232: phul du mkhas pas dbyung bar bslab pa dang /
NK119(he)001:1233: sgo kun nas bsdur bar bslab pa dang /
NK119(he)001:1234: rim pa dbang gis bsgrod par bslab pa dang /
NK119(he)001:1235: la spyod pas dor bar bslab pa dang /
NK119(he)001:1236: thag lta bas bcad par bslab pa dang /
NK119(he)001:1237: nyams su ting nge 'dzin gyis blang bar bslab pa dang /
NK119(he)001:1238: don man ngag gis bsgrub par bslab pa dang /
NK119(he)001:1239: mdo don gcig tu bsdu bar bslab pa'o //
NK119(he)001:1241: 'di ni lam gyi skabs thams cad rim gyis 'jug
NK119(he)001:1242: pa la dgongs kyi nyan rang gi lam la shes
NK119(he)001:1243: pa'i sngon nas thams cad slob par bshad pa ni
NK119(he)001:1244: ma yin no // grub mtha' bzhi ni /
NK119(he)001:1246: nyan thos pa dang rang rgyal dang //
NK119(he)001:1247: gsum pa byang chub sems dpa' ste //
NK119(he)001:1248: sangs rgyas pa la bzhi pa yin //
NK119(he)001:1250: sems tsam dbu ma gnyis dang bzhi'o //
NK119(he)001:1252: rang lugs nges pas gtan la dbab pa la'ang /
NK119(he)001:1253: sdom gsum gyi gnas lugs spyir btang du bshad pa /
NK119(he)001:1254: dgos pa'i gnad kyis dmigs bsal ba /
NK119(he)001:1255: brjod bya'i bsdus don gyis chings su bcings pa gsum las /
NK119(he)001:1257: de ltar sdom gsum thob tshul gsum gyi //
NK119(he)001:1258: 'dir ni dbang po 'bring gi tshul 'chad de //
NK119(he)001:1259: dge slong dge tshul dge bsnyen sdom ldan de //
NK119(he)001:1260: rdo rje 'dzin pa'i rab 'bring tha yin zhes //
NK119(he)001:1261: phur ba'i rgyud dang dus 'khor las gsungs shing //
NK119(he)001:1262: 'on kyang ye shes ldan pa gtso bor bzung //
NK119(he)001:1263: de skad du dus 'khor gyi rgyud dam pa dang po las /
NK119(he)001:1264: rten ni gsum la dge slong mchog /'bring ni dge tshul yin par 'dod //
NK119(he)001:1265: khyim na gnas pa tha ma'o //
NK119(he)001:1267: 'o na rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa las /
NK119(he)001:1268: 'bras bu gsang sngags ches 'phags tshul du ma gsungs na /
NK119(he)001:1269: der zhugs pa'i rnal 'byor pa ni phal cher rten dge bsnyen yin pas 'phags par ma gyur te /
NK119(he)001:1270: rdo rje 'dzin pa tha ma yin pa'i phyir /
NK119(he)001:1272: rten gyi sgo nas dge slong mchog yin kyang /
NK119(he)001:1273: ye shes ldan pa gtso che bas /
NK119(he)001:1274: rtogs pa'i sgo nas sngags kyi rdo rje 'dzin pa ches 'phags pa ste /
NK119(he)001:1275: sa'i snying po 'khor lo bcu pa'i mdo las /
NK119(he)001:1276: don dam pa'i dge slong ni /
NK119(he)001:1277: khyim na gnas shing skra dang kha spu ma bregs /
NK119(he)001:1280: 'phags pa'i mtshan nyid dang ldan pa de ni /
NK119(he)001:1281: don dam pa'i dge slong zhes bya'o //
NK119(he)001:1282: zhes dang 'jam dpal rnam par rol pa'i mdo las /
NK119(he)001:1285: byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi rab tu byung ba ma lags kyi /
NK119(he)001:1287: gang sems can rnams kyi nyon mongs pa gcod pa'i phyir brtson pa ni /
NK119(he)001:1288: byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi rab tu byung ba yin no //
NK119(he)001:1290: des na stong nyid snying rje'i ye shes ni 'phags pa'i mtshan nyid dang ldan pa ste /
NK119(he)001:1291: don dam pa'i dge slong du gsungs la /
NK119(he)001:1292: de dang ma ldan na kun rdzob ming gi dge slong ste 'phags pa min par /
NK119(he)001:1293: slob dpon b+ha bya'i rtog ge 'bar bar mdo lung drangs pa /
NK119(he)001:1294: gang gis ngur smrig bgos kyang sems kyi skyon ma spangs //
NK119(he)001:1295: lag tu lhung bzed thogs kyang yon tan snod ma gyur //
NK119(he)001:1296: skra dang kha spu bregs kyang dge sbyong tshul ma zhugs //
NK119(he)001:1297: rab tu byung yang dngos po kun las nges ma 'byung //
NK119(he)001:1298: dge slong de ni dge sbyong ma yin khyim pa'ang min //
NK119(he)001:1299: chu med khron pa ri mo'i mar me bzhin //
NK119(he)001:1301: ched du brjod pa'i tshoms las /
NK119(he)001:1302: dge sbyong mgo regs la byang chub ga la yod /
NK119(he)001:1303: snal ma ser po la byang chub ga la yod /
NK119(he)001:1304: chus bkrus pa la byang chub ga la yod /
NK119(he)001:1305: dgong lto bcag pa la byang chub ga la yod /
NK119(he)001:1306: ces gsungs pas 'khor rnams the tshom pa la bka' stsal pa /
NK119(he)001:1307: shes rab kyis spu gris nyon mongs pa'i skra bregs par bya'o //
NK119(he)001:1308: stong pa nyid kyi gos kyis nyon mongs pa'i tshad las skyob par bya'o //
NK119(he)001:1309: ye shes kyi chus ma rig pa'i dri ma dkru bar bya'o //
NK119(he)001:1310: bsam gtan gyi zas kyis 'dod pa'i bkres pa gso bar bya'o //
NK119(he)001:1312: de nas bu mo gser mchog 'od dpal la 'jam dpal gyis bka' stsal pa /
NK119(he)001:1313: lus rab tu byung yang 'jigs pa las mi skyob /
NK119(he)001:1314: sems rab tu byung bar bya'i /
NK119(he)001:1317: snga 'gyur rgyud sde'i rtsa ba kun 'dus las /
NK119(he)001:1318: rang dang gzhan don phan pa cher bshad pa //
NK119(he)001:1319: so thar sems bskyed dbang bskur nyid yin te //
NK119(he)001:1320: so sor 'dzin na nyan thos byang sems dang //
NK119(he)001:1321: rig pa 'dzin pa zhes su mkhas la grags //
NK119(he)001:1322: de yang a nu lung gi mdo lnga'i kun 'dus rig pa las /
NK119(he)001:1323: de ltar sdom pa gsum po yang //
NK119(he)001:1324: rang dang gzhan don phan pa che zhes pas //
NK119(he)001:1325: rang gi don du byang chub 'dod pas gzhan gnod
NK119(he)001:1326: gzhi bcas spang ba nyan thos kyi sdom pa so
NK119(he)001:1327: sor thar pa / de'i steng du gzhan la phan
NK119(he)001:1328: pa lhur len pa byang chub sems dpa'i bslab pa
NK119(he)001:1329: sor thar pa / / de'ang rang gzhan gnyis ka
NK119(he)001:1330: byang chub la 'god pa'i thabs rgya che ba rig
NK119(he)001:1331: pa 'dzin pa sngags kyi dam tshig ste sdom pa
NK119(he)001:1332: sor thar pa / / gsum mo // yo ga rdo rje rtse mo las /
NK119(he)001:1333: so so thar dang byang chub sems //
NK119(he)001:1337: de ltar thun mong sdom pa 'og ma gnyis //
NK119(he)001:1338: 'dir ni bla med dbang gi yan lag tu //
NK119(he)001:1339: rgyud sde rgya mtshor bshad ltar 'dir 'chad do //
NK119(he)001:1340: sdom gsum phyogs gcig tu bsgrigs pa'i rnam bzhag ni gsang sngags las gzhan la med de /
NK119(he)001:1341: nyan thos kyi sde snod la sdom pa gong ma gnyis med /
NK119(he)001:1342: byang sdom la sngags sdom med pa'i phyir ro //
NK119(he)001:1343: bla na med pa'i byang chub bsgrub pa la gtso
NK119(he)001:1344: bor sngags sdom dgos kyang de'i rten du byang sems
NK119(he)001:1345: dang so thar nges par dgos te /
NK119(he)001:1346: dang po smin grol la 'jug pa'i dus su yang //
NK119(he)001:1347: dkon mchog gsum la bdag skyabs mchi //
NK119(he)001:1349: so sor thar ba'i sdom pa la'ang //
NK119(he)001:1350: rim pa bzhin du bslab par bgyi //
NK119(he)001:1352: bla med smon 'jug byang chub sems //
NK119(he)001:1353: dam pa bdag gis bskyed par bgyi //
NK119(he)001:1355: rtsa ba yan lag dam tshig kun //
NK119(he)001:1356: ma lus bdag gis yongs su bzung //
NK119(he)001:1357: zhes khas blangs ba'i phyir dang /
NK119(he)001:1358: sngags kyi dam tshig bsrung dus kyang //
NK119(he)001:1360: bde gshegs bka' 'das kyi rtsa ltung bsrung tshul las shes so //
NK119(he)001:1362: 'og tu 'chad pa'i sdom gsum so sor khog phub gleng gzhi dang /
NK119(he)001:1363: dang po sdom pa ma thob thob tshul dang /
NK119(he)001:1364: bar du thob pa mi nyams bsrung ba'i thabs /
NK119(he)001:1365: tha ma nyams na gso tshul bzhi res sdoms /
NK119(he)001:1368: sngags sdom gsum po re re la'ang sdom bzhi po des 'chings nas bshad par ston to //
NK119(he)001:1369: rigs bdun so thar dpag bsam ljon pa'i shing /
NK119(he)001:1370: byang chub sems mchog yal 'dab nam mkhar gdal /
NK119(he)001:1371: rig pa 'dzin pa'i 'bras mang rab smin te /
NK119(he)001:1372: skal bzang bya tshogs dga' bas brten par shog /
NK119(he)001:1373: sde snod gsum gyi rnam rgyal khang bzang du /
NK119(he)001:1374: gzhan don brlabs chen dbang po rdo rje 'chang /
NK119(he)001:1375: gsang sngags snying po'i rtse brgya gdengs tsam gyis /
NK119(he)001:1376: nyes tshogs lha min g.yul ngo mthar byed shog /
NK119(he)001:1377: sangs rgyas bstan pa'i zhing sa gshin po la /
NK119(he)001:1378: gsum ldan bshes gnyen myu gus yongs khyab par /
NK119(he)001:1379: legs bshad bdud rtsi'i char gyi tshogs bsil bas /
NK119(he)001:1380: log rtog mi nges ming gi mthar byed shog /
NK119(he)001:1381: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i lam gyi cha lag
NK119(he)001:1382: sdom pa gsum rnam par nges pa'i 'grel pa rnam
NK119(he)001:1384: sdom gsum spyi'i bshad gzhi'i rim par phye ba ste /
NK119(he)001:1385: dang po'i rnam bshad bstan zin to //
NK119(he)001:1386: da ni rim par phye ba gnyis pa 'dul ba
NK119(he)001:1387: so thar gyi sdom pa bshad par bya ba'ang bzhi
NK119(he)001:1393: ston pa'i 'dul ba'i sde snod gsungs shing bka'i bsdus tshul /
NK119(he)001:1394: de nyid 'dzin pa'i bla ma brgyud pa /
NK119(he)001:1399: gleng gzhi ston pa sa w+aa ra na si ru /
NK119(he)001:1400: lhag pa'i tshul khrims gtsor ston bden pa bzhi /
NK119(he)001:1401: lnga sder gsungs pa 'od srung sogs kyis bsdus /
NK119(he)001:1402: bye brag bshad mdzod la sogs 'phags pas brtsam /
NK119(he)001:1403: yon tan 'od dang sh+aakya 'od kyis spel /
NK119(he)001:1404: de yang bdag cag gi ston pa thub pa'i dbang
NK119(he)001:1405: po 'di nyid theg chung thun mong du grags pa'i
NK119(he)001:1406: lugs ltar na / bskal pa dpag tu med pa'i
NK119(he)001:1407: sngon nas dge ba'i rtsa ba rgya chen po bsags
NK119(he)001:1408: lugs ltar na / pa yin kyang / las kyi
NK119(he)001:1409: lhag ma zhig gi dbang gis dmyal ba'i shing rta
NK119(he)001:1410: 'dren pa'i gyad pag shi tar gyur pa'i tshe /
NK119(he)001:1411: rang gi grogs la snying rje chen pos 'di'i sdug bsngal yang bdag gis khur bar zhus pas /
NK119(he)001:1412: dmyal srung a wam khros te /
NK119(he)001:1413: lcags kyi tho ba me 'bar ba spyi bor bsnun
NK119(he)001:1414: pas tshe de'i dus byas te lhar skyes te shi
NK119(he)001:1415: 'phos nas / lho phyogs kyi rgyud du rdza mkhan
NK119(he)001:1416: gyi khye'u snang byed du gyur bar drin lan bsabs
NK119(he)001:1418: des sangs rgyas thub pa chen po la gdugs gcig /
NK119(he)001:1420: rdza'i bum pa gcig /'gron bu lnga phul te sems
NK119(he)001:1421: bskyed nas bskal pa grangs med gsum du tshogs bsags
NK119(he)001:1422: pa las / grangs med dang po la gzhon nu brtson 'grus spyod du gyur te /
NK119(he)001:1423: 'dren pa yul 'khor skyongs la sogs sangs rgyas lnga khri lnga stong la tshogs bsags /
NK119(he)001:1424: gnyis pa la tshong dpon shes rab bzang por gyur
NK119(he)001:1425: te sangs rgyas legs mdzad la sogs drug khri drug
NK119(he)001:1428: gzhon nu chos kyi sprin du gyur te mar me
NK119(he)001:1429: mdzad la sogs sangs rgyas bdun khri bdun stong mnyes
NK119(he)001:1430: par mdzad de / 'dul ba lung gzhi las /
NK119(he)001:1432: sangs rgyas rnam gzigs bar dag tu //
NK119(he)001:1433: lnga khri lnga stong tshang ba yi //
NK119(he)001:1434: sangs rgyas rnams ni ngas mchod de //
NK119(he)001:1435: de tshe nga la skyo sems med //
NK119(he)001:1436: sangs rgyas legs mdzad nas bzung ste //
NK119(he)001:1437: dbang po'i rgyal mtshan thub pa'i bar //
NK119(he)001:1438: drug khri drug stong tshang ba yi //
NK119(he)001:1439: sangs rgyas rnams ni ngas mchod de //
NK119(he)001:1440: de tshe nga la skyo sems med //
NK119(he)001:1441: sangs rgyas mar me mdzad nas ni //
NK119(he)001:1442: rin chen gtsug tor can bar du //
NK119(he)001:1443: bdun khri bdun stong tshang ba yi //
NK119(he)001:1444: sangs rgyas rnams ni ngas mchod de //
NK119(he)001:1445: de tshe nga la skyo sems med //
NK119(he)001:1448: rnam gzigs mar me rin chen gtsug /
NK119(he)001:1449: grangs med gsum gyi tha ma 'byung //
NK119(he)001:1450: go rim de las ldog pa ste //
NK119(he)001:1451: dang po sh+aakya thub pa yin //
NK119(he)001:1453: de yang tshogs lam gyis bsdus pa'i tshogs grangs med gsum du bsags na /
NK119(he)001:1454: rdo rje gdan du tshogs lam chen po'i rten de
NK119(he)001:1455: las sbyor mthong bsgom pa mi slob pa'i lam dang
NK119(he)001:1456: bcas pa lam lnga ka stan thog gcig tu mngon
NK119(he)001:1457: du mdzad de rang sangs rgyas dbang po rnon po
NK119(he)001:1458: dang mthun par de nyid las /
NK119(he)001:1459: ston dang bse ru byang chub bar //
NK119(he)001:1460: bsam gtan mtha' rten gcig la kun //
NK119(he)001:1461: sngon dang de yi thar cha mthun //
NK119(he)001:1463: mthar mdzad pa bcu gnyis kyis sangs rgyas nas /
NK119(he)001:1464: lhag ma med par mya ngan las 'das te zhi ba'i dbyings su bzhugs par 'dod do //
NK119(he)001:1465: de ltar sangs rgyas nas chos kyi 'khor lo ji ltar bskor na /
NK119(he)001:1467: zhag bdun phrag bdun du chos ma gsungs pa las /
NK119(he)001:1468: tshangs pa dang brgya byin gyis gsol ba btab pa'i ngor /
NK119(he)001:1469: gnas phun sum tshogs pa w+aa ra na si drang srong lhung ba ri dwags kyi gnas su /
NK119(he)001:1470: ston pa phun sum tshogs pa sh+aakya thub pas /
NK119(he)001:1471: 'khor phun sum tshogs pa kun shes koo di nya /
NK119(he)001:1475: bzang ldan te lnga sde bzang po lha brgyad khri dang bcas pa la /
NK119(he)001:1481: bden pa bzhi'i chos kyi rnam grangs /
NK119(he)001:1482: dus phun sum tshogs pa dgung lo sum cu rtsa
NK119(he)001:1483: drug nas bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi bar gsungs so
NK119(he)001:1484: // 'di la gnas gcig dang tha dad /
NK119(he)001:1486: gcig char du 'dod pa la sogs grub mtha' mi 'dra ba 'ga' yod kyang /
NK119(he)001:1487: theg pa che chung thun mong dang khyad par gyis dbye bas gsal bar bya ba nyid do //
NK119(he)001:1488: de yang 'dul ba'i sde snod tshul khrims kyi bslab pa gtso bor ston pa las brtsam ste /
NK119(he)001:1489: 'dul ba'i 'dul ba bcas pa dang rang bzhin gyi rnam bzhag che long rnams dang /
NK119(he)001:1490: 'dul ba'i mdo sde ting nge 'dzin dang tshangs spyod rnal 'byor du bya ba'i rim pa /
NK119(he)001:1491: 'dul ba'i mngon pa de dag gi rgya cher dbye ba ji snyed pa rnams te /
NK119(he)001:1497: ltung rkang nyis brgya lnga bcu rtsa gsum /
NK119(he)001:1498: rtsod pa zhi byed kyi chos bdun gtso bor ston pa dge slong pha'i so thar gyi mdo dang /
NK119(he)001:1499: ltung rkang sum brgya drug cu rtsa bzhi'i rnam bzhag
NK119(he)001:1500: gtso bor ston pa dge slong ma'i so thar gyi
NK119(he)001:1501: mdo lta bu'o // gnyis pa la'ang /
NK119(he)001:1503: phyogs mthun gyi lung gnyis las /
NK119(he)001:1505: dge slong pha'i rnam 'byed la bam po brgyad cu rtsa gsum /
NK119(he)001:1506: ma'i rnam 'byed la bam po nyi shu rtsa brgyad do //
NK119(he)001:1507: lung gzhi bam po brgya dang dgu /
NK119(he)001:1508: lung phran tshegs bam po lnga bcu rtsa dgu /
NK119(he)001:1509: gzhung dam pa pa'am gzhung bla ma zhes bam po drug cu rtsa lnga /
NK119(he)001:1510: 'di'i le'u bcu gcig las bod du ma 'gyur bar bshad do //
NK119(he)001:1512: gnyis pa phyogs mthun gyi lung ni /
NK119(he)001:1513: dge slong la rab tu gces pa'i mdo /
NK119(he)001:1514: tshul khrims yang dag pa'i mdo /
NK119(he)001:1515: ltung ba sde lnga'i dge mi dge bstan pa'i mdo /
NK119(he)001:1516: tshul khrims 'chal ba'i rnam par smin pa lci yang bstan pa'i mdo /
NK119(he)001:1518: mkhar sil 'chang ba'i kun tu spyod pa ston pa'i mdo /
NK119(he)001:1520: sbyangs pa'i yon tan gyi mdo la sogs pa rnams so //
NK119(he)001:1521: de ltar gsungs pa'i sde snod de dag ji ltar bsdus zhe na /
NK119(he)001:1522: sangs rgyas mya ngan las 'das nas bstan pa 'od
NK119(he)001:1523: srung la gtad pas ston pa 'das nas phyis de'i
NK119(he)001:1524: dbyar la / rgyal po ma skyes sgras sbyin bdag byas te rgyal po'i khab tu /
NK119(he)001:1525: lha'i bus 'phya ba bsal ba'i ched du bsdu ba mdzad de /
NK119(he)001:1526: 'od srung dang nye ba 'khor la sogs pa dgra bcom pa lnga brgyar gcig gis ma tshang bas /
NK119(he)001:1527: kun dga' bo spyod pas 'dul bar dgongs nas 'od srung gis /
NK119(he)001:1529: 'di thams cad ni dgra bcom pa sha stag yin gyi /
NK119(he)001:1530: khyod slob pa rgyun du zhugs pa yin pas 'dir ma 'dug par song zhig gsungs pas /
NK119(he)001:1532: bdag gis tshul khrims dang lta ba dang 'tsho ba
NK119(he)001:1533: sogs gang la'ang nyes pa med kyi de skad ma
NK119(he)001:1534: gsungs zhus pas / sangs rgyas dang yun ring du
NK119(he)001:1535: 'grogs pas de tsam yon tan du mi che la
NK119(he)001:1536: gsungs zhus pas / / nyes pa brgyad yod pas tshul shing longs shig gsungs so //
NK119(he)001:1538: zhus dang ma zhus lan log bardzisa //
NK119(he)001:1539: chu dang bag yangs bstan pa gnyis //
NK119(he)001:1542: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa lnga brgya phrag bcur gnas
NK119(he)001:1543: pa las skye dgu'i bdag mo rab tu byung bar
NK119(he)001:1544: zhus pas lnga brgya phrag tha ma rtags tsam 'dzin
NK119(he)001:1547: sangs rgyas mya ngan las mi 'da' bar gsol ba
NK119(he)001:1548: btab nas bskal ba'i lhag mar yang gnas pa la
NK119(he)001:1551: ston pas thugs phab nas smras pa la lan log btab pas nyes /
NK119(he)001:1553: na bzang tshems pa'i tshe nam mkhar brkyong na lhas 'dzin pa la rdog pas bardzisa pas nyes /
NK119(he)001:1555: zhal skyems pa la lhung bzed nam mkhar zed na
NK119(he)001:1556: lhas bdud rtsi 'bul ba las rnyog chu drangs pas
NK119(he)001:1558: dka' zhing nye bar 'tshe ba'i tshe /
NK119(he)001:1559: bslab pa'i gzhi 'ga' zhig bag yangs su bya'o gsungs pa la ji ltar bya ma zhus pas nyes /
NK119(he)001:1561: gsang ba'i sba ba sbubs su nub pa bud med dang khyim pa'i 'khor la bstan pas nyes /
NK119(he)001:1563: sku gser gyi kha dog khyim pa la bstan pas nyes //
NK119(he)001:1565: pha spun 'dren sems kyis bshos lhag dang /
NK119(he)001:1566: na bza' rnying pa ma gsol bas nyes zhes spyo chung dang dgur mdzad de /
NK119(he)001:1567: mchim lham bsnun te bskrad do //
NK119(he)001:1568: de nas kun dga' bo rang gi slob ma bri dza'i gnas su byon pas /
NK119(he)001:1570: mkhan po dben par bzhag par zhus pas /
NK119(he)001:1571: de nyid dgra bcom pa thob ste dgra bcom pa lnga brgya 'dus te /
NK119(he)001:1574: nye bar 'khor gyis mngon pa bsdus te thugs las tsha ra gcig gsungs par bshad do //
NK119(he)001:1576: 'das nas lo brgya dang bcu na rgyal po a shwa kas /
NK119(he)001:1577: sbyin bdag byas te yangs pa can du grags pa la sogs pa dgra bcom pa lnga brgyas /
NK119(he)001:1578: yangs pa can gyi dge slong lha chen pos mi
NK119(he)001:1579: rung ba'i gzhi bcu bsal ba'i ched du sde snod
NK119(he)001:1580: gsum zhal thon du mdzad de bsdus so //
NK119(he)001:1582: hu lu hu lu yi rang dang //
NK119(he)001:1583: kun spyod snod dang lan tsh+wa dang //
NK119(he)001:1584: lam dang sor gnyis dkrug dang gding //
NK119(he)001:1585: gser la rung bar bya ba ste //
NK119(he)001:1587: de yang 'dul ba dang 'gal ba'i las byas na
NK119(he)001:1588: hu lu hu lu zhes thal mo brdab pas ltung
NK119(he)001:1590: rang gi bya ba ma yin pa byas na chos
NK119(he)001:1591: ldan gyi gang zag gzhan la rjes su yi rangs
NK119(he)001:1592: byas pas dag par 'dod pa dang /
NK119(he)001:1593: sa chen po 'di la kun spyod pas dge slong gis sa brkos kyang rung bar 'dod pa dang /
NK119(he)001:1594: na ba la snod sbu gu can nas srin bu
