NK119(he)001:1595: pad pa'i 'jibs stangs kyis chang 'thung rung bar 'dod
NK119(he)001:1596: pa dang / dus rung gi kha zas lan tsh+wa
NK119(he)001:1597: dang cig phyi dro longs spyod rung bar 'dod pa
NK119(he)001:1598: pa dang / dang / yang yang za ba la
NK119(he)001:1599: lam dpag tshad phyed du 'gro mi dgos par rgyang
NK119(he)001:1600: grags gcig byin pas chog par 'dod pa dang /
NK119(he)001:1601: lhag por byed pa la sor mo gnyis kyi ri mo gtod pas chog par 'dod pa dang /
NK119(he)001:1602: phyi dro dus su za ba dang /
NK119(he)001:1603: dus min du rung ba zho dang 'o ma lta bu dkrug nas za ba dang /
NK119(he)001:1604: gding ba byed pa la gding ba rnying pa nas
NK119(he)001:1605: bde bar gshegs pa'i mtho gang slan mi dgos par
NK119(he)001:1606: rang gi mtho gang gis chog par 'dod pa dang
NK119(he)001:1607: / bsnyen par ma rdzogs pa'i mgo thog tu khri'u'i steng du lhung bzed bzhag /
NK119(he)001:1608: de'i nang du gser sogs rin po che bzhag nas
NK119(he)001:1609: blangs pas gser la rung bar 'dod pa dang bcu'o
NK119(he)001:1611: ston pa mya ngan las 'das nas lo sum brgya na /
NK119(he)001:1612: kha che me tog brtsegs pa'i kun dga' ra bar /
NK119(he)001:1613: rgyal po ka ni kas sbyin bdag byas te /
NK119(he)001:1616: so so'i skye bo'i dge slong khri drug stong 'dus te /
NK119(he)001:1617: bdud sdig can dge slong gi cha byad du sprul
NK119(he)001:1618: pa bzang po zhes bya bas dbyen spyos te sde
NK119(he)001:1619: pa phan tshun 'khrug long du gyur pa bsal zhing
NK119(he)001:1620: sde ba bco brgyad chos su gcig par byas te
NK119(he)001:1621: / sde snod glegs bam du bsdus te sdud pa
NK119(he)001:1622: po'i gtso bo ni byang chub sems dpa' su mi
NK119(he)001:1623: / tra dang / dgra bcom pa pur+ni ka'i /
NK119(he)001:1624: de yang sde pa bzhi dang gyes pa bco brgyad ni /
NK119(he)001:1625: dang po sde pa thams cad kyi rtsa ba gzhi thams cad yod smra yin la /
NK119(he)001:1628: mang bkur ba dang gsum gyes /
NK119(he)001:1629: de las sde pa bco brgyad gyes par 'dul ba 'od ldan dang /
NK119(he)001:1630: pan chen dul ba lhas gsungs so //
NK119(he)001:1631: de la gzhi thams cad yod par smra ba la dbye na /
NK119(he)001:1635: mang du thos par smra ba /
NK119(he)001:1638: rnam par phye ste smra ba'i sde dang bdun no //
NK119(he)001:1639: 'di dag ston pa'i sras rgyal rigs sgra gcan 'dzin
NK119(he)001:1640: bslab pa la gus pa'i mchog tu lung bstan pa'i
NK119(he)001:1641: slob rgyud de / skad ni so thar gyi mdo
NK119(he)001:1642: 'don pa'i tshe legs sbyar sam skri ta'i skad du
NK119(he)001:1643: sum bcu rtsa gsum gyi lha rnams dang mthun par
NK119(he)001:1644: slob rgyud de / 'don / snam sbyar gyi snam
NK119(he)001:1645: phran dgu yan nyer lnga man chad zung ma gtogs
NK119(he)001:1646: slob rgyud de / 'don / pa / grwa'i rtags pad ma /
NK119(he)001:1649: zas la lag pa bkan pa'i tshul gyis byin len byed cing /
NK119(he)001:1651: e thang pa la gru phye dang dgus bar chod na thub par 'dod do //
NK119(he)001:1652: phal chen pa la dbye na /
NK119(he)001:1657: 'jig rten las 'das par smra ba'i sde dang lnga'o //
NK119(he)001:1658: 'di dag bram ze'i rigs sbyangs pa'i yon tan dang
NK119(he)001:1659: ldan pa'i mchog gnas brtan 'od bsrung chen po'i slob
NK119(he)001:1660: rgyud de / skad ni pra kri ta ste 'od gsal gyi lha dang mthun la /
NK119(he)001:1661: snam phran dgu yan nyer gsum man chad rtags ni g.yung drung dang /
NK119(he)001:1664: snod la byin len byas pas 'chag par 'dod la /
NK119(he)001:1665: nyal 'gog yol bas bar chod pa'o //
NK119(he)001:1666: gnas brtan pa la dbye na /
NK119(he)001:1667: rgyal byed tshal na gnas pa'i sde /
NK119(he)001:1668: 'jigs med ri la gnas pa'i sde /
NK119(he)001:1669: gtsug lag khang la gnas pa'i sde dang gsum mo //
NK119(he)001:1670: 'di dag smyig ma mkhan gyi rigs /
NK119(he)001:1671: mtha' 'khob 'dul ba'i mchog 'phags pa ka ta ya na'i slob rgyud de /
NK119(he)001:1672: skad ni a ba b+h+ram sha ta ste zur chags pas sha za dang mthun pa /
NK119(he)001:1673: snam phran dgu yan nyer gcig man chad la /
NK119(he)001:1676: sbyin len dkyur thabs su byed cing /
NK119(he)001:1677: nyal 'gog thag pas bar chad na thub par 'dod do //
NK119(he)001:1678: mang pos bkur ba la dbye na /
NK119(he)001:1681: gnas ma bu'i sde dang gsum mo //
NK119(he)001:1682: 'di dag 'dreg mkhan gyi rigs 'dul ba 'dzin pa
NK119(he)001:1683: rnams kyi mchog /'phags pa nye bar 'khor gyi slob
NK119(he)001:1684: rgyud de / skad ni bi sh+aa tsi ste gnas gtsang ma'i lha dang mthun pa /
NK119(he)001:1685: snam phran lnga nas nyer gcig bar /
NK119(he)001:1686: rtags ni dung ngam dpal be'u 'o //
NK119(he)001:1687: sbyin len 'phrog thabs su byed cing /
NK119(he)001:1688: nyal 'gog bsnyen par rdzogs ma rdzogs kyi bar du
NK119(he)001:1689: ri mos chod pas nub lhag nyal thub par 'dod
NK119(he)001:1690: do // de skad du'ang sa pan gyis /
NK119(he)001:1691: nyan thos rtsa ba'i sde bzhi la //
NK119(he)001:1693: skad kyang legs sbyar rang bzhin dang //
NK119(he)001:1694: zhes sogs gsungs shing 'di dag gi rnam dbye rgyas
NK119(he)001:1695: pa ni yid bzhin mdzod la sogs par gsal lo
NK119(he)001:1696: // de ltar bsdu ba gnyis pa'i dus su dgra
NK119(he)001:1697: bcom pa nyer sbas la sogs pa dgra bcom pa
NK119(he)001:1698: lnga brgyas bye brag bshad mdzod chen mo mdzad cing
NK119(he)001:1699: // / kha cig byang phyogs ri bo 'big byed
NK119(he)001:1700: gar mkhan gyi gtsug lag khang du dgra bcom pa
NK119(he)001:1701: lnga brgya 'dus nas bye brag bshad mdzod chen mo
NK119(he)001:1702: sho lo ka 'bum yod pa mdzad de mngon pa'i
NK119(he)001:1703: 'grel yin no zhes pa'ang re zhig brtag par bya'o
NK119(he)001:1704: // / // de ltar dam chos 'dul ba'i sde
NK119(he)001:1705: snod la gces spras su mdzad pa'i mchog ni rgyan
NK119(he)001:1706: drug nang nas yon tan 'od dang sh+aakya 'od gnyis
NK119(he)001:1707: // / // yin te / de yang rgya cher 'grel las /
NK119(he)001:1708: 'phags pa gzhi thams yod par smra ba'i 'dul ba
NK119(he)001:1709: 'dzin pa chen po bram ze'i btsun pa yon tan
NK119(he)001:1710: 'od bdag dang gzhan gyi grub pa'i mtha' rgya mtsho'i
NK119(he)001:1711: pha rol tu son pa bde bar gshegs pa'i chos
NK119(he)001:1712: 'dul ba bdud rtsi'i snying khus shes rab kyi dbang
NK119(he)001:1713: po rgyas pa de bzhin gshegs pa'i bka' dam pa
NK119(he)001:1714: nan tan snying por sgrub pa /
NK119(he)001:1715: zhes bshad pa'i yon tan dang ldan pa'o //
NK119(he)001:1716: phyis bsod nams grags dang zhi ba'i 'od kyi slob ma sh+aakya 'od de /
NK119(he)001:1717: 'dul ba bdud rtsi'i rgyan gyur yon sh+aaka rnam gnyis zhes bya'o //
NK119(he)001:1718: de ltar gong du bshad pa'i 'dul ba'i bka' de dag gi dgongs 'grel gyi bstan bcos la /
NK119(he)001:1719: so thar mdo dngos kyi 'grel pa dang /
NK119(he)001:1721: de gnyis ka'i don 'grel gsum las /
NK119(he)001:1723: dri med bshes gnyen gyis mdzad pa'i rgya cher 'grel bam po lnga bcu pa /
NK119(he)001:1724: dpa' bos mdzad pa'i 'grel pa bam po nyer bdun pa /
NK119(he)001:1725: d+aa na sh+ai las mdzad pa'i tshig gi brjod byang zhes bya ba bam po gnyis yod do //
NK119(he)001:1727: rnam 'byed la dul ba lhas mdzad pa'i 'grel pa /
NK119(he)001:1728: gzhi dang gzhung dam pa la /
NK119(he)001:1729: slob dpon dge legs bshes gnyen gyis mdzad pa'i 'grel pa cung zad ma tshang ba /
NK119(he)001:1730: phran tshegs kyi 'grel pa slob dpon tshul khrims skyongs kyis mdzad pa dang /
NK119(he)001:1733: lung sde bzhi'i dgongs pa phyogs gcig tu mdzad pa
NK119(he)001:1734: slob dpon yon tan 'od kyis mdzad pa'i mdo rtsa
NK119(he)001:1735: / de'i rang 'grel nyid kyi rnam bshad shwa lo ka stong phrag bcu gnyis pa /
NK119(he)001:1738: las brgya rtsa gcig gi rnam bzhag bye brag tu 'chad pa karma sha tam /
NK119(he)001:1739: de rnams yon tan 'od kyis mdzad /
NK119(he)001:1740: slob dpon chos bshes kyis mdzad pa'i mdo rtsa'i rgya
NK119(he)001:1741: cher 'grel bam po bdun cu pa slob dpon shes
NK119(he)001:1742: rab byed pas mdzad pa'i mdo rtsa'i 'grel pa /
NK119(he)001:1743: slob dpon pad ma 'byung gnas kyis mdzad pa'i dge slong gi lo dri ba dang /
NK119(he)001:1744: dge tshul gyi lo dri ba /
NK119(he)001:1745: sa ga'i lhas mdzad pa'i 'dul ba tshigs le 'ur byas pa /
NK119(he)001:1746: thogs med kyis mdzad pa'i 'dul ba bsdus pa /
NK119(he)001:1747: slob dpon sh+aakya 'od kyis mdzad pa'i 'dul ba sum brgya pa /
NK119(he)001:1749: gzhan yang 'dul ba'i gzhung phran slob dpon chos kyi
NK119(he)001:1750: tshong dpon kyis mdzad pa'i 'dul ba la bstod pa
NK119(he)001:1751: / kha che 'dus bzang gis mdzad pa'i ka ri
NK119(he)001:1752: ka lnga bcu la sogs bstan 'gyur na mang du
NK119(he)001:1753: / bzhugs pa la / bod du'ang snga phyi'i dge
NK119(he)001:1754: ba'i bshes gnyen rnams kyis mdzad pa ni mtha' yas
NK119(he)001:1755: / bzhugs pa la / so // gnyis pa de
NK119(he)001:1756: nyid 'dzin pa'i bla ma brgyud pa ji ltar yin
NK119(he)001:1757: / bzhugs pa la / so // zhe na / snga 'gyur sdom rgyun zhi ba 'tsho dang ni //
NK119(he)001:1758: phyis nas sh+aakya sh+r+ai las kyang dar //
NK119(he)001:1759: zhes pa'i don la gnyis te /
NK119(he)001:1760: snga dar phyi dar gyi lo rgyus spyir bstan pa dang /
NK119(he)001:1761: rang gi sdom rgyun bye brag tu bshad pa'o //
NK119(he)001:1763: bod 'dir mnga' bdag chos skyong ba'i rgyal po khri
NK119(he)001:1764: srong lde'u btsan gyis za hor gyis yul nas gzhi
NK119(he)001:1765: thams cad yod par smra ba'i mkhan po bo d+hi
NK119(he)001:1766: sa t+wa'am / shan+ta rak+shi ta zhes slob dpon zhi
NK119(he)001:1767: ba 'tsho spyan drangs te bod du dam chos 'dul
NK119(he)001:1768: ba'i bstan pa 'dzug par dgongs nas /
NK119(he)001:1769: sdom rten 'dug gam nyams sad pa'i phyir du /
NK119(he)001:1771: dba' ye shes dbang po bsrung ba /
NK119(he)001:1772: rin chen dbang po bsrung ba /
NK119(he)001:1773: rlangs bde gshegs go cha bsrung ba /
NK119(he)001:1774: bee ro tsa na rnam par snang mdzad bsrung ba /
NK119(he)001:1776: gtsang pa de wen+d+ra lha'i dbang po bsrung ba ste /
NK119(he)001:1777: sad mi mi bdun rab tu byung nas /
NK119(he)001:1778: slar yang rma rin chen mchog /
NK119(he)001:1779: nam mkha'i snying po la sogs pa dge slong mi
NK119(he)001:1780: lngas gtsor byas la sdom rgyun ji rigs su dar
NK119(he)001:1781: zhing rgyas so // de nas mnga' bdag khri ral
NK119(he)001:1782: gyi dus su kha che'i yul nas dzi n+aa mi
NK119(he)001:1783: zhing rgyas so // tra dang / su len+d+ra bo
NK119(he)001:1784: d+hi la sogs spyan drangs nas sdom rgyun cher 'bar
NK119(he)001:1785: zhing rgyas so // tra dang / ba yin na'ang
NK119(he)001:1786: / khri ral 'das rjes glang dar mas sangs rgyas
NK119(he)001:1787: kyi bstan pa bshig ste dge 'dun thams cad ming
NK119(he)001:1788: med par byas pa'i skabs su /
NK119(he)001:1789: g.yor stod kyi dmar ban sh+aakya mu ne /
NK119(he)001:1790: rgya ram pa'i gtsang rab gsal /
NK119(he)001:1791: dra chung mdo'i g.yo dge 'byung gsum gyis /
NK119(he)001:1792: dpal chu bo ri'i dgon nas /
NK119(he)001:1793: 'dul ba dre'u khal gcig bkal nas /
NK119(he)001:1794: hor yul du byon pas chos la 'god ma thub /
NK119(he)001:1797: mdo smad an chung gi dgon pa'am /
NK119(he)001:1799: rma klung dan tig shel gyi dgon pa zhes bya bar bzhugs pa la /
NK119(he)001:1800: bon po dge ba gsal bya ba dad de rab
NK119(he)001:1801: tu byung bas mtshan bla chen mu zung dgongs pa
NK119(he)001:1802: gsal du btags des sdom rgyun ji snyed gnang ba
NK119(he)001:1803: la 'dul ba smad lugs zhes sam /
NK119(he)001:1804: bla chen sdom rgyun du grags so //
NK119(he)001:1805: de dus gtsang nas lo ston rdo rje dbang phyug /
NK119(he)001:1806: gtsang dge shes rab seng ge /
NK119(he)001:1807: dbus pa klu mes shes rab /
NK119(he)001:1809: sum pa ye shes blo gros /
NK119(he)001:1810: rba btsun blo gros grags dang drug byon nas /
NK119(he)001:1811: blo gros grags ni sngon nas dge slong yin zhing /
NK119(he)001:1812: gzhan lnga po rgyal so kha phyag gi dgon par bla chen las rab tu byung /
NK119(he)001:1815: lo ston dang sum pa mthu che bas bstan pa srungs /
NK119(he)001:1816: khyed tsho yar song la dge 'dun gyi sde tshugs gsungs pas yar byon nas /
NK119(he)001:1817: rag+shi tshul khrims gzhon nus khong lnga'i phyi snyegs pas ma slebs pas /
NK119(he)001:1818: khams su bla chen gyi slob ma 'grum ye shes g.yung drung gis rab tu byung ste /
NK119(he)001:1819: phyis khong rnams dang bsdebs nas yar byon /
NK119(he)001:1821: gtsang du lo ston rdo rje dbang phyug las gyes pas bong chos stod smad gnyis /
NK119(he)001:1822: gtsang dge shes rab las gyes pas gtsang chos lnga /
NK119(he)001:1823: dbus su rba btsun blo gros grags /
NK119(he)001:1824: rag shi tshul khrims gzhon nu /
NK119(he)001:1826: sum ye shes blo gros bzhi las gyes pas ka ba bzhi /
NK119(he)001:1828: rten ma sum cu rtsa gnyis la sogs pa byung /
NK119(he)001:1829: 'bre ye shes yon tan de rnams kyis gnas brtan
NK119(he)001:1830: byas nas phyi'i bu bzhi nang gi bu bzhi la
NK119(he)001:1831: sogs pa / chos ldan dag pa 'bre'i skor zhes pa byung ngo //
NK119(he)001:1832: des na pad+ma bka' thang las /
NK119(he)001:1833: de nas dam chos 'dul ba'i bstan pa ni //
NK119(he)001:1834: me ro tsam zhig mdo khams smad nas dar //
NK119(he)001:1836: de dag la snga 'gyur sdom rgyun zhes bya'o //
NK119(he)001:1837: phyis kha che pan chen sh+aakya sh+r+ai sa chen kun snying gi dus byung ste /
NK119(he)001:1838: bod du sdom rgyun gnang bas 'dul ba phyis dar dang stod lugs zhes dang /
NK119(he)001:1839: jo bo rje phal chen sde pa yin te /
NK119(he)001:1840: chos gos dkar po la sogs yin kyang bod du
NK119(he)001:1841: byon dus kho bo yang mkhan po'i rjes su slob
NK119(he)001:1842: pa lags zhes yod smra'i lugs mdzad de zhes chos
NK119(he)001:1844: jo bos bod du sdom rgyun gnang ba yod grang yang /
NK119(he)001:1845: dge ldan pa la sogs pa'i rgyud yig tu bsgrangs pa ma mthong ngo //
NK119(he)001:1846: 'di dag gi rnam bzhag rgyas par ni gsar rnying gi chos 'byung rnams su gsal la /
NK119(he)001:1847: 'dir ni yig tshogs la 'jigs pas sa bon tsam du bsdus pa'o //
NK119(he)001:1848: gnyis pa rang gi sdom rgyun bye brag tu bshad pa la /
NK119(he)001:1849: so thar sdom rgyun bla chen nas kahthoga tu brgyud tshul gyi rim pa dang /
NK119(he)001:1850: 'dul ba gzhung bshad kyi rim pa bye brag tu brgyud tshul gnyis las /
NK119(he)001:1859: mkhan chen bo d+hi sa t+wa /
NK119(he)001:1860: sad mi bdun las rba rat+na /
NK119(he)001:1864: bla chen dgongs pa rab gsal /
NK119(he)001:1865: klu mes tshul khrims shes rab /
NK119(he)001:1870: sde pa nags kyi mkhan chen /
NK119(he)001:1871: kahthoga pa bde gshegs shes rab seng ge /
NK119(he)001:1872: chos rje gtsang ston rdo rje rgyal mtshan /
NK119(he)001:1875: g.yan pa dbu 'od pa byang chub dpal /
NK119(he)001:1876: ma bcos bsod nams bzang po /
NK119(he)001:1883: drung pa byang chub rgyal mtshan /
NK119(he)001:1887: stag phu 'dul 'dzin pad+ma ma ti las so //
NK119(he)001:1893: dgra bcom pa nyi ma'i gung /
NK119(he)001:1899: dgra bcom blos mi phebs pa /
NK119(he)001:1904: zhi ba 'od dang bsod nams grags /
NK119(he)001:1908: kha che dzi na mi tra /
NK119(he)001:1913: bla chen dgongs pa rab gsal /
NK119(he)001:1914: spa god khams pa ye shes g.yung drung /
NK119(he)001:1920: sde pa nags kyi mkhan chen /
NK119(he)001:1921: kahdama pa bde gshegs man chad gong dang 'dra ba'o //
NK119(he)001:1922: gsum pa so thar gyi sdom pa'i ngo bo gang zhe na /
NK119(he)001:1923: ngo bo nges 'byung bsam pas kun bslangs na //
NK119(he)001:1924: gzhan gnod gzhi bcas ldog pa lus ngag las //
NK119(he)001:1925: skye phyir gzugs can yin zhes 'dod pa dang //
NK119(he)001:1926: spang sems rgyun chags sa bon la 'dod pas //
NK119(he)001:1927: rang gi sde pa gong 'og so so'i lugs //
NK119(he)001:1929: de yang phyi ma lha mi'i bde 'bras tsam 'dod pa legs smon dang /
NK119(he)001:1930: tshe 'dir rgyal po'i chad pa la sogs las skyob
NK119(he)001:1931: 'dod pa ni 'jigs skyob kyi tshul khrims yin te
NK119(he)001:1932: / so thar mtshan nyid pa mi rung la /
NK119(he)001:1933: so thar gyi sdom pa ni 'khor ba las nges
NK119(he)001:1934: par 'byung ba'i bsam pa khyad par can dgos te
NK119(he)001:1936: nges par 'byung ba'i tshul khrims kyi dbang du byas te /
NK119(he)001:1939: nges par 'byung ba'i tshul khrims sdug bsngal spongs //
NK119(he)001:1941: de yang so thar gyi sdom pa'i ngo bo la 'dod lugs gnyis te /
NK119(he)001:1942: nyan thos bye brag tu smra bas sdom pa ngo
NK119(he)001:1943: bo gzhan la gnod pa gzhi dang bcas pa spang
NK119(he)001:1944: ba ni lus ngag las skye ba'i phyir rnam par
NK119(he)001:1945: rig byed dang rig byed ma yin pa'i gzugs can
NK119(he)001:1947: rnam rig min rnams gsum zhes bya //
NK119(he)001:1948: sdom dang sdom pa min dang gzhan //
NK119(he)001:1949: sdom pa so sor thar zhes bya //
NK119(he)001:1952: gzhan gnod gzhi dang bcas pa spang ba'i sems rgyun
NK119(he)001:1953: chags su gnas pa sa bon dang bcas pa ste
NK119(he)001:1954: / sems pa can du 'dod pa ste /
NK119(he)001:1956: spang ba'i sems ni thob pa la //
NK119(he)001:1957: tshul khrims pha rol phyin par brjod //
NK119(he)001:1959: bzhi pa so thar gyi dbye ba ni dbye ba bsnyen gnas dge bsnyen pha ma gnyis //
NK119(he)001:1960: khyim pa'i phyogs yin dge tshul pha ma gnyis //
NK119(he)001:1961: dge slob ma dang dge slong pha ma lnga //
NK119(he)001:1962: rab byung la yin so thar rigs brgyad po //
NK119(he)001:1963: rdzas su bsdu na bzhir 'dod mdzod kyi lugs //
NK119(he)001:1964: de yang so sor thar pa rigs brgyad ces bya ste /
NK119(he)001:1965: yan lag brgyad dang ldan pa'i bsnyen gnas /
NK119(he)001:1966: khrims lnga dang bcas pa'i dge bsnyen pha ma gnyis dang gsum ni khyim pa'i phyogs yin la /
NK119(he)001:1967: rags ldog bcu la sogs pa dang bcas pa'i dge tshul pha ma gnyis /
NK119(he)001:1968: spang ba'i chos bcu gnyis dang ldan pa'i dge slob ma dang gsum /
NK119(he)001:1969: nyis brgya lnga bcu rtsa gsum dang bcas pa'i dge slong dang /
NK119(he)001:1970: sum brgya drug cu rtsa gnyis bsrung ba'i dge slong
NK119(he)001:1971: ma dang lnga ni rab tu byung ba'i phyogs yin
NK119(he)001:1972: la / de yang rigs dang rdzas su bsdu na bzhir 'dus te /
NK119(he)001:1973: dge slong pha ma gnyis rdzas rigs gcig /
NK119(he)001:1974: dge tshul pha ma dge slob ma dang gsum rdzas rigs gcig /
NK119(he)001:1975: dge bsnyen pha ma gnyis gcig /
NK119(he)001:1976: bsnyen gnas gcig te bzhir 'dus pa ni /
NK119(he)001:1978: spang bya lnga brgyad bcu dang ni //
NK119(he)001:1979: thams cad spang bar mnos pa las //
NK119(he)001:1980: dge bsnyen dang ni bsnyen gnas dang //
NK119(he)001:1981: dge tshul ched dang dge slong nyid //
NK119(he)001:1983: so sor thar pa rigs rnam brgyad //
NK119(he)001:1984: rdzas su rnam pa bzhi yin te //
NK119(he)001:1986: spyi don gnyis pa sdom pa ji ltar blang zhing thob pa'i tshul ni /
NK119(he)001:1987: dang po sdom pa ma thob thob tshul ni //
NK119(he)001:1988: len tshul gnyis las sngon gyi cho ga ni //
NK119(he)001:1989: rang byung ye shes khong chud 'phrin gyis rdzogs //
NK119(he)001:1990: ston par khas blang tshur shog gsol bzhi dang //
NK119(he)001:1991: dris pa'i lan ldon lci chos khas blangs sogs //
NK119(he)001:1992: gdul bya blo dag mkhan po 'phags pas yin //
NK119(he)001:1993: zhes pas sngon gyi cho ga dang /
NK119(he)001:1994: da lta'i cho ga gnyis las /
NK119(he)001:1995: dang po sngon gyi cho ga la rnam pa bcu ste /
NK119(he)001:1997: ye shes khong chud kyis bsnyen rdzogs /
NK119(he)001:1999: ston par khas blangs kyis bsnyen rdzogs /
NK119(he)001:2001: dris pa'i lan ldon gyis bsnyen rdzogs /
NK119(he)001:2002: lci chos khas blangs kyis bsnyen rdzogs /
NK119(he)001:2003: skyabs gsum khas blangs kyis bsnyen rdzogs /
NK119(he)001:2006: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas dang /
NK119(he)001:2007: rang sangs rgyas mkhan slob med par rang gi ngang gis bsnyen par rdzogs pa dang /
NK119(he)001:2009: lnga sde bzang po la mthong lam gyi rtogs pa skyes pas ye shes khong chud dam /
NK119(he)001:2010: nges zhugs kyi bsnyen rdzogs zhes kyang bya'o //
NK119(he)001:2012: grong khyer mnyan yod na khyim bdag sbyin pa'i bu
NK119(he)001:2013: mo mchod sbyin ma rab tu byung bar 'dod kyang
NK119(he)001:2014: pha mas khyim gyi phyi rol du'ang 'gror ma bcug
NK119(he)001:2015: pa las / dge slong ma ut+pala'i mdog can la
NK119(he)001:2016: bdag rab tu byung bar 'dod kyang pha mas ma
NK119(he)001:2017: gnang yang ci nas kyang bdag rab tu byung bar
NK119(he)001:2018: pa las / zhus pas / dge slong mas ston
NK119(he)001:2019: pa la zhus pas 'phrin gyi sgo nas rab byung
NK119(he)001:2020: bsnyen rdzogs rim gyis byed par gnang bas dge slong
NK119(he)001:2021: ma rnams kyis ut+pa la'i mdog can 'phrin du btang
NK119(he)001:2022: pa las / zhus pas / nas / dge bsnyen
NK119(he)001:2023: ma nas dge slong ma'i bar gnang bas dgra bcom
NK119(he)001:2024: thob par bshad pa lta bu ste /
NK119(he)001:2025: gdul bya skal ba dang ldan pa da lta yang 'phrin gyis bsnyen rdzogs rungs te /
NK119(he)001:2027: skal ba dang ldan pa'i rang bzhin can la mngags pa dang 'dra bas /
NK119(he)001:2028: rab tu 'byin du zhugs pa ni cho ga ma yin pa ma yin no //
NK119(he)001:2031: 'od srung chen pos ston pa sangs rgyas la khyod ni kho bo'i ston pa'o //
NK119(he)001:2032: kho bo ni khyod kyi nyan thos so //
NK119(he)001:2033: zhes yid ches kyi dad pas ston par khas blangs mod la bsnyen rdzogs su gyur pa lta bu'o //
NK119(he)001:2035: ston pas grags pa la sogs la dge slong dag da tshur shog /
NK119(he)001:2036: tshangs par spyod pa la spyod cig gsungs pa tsam gyis skra dang kha spu byi /
NK119(he)001:2037: lus chos gos dang bcas te bsnyen par rdzogs nas
NK119(he)001:2038: lo brgya lon pa'i spyod lam lta bur gyur pa
NK119(he)001:2041: ston pas legs sbyin gcig tu dge ba ni gang /
NK119(he)001:2043: de la mkho ba ni gang /
NK119(he)001:2045: zhes dris pa'i lan la thugs dgyes pas bsnyen rdzogs kyi sdom pa mngon du gyur pa lta bu'o //
NK119(he)001:2047: bzang sde'i tshogs drug cu'i yid ches kyi dad pa
NK119(he)001:2048: dang ldan pa'i sgo nas dkon mchog gsum skyabs su
NK119(he)001:2049: khas blangs bzhin bsnyen rdzogs mngon du gyur pa lta
NK119(he)001:2052: yul dbus su mtshams nang de na yod pa'i dge 'dun thams cad 'dus pa'am /
NK119(he)001:2053: ma mtha' bcu yan chad kyis gsol bzhi'i las kyis
NK119(he)001:2054: rab byung bsnyen rdzogs gcig char du sgrub pa'i cho
NK119(he)001:2055: ga dang / mtha' 'khob tu mtshams nang der yod pa de dge slong thams cad dam /
NK119(he)001:2056: ma mtha' lnga yan chad kyi rab byung bsnyen rdzogs gcig char du sgrub pa'o //
NK119(he)001:2057: de yang dbus dang mtha' 'khob kyi khyad par la gnyis te /
NK119(he)001:2058: chos tshigs kyis dbye ba dang /
NK119(he)001:2061: gang du bsnyen rdzogs kyi sdom pa 'bog pa'i mkhan
NK119(he)001:2062: po dang cho ga dang bslab bya tshul bzhin du
NK119(he)001:2063: slob pa'i bstan pa yod pa'i sa phyogs ni chos
NK119(he)001:2064: tshigs kyis phye ba'i yul dbus yin la /
NK119(he)001:2065: de med pa ni mtha' 'khob yin no //
NK119(he)001:2067: rdo rje'i gdan ni 'dzam bu'i gling gi lte ba yin zhing /
NK119(he)001:2068: de'i phyogs mtshams na li kha shing 'phel la sogs dbus yin la gzhan ni mtha' 'khob ste /
NK119(he)001:2069: 'dul ba tshigs le'ura byas pa las /
NK119(he)001:2070: li kha ra na tshang tshing nags //
NK119(he)001:2071: li khar shing 'phel shar phyogs nyid //
NK119(he)001:2072: u shi ra zhes brjod pa yi //
NK119(he)001:2073: ri bo mun pa can gyi byang //
NK119(he)001:2074: ka ba nye ba'i ka ba yi //
NK119(he)001:2075: grong khyer nu ban gnas pa yin //
NK119(he)001:2076: grong khyer 'dam bu can gyi drung //
NK119(he)001:2077: chu rlung 'dam bu can ni lho //
NK119(he)001:2078: 'di dag gi ni bar rnams la //
NK119(he)001:2079: yul dbus su ni shes bya ste //
NK119(he)001:2080: phyi rol mtha' 'khob ces byar ni //
NK119(he)001:2081: mtha' yas mkhyen pas gsungs pa yin //
NK119(he)001:2083: de yang sngon gyi dus su gdul bya rnams kyang gong ltar brgyud pa yin zhing /
NK119(he)001:2084: nad dang nyer 'tshe 'byung dka' la cung zad byung
NK119(he)001:2085: na'ang nad g.yog dang sman sogs rnyed sla bas 'khrid
NK119(he)001:2086: cing skyong bar byed pa'i mkhan slob la gtso bor
NK119(he)001:2088: mkhan po yang slob pa so so'i skye bo ma yin te /
NK119(he)001:2089: mi slob pa'i 'phags pa sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK119(he)001:2090: gnyis pa da ltar gyi cho ga la gsum ste /
NK119(he)001:2091: sdom rten gang zag gi mtshan nyid /
NK119(he)001:2093: des ji ltar sdom pa 'bog tshul lo //
NK119(he)001:2095: da lta'i cho ga nges pa lnga bral zhing //
NK119(he)001:2096: ma ning la sogs skye ba'i bar chad dang //
NK119(he)001:2097: rgyal pos ma gnang la sogs gnas pa dang //
NK119(he)001:2098: bya rog skrod mi nus sogs khyad par dang //
NK119(he)001:2099: skra ser la sogs mdzes pa'i bar chad med //
NK119(he)001:2100: nges 'byung blo can skal bzang skyes bu de //
NK119(he)001:2102: bsnyen gnas ma gtogs pa'i so thar ris bdun gyi
NK119(he)001:2103: rten de nges pa lnga dang bral zhing bar chad
NK119(he)001:2104: bzhi med pa zhig dgos te /
NK119(he)001:2105: de yang nges pa lnga ni /
NK119(he)001:2107: kha cig mi spangs lta bu yan lag nges pa dang /
NK119(he)001:2108: sems can kha cig la spangs /
NK119(he)001:2109: kha cig la mi spangs lta bu sems can nges pa dang /
NK119(he)001:2110: yul che ge mo zhig tu spangs /
NK119(he)001:2111: che ge mo zhig tu mi spangs lta bu yul nges pa dang /
NK119(he)001:2112: zla ba gcig gam lo gcig tsam du spangs ba lta bu dus nges pa dang /
NK119(he)001:2114: gzhan du spangs lta bu gnas skabs nges pa'o //
NK119(he)001:2115: de lnga gang rung gcig dang lnga yang mi skye'o //
NK119(he)001:2117: dang po sdom pa skye ba'i bar chad du gyur pa ni mi ma yin pa'o //
NK119(he)001:2120: mtshan gnyis gcig char du byung ba za ma ma ning la sogs pa'o //
NK119(he)001:2128: skyes tsam nyid nas skyes pa pho mo'i mtshan gnyis gcig char du byung ba'am /
NK119(he)001:2129: 'di la za ma ma ning zhes kyang bya'o //
NK119(he)001:2130: don byed nus pa med pa'o //
NK119(he)001:2133: zla smad bud med kyi mtshan mar 'gyur ba'o /
NK119(he)001:2135: bud med la sogs pas 'khyud dus dbang po las su rung la /
NK119(he)001:2138: gzhan pho mo spyod pa mthong na phrag dog gis las su rung la gzhan du mi rung ba'o //
NK119(he)001:2140: skyes pa'i dbang po mtshon la sogs pas bcad nas nyams pa'o //
NK119(he)001:2143: nye ba lnga byas pa la sogs pa'o //
NK119(he)001:2144: gnyis pa skyes pa gnas pa'i bar chad ni /
NK119(he)001:2145: rgyal pos ma gnang ba dang /
NK119(he)001:2146: rgyal pos bkrabs pa zhes rgyal po'i las ka 'dzin pa'i blon po lta bu dang /
NK119(he)001:2150: bu lon can nor bdag gi /
NK119(he)001:2151: bran rje bo'i dbang du song ba lta bu'o //
NK119(he)001:2152: gsum pa gnas khyad par gyi bar chad ni /
NK119(he)001:2154: sems mya ngan gyis gzir ba /
NK119(he)001:2155: lus ngal dub kyi rang bzhin can /
NK119(he)001:2156: lo bco lnga ma lon pa dang /
NK119(he)001:2157: lo bco lnga lon pa bya rog skrod mi nus pa la sogs pa'o //
NK119(he)001:2158: bzhi pa rten mdzes pa'i bar chad ni /
NK119(he)001:2160: kha dog la skyon chags pa skra ser can dang /
NK119(he)001:2161: dbyibs la skyon chags pa lag rdum sogs pa ste /
NK119(he)001:2163: lag rdum dag dang rkang rdum dang //
NK119(he)001:2164: lag sor zlum po 'dzas pa dang //
NK119(he)001:2165: mchu med lus la rma mtshan can //
NK119(he)001:2166: rgas ches pa dang gzhon ches pa //
NK119(he)001:2168: lag sor rdum sgur mi'u thung dang //
NK119(he)001:2169: lba ba lkugs pa 'on pa dang //
NK119(he)001:2170: rten 'phyo dang ni rkang bam dang //
NK119(he)001:2171: bud med kyis dub khur gyis dub //
NK119(he)001:2172: mi gang lam gyis dub pa dang //
NK119(he)001:2173: ya za ma lug gtad dgam dang //
NK119(he)001:2174: de lta bu yi mi rnams ni //
NK119(he)001:2175: drang srong chen pos dgag pa mdzad //
NK119(he)001:2177: de yang bar chad gong ma gnyis dang ldan pa ni sdom pa'i rten min la /
NK119(he)001:2178: phyi ma gnyis la sdom pa phog kyang slob dpon
NK119(he)001:2179: la bcas pa'i 'gal ba cung zad yod kyang skye
NK119(he)001:2180: ba dang gnas pa'i sgo nas phan pa rgya chen
NK119(he)001:2181: po yod pas rung bar sa pan gyis gsungs so
NK119(he)001:2182: // de ltar bar chad med cing nges 'byung gi
NK119(he)001:2183: blo dang ldan pa'i skal bzang gi skye bo de
NK119(he)001:2184: dag la rigs bdun gyi sdom pa 'bog par bya'o
NK119(he)001:2185: // // gnyis pa 'bog byed mkhan po'i mtshan nyid ni /
NK119(he)001:2186: legs gsungs 'dul ba rgya mtsho mtha' dag dang /
NK119(he)001:2187: brgya rtsa gcig pa'i las phran la byang ba'i /
NK119(he)001:2188: mkhan por bcas pas rim bzhin bsnyen par rdzogs /
NK119(he)001:2189: de yang 'bog byed kyi mkhan po de yang /
NK119(he)001:2190: 'dul ba gzhung bzhi dgongs 'grel dang bcas pa'i don khong du chud cing /
NK119(he)001:2191: las brgya rtsa gcig gi rnam bzhag karma sha tam la sogs las chog la shin tu byang ba /
NK119(he)001:2192: nad pa sogs la snying rje khyad par can dang ldan pa'i dge ba'i bshes gnyen te /
NK119(he)001:2194: tshul khrims ldan 'dul ba'i cho ga shes //
NK119(he)001:2195: nad par snying brtse 'khor ni dag pa dang //
NK119(he)001:2196: chos dang zang zing zhing phan 'dogs kyis brtson pa //
NK119(he)001:2197: dus su 'doms pa de dag bla mar basngagasa //
NK119(he)001:2202: rab byung gi mkhan po dang /
NK119(he)001:2203: bsnyen rdzogs kyi mkhan po gnyis kyi /
NK119(he)001:2205: 'dul ba'i dgag sgrub gnang gsum gyi bslab bya tshul
NK119(he)001:2206: bzhin du slob pa ni btsun pa'i yon tan dang
NK119(he)001:2207: / bsnyen par rdzogs nas lo bcu bar ma chad
NK119(he)001:2208: du lon pa ni brtan pa'i yon tan gnyis dang
NK119(he)001:2209: / ldan pa'o // gnyis pa bsnyen rdzogs kyi mkhan po ni /
NK119(he)001:2210: de'i steng du lnga phrugs su sbyar ba nyer gcig
NK119(he)001:2211: po gang rung dang ldan pa ni mkhas pa'i yon
NK119(he)001:2212: tan te gsum dang ldan pa'o //
NK119(he)001:2215: lo bcu 'dzin dang mkhas pa dang //
NK119(he)001:2217: slob dang slob 'jug rnam pa gnyis //
NK119(he)001:2218: phun sum tshogs gnyis rnam pa gsum //
NK119(he)001:2219: slob dang mi slob byung shes dang //
NK119(he)001:2221: lho yi ri la rgyu ba yi //
NK119(he)001:2222: sde tshan yang dag bsdus pa yin //
NK119(he)001:2224: dang po lo bcu zhes pa'i lnga ni /
NK119(he)001:2225: lo bcu lon pa nad g.yog /'gyod bsal /
NK119(he)001:2228: de bzhin du re re bzhin lnga lnga ste rgyas par gzhan du shes so //
NK119(he)001:2229: gnyis pa slob dpon la lnga ste /
NK119(he)001:2230: dge tshul gyi slob dpon gsang ste ston pa'i slob dpon /
NK119(he)001:2235: de ni slob dpon yin no //
NK119(he)001:2242: sgrub bya la dge tshul gyi sdom pa 'bog pa'i dge slong ngo //
NK119(he)001:2244: gsang ston du bskos pas sgrub bya la lkog tu
NK119(he)001:2245: bar chad dris te dge 'dun la go bar byed
NK119(he)001:2248: dge 'dun gyi dbus su gsol bzhi'i cho ga brda sprod pa'i dge slong ngo //
NK119(he)001:2250: slob ma la dgag sgrub gnang gsum gyi bslab bya slob par byed pa'i dge slong ngo //
NK119(he)001:2252: slob ma la lung rtogs kyi yon tan 'phel phyir gdams ngag 'bog pa'i dge slong ngo //
NK119(he)001:2253: de ltar rang gi mkhan po dang slob dpon du gyur phyin chad /
NK119(he)001:2257: btsun pa la sogs mi smra bar /
NK119(he)001:2260: de bzhin gshegs pa zhes pa dang /
NK119(he)001:2261: bdag gi slob dpon mtshan 'di zhes bya ba dang /
NK119(he)001:2262: don gyi slad du mtshan nas smos te bdag gi mkhan po 'di zhes bya ba /
NK119(he)001:2266: mkhan po la sogs dris na nyes pa med la /
NK119(he)001:2267: rang gi mkhan slob tu ma gyur pa gzhan la zhes pa'i tshig mi dgos te /
NK119(he)001:2269: mkhyen pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa la /
NK119(he)001:2270: brtul zhugs can gyis tshe ldan dang //
NK119(he)001:2271: rigs rus mtshan nas smos pa dang //
NK119(he)001:2272: yul nas brjod par mi bya'o //
NK119(he)001:2274: the tshom bsal ba'i don du ni //
NK119(he)001:2275: sangs rgyas gdung ni gang yin pa //
NK119(he)001:2276: rgyal rigs las gang rab byung ba //
NK119(he)001:2277: zhes sogs smra ba nyes pa med //
NK119(he)001:2280: nyid las gzhan du nye bar mi brjod do //
NK119(he)001:2283: gsum pa ji ltar sdom pa 'bog tshul la gsum ste /
NK119(he)001:2286: zhar la 'phros don dang thob mtshams ngos bzung ba'o //
NK119(he)001:2290: len pa'i cho ga dang gsum las dang po ni /
NK119(he)001:2291: nyan thos bye brag tu smra ba ltar na /
NK119(he)001:2292: yul gang zag gzhan dge slong las len dgos par bzhed la /
NK119(he)001:2294: dge slong kho na las len dgos pa min te /
NK119(he)001:2295: gnas 'jug gi bus zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK119(he)001:2296: yan lag brgyad dang ldan pa'i bsnyen gnas la gnas par 'dod pa des /
NK119(he)001:2300: khyim pa gzhan gang yang rung ba cho ga shes pa zhig gi drung du song nas /
NK119(he)001:2302: gnyis pa blang ba'i gang zag kyang /
NK119(he)001:2303: bye brag tu smra ba ltar na /
NK119(he)001:2304: gling gsum gyi skyes pa bud med ma gtogs pa sdom rten du mi 'dod de /
NK119(he)001:2306: mi ma yin pa'i 'gro ba dang /
NK119(he)001:2307: byang gi sgra mi snyan pa gnyis ni sdom pa'i zhing nyid ma yin no //
NK119(he)001:2310: bsnyen gnas kyi rten gnas dud 'gro la sogs la'ang rung bar bzhed de /
NK119(he)001:2312: klu gzhon nu tsam pa zhes bya bas tshes brgyad la bsnyen gnas bsrung bar bshad pa dang /
NK119(he)001:2314: ri bong dang seng ge sogs kyang bsnyen gnas bsrung bar bshad pa bzhin no //
NK119(he)001:2315: gsum pa len pa'i cho ga la'ang /
NK119(he)001:2316: cho ga'i ngag 'don gzhan du shes la /
NK119(he)001:2318: dang por slob dpon gyi drung du song nas sang nyi ma ma shar gyi bar khas blang nas /
NK119(he)001:2319: phyis zla ba byung ngo cog gi tshes brgyad dang /
NK119(he)001:2321: gnam stong la khas blangs pas /
NK119(he)001:2322: ma 'ongs pa na tshes brgyad la sogs par zas
NK119(he)001:2323: la longs spyod pa'i rjes su slob dpon gyi drung
NK119(he)001:2324: du blangs pas skye bar 'dod de /
NK119(he)001:2326: sngon yang dag par khas blangs pa des ni /
NK119(he)001:2327: zan zos kyang nod par bya'o //
NK119(he)001:2330: dang por slob dpon gyi drung du chos brgyad dang bco lnga la sogs khas blangs pas /
NK119(he)001:2331: phyis rten la sogs pa'i drung du blangs pas skye ba yin te /
NK119(he)001:2333: mdo sde ba yi lugs bzhin du //
NK119(he)001:2334: ji ltar 'dod tshe len na yang //
NK119(he)001:2337: dang po rten la sogs pa'i drung du len /
NK119(he)001:2338: phyis kyang der len par bzhed pa'o //
NK119(he)001:2339: gnyis pa so thar rigs bdun gyi sdom pa 'bog pa po'i tshul la gsum ste /
NK119(he)001:2340: tshigs snga ma dge tshul du bsgrub pa /
NK119(he)001:2341: phyi ma bsnyen rdzogs su bsgrub pa /
NK119(he)001:2342: bud med kyi cho ga'i khyad par gzhan bstan pa'o //
NK119(he)001:2345: sngon dang dge bsnyen bslab pa dang //
NK119(he)001:2347: bstan pa la rim gyis 'jug pa'i ched du dge bsnyen du bsgrub pa dang /
NK119(he)001:2348: dge tshul gyi brtul zhugs myur du thob par bya
NK119(he)001:2349: ba'i phyir du bar ma rab byung du bsgrub pa
NK119(he)001:2351: nyes med phun sum tshogs pa'i bsnyen rdzogs kyi sdom pa skye ba la /
NK119(he)001:2352: dge bsnyen nas rim gyis bsgrub dgos te /
NK119(he)001:2356: dge slong dag gis snga ma bsnyen par ma rdzogs pa la phyi ma mi bya'o //
NK119(he)001:2357: zhes pas dge bsnyen dge tshul gnyis sngon du ma song bar bsnyen rdzogs mi skye bas /
NK119(he)001:2358: dang po dge bsnyen gyi sdom pa ni /
NK119(he)001:2359: yul dge 'dun med kha med du mi dgos te /
NK119(he)001:2360: bsdu bar khyim pa sogs las blang du rung bar gsungs shing /
NK119(he)001:2362: yongs rdzogs sogs 'og nas 'byung ba ltar blang ba'o //
NK119(he)001:2363: gnyis pa dge tshul gyi brtul zhugs myur du thob
NK119(he)001:2364: par bya ba'i phyir bar ma rab byung du bsgrub
NK119(he)001:2365: pa ni / blang ba'i yul dge tshul gyi sdom
NK119(he)001:2366: pa gang zag las skye bas dge 'dun med kha
NK119(he)001:2367: med mi dgos par mkhas pa bus gsungs kyang /
NK119(he)001:2368: yon tan gyi che ba dang /
NK119(he)001:2370: dge 'dun bzhi'i yan chad dgos la /
NK119(he)001:2371: zhu ba po yang gsum yan chad mi rungs te /
NK119(he)001:2373: gsum man chad tshigs gcig gis bsnyen par rdzogs par bya rung ngo //
NK119(he)001:2375: de yang dge tshul gyi sdom pa lan gcig nod
NK119(he)001:2376: nas rtsa ltung 'chab bcas byung na slar blang du
NK119(he)001:2377: mi btub ste / ngo tsha khrel med kyis rgyud dregs pa'i phyir /
NK119(he)001:2379: mi gsod la sogs rnam bzhi yis //
NK119(he)001:2380: dge tshul las ni nyams gyur pa //
NK119(he)001:2381: dge slong bzhin du dge tshul yang //
NK119(he)001:2382: phyis nas sdom skyes skal ba med //
NK119(he)001:2384: de ltar ma yin pa la /
NK119(he)001:2386: zhu dang mkhan po dang po dang //
NK119(he)001:2387: rab byung dge tshul grib tshod dang //
NK119(he)001:2388: bslab pa brjod pa tha ma yin //
NK119(he)001:2389: zhes pa ni las chog gi sdom ste /
NK119(he)001:2391: bsgrub bya de rab byung zhu ba'i dge slong la gtad nas /
NK119(he)001:2392: des kyang dge 'dun la zhu ba'o //
NK119(he)001:2393: mkhan po zhes pas mkhan por gsol ba gdab pa'o //
NK119(he)001:2394: dang po zhes pa de'i 'og tu dge slong gzhan zhig gis de'i skra dang kha spu bregs te /
NK119(he)001:2395: spyi bor gtsug phud bzhag pa la /
NK119(he)001:2396: gtsug phud bregs par spro'am byas pas /
NK119(he)001:2397: spro lags zhus te bregs nas dgun chu dron /
NK119(he)001:2398: dbyar chu grang gis khrus byas te /
NK119(he)001:2404: chu tshags te yo byad lnga gtad de /
NK119(he)001:2406: sde pa'i ming gi mtha' can dpal dang /
NK119(he)001:2409: bzang po la sogs pas spras pa 'dog go //
NK119(he)001:2411: bar ma rab byung du bsgrub pa'o //
NK119(he)001:2413: skyabs 'gro rtsom byed du byas nas dge tshul bsgrub
NK119(he)001:2414: pa'i cho ga'i sngags tshig lan gsum brjod de dge
NK119(he)001:2417: grib tshod gzhal te de'i 'og tu dus brjod pa'o //
NK119(he)001:2418: bslab pa brjod pa zhes pas dge tshul gyi bslab
NK119(he)001:2419: pa'i gzhi bcu brjod pa ste dge tshul du bsgrub
NK119(he)001:2420: pa'o // gnyis pa tshigs phyi ma bsnyen rdzogs su bsgrub pa la /
NK119(he)001:2421: yul dbus su dge slong bcu dang /
NK119(he)001:2422: mtha' 'khob tu lnga yan chad 'dus pa la skyes pa bsnyen par rdzogs dgos la /
NK119(he)001:2423: de yang karma sha tam las /
NK119(he)001:2424: dang por bya dang mkhan po dang //
NK119(he)001:2425: chos gos gnyis dang lhung bzed gnyis //
NK119(he)001:2426: spro bya gsol ba gsang ston dang //
NK119(he)001:2427: zhu dang gsol dang gsal ba dang //
NK119(he)001:2428: dri dang las dang grib tshod dang //
NK119(he)001:2429: nyin mtshan dus tshod gnas rnams dang //
NK119(he)001:2430: ltung byed dge sbyong mchog 'dod dang //
NK119(he)001:2431: tshul khrims mnyes dang tshul 'brel dang //
NK119(he)001:2432: dul dang dgos dang ma brjod dang //
NK119(he)001:2433: gus pa dang ni bsgrub bya ba //
NK119(he)001:2434: mu stegs gnang ba sbyin pa yis //
NK119(he)001:2435: sde tshan yang dag bsdus pa yin //
NK119(he)001:2437: dang por bya dang zhes pa ni /
NK119(he)001:2438: sgrub bya de lo nyi shu lon /
NK119(he)001:2439: snam sbyar bla gos mthing gos te chos gos gsum dang lhung bzed kyang tshang /
NK119(he)001:2440: bsnyen par rdzogs par 'dod pa na mkhan por 'dod pa des /
NK119(he)001:2443: las gral du 'dus pa'i dge slong rnams la gsol ba btab nas /
NK119(he)001:2445: rang rang gi ltung ba bshags 'os rnams bshags /
NK119(he)001:2446: byin gyis brlab 'os rnams byin gyis brlabs te las gral du 'dus pa'o //
NK119(he)001:2447: mkhan po zhes pas bsnyen rdzogs kyi mkhan por gsol ba gdab pa'o //
NK119(he)001:2448: chos gos dang po ni mkhan pos chos gos gsum byin gyis brlabs nas gnang ba'o //
NK119(he)001:2449: chos gos gnyis pa ni chos gos drubs zin pa
NK119(he)001:2450: med na chos gos kyi rgyu byin gyis brlabs nas
NK119(he)001:2451: gnang ba'o // lhung bzed dang po ni dge 'dun la mi che'am /
NK119(he)001:2454: gnyis pa ni mkhan pos byin gyis brlabs nas gnang ba'o //
NK119(he)001:2455: spro bya zhes las slob kyis gang yin dris nas spror gzhugs pa'o //
NK119(he)001:2456: gsol ba zhes gsang ston bsko ba'i gsol ba 'ba' zhig go //
NK119(he)001:2457: gsang ston zhes pas gsang ston gyis sgrub bya la lkog tu bar chad dri ba'o //
NK119(he)001:2458: zhu dang zhes gsang ston gyi dge 'dun la bar chad dag go zhu ba'o //
NK119(he)001:2459: gsol dang zhes bsnyen par rdzogs phyir bsgrub bya las
NK119(he)001:2460: slob kyis rjes zlos byas te gsol ba btab pa'o
NK119(he)001:2461: // gsol ba zhes pas las slob kyis bsgrub bya
NK119(he)001:2462: la sngon du bar chad dri ba'i ched du gsol
NK119(he)001:2463: ba 'ba' zhig pa'i las byed pa'o //
NK119(he)001:2464: dri dang zhes pas mngon du dri ba'o //
NK119(he)001:2465: las dang zhes pas bsnyen par rdzogs pa'i dngos gzhi'i las byed pa'o //
NK119(he)001:2466: grib tshod ces pas thur ma sor bzhi pa skyes bu zhes de'i nyi ma'i grib tshad gzhal ba'o //
NK119(he)001:2467: de yang grib ma sor bzhi la skyes bu dang
NK119(he)001:2468: gsum man chad la rkang pa zhes tha snyad brjod
NK119(he)001:2469: do // nyin mtshan zhes pas nyin mo'i cha shas bcu bzhi /
NK119(he)001:2470: mtshan mo'i brgyad de nyer gnyis brjod pa'o //
NK119(he)001:2476: nyi ma'i brgyad cha shar ba /
NK119(he)001:2482: nyi ma'i bzhi cha lus pa /
NK119(he)001:2496: dus tshod ces dus tshigs lnga brjod pa ste /
NK119(he)001:2503: dang po gnyis ni zla ba bzhi bzhi'o //
NK119(he)001:2504: 'og ma ni zla ba gcig go //
NK119(he)001:2505: de'i 'og ma ni nyid zhag gcig go //
NK119(he)001:2506: tha ma ni zla ba gsum du ma chag pa'o //
NK119(he)001:2508: gnas rnams zhes pa nas bsgrub bya zhes pa'i bar ni gdams ngag bcu gcig brjod pa'o //
NK119(he)001:2509: mu stegs gnas pa sbyin pa zhes sbyor ba'i cho ga'i spros pa'o //
NK119(he)001:2510: 'di dag go rim mi 'khrug pa'i sa bcad mdor
NK119(he)001:2511: bstan pa ste rgyas par las chog las rtogs par
NK119(he)001:2512: bya'o // gsum pa bud med kyi cho ga'i khyad
NK119(he)001:2513: par gzhan bstan pa la gsum gyi dang po dge
NK119(he)001:2514: bsnyen ma dang dge tshul mar bsgrub pa'i cho ga
NK119(he)001:2515: ni skyes pa'i mal du bud med dang /
NK119(he)001:2516: dge slong gi mal du dge slong ma sbyar ba las gzhan sngar dang 'dra ste /
NK119(he)001:2518: dge slong gi gnas su dge slong ma'o //
NK119(he)001:2519: rab tu byung ba thams cad kyi'o //
NK119(he)001:2521: gnyis pa dge slob ma'i sdom pa ni bsnyen par
NK119(he)001:2522: ma rdzogs pa'i lo gnyis kyi gong du blang dgos
NK119(he)001:2523: te / de yang dbus su dge slong ma bcu gnyis /
NK119(he)001:2524: mtha' 'khob tu drug tshogs kyis sbyin par bya'o //
NK119(he)001:2525: gsum pa dge slong mar bsgrub pa la cho ga phal cher dge slong dang 'dra la /
NK119(he)001:2526: blang yul dge 'dun gnyis ka dgos te dbus su
NK119(he)001:2527: dge slong bcu dge slong ma bcu gnyis te nyer
NK119(he)001:2528: gnyis / mtha' 'khob tu dge slong lnga /
NK119(he)001:2529: dge slong ma drug te bcu gcig dgos la /
NK119(he)001:2530: gsang ston pa'i 'og tu tshangs spyod nyer gnas kyi
NK119(he)001:2531: slob dpon mas bar chad dris nas tshangs spyod kyi
NK119(he)001:2532: sdom pa sbyin zhing chos gos kyi skabs su chos
NK119(he)001:2534: rngul gzan shing nga dpung bcad gnyis te lnga dgos la /
NK119(he)001:2535: shing drung mi brjod la lci chos brgyad brjod pa
NK119(he)001:2536: la sogs zhib par las chog las rtogs par bya'o
NK119(he)001:2537: // gsum pa zhar la 'phros don dang thob mtshams ngos bzung ba ni /
NK119(he)001:2538: snga ma ma byas rdzogs pa'i mdo sder snang /
NK119(he)001:2539: thob mtshams brjod pa gsum gyi tha mar 'dod //
NK119(he)001:2542: snga ma ma byas bsnyen par rdzogs pa des //
NK119(he)001:2543: gzhan gnyis zhar gyis thob pa mdo sder snang //
NK119(he)001:2544: de dus kun slong sems bskyed kyis zin na //
NK119(he)001:2545: theg chen so sor thar par mkhas rnams bzhed //
NK119(he)001:2548: des na da lta'i cho ga ni /
NK119(he)001:2549: bsam pa sems bskyed kyis zin pa'i //
NK119(he)001:2550: cho ga nyan thos lugs bzhin gyis //
NK119(he)001:2551: so thar sdom pa rigs brgyad po //
NK119(he)001:2552: byang sems so so thar par 'gyur //
NK119(he)001:2555: cho ga'i rjes zlos lan gsum gyis rjes su thob pa ste /
NK119(he)001:2558: gzhan brjod gsum gyi lan gsum pa'i bdag brjod rdzogs
NK119(he)001:2559: ma thag tu dge tshul lam dge slong gi sdom
NK119(he)001:2561: de dus thob par ngo shes dgos te /
NK119(he)001:2563: gang zag gsum ni bsnyen par ma rdzogs pa zhes gsungs pa ste /
NK119(he)001:2564: gang bdag gi ming ma brjod pa dang /
NK119(he)001:2565: mkhan po'i ming ma brjod pa dang /
NK119(he)001:2566: sdom pa thob pa'i dus mi shes pa'o //
NK119(he)001:2567: zhes pas de'i dus na grib tshod la sogs rigs par bya zhing /
NK119(he)001:2568: de yang rtogs sla bar brjod de /
NK119(he)001:2569: 'di ltar lo bcu gnyis yod pa'i nang nas byi ba /
NK119(he)001:2571: de'i nang nas dgun ra ba /
NK119(he)001:2572: de yang ngo gnyis las yar ngo'i tshes gcig /
NK119(he)001:2573: nyin mtshan gnyis kyi nyin mo /
NK119(he)001:2574: de la'ang cha shas bcu bzhi yod pa'i snga dro'i dus su /
NK119(he)001:2575: gtsug lag khang 'di zhes par mkhan slob 'di zhes
NK119(he)001:2576: pa las rab byung bsnyen rdzogs thob pa yin pas
NK119(he)001:2577: 'di las grib tshod gang snga ba rnams bslab pa
NK119(he)001:2578: rgan pa yin pas gral gong du bzhag cing rim
NK119(he)001:2580: 'di las phyi ba rnams la rang rgan pas gang
NK119(he)001:2581: du 'dug pa la sogs bkrol nas bslab bya gang
NK119(he)001:2582: yin de lan gcig brjod pa'o //
NK119(he)001:2583: lan gsum brjod par 'dod pa ni gzhung don ma rtogs par zad do //
NK119(he)001:2584: spyi don gnyis pa thob pa mi nyams bsrung ba'i thabs la gsum ste /
NK119(he)001:2585: sdom pa'i rnam dbye rgyas par bshad pa /
NK119(he)001:2586: gnang bkag gi don mdor bstan pa /
NK119(he)001:2587: zhar la sdom pa'i rten bshad pa'o //
NK119(he)001:2590: bsnyen gnas kyi dge bsnyen dge tshul dge slob ma'o //
NK119(he)001:2591: dge slong gi dge slong ma'i bslab bya bstan pa'o //
NK119(he)001:2593: bar du thob pa mi nyams bsrung ba la //
NK119(he)001:2594: bslab bya skyabs 'gro'i thun mong min gsum ni //
NK119(he)001:2595: skyabs gzhan mi 'tshol sems can 'tshe ba spangs //
NK119(he)001:2596: mu stegs mi 'grogs so sor gus bskyed do //
NK119(he)001:2597: de yang bslab bya dngos dang /
NK119(he)001:2598: thun mong ma yin pa dang /
NK119(he)001:2599: thun mong gi bslab bya gsum las /
NK119(he)001:2602: gang zhig sangs rgyas skyabs song ba //
NK119(he)001:2603: de ni yang dag dge bsnyen te //
NK119(he)001:2604: nam du yang ni lha gzhan la //
NK119(he)001:2605: skyabs su 'gro ba ma yin no //
NK119(he)001:2606: dam pa'i chos la skyabs song nas //
NK119(he)001:2607: 'tshe zhing gnod pa'i sems dang bral //
NK119(he)001:2608: dge 'dun dag la skyabs song nas //
NK119(he)001:2609: mu stegs can dang 'grogs mi bya //
NK119(he)001:2613: dge 'dun la gus pa bskyed par bya'o //
NK119(he)001:2615: srog dang bya dgar dkon mchog gsum mi spangs //
NK119(he)001:2616: dgos gal che yang thabs gzhan mi 'tshol zhing //
NK119(he)001:2617: dus mchod mi bcag rang gzhan skyabs 'gror 'god //
NK119(he)001:2618: gar 'gro'i phyogs su sangs rgyas la phyag 'tshal //
NK119(he)001:2619: lnga rnams thun mong bslab byar jo bos bzhed //
NK119(he)001:2620: de yang rang gi srog la thug pa'am bya dga'
NK119(he)001:2621: chen po'i ched du'ang dkon mchog gsum mi spang ba
NK119(he)001:2622: dang / nad sogs kyis nyes pa lta bu dgos
NK119(he)001:2623: gal che na yang srog gcod mchod sbyin lta bu
NK119(he)001:2624: sangs rgyas par ldog pa'i thabs gzhan mi 'tshol ba
NK119(he)001:2625: dang / dang / dus rtag par mchod pa khyad
NK119(he)001:2626: par dus chen bzhi la sogs su mchod pa ci
NK119(he)001:2627: za ci 'thung gi phud kyis mchod pa mi bcag
NK119(he)001:2628: dang / dang / pa dang / rang nyid skyabs
NK119(he)001:2629: su 'gro zhing gzhan yang skyabs 'gror 'god pa dang
NK119(he)001:2630: dang / dang / pa dang / / rang phyogs
NK119(he)001:2631: gang du 'gro ba'i phyogs de'i sangs rgyas la phyag
NK119(he)001:2632: 'tshal ba dang lnga ni skyabs 'gro'i thun mong gi
NK119(he)001:2633: bslab byar dpal jo bo rjes bzhed do //
NK119(he)001:2634: gnyis pa bsnyen gnas yan lag brgyad pa ni /
NK119(he)001:2640: chang spangs bag yod yan lag mal che mtho //
NK119(he)001:2641: gar sogs phreng sogs phyi dro'i kha zas gsum //
NK119(he)001:2642: brtul zhugs yan lag bsnyen gnas sdom pa yin //
NK119(he)001:2644: tshul khrims yan lag bag yod pa'i //
NK119(he)001:2645: yan lag brtul zhugs yan lag ste //
NK119(he)001:2646: gzhi gcig de bzhin gsum rim bzhin //
NK119(he)001:2648: rtsa bzhi spang bas tshul khrims kyi yan lag /
NK119(he)001:2649: de'i steng du chang spangs ba bag yod kyi yan lag /
NK119(he)001:2651: rin po che las byas pa dang /
NK119(he)001:2652: mthon po zhes mtho gang las lhag pa dang gcig /
NK119(he)001:2653: gar sogs phreng sogs dang gnyis /
NK119(he)001:2654: phyi dro'i kha zas spang ba gsum ni brtul zhugs
NK119(he)001:2655: kyi yan lag ste bsnyen gnas yan lag brgyad pa'o
NK119(he)001:2656: // yan lag 'di brgyad gtan du ma yin pas /
NK119(he)001:2657: yon tan rten min de phyir so thar ni /
NK119(he)001:2658: mtshan nyid ldan pa rigs bdun kho na yin /
NK119(he)001:2659: de la kun mkhyen klong chen pas /
NK119(he)001:2660: bsnyen gnas dus ni dus res 'ga' ba yin pas
NK119(he)001:2661: yon tan gyi rten du ma bzhag go zhes pas
NK119(he)001:2662: so thar mtshan nyid pa ni rigs bdun po yin
NK119(he)001:2664: zla ba byung ngo cog gi tshes brgyad sogs la
NK119(he)001:2665: khas blangs pas des phyis tshes brgyad sogs la sdom
NK119(he)001:2666: pa len mi dgos te bsrung bas chog par 'dod
NK119(he)001:2668: 'o na zla ba byung go cog gi tshes brgyad
NK119(he)001:2669: sogs par bsnyen gnas bsrung bar khas blangs pa'i gang
NK119(he)001:2670: zag des tshes brgyad kyi mtshan mo 'das pa na
NK119(he)001:2671: sdom pa gtong ngam mi gtong gtong na zla ba
NK119(he)001:2672: phyi ma'i tshes brgyad sogs par bsnyen gnas cho ga'i
NK119(he)001:2673: sgo nas len dgos par thal /
NK119(he)001:2674: de'i dus su sngar gyi sdom pa btang zin pa gang zhig /
NK119(he)001:2675: sdom pa rgyud la med pas bsrung ba la dgos pa med pa'i phyir /
NK119(he)001:2677: bsnyen gnas kyi sdom pa gang zhig /
NK119(he)001:2678: nyin zhag gi mtha' can ma yin par thal ba dang /
NK119(he)001:2679: tshes brgyad du ma zad dgu dang bcu la bsrung dgos par thal /
NK119(he)001:2683: bsnyen gnas mtshan mo 'das pa na /
NK119(he)001:2686: des na dus res 'ga' ba ste /
NK119(he)001:2687: sngar tshes brgyad la sogs par khas blangs pa des /
NK119(he)001:2688: phyis tshes brgyad sogs la nges par cho ga'i sgo nas bsnyen gnas len dgos so //
NK119(he)001:2689: de yang kun tu rgyu sen rengs kyi zhus pa
NK119(he)001:2690: la sogs par bsnyen gnas yan lag 'di brgyad ji
NK119(he)001:2692: go ma'i dge bsnyen yin kyang yod smra'i min /
NK119(he)001:2693: gnas brtan sde pa'i lugs su dbyig gnyen bzhed /
NK119(he)001:2694: yan lag brgyad ji srid 'tsho ba'i bar du bsrung na /
NK119(he)001:2695: go ma'i dge bsnyen yin zhes gnas brtan sde pas 'dod la yod smra bas mi 'dod te /
NK119(he)001:2697: go ma'i dge bsnyen zhes bya ba 'di ni 'phags
NK119(he)001:2698: pa gnas brtan pa'i man ngag brgyud pa las thos
NK119(he)001:2699: kyi / bde bar gshegs pas gsungs pa ni ma mthong ngo //
NK119(he)001:2701: gsum pa dge bsnyen gyi bslab pa ni /
NK119(he)001:2702: dge bsnyen gyi gtan khrims lnga zhes /
NK119(he)001:2703: gsod rku rdzun smra 'dod pas log par g.yem /
NK119(he)001:2704: myos gyur spang rnams dge bsnyen sdom pa ste /
NK119(he)001:2705: de yang dge bsnyen la rtsa ba bzhi'i mi tshangs spyod cha spong mi dgos te /
NK119(he)001:2706: bdag pos bsrung ba mi gzhan gyis bzung pa /
NK119(he)001:2707: rigs kyi bsrung ba ma sring lta bu /
NK119(he)001:2708: chos kyi bsrung ba dge tshul dang dge slong ma lta bu ste gsum /
NK119(he)001:2709: yul gyi mi rung ba dkon mchog gi rten dang pha ma'i drung /
NK119(he)001:2710: dus kyi mi rung ba zla mtshan ldan dus dang dus gnyan /
NK119(he)001:2711: yan lag gi mi rung ba dang kha bshang lam ste gsum 'gog la /
NK119(he)001:2712: bdag gir ba ni mi 'gog la /
NK119(he)001:2713: de steng du chang spang ba'o //
NK119(he)001:2715: nyan thos sde ba dag gis skyabs gsum 'dzin pa'i dge bsnyen /
NK119(he)001:2716: srog gcod spang ba lta bu sna gcig gcod pa'i /
NK119(he)001:2717: gsod rku gnyis spang ba lta bu sna 'ga' gcod pa'i /
NK119(he)001:2718: gsod rku rdzun gsum spang ba lta bu phal cher gcod pa'i /
NK119(he)001:2719: kun bsrung na yongs rdzogs kyi dge bsnyen zhes lnga dang /
NK119(he)001:2720: gzhan dag de'i steng du mi tshangs spyod cha bcas
NK119(he)001:2721: spang bas tshangs spyod nyer gnas kyi dge bsnyen dang
NK119(he)001:2722: yan lag brgyad ji srid 'tsho ba'i bar bsrung bas
NK119(he)001:2723: go ma'i dge bsnyen dang bdun du bzhed de /
NK119(he)001:2725: gang 'dod khas len grangs ltar sna gcig spyod //
NK119(he)001:2726: sna 'ga' phal cher spyod dang yongs rdzogs spyod //
NK119(he)001:2727: gcig gnyis gsum dang lnga spang de yi steng //
NK119(he)001:2728: mi tshangs spyod spang tshangs spyod dge bsnyen no //
NK119(he)001:2729: de'i 'phros bshad bshad ma thag pa las //
NK119(he)001:2732: ji srid 'tsho bar tshangs bar spyod byed cing //
NK119(he)001:2733: gso sbyong yan lag brgyad pa'ang blang bar bgyi //
NK119(he)001:2736: 'di dang go mi gnyis ni khyim pa dang /
NK119(he)001:2737: rab byung gnyis ka min zhes mkhas la grags //
NK119(he)001:2738: zhes pas mi tshangs spyod cha dang bcas pa spangs pas khyim pa'ang min la /
NK119(he)001:2739: rags ldog lnga sogs pa'i bslab bya mtshan nyid pa
NK119(he)001:2740: med pas rab byung du'ang mi 'dod zhes mkhas pa
NK119(he)001:2741: dag gis tha snyad brjod do //
NK119(he)001:2743: rig 'dzin sngags kyi sdom pa 'dzin pas gong ltar rtsa ba bzhi dang /
NK119(he)001:2744: mi dge lhag drug phyogs mthun spangs bya dang //
NK119(he)001:2745: dge bsnyen sdom ldan rig pa 'dzin pas kyang //
NK119(he)001:2746: rab byung rtags dang cho ga ma gtogs pa //
NK119(he)001:2747: lhag rnams nyams su len pa dpung bzang bshad //
NK119(he)001:2753: log lta ste mi dge bcu'i lhag ma drug phyogs mthun dang bcas pa spang zhing /
NK119(he)001:2754: rab tu byung ba'i cho ga dang /
NK119(he)001:2755: chos gos lhung bzed la sogs pa'i rtags ma gtogs
NK119(he)001:2756: 'dul ba las gsungs pa'i chos de dag sngags pa
NK119(he)001:2757: khyim pas kyang bsrung dgos par /
NK119(he)001:2759: rgyal ba ngas gsungs so sor thar ba yi //
NK119(he)001:2760: tshul khrims rnam dag 'dul ba ma lus las //
NK119(he)001:2761: sngags pas khyim pa rtags dang cho ga spangs //
NK119(he)001:2762: lhag ma rnams ni nyams su len par bya //
NK119(he)001:2764: bzhi pa dge tshul gyi bslab bya la gsum ste /
NK119(he)001:2766: gnang ba nyes med bcu gsum /
NK119(he)001:2767: nyams pa'i chos gsum bstan pa'o //
NK119(he)001:2769: srog gcod rku dang mi tshangs spyod dang rdzun //
NK119(he)001:2770: chang 'thung gar sogs phreng sogs mal che mtho //
NK119(he)001:2771: phyi dro'i kha zas gser dngul len pa ste //
NK119(he)001:2772: zhum pa spang phyir rags pa bcur dril gsungs //
NK119(he)001:2774: gang zhig srog gcod gzhan gyi nor 'phrog dang //
NK119(he)001:2775: mi tshangs spyod brdzun bcos pa'i chang la sogs //
NK119(he)001:2776: gar sogs phreng sogs mal che mtho ba dang //
NK119(he)001:2777: phyi dro'i kha zas gser dngul len pa spangs //
NK119(he)001:2778: zhes gsungs pa'i tshig 'di dag la dmigs bsal mi dgos par gsal ba nyid do //
NK119(he)001:2779: gar sogs phreng sogs gnyis su brtsis te dngos po
NK119(he)001:2780: gang rags la ldog par sla ba bcu ste dge
NK119(he)001:2781: tshul gyi rags ldog bcu zhes bya'o //
NK119(he)001:2782: gnyis pa gnang bas nyes med bcu gsum ni /
NK119(he)001:2783: chos gos lhung bzed 'chang dang bral ba dang //
NK119(he)001:2784: sa rko rin chen reg dang me la reg /
NK119(he)001:2785: btang nas za dang shing 'dzeg shing gcod dang //
NK119(he)001:2786: sbyin len r+ts+wa sngon khrod du mi gtsang 'dor //
NK119(he)001:2787: bsog 'jog za dang sa bon 'joms pa rnams //
NK119(he)001:2788: gnang ba'i nyes med bcu gsum ma gtogs pa //
NK119(he)001:2789: dge slong ji bzhin spang blang mtha' dag gcig /
NK119(he)001:2790: de yang chos gos kha dog dang mtshan nyid ma tshang ba dang /
NK119(he)001:2791: lhung bzed mtshan nyid mi ldan pa'am lcags las byas pa ma yin pa gnyis 'chang ba dang /
NK119(he)001:2792: 'bral ba dang sa rko ba dang /
NK119(he)001:2793: gser sogs rin po che la reg pa dang /
NK119(he)001:2798: sbyin len ma byas par za ba dang /
NK119(he)001:2799: r+ts+wa sngon gyi khrod dang chu la sogs par snabs lud bshang gci 'dor ba dang /
NK119(he)001:2800: gsog 'jog byas te za ba dang /
NK119(he)001:2802: nas sogs kyi sa bon 'joms pa bcu gsum ni
NK119(he)001:2803: gnang ba ste nyes med tsam du yod la gzhan
NK119(he)001:2804: spang blang dge slong bzhin dgos par gsungs so //
NK119(he)001:2805: gzhan yang gnang ba de dag dang phyogs mthun nam rigs su bsdus te gnang ba gsum yod do //
NK119(he)001:2806: 'chang ba'i zlar bsdu gos rgyu zla bar 'jog /'bral ba'i zlar bsdu dgon pa'i 'bral spangs dang /
NK119(he)001:2807: bsog 'jog zlar bsdu bsog 'jog byed pa'ang gnang /
NK119(he)001:2808: de ni gzhung tshig 'di nyid kyis gsal zhing rgya cher yi ges zhed do //
NK119(he)001:2809: gsum pa nyams pa'i chos gsum ni /
NK119(he)001:2810: khyim rtags spang nyams rab byung rtags len nyams /
NK119(he)001:2811: brnyas pas mkhan por nyams te nyams pa gsum /
NK119(he)001:2812: spang ba dge tshul sdom pa'i bslab bya'o //
NK119(he)001:2814: rab tu byung dus khyim rtags spang bar khas blang pas phyis gos dkar po dang /
NK119(he)001:2815: kha tshar can la sogs khyim pa'i gos gon pa dang /
NK119(he)001:2816: skra dang kha spu ma bregs pa la sogs pa byas na nyams la gnyis pa ni /
NK119(he)001:2817: rab byung gi rtags ma yin pa /
NK119(he)001:2818: keng rus la sogs pas brgyan pa /
NK119(he)001:2819: skra 'bal ba la sogs byas pas nyams la /
NK119(he)001:2821: mkhan po la ma gus pas brnyas pa dang tshe
NK119(he)001:2822: dang ldan pa la sogs ming chung ba nas brjod
NK119(he)001:2824: de dag spang ba ni dge tshul gyi bslab bya'o //
NK119(he)001:2825: lnga pa dge slob ma'i bslab bya la gnyis /
NK119(he)001:2826: spang bya rtsa ba'i chos drug /
NK119(he)001:2827: rjes mthun gyi chos drug go //
NK119(he)001:2829: dge slob ma ni dge tshul thob pa'i steng /
NK119(he)001:2830: gcig 'gro chu rkyal skyes reg lhan gcig 'dug /
NK119(he)001:2831: smyan bya nyes 'chab rtsa ba'i chos drug go //
NK119(he)001:2833: gcig pu lam du 'gro mi byed //
NK119(he)001:2834: chu bo'i pha rol rkyal mi bya //
NK119(he)001:2835: skyes pa la ni reg mi bya //
NK119(he)001:2836: skyes pa dang ni 'dug mi bya //
NK119(he)001:2837: smyan du gyur pa mi bya zhing //
NK119(he)001:2838: kha na ma tho bcas mi bya //
NK119(he)001:2840: smyan bya zhes pa ni brda rnying ste /
NK119(he)001:2841: skyes pa dag la bud med che ge mo khyod
NK119(he)001:2842: 'ba' zhig yid la byed do la sogs pa dang
NK119(he)001:2843: / bud med la skyes pa des de ltar smra'o zhes phan tshun mthun par byas nas /
NK119(he)001:2846: gser bzung 'doms spu breg dang sa rko spangs /
NK119(he)001:2847: byin len ma byas bsog 'jog byas mi za /
NK119(he)001:2848: rtsa sngon mi gtsang dor yang rjes mthun drug /
NK119(he)001:2849: de ltar lung de nyid las /
NK119(he)001:2850: gser la bzung bar mi bya zhing //
NK119(he)001:2851: 'doms kyi spu ni breg mi bya //
NK119(he)001:2852: sa ni rko bar mi bya zhing //
NK119(he)001:2853: byin len ma byas bza' mi bya //
NK119(he)001:2854: bsog 'jog byas pa mi bza' zhing //
NK119(he)001:2855: r+ts+wa sngon mi gtsang dor mi bya //
NK119(he)001:2857: drug pa dge slong gi khrims la'ang spang ba'i bslab bya dang /
NK119(he)001:2858: bsgrub pa'i bslab bya gnyis las /
NK119(he)001:2860: dge slong khrims la gnyis brgya lnga bcu gsum /
NK119(he)001:2863: dge 'dun lhag ma bcu gsum dang /
NK119(he)001:2865: ltung byed 'ba' zhig pa dgu bcu so sor bshags pa bzhi /
NK119(he)001:2866: nyes byas brgya dang bcu gnyis te ltung ba sde
NK119(he)001:2867: lnga las khrims nyis brgya dang lnga bcu rtsa gsum
NK119(he)001:2869: sdom pa'i rtsa ba pham pa bzhi zhes pa /
NK119(he)001:2873: rdzun smra ba dang bzhi las /
NK119(he)001:2874: dang po la'ang bslab pa 'cha' ba'i snyad ka gleng gzhi dang /
NK119(he)001:2875: dgag bya dngos bstan pa gnyis las /
NK119(he)001:2877: lo bcu gnyis kyi bar du dge slong la pham
NK119(he)001:2878: pa la sogs pa'i nyes pa med pa gnas pa
NK119(he)001:2879: na / lo bcu gsum pa la ma nyan yod
NK119(he)001:2880: du gang zag sh+aakya bzang sbyin gyis bud med la
NK119(he)001:2881: 'khrigs pa spyod pa las pham pa'i bcas pa dang
NK119(he)001:2882: na / po mdzad la / de'i rjes su dge
NK119(he)001:2883: slong dgon pas spra mo la sogs par spyod pas
NK119(he)001:2884: bcas pa gnyis pa mdzad de /
NK119(he)001:2886: ston pa'i bstan pa bcu gnyis lor //
NK119(he)001:2887: ltung ba med par legs byas te //
NK119(he)001:2888: de nas bzang spyin bu yi phyir //
NK119(he)001:2889: chung ma la ni 'khrigs pa spyad //
NK119(he)001:2890: dge slong dgon pa ba yis kyang //
NK119(he)001:2891: spra mor log zhugs kun mkhyen gyis //
NK119(he)001:2892: bslab pa'i gzhi ni bcas par mdzad //
NK119(he)001:2894: gnyis pa mi tshangs spyod kyi pham pa dngos la /
NK119(he)001:2895: gzhi ni yan lag cha kun bzung 'os la //
NK119(he)001:2896: skye gnas lam du pho dbang las rung ni //
NK119(he)001:2897: bsam pa ngo tsha 'jigs med chags sems kyis //
NK119(he)001:2898: sbyor ba drud pa mthar thug sim pa thob //
NK119(he)001:2899: de ni tshangs par spyod las rnam par nyams //
NK119(he)001:2901: gzhi bsam pa sbyor ba mthar thug bzhi las /
NK119(he)001:2903: mi dang mi ma lags pa gang yin kyang rung
NK119(he)001:2904: ste gson po dang lus phyed tshal du longs pa'i
NK119(he)001:2905: ro yin kyang de la yod pa'i kha dang bshang
NK119(he)001:2906: lam zag byed ces skye gnas kyi lam ste rma'i
NK119(he)001:2907: sgo gsum gang yang rung ba bde ba bskyed nus
NK119(he)001:2909: brten byed pho'i dbang po ma nyams shing las su rung pa'o //
NK119(he)001:2911: mchil ma gci dang bshang pa yi //
NK119(he)001:2912: lam du chags can zhugs na ni //
NK119(he)001:2913: gso byar mi rung gdug pa yi //
NK119(he)001:2914: phas pham sbrul gyi dge slong zin //
NK119(he)001:2917: 'du shes 'khrul ma 'khrul gang yang ngo tsha dang
NK119(he)001:2918: 'jigs pa'i sems med cing 'dod chags kyi sems kyis
NK119(he)001:2919: reg pa bde ba bdag gir ba byed 'dod rgyun
NK119(he)001:2920: ma chad pa'o // sbyor ba dang por bcug /
NK119(he)001:2921: bar du bsgul spyod la sogs byas pas /
NK119(he)001:2922: mthar thug kha'i swo phan chad /
NK119(he)001:2923: zag byed kyi pags rim phan chad /
NK119(he)001:2924: bshang lam gyi sbu gu phan chad 'das te bde
NK119(he)001:2925: ba lus kyis myong ba yid kyis bdag gir byas
NK119(he)001:2927: kha shun swo dang pags pa las //
NK119(he)001:2928: nor bu 'das na phas pham ste //
NK119(he)001:2930: gnyis pa ma byin len gyi pham pa la sngar ltar gnyis las /
NK119(he)001:2932: yul rgyal po'i khab tu dge slong nor can gyis rang gi khang khyim brtsegs pa'i phyir du /
NK119(he)001:2933: rgyal po'i shing brkus pa la brten nas bcas pa mdzad de /
NK119(he)001:2935: rang gi khang pa brtsegs pa'i phyir //
NK119(he)001:2936: rgyal po ma skyes sgra yi shing //
NK119(he)001:2937: dge slong nor can gyis rkus pas //
NK119(he)001:2938: de brten 'di dag kun blang bcas //
NK119(he)001:2941: rku ba'i gzhi ni mi gzhan nor yin la //
NK119(he)001:2942: bsam pa rang nyid 'tsho phyir brku sems kyis //
NK119(he)001:2943: yul dus rin thang tshang ba sbyor bas brkus //
NK119(he)001:2944: mthar thug brkus sam rkur bcug brtsad nas thob //
NK119(he)001:2945: ces gzhi bsam pa sbyor ba mthar thug bzhi las /
NK119(he)001:2947: rang ma yin pa gzhan gyi nor zhig bsam pa
NK119(he)001:2948: 'du shes ma 'khrul bar brku sems rgyun chags pa'o
NK119(he)001:2951: rin thang tshang ba brkus pa'o //
NK119(he)001:2953: gang gi yul ni de yi dus //
NK119(he)001:2954: gang gi tshad kyi mgron bu ni //
NK119(he)001:2955: de yi bzhi cha brkus pa gang //
NK119(he)001:2956: dge slong la ni pham par 'gyur //
NK119(he)001:2958: rin thang ji ltar zhe na /
NK119(he)001:2959: ka sha pa ni bzhi cha'i tshad du longs ba'i nor gang zhig ste /
NK119(he)001:2960: de yang kar+sha pa ni'i bzhi cha la nas khal phyed tsam yin par mkhas pa dmar ston dang /
NK119(he)001:2961: rje btsun grags pas bzhed la /
NK119(he)001:2962: gzhan gyi 'dod tshul ni mtha' yas pa zhig 'dug go //
NK119(he)001:2963: mthar thug dngos su brkus sam /
NK119(he)001:2964: brgyud dam brtsad nas brkur bcug kyang rung rang gis thob pa'o //
NK119(he)001:2965: gsum pa srog gcod kyi pham pa la gnyis kyi gleng gzhi ni /
NK119(he)001:2966: yul spang byed du dge slong mang pos mi sdug pa'i ting nge 'dzin bsgom te /
NK119(he)001:2967: lus mi gtsang ba 'di dang bral na ci ma
NK119(he)001:2968: rung snyam nas dge sbyong sbed la chos gos lhung
NK119(he)001:2969: bzed la sogs byin nas gsod du bcug pa las
NK119(he)001:2971: dge slong mi gtsang yid dbyung gang //
NK119(he)001:2972: ri dwags dbyug thogs ces pas gsod //
NK119(he)001:2973: bsod nams thob dang lhung bzed sogs //
NK119(he)001:2974: 'dod pa de brten bkag pa yin //
NK119(he)001:2977: srog gcod gzhi ni mi gzhan ma 'khrul bar //
NK119(he)001:2978: bsam pa gsod sems gsod bya der shes pas //
NK119(he)001:2979: sbyor ba gsod par brtsam nas ma ldog pa //
NK119(he)001:2980: mthar thug srog gi dbang po 'gag pa dang //
NK119(he)001:2981: gsod bcug yi rangs sngags pa brjod byas pa //
NK119(he)001:2982: de la gzhi bsam pa sbyor ba mthar thug bzhi las /
NK119(he)001:2984: khams drug dang ldan pa'i skyes pa bud med ma ning ste mi dang /
NK119(he)001:2985: srog yid lus kyi dbang po 'dus pa mer mer po la sogs mir chags pa'o //
NK119(he)001:2986: mi las gzhan dud 'gro la sogs pa yang ngo //
NK119(he)001:2987: bsam pa 'du shes ma 'khrul bar rang gis bsad sems dang bsad bya'i bsam pas /
NK119(he)001:2988: sbyor ba rang ngam gzhan la bskos pas so //
NK119(he)001:2989: mthar thug rang ma shi ba'i sngon du bsad bya'i srog gi dbang po 'gag pa ste /
NK119(he)001:2991: mi gzhan yin la mir ni 'du shes dang //
NK119(he)001:2992: bsad pa'i bsam pas 'khrul med gsod byed cing //
NK119(he)001:2993: mi shi rmi lam ma gtogs de brlag 'gyur //
NK119(he)001:2995: des na mi bsad pa la pham pa /
NK119(he)001:2996: lha gsod pa la sbom po /
NK119(he)001:2997: dud 'gro bsad pa la ltung byed du bshad do //
NK119(he)001:2998: bzhi pa rdzun du smra ba'i pham pa la gnyis kyi gleng gzhi ni /
NK119(he)001:2999: yul yangs pa can du nya pa'i rigs las rab
NK119(he)001:3000: tu byung ba'i dge slong lnga brgyas longs spyod la
NK119(he)001:3001: chags pa dang grags pa 'dod pa'i phyir mi chos
NK119(he)001:3002: bla ma'i rdzun smras pa la bcas pa yin te
NK119(he)001:3004: mu ge'i dus shig dge slong rnams //
NK119(he)001:3005: mi srid bla mi'i yon tan rnams //
NK119(he)001:3006: phan tshun bsgrags te go byas rgyus //
NK119(he)001:3007: 'tsho ba byas tshe bkag pa mdzad //
NK119(he)001:3010: rdzun gyi gzhi ni smra shes don go'i mir //
NK119(he)001:3011: bsam pa 'du shes bsgyur nas brjod blo skyes //
NK119(he)001:3012: sbyor ba mngon shes la sogs yon tan tshogs //
NK119(he)001:3013: med kyang yod ces bla ma'i rdzun smras pa //
NK119(he)001:3014: mthar thug gzhan gyis brdzun de go na nyams //
NK119(he)001:3020: gang rang las gzhan pa'i mi smra shes don go ba can no //
NK119(he)001:3021: bsam pa bden pa'i 'du shes bsgyur nas rdzun pa'i 'du shes kyis smra 'dod rgyun ma chad pa'o //
NK119(he)001:3022: sbyor ba ngag gsal la ma nor bar ngas ni
NK119(he)001:3023: lha klu gnod sbyin la sogs pa'i sgra thos so
NK119(he)001:3025: lhan gcig gtam mo lta bu 'bras bu'i sgo nas rdzun dang /
NK119(he)001:3026: bdag ni mi rtag pa dang /
NK119(he)001:3031: mngon shes drug la sogs pa thob po zhes ngo bo'i sgo nas rdzun dang /
NK119(he)001:3032: gang du stan khra bo dbang po ni dgra bcom pa yin te /
NK119(he)001:3033: kho bo yang stan khra bo la dbang ngo //
NK119(he)001:3034: zhes ldan pa'i sgo nas mi chos bla ma'i rdzun smra ba'o //
NK119(he)001:3035: mthar thug pha rol pos tshig thos shing don go na nyams pa'o //
NK119(he)001:3037: dge 'dun lhag ma bcu gsum zhes grags pa /
NK119(he)001:3038: bgrod min gnas su khu ba 'byin pa dang /
NK119(he)001:3039: de la dang po 'byin pa'i dge 'dun lhag ma la'ang /
NK119(he)001:3041: ltung ba dngos ngos bzung ba gnyis las /
NK119(he)001:3043: mnyan yod du dge slong 'char kas 'dod chags kyi
NK119(he)001:3044: dbang gis rang gi dbang po las su rung bar
NK119(he)001:3045: byas te bsam bzhin du khu ba phyung ba la
NK119(he)001:3048: dge slong gis bsam bzhin du rma'i sgo gsum las
NK119(he)001:3049: gzhan pa'i sems can gyi yan lag las khu ba
NK119(he)001:3050: dbyung ba'o // 'di dag thams cad la nges byed
NK119(he)001:3051: kyi lung re sbyar du yod kyang yi ges 'jigs
NK119(he)001:3052: phyir lung don ma nor ba yin pas khungs thob
NK119(he)001:3053: dbyung ba'o // pa'o // gnyis pa ni /
NK119(he)001:3054: chags pas bud med lus kyi cha shas 'dzin /
NK119(he)001:3055: reg pa'i lhag ma la'ang gnyis las gleng gzhi ni /
NK119(he)001:3056: rgyal byed kyi tshal du khyim bdag gi chung ma
NK119(he)001:3057: dad pa can ston pa la bsnyen bkur byed par
NK119(he)001:3058: 'ong pa na / 'char kas rang gi spyil bu'i nang du chos ston par brtsam pa dang /
NK119(he)001:3059: chags pas lus la reg pa sna tshogs byas pas khyim bdag mo ma dad pa la bcas so //
NK119(he)001:3060: gnyis pa ltung ba dngos ni /
NK119(he)001:3061: dge slong gis chags pas bud med kyi lus la reg pa'o //
NK119(he)001:3062: gsum pa 'khrig tshig rjen smra ba'i lhag ma la gnyis las dang po ni /
NK119(he)001:3063: rgyal byed kyi tshal du dge slong 'char kas chags
NK119(he)001:3064: pas bslang ste khyim bdag gi chung ma dad pa
NK119(he)001:3065: can la 'khrig pa'i tshig sna tshogs brjod pa la
NK119(he)001:3067: bud med la chags sems kyis 'khrig tshig smra ba'o //
NK119(he)001:3068: bzhi pa bud med chags phyir bkur /
NK119(he)001:3069: de'i dang po gleng gzhi sngar dang 'dra la /
NK119(he)001:3071: bud med la 'khrig pa'i basngagasa pa brjod cing chags pas bsnyen bkur byed ba'o //
NK119(he)001:3073: pho mo phan tshun smyan byas 'dus te 'phrad /
NK119(he)001:3074: gnyen byed kyi lhag ma la gnyis las dang po ni /
NK119(he)001:3075: mnyan yod du 'char ka dang 'dul pa gnyis dga' bo dang nyer dga' gnyis /
NK119(he)001:3076: 'gro bzang dang 'gro mgyogs gnyis te drug sdes khye'u
NK119(he)001:3077: bu mo la 'phrin gsum gyis sbyor ba byas pas
NK119(he)001:3078: phrad pa la khyim pa dang mu stegs can ma
NK119(he)001:3081: skyes pa bud med sngar mi mthun pa la dge
NK119(he)001:3082: slong gis gnyen byed pa'i bsam pas 'phrin bu mo
NK119(he)001:3083: la skyal / bu mo'i 'phrin skyes pa la smra bar byed /
NK119(he)001:3084: slar des smras pa bu mo la skyal bas 'phrad par gyur ba'o //
NK119(he)001:3085: drug pa dang bdun pa ni /
NK119(he)001:3086: rang don tshad lhag khang pa khang chen brtsigs /
NK119(he)001:3087: de la tshad lhag dang khang chen gyi lhag ma la gnyis las /
NK119(he)001:3089: ston pa koo sham+b+hi gdangs can gyi kun dga' ra ba na bzhugs dus /
NK119(he)001:3090: drug yang na dga' bo nye daga'o //
NK119(he)001:3094: 'char ka drug go sdes gzhan gyi gtsug lag khang
NK119(he)001:3095: la smad pa na gzhan gyis rang gis sa rdo
NK119(he)001:3096: tsam yang spri mi nus par gzhan la 'phya ba
NK119(he)001:3097: 'di zer bas / drug sdes ma bzod par stobs
NK119(he)001:3098: rtsal dang yid gzhungs pa'i dge slong 'dun pas bram
NK119(he)001:3099: ze nor che la sar sna che ba gcig la
NK119(he)001:3100: sbyin pa'i phan yon dang khyad par gtsug lag khang
NK119(he)001:3101: brtsigs pa'i phan yon brjod de /
NK119(he)001:3102: spyod blangs bram ze'i khye'u lnga brgyas rgyab brten pa'i
NK119(he)001:3103: shing ljon pa yod pa drug sdes bcad nas tshad
NK119(he)001:3104: lhag gi khang pa brtsigs pa la bcas so //
NK119(he)001:3106: sa phyogs srog chags kyis gang ba gzhan gyis bdag
NK119(he)001:3107: tu bzung bar gang zag gzhan las spyod blangs te
NK119(he)001:3108: tshad las lhag pa'i khang pa brtsigs pa'o //
NK119(he)001:3109: tshad dang ldan pa ni spyod lam bzhi shong ba ste langs pa na lag pa mi thogs /
NK119(he)001:3110: nyal ba na rkang lag brkyang bskum mi 'thog /'gro
NK119(he)001:3111: ba na phyogs re la gom pa gsum re 'dor
NK119(he)001:3112: du rung ba / 'dug pa na skyil mo krung mi 'thog pa'o //
NK119(he)001:3114: chur bde bar gshegs pa'i mtho bcu gnyis /
NK119(he)001:3115: zheng du de'i mtho bdun yin la /
NK119(he)001:3117: mi 'bring tshad kyi khru phyed dang gnyis so /
NK119(he)001:3118: brgyad pa brjod gzhi med pa dang /
NK119(he)001:3119: zhes gzhi med kyi lhag ma la gnyis las /
NK119(he)001:3121: ston pa 'od ma'i tshal na bzhugs tshe dge slong
NK119(he)001:3122: mdza' bo dang sa ga skyes gnyis sngon gyi zhe
NK119(he)001:3123: mkhon gyi rgyus / 'phags pa gyad bu nor la
NK119(he)001:3124: dge slong ma mdza' mo la mi tshangs spyod kyi
NK119(he)001:3126: mdza' mos dge 'dun gyi dbus su 'phags pa gyad
NK119(he)001:3127: bu nor ni bzang po ma lags te bdag la
NK119(he)001:3128: chags pa spyod do zhes brjod pas nam mkha' nas
NK119(he)001:3129: lhas 'jig rten na su zhig yang dag par smra
NK119(he)001:3130: / 'phags pa gyad bu nor la yang bskur pa btab zhes la 'phyas pa las bcas so //
NK119(he)001:3132: dge slong la brjod gzhi med bzhin du skur ba btab pa'o //
NK119(he)001:3133: dgu pa snyad ka bag tsam la /
NK119(he)001:3134: brten nas dge slong bskur btab /
NK119(he)001:3135: ces bag tsam gyi lhag ma la gnyis las /
NK119(he)001:3137: gong dang 'dra bar 'phags pa gyad bu nor gyis
NK119(he)001:3138: dge slong ma ut+pala'i mdog can la chos bstan pa
NK119(he)001:3139: las / slar yang gnyis pos mi tshangs spyod kyi skur pa btab pa la bcas so //
NK119(he)001:3141: snyad dang cung zad yod pa la pham pa'i bskur ba btab pa'o //
NK119(he)001:3144: bcu gcig dbyen de'i rjes phyogs bslab pa dang 'gal ba /
NK119(he)001:3145: de gnyis kyi gleng gzhi dang dngos /
NK119(he)001:3147: ston pa rgyal po'i khab na bzhugs tshe /
NK119(he)001:3148: dge slong lhas sbyin gyis gzhon nu ma skyes dgra
NK119(he)001:3149: dad par byas pas lhas sbyin la bsnyen bskur mang
NK119(he)001:3150: du byung pas 'khor lnga brgya tsam dang bcas pa
NK119(he)001:3151: la lhas sbyin gyis 'khor rnams la dge slong goo
NK119(he)001:3152: ta ma ni sha za ba dang gos gras shing
NK119(he)001:3156: dgon par gnas par byed do //
NK119(he)001:3157: 'u cag ni de dag mi bya'o //
NK119(he)001:3159: gzhi de dag la brten nas srog chags la gnod pa dang tha ga pa'i brtsal bcom pa dang /
NK119(he)001:3161: dbang phyug gi mi gtsang ba yin pa dang /
NK119(he)001:3162: sems can gyi don mi 'grub pa'i phyir ro //
NK119(he)001:3163: zhes bslab tshigs lnga bcas te dge 'dun gyi dbyen
NK119(he)001:3164: la zhugs pa la dge slong gzhan gyis bzlog kyang
NK119(he)001:3165: mi gtong ba la dang po bcas so //
NK119(he)001:3166: dge slong ko ka li kha dang /
NK119(he)001:3169: ka ti'i mo ra bzhis lhas sbyin gyi dbyen grogs
NK119(he)001:3170: byas te dge slong gzhan gyis bzlog kyang mi gtong
NK119(he)001:3171: ba la gnyis pa bcas so //
NK119(he)001:3173: dge slong rang bzhin du gnas pas dge 'dun gyi
NK119(he)001:3174: dbyen gyi gzhi la zhugs pa la bzlog kyang mi
NK119(he)001:3175: bzlog pa ni dang po yin la /
NK119(he)001:3176: dbyen gyi grogs byed pa la bzhugs pa bzlog kyang mi gtong ba ni gnyis pa'o //
NK119(he)001:3178: khyim sun 'byin tshe skrod byed la bsnyon pa /
NK119(he)001:3179: khyim sun 'byin la gnyis las dang po ni /
NK119(he)001:3180: mnyan yod du dge slong nabs so //
NK119(he)001:3181: 'gro mgyogs dmar ser can gsum gyis dad pa can
NK119(he)001:3182: la spyod ngan sna tshogs pas ma dad par gyur
NK119(he)001:3183: te / dge slong gzhan gyis bsod snyoms rnyed par ma gyur to //
NK119(he)001:3185: khyim pa sun 'byin pa dag gtsug lag khang nas bskrad pa'i las gyis shig gsungs pas /
NK119(he)001:3186: dmar ser can gyis nyes pa phyir bcos /
NK119(he)001:3187: gnyis po gtsug lag khang nas phyir bskrad pas /
NK119(he)001:3188: dge 'dun rnams la gshe bskur btab pa la gzhan gyis bzlog kyang mi gtong ba la bcas pa'o //
NK119(he)001:3190: yul bud med dang lhan cig brtse zhing 'grogs par byed pa dang /
NK119(he)001:3191: phyi dro'i dus su khyim pa dang lhan cig tu bza' btung la longs spyod pas /
NK119(he)001:3192: khyim sun 'byin tshe phyir mi bcos par bzlog kyang bskrod byed la bsnyon te mi gtong ba'o //
NK119(he)001:3194: ltung 'byung bskul tshe bka' blo mi bde ba'o //
NK119(he)001:3199: srog chags dang bcas pa'i chu la spyad pa'i ltung ba byung ba na /
NK119(he)001:3202: khyed dge rung sdig rung khyed la ltung ba mi gleng ngo //
NK119(he)001:3203: nga dge rung sdig rung nga la ltung ba ma
NK119(he)001:3204: gleng zhes bzlog kyang mi ldog pa la bcas so
NK119(he)001:3206: ltung ba byung ba phyir bcos kyi mi bcos par slar dka' blo mi bde ba'o //
NK119(he)001:3207: de dag gso ba dge 'dun la rag las shing
NK119(he)001:3208: sdom pa rnam dag gi lhag ma lus pas na
NK119(he)001:3212: ltung byed 'ba' zhig pa gnyis las /
NK119(he)001:3214: spang ba'i ltung byed sum cu'i sde bshad pa /
NK119(he)001:3215: de la sum cu yod pa las /
NK119(he)001:3217: rang gi gos lhag zhag bcu 'das par 'chang /
NK119(he)001:3221: ston pa 'khor bcas mnyan yod na bzhugs tshe dge
NK119(he)001:3222: slong mang pos gos kyi phrug du ma bcangs shing
NK119(he)001:3223: rtsol sgrub byas pas bsam gtan dang klog pa la
NK119(he)001:3224: bar chad du gyur pa la bcas so //
NK119(he)001:3226: chos gos kyi rgyur ma bsngosa shing byin gyis ma
NK119(he)001:3227: brlabs pa zhag bcu las 'das shing bcu gcig gi
NK119(he)001:3230: chos gos dang bral zhag gcig lon pa dang /
NK119(he)001:3231: de la gnyis kyi dang po ni /
NK119(he)001:3232: ston pa mnyan yod na bzhugs tshe dge slong mang
NK119(he)001:3233: pos chos gos mang po yod bzhin du stod g.yogs
NK119(he)001:3234: smad g.yogs tsam la brten nas ljongs rgyu ba na
NK119(he)001:3235: khyim pa dang mu stegs can 'phya ba la bcas
NK119(he)001:3237: byin gyis brlabs pa'i chos gos yod bzhin du zhag
NK119(he)001:3238: gcig bral nas zhag gnyis pa'i skya rengs shar bar
NK119(he)001:3240: gos rgyu zla gcig 'jog dang zhes pa la gnyis las /
NK119(he)001:3242: ston pa mnyan yod na bzhugs tshe dge slong mang pos chos gos kyi rgyu sngon po dang /
NK119(he)001:3244: dmar po la sogs grangs mang po yun du 'jog
NK119(he)001:3245: pa'i rtsol bas thos bsam gyi bar chad du gyur
NK119(he)001:3247: gnyis pa ni chos gos kyi rgyu khru gang gi
NK119(he)001:3248: tshad du longs pa byin gyis brlabs pa'am ma brlab
NK119(he)001:3249: pa yun ring 'chang 'dod kyi bsam pas zla ba
NK119(he)001:3251: dge slong mar chos gos khrur 'jug pa'i spang ba la gnyis las dang po ni /
NK119(he)001:3252: ston pa mnyan yod na bzhugs tshe 'char kas /
NK119(he)001:3253: rang gi sa bon gyis gos pa'i chos gos rnying
NK119(he)001:3254: pa dge slong ma sbad ma la 'khrur bcug pa
NK119(he)001:3255: la mos chags pa'i rkyen gyis chos gos la gos
NK119(he)001:3256: pa'i sa bon rang gi mngal du blug pas khye'u
NK119(he)001:3257: chags pa la gzhan ma dad pa la bcas so
NK119(he)001:3259: dge slong rang gi chos gos nye du ma yin pa'i dge slong ma la 'khrur 'jug pa'o //
NK119(he)001:3262: de las gos rgyu len pa'i spang ba la /
NK119(he)001:3264: dge slong ma ut+pa la'i mdog can la ded dpon
NK119(he)001:3265: gyis ras yug phul ba 'phags pa nyer dgas nan
NK119(he)001:3266: gyis blangs pas dge slong ma shin tu chos gos
NK119(he)001:3267: rnying pa gyur pa la bcas so //
NK119(he)001:3269: dge slong gis chos gos rnam gsum yod bzhin du
NK119(he)001:3270: nye du ma yin pa'i dge slong ma las gos
NK119(he)001:3273: nye min khyim par gos rgyu blang ba dang /
NK119(he)001:3274: de la gnyis kyi dang po ni /
NK119(he)001:3275: ston pa rgyal byed tshal du bzhugs la khyim bdag
NK119(he)001:3276: gi ras yug zung dang bcas te phyag 'tshal du
NK119(he)001:3277: phyin pa nyer dgas kha chos kyi bslus te nan
NK119(he)001:3278: gyis bslangs pas khyim bdag ma dad pa la bcas
NK119(he)001:3280: rang la chos gos rnam gsum yod bzhin du khyim
NK119(he)001:3281: pa nye du ma yin pa la nan gyis slang
NK119(he)001:3283: ster na stod g.yogs smad g.yogs lhag por len /
NK119(he)001:3286: ston pa mnyan yod la bzhugs tshe grong khyer phreng
NK119(he)001:3287: ba can gyi dge slong bzhi bcu chom rkun pas
NK119(he)001:3288: bcom pa sbyin bdag la gos slangs su gnang ba
NK119(he)001:3289: la nyer dgas 'di la brten nas rnyed pa rgya
NK119(he)001:3290: chen po bsgrub po snyam nas khyim pa rnams la
NK119(he)001:3292: dge slong de dag la stod g.yogs tsam byin nas
NK119(he)001:3293: gzhan kho rang gis byas pas gzhan ma dad pa
NK119(he)001:3294: la bcas so // gnyis pa ni /
NK119(he)001:3295: chos gos rnam gsum med pa'i dge slong gis khyim
NK119(he)001:3296: pa nye du ma yin pa la bstod g.yogs smad
NK119(he)001:3297: g.yogs zung gcig las lhag par slong ba'i spang ba'o
