NK119(he)001:3299: rang la ster bsam chos gos gnas dpog pa /
NK119(he)001:3300: de la gnyis las dang po ni /
NK119(he)001:3301: ston pa mnyan yod na bzhugs tshe gza' mi gnyis
NK119(he)001:3302: phan tshun log g.yem spyad pas khyim gyi 'byor ba
NK119(he)001:3303: srab pas phan tshun 'thab cing bran mo gcig yod
NK119(he)001:3304: pa yang brdeg 'tshogs kyi las byed do //
NK119(he)001:3305: de tshe nyer dgas gza' mi gnyis la log g.yem
NK119(he)001:3306: gyi nyes dmigs dang spang ba'i phan yon bstan dge
NK119(he)001:3307: bsnyen gyi bslab pa la bkod pas 'byor pa rgyas
NK119(he)001:3308: te phan tshun mthun zhing bran mo yang skyid do
NK119(he)001:3309: // de nas gza' mi gnyis kyi nyer dga' la
NK119(he)001:3310: ras yug gcig phul bar glengs pa bran mos thos
NK119(he)001:3311: nas nyer dga' la brjod pas nyer dga' gza' mi
NK119(he)001:3312: gnyis sar phyin pa ras yug phul bas 'di las
NK119(he)001:3313: bzang ba'i ras yug dgos zer bas gza' mis tshong
NK119(he)001:3314: dus nas ras yug bzang po nyos nas phul bas
NK119(he)001:3315: // khas blangs / de'i rin ma khyer ba na
NK119(he)001:3316: khyim bdag la brdeg 'tshogs byung ba la bcas so
NK119(he)001:3318: dge slong gis nye du ma yin khyim bdag gi
NK119(he)001:3319: blos dpag pa'i spyod las lhag pa nan gyis bslangs
NK119(he)001:3322: rin dang khru tshad kyis bslang brtag dran slong /
NK119(he)001:3323: de la gleng gzhi ni gong dang 'dra la /
NK119(he)001:3325: khyim bdag pho mos so so nas ras yug re
NK119(he)001:3326: re sbyin par blos dpag pa de la rin dang
NK119(he)001:3327: khru tshad la sogs pas lhag pa bslangs pa'o //
NK119(he)001:3329: gos rin rin chen bskur ba len rnams dang /
NK119(he)001:3331: ston pa rgyal po'i khab na bzhugs tshe /
NK119(he)001:3332: bram ze dbyal tshul zhes bya ba la nyer dgas
NK119(he)001:3333: yi ge slob pa'i grogs byas nas rnyed pa slong
NK119(he)001:3334: ngo // de dus ston pa 'khor bcas mnyan yod
NK119(he)001:3335: du gshegs pa dang bram zes mnyan yod du 'gro
NK119(he)001:3336: ba'i tshong pa gcig la pa na drug bcu rgyas
NK119(he)001:3337: btab nas bskur te nyer dga' la phul dgos pas
NK119(he)001:3338: ngo // / tshong pa des nyer dga' la phul bas /
NK119(he)001:3339: des spos 'tshong gi khye'u dad pa can gcig la bcol nas ston pa'i drung du song ngo //
NK119(he)001:3340: tshong ba rnams kyis nyi shar la tshong khang du
NK119(he)001:3341: ma 'dus pa la pa na drug bcu'i chad pa
NK119(he)001:3342: bcas so // yang nangs par nye dgas spos 'tshong
NK119(he)001:3343: gi drung du 'ong nas pa na'i rgya lta ba
NK119(he)001:3344: sogs skad mang du byas pas /
NK119(he)001:3346: spos 'tshong la pa na drug cu'i chad pa bcad pas gzhan ma dad pa la bcas so //
NK119(he)001:3348: khyim bdag dad ldan gyis gos rin rin po che bskur ba dge slong la gtad /
NK119(he)001:3349: des zhal ta ba la 'dis sgrub grogs gyis zhes smras nas pho nya la bskur /
NK119(he)001:3350: des rgyu mtshan brjod nas go bar byas /
NK119(he)001:3351: de nas dge slong des zhal ta ba la gos 'dod do zhes lan gsum bskul /
NK119(he)001:3352: zhal ta bas gos ma lon mthong sar cang mi
NK119(he)001:3353: smra bar 'dug pa la slar yang gos 'dod zhes
NK119(he)001:3356: srin bal nang 'tshang byas pa'i stan byed dang /
NK119(he)001:3357: de dang 'og ma gnyis dang gsum gyi gleng gzhi ni /
NK119(he)001:3358: ston pa mnyan yod na bzhugs tshe /
NK119(he)001:3359: dge slong mang pos dang por srin bal gyi gdan /
NK119(he)001:3360: de'i rjes su nag po 'ba' zhig gi gdan /
NK119(he)001:3361: de'i rjes su cha gsum nag po dang cha gcig
NK119(he)001:3362: dkar po la byas pa'i gdan byas pas khyim pa
NK119(he)001:3363: ma dad pa la bcas so //
NK119(he)001:3365: dge slong gi srin bal srang bcu yan chad 'khor
NK119(he)001:3366: gsum khebs pa'i matha'i tshad du longs pa'i gdan nang
NK119(he)001:3369: dkon sar bal nag po 'ba' zhig stan du 'ding /
NK119(he)001:3370: de ni bal nag 'ba' zhig srang bcu yan chad las gdan byed pa'o //
NK119(he)001:3372: bal nag cha gnyis stan byed ces pas bal nag
NK119(he)001:3373: cha gnyis dkar po'i cha gcig 'khob bal cha gcig
NK119(he)001:3374: ste bzhi bsres nas gdan du byed pa la ltung
NK119(he)001:3375: ba med cing nag po cha gnyis las lhag pa
NK119(he)001:3379: ma song stan gsar byed dang /
NK119(he)001:3381: ston pa mnyan yod na bzhugs tshe dge slong mang
NK119(he)001:3382: pos gding ba ring thung mang po byas pas klog
NK119(he)001:3383: pa dang bsam gtan la gnod pas bcas so //
NK119(he)001:3385: dge slong gis lo drug gi nang du stan gsar pa gzhan 'bad pas byas so //
NK119(he)001:3387: tshad ldan gyi gding ba yod kyang slar bzo /
NK119(he)001:3388: de la gnyis las dang po ni /
NK119(he)001:3389: ston pa mnyan yod na bzhugs so //
NK119(he)001:3390: dge slong mang pos gding ba rnying pa rnams gtsug
NK119(he)001:3391: lag khang bla gab med par spung nas gsar pa
NK119(he)001:3393: gding ba rnying pa rnams rul zhing srin bus gang
NK119(he)001:3394: ba ston bas gzigs nas sbyin bdag gis dad zas
NK119(he)001:3395: chud mi za ba'i phyir gding ba rnying pa nas
NK119(he)001:3396: bde bar gshegs pa'i mtho gang gding ba gsar ba
NK119(he)001:3397: la lhan dgos pa'i bcas pa mdzad /
NK119(he)001:3399: dge slong gis phyags dar khrod kyi gding ba rnying
NK119(he)001:3400: pa nas gsar pa la bde bar gshegs pa'i mtho
NK119(he)001:3401: gang ma lhan par gding ba rnying pa dor zhing
NK119(he)001:3405: rnyed nas lam gyi dpag tshad gsum mthar byed //
NK119(he)001:3406: ces lam du bal thogs pa'i spang ba la gnyis las /
NK119(he)001:3408: drug sdes rnyed pa 'dod phyir bal yul du tshong pa rnams dang lhan cig phyin /
NK119(he)001:3409: slar rgya gar du 'ong ba'i shing rta bal gyis bkang pa'i srog shing chag /
NK119(he)001:3410: bal gyi phung po lam du spungs pa drug sdes
NK119(he)001:3411: bal khur chen po ri lta bu khur nas 'ong
NK119(he)001:3412: pas 'ga' zhig skrag /'ga' zhig ma dad pa la
NK119(he)001:3413: brten nas rgyang grags las 'das pa dpag tshad gsum
NK119(he)001:3414: la sogs par 'khur chen po mi 'khur bar bcas
NK119(he)001:3416: chags pas slong ste bal la sogs pa'i khur chen
NK119(he)001:3417: khur te nyin gcig la rgyang grags las 'da' na
NK119(he)001:3420: dge slong ma la bal 'khru smel bcug dang /
NK119(he)001:3421: de la gnyis las dang po ni /
NK119(he)001:3422: ston pa mnyan yod na bzhugs tshe /
NK119(he)001:3423: drug sdes dge slong ma rnams la bal 'khru ba
NK119(he)001:3424: dang smel ba dang tshos su bcug pa las dge
NK119(he)001:3425: slong ma rnams kyi lag pa btso lag mkhan gyi
NK119(he)001:3426: lag pa ltar gyur pa ston pas gzigs nas bcas
NK119(he)001:3428: dge slong gis nye du min pa'i dge slong ma la bal 'khru la sogs bcol ba'o //
NK119(he)001:3432: drug sdes rin po che rang gis dngos su len pa dang /
NK119(he)001:3433: gzhan len du 'jug pas mu stegs dag 'phya ba la bcas so //
NK119(he)001:3435: dge slong gis gser dngul la sogs rin po che la chags sems kyis reg cing len pa'o //
NK119(he)001:3439: drug sdes rin po che gzhan la khe spogs byed
NK119(he)001:3440: bcug pas mu stegs can ma dad pa la bcas
NK119(he)001:3442: chags pa'i dbang gis khyim pa nye du ma yin pa la rin po che khe spogs bcug pa'o //
NK119(he)001:3444: ched du tshong byed pa la gnyis las /
NK119(he)001:3446: drug sdes rin po che las gzhan pa'i yo byad la khe spogs byas pa la bcas so //
NK119(he)001:3448: dge slong longs spyod la chags pa rin po che
NK119(he)001:3449: las gzhan pa'i spyod la tshong bun khe spogs byed
NK119(he)001:3452: zhag bcu 'das 'chang ba la gnyis las /
NK119(he)001:3454: ston pa mnyan yod na bzhugs dus drug sdes lhung
NK119(he)001:3455: bzed mang du bsags nas 'chang ba la gzhan ma
NK119(he)001:3458: dge slong gis byin gyis ma brlabs pa'i lhung bzed
NK119(he)001:3459: lhag po zhag bcu 'das nas bcu gcig gi skya
NK119(he)001:3462: lhung bzed zung 'chang ba la gnyis kyi dang po ni /
NK119(he)001:3463: spos 'tshong gi khye'u zhig gis lhung bzed rnyed pa
NK119(he)001:3464: bsod snyoms pa zhig la byin pa des mi 'dod
NK119(he)001:3465: zer ba nyer dgas thos te /
NK119(he)001:3466: khye'u la lhung bzed slangs pas dge slong hral por shes pas ma byin no //
NK119(he)001:3467: de tshe nyer dgas lhung bzed 'di kho bo'i lag
NK119(he)001:3468: tu ma thob na nyer dga' shi'o zer nas gzhan
NK119(he)001:3469: gyi khyim bdag dad ldan zhig la nyo bcug nas
NK119(he)001:3470: lhung bzed thob pa dang khye'u la lhung bzed ga
NK119(he)001:3471: re zhes ma mdzes pa sna tshogs brjod pa dang
NK119(he)001:3472: gzhan ma dad pa la bcas so //
NK119(he)001:3474: rang la lhung bzed yod bzhin du nye du ma
NK119(he)001:3475: yin pa'i khyim pa la lhung bzed 'bad de btsal
NK119(he)001:3476: bas lag tu thob na zung zhes gnyis 'chang ba'i
NK119(he)001:3478: gla rngan med par 'thag 'jug pa la gnyis las dang po ni /
NK119(he)001:3479: nyer dgas dog pa mang po rnyed pa thags mkhan spyi ther ba'i rtsar khur nas /
NK119(he)001:3480: mkhas pa rgyang nas rab gsal ba //
NK119(he)001:3481: gangs dang ldan pa'i ri bo 'dra //
NK119(he)001:3482: mi mkhas rnam par mi gsal ba //
NK119(he)001:3485: thags mkhan gyis dog pa yod na kho bos 'thag
NK119(he)001:3486: go zer nas 'thag tu bcug ste gla rngan ma
NK119(he)001:3487: byin pa dang gzhan ma dad pa las bcas so
NK119(he)001:3489: dge slong gi nye du ma yin pa la gla
NK119(he)001:3490: rngan ma byin par 'thag bcol nas lag tu len
NK119(he)001:3495: ston pa mnyan yod na bzhugs tshe khyim bdag pho
NK119(he)001:3496: mo gnyis dang por mi mthun pa'i rkyen gyis khyim
NK119(he)001:3498: nyer dgas mthun par byas pa'i bka' drin du ras yug btags nas 'bul lo smras pas /
NK119(he)001:3499: nyer dgas thos nas tha ga pa'i drung du song
NK119(he)001:3500: nas hwags kyi la du byin nas ras yug 'di
NK119(he)001:3501: dkyus ring ba zheng che ba thags bzang ba yis
NK119(he)001:3502: byas pas khyim bdag gi bdog pa mang du zad
NK119(he)001:3503: pa la gzhan ma dad pa las bcas so //
NK119(he)001:3505: nye min khyim par blos dpag pa'i ras yug las
NK119(he)001:3506: lhag pa tha ga ba la gla rngan cung zad
NK119(he)001:3509: dge slong gos sbyin slar 'phrog ces pas dang po ni /
NK119(he)001:3510: ston pa mnyan yod na bzhugs tshe nyer dgas rang
NK119(he)001:3511: gis lhan gcig gnas pa'i dge slong chos zhes bya
NK119(he)001:3512: ba la gos byin nas phyi bzhin 'brang ma btub
NK119(he)001:3513: pas / ngas glen pa khyod la chos la bsam
NK119(he)001:3514: nas gos sbyin pa ma yin gyi rjes su mi
NK119(he)001:3515: 'brang na tshur thong zer nas gos 'phrog pa las
NK119(he)001:3516: pas / bcas so // gnyis pa ni /
NK119(he)001:3517: gzhan la gos sam lhung bzhed sogs byin zin nas slar 'phrog pa'o //
NK119(he)001:3520: sbyin dus bshad las snga bar bdag gir byas /
NK119(he)001:3523: ston pa mnyan yod na bzhugs tshe ri rags kyi
NK119(he)001:3524: dgon par tshong pas dbyar gyi rnyed pa phul bas
NK119(he)001:3525: drug sdes de rnams kha zas su byas nas zad
NK119(he)001:3526: par byas pa dang tshong pa rnams ma dad pa
NK119(he)001:3527: la bcas so // gnyis pa ni /
NK119(he)001:3528: dge 'dun gyi dbyar gyi rnyed pa dus min du
NK119(he)001:3529: bdag gir byas pa la gtad pa las byung ba'i
NK119(he)001:3531: dgon par 'jigs bcas gos bral zhag bdun 'das /
NK119(he)001:3532: de la gnyis te dang po ni /
NK119(he)001:3533: ston pa mnyan yod na bzhugs dus dge slong 'ga'
NK119(he)001:3534: zhig ri rags su dbyar gnas pa khas blang ba
NK119(he)001:3535: na sbyin bdag gi rnyed pa rgya chen phul ba
NK119(he)001:3536: chom rkun pas dge slong rnams mtshan mo'i tshe sgren
NK119(he)001:3537: mor mnyan yod du lhags pa ston pas gsan nas
NK119(he)001:3538: / dgon par gnas pa'i dge slong gis zhag drug
NK119(he)001:3539: tshun chad chos gos dang bral yang nyes pa med
NK119(he)001:3540: par gnang ba la drug sdes de las kyang lhag
NK119(he)001:3543: dge slong gi zhag bdun phan chad du byin gyis
NK119(he)001:3544: brlabs pa'i chos gos gsum dang bral ba la dgon
NK119(he)001:3547: ras chen dgag dbye zin kyang zla phyed 'das /
NK119(he)001:3549: dge slong gis dbyar gyi gos ras chen de dbyar
NK119(he)001:3550: khas len pa'i snga rol zla gcig tu btsal nas
NK119(he)001:3551: dgag dbye byas nas zla phyed tshun chad de zla
NK119(he)001:3552: ba phyed lngar bcas pa las /
NK119(he)001:3553: de la gzhan du tshol ba dang bcangs pa spang bya'o //
NK119(he)001:3555: dge 'dun bsngosa pa'i rnyed pa bdag tu bzung /
NK119(he)001:3556: de la gnyis kyi dang po ni /
NK119(he)001:3557: ston pa mnyan yod du bzhugs tshe bsod snyoms pa
NK119(he)001:3558: zhig gis khyim bdag 'ga' zhig dad par byas pas
NK119(he)001:3559: dge 'dun la ras yug 'phul bar bsngosa pa nyer
NK119(he)001:3560: dgas bdag nyid la bsgyur ba dang gzhan dag kha
NK119(he)001:3563: dge 'dun la bsngosa pa'i yo byad rang gis bdag tu byas pa'o //
NK119(he)001:3565: na sman zhag bdun 'das na gsog 'jog go //
NK119(he)001:3566: de la gnyis las dang po ni /
NK119(he)001:3567: ston pa rgyal po'i khab na bzhugs tshe dge slong
NK119(he)001:3568: mang pos sman byin gyis brlabs nas bzhag pa yun
NK119(he)001:3569: ring bas rul ba dang myags pa las bcas so
NK119(he)001:3571: sman snga dro byin len byas pa phyi dro'i dus
NK119(he)001:3572: su byin len ma zhig par bcangs pa dang sman
NK119(he)001:3573: byin len byas pa thun tshod las 'das par bcangs
NK119(he)001:3574: pa dang / zhag bdun pa'i sman byin gyis brlabs
NK119(he)001:3575: pa de las 'das par bcangs pa ste dus las
NK119(he)001:3576: 'das pas gsog 'jog gi spang bar 'gyur ro //
NK119(he)001:3577: 'tsho bcangs kyi sman zhes ji srid 'tsho bar bcangs
NK119(he)001:3578: pa gnang ste de 'das tshe ltung ba 'byung ba'i
NK119(he)001:3579: gzhi med phyir skabs 'di'i ltung bar mi 'gyur ro
NK119(he)001:3580: // 'di dag bshags pa'i tshe gang la ltung ba
NK119(he)001:3581: byung ba'i dngos po de gzhan la spang dgos pas
NK119(he)001:3582: na spang lhung zhes bya ste bshad zin to //
NK119(he)001:3584: ltung byed 'ba' zhig dgu bcu tham pa ni /
NK119(he)001:3586: shes bzhin rdzun du smra ba'i ltung byed la /
NK119(he)001:3587: gleng gzhi dang ngo bo gnyis las /
NK119(he)001:3589: dge slong sh+aakya lag rgyud kyis bram ze mkhas pa zhig dang rtsod par khas blangs shing /
NK119(he)001:3590: bdag gal te pham na grags pa nyams nges snyam
NK119(he)001:3591: nas dus las 'das te shes bzhin du rdzun smras
NK119(he)001:3594: de'ang sngar bshad pa lta bu ni pham pa /
NK119(he)001:3595: gzhi med dang bag tsam ni lhag ma dge 'dun
NK119(he)001:3596: gyi dbus su shes bzhin chos ma yin pa chos
NK119(he)001:3598: ltung ba dag gam dris tshe ma dag kyang cang mi smra na nyes byas /
NK119(he)001:3599: ltung ba bzhi po de las gzhan pa'i rdzun smra na ltung byed du 'gyur ro //
NK119(he)001:3604: drug sdes dge slong rnams la yan lag nyams pa dang /
NK119(he)001:3605: rigs rus sogs kyi sgo nas skyon brjod pas dge
NK119(he)001:3606: slong de dag yid mi bde bar gyur pa las
NK119(he)001:3608: dge slong gzhan la rigs rus sogs kyis sgo nas skyon brjod pa'o //
NK119(he)001:3612: drug sdes dge slong rnams kyi bar du phra ma
NK119(he)001:3613: byas pas bsam gtan dang klog pa'i bar chad du
NK119(he)001:3616: dge slong phan tshun 'byed par 'dod pas phra ma byed pa'i rdzun tshig go //
NK119(he)001:3620: dge slong phan tshun rtsod pa gzhan gyis zhi bar
NK119(he)001:3621: byas pa drug sdes zhi bar byas pa ma yin
NK119(he)001:3622: no zhes zer bas phan tshun rtsod pa las bcas
NK119(he)001:3623: so // gnyis pa ni gzhan gyi zhi bar byas
NK119(he)001:3624: pa'i rtsod pa slar yang skyo sngogs kyi sgo nas
NK119(he)001:3625: rtsod pa slong bar byed pa'o //
NK119(he)001:3627: bud med chos ston gnyis te /
NK119(he)001:3629: dge slong 'char kas bud med la chos ston pa
NK119(he)001:3630: na nu ma dang sha tshan la reg pa la
NK119(he)001:3631: sogs pa byas pas gzhan ma dad pa la bcas
NK119(he)001:3633: skyes pa gzhan med par bud med la chos tshig lnga'am drug las lhag par ston pa'o //
NK119(he)001:3636: lhan gcig chos 'don pa la gnyis te /
NK119(he)001:3638: drug sdes bsnyen par ma rdzogs pa dang rgod bag
NK119(he)001:3639: gis skad gdangs sna tshogs kyis chos 'don pa na
NK119(he)001:3640: gzhan ma dad pa la bcas so //
NK119(he)001:3642: dge slong gis rgod bag gis bsnyen par ma rdzogs
NK119(he)001:3643: pa dang lhan cig chos kyi tshig skad gdangs sna
NK119(he)001:3645: brgyad pa gnas ngan len ltung brjod /
NK119(he)001:3647: dge slong rgan bu 'ga' zhig dge 'dun lhag ma'i ltung ba byung nas /
NK119(he)001:3649: dge 'dun gyi gnas mal phyags dar byed pa sogs
NK119(he)001:3650: la drug sdes 'di dag dad pa che ba ma
NK119(he)001:3651: lags / dge 'dun lhag ma'i ltung ba phyir bcos kyi ched yin no //
NK119(he)001:3652: smras pas gzhan dag kye ma gnas brtan rgan po dag kyang 'di 'dra na /
NK119(he)001:3653: gzhan pa lta ci smos zhes 'phya ba la bcas so //
NK119(he)001:3655: ltung ba dang ldan pa'i dge slong la ltung ba
NK119(he)001:3656: glengs par ma bskos pas bsnyen par ma rdzogs pa'i
NK119(he)001:3657: drung du ltung ba ldan par go bar byed pa'o
NK119(he)001:3659: mi chos bla ma bden smra ba'i gleng gzhi ni /
NK119(he)001:3660: nya ba'i rigs las rab tu byung ba'i dge slong lnga brgyas dgra bcom thob tshe /
NK119(he)001:3661: mu ge'i dus shig nya ba'i drung du mi chos
NK119(he)001:3662: bla ma thob par khas blangs shing brjod nas 'tsho
NK119(he)001:3663: ba'i yo byad mang po blangs pas gzhan ma dad
NK119(he)001:3666: bsnyen par ma rdzogs pa la dgos pa med bzhin
NK119(he)001:3667: du mi chos bla ma'i yon tan thob ces smra
NK119(he)001:3671: dge slong gyad bu nor dge 'dun gyi bya ba
NK119(he)001:3672: la brtson pas chos gos ngan par gyur pa dge
NK119(he)001:3673: 'dun gyi ras yug gcig chos gos rgyur byin pas
NK119(he)001:3674: / mdza' bo dang sa la skyes gnyis kyis dge
NK119(he)001:3675: 'dun 'di dag ni bshes ngor byed cing spyi'i rdzas
NK119(he)001:3676: chud gson pa yin no zhes dge 'dun la skur
NK119(he)001:3677: pa btab pa la bcas so //
NK119(he)001:3679: dge 'dun la bya ba byed pa de la yo
NK119(he)001:3680: byad cung zad byin pa la skur ba btab pa'o
NK119(he)001:3682: bslab gzhi khyad bsad kyi dang po ni /
NK119(he)001:3683: drug sdes so sor thar pa'i mdo 'don tshe bslab
NK119(he)001:3684: gzhi phra zhing phra ba 'di dag gis ci byar
NK119(he)001:3685: zer nas bslab bya khyad du bsad pa la bcas
NK119(he)001:3687: 'dul ba'i bslab bya khyad du bsad pa'i rigs byed do //
NK119(he)001:3689: sa bon skye ba gcod pa'i gleng gzhi ni /
NK119(he)001:3690: drug sdes rang gis shing ljon pa gcod cing gzhan
NK119(he)001:3691: gcod du 'jug pa las gzhan gyis 'phya ba las
NK119(he)001:3693: dgos pa med bzhin phyi rol gyi sa bon myu
NK119(he)001:3694: gu sogs bskyed pa'i nus pa nyams par byas pa'o
NK119(he)001:3696: bdag gi ngor 'phya ba la gnyis te dang po ni /
NK119(he)001:3697: mdza' bo dang sa la skyes gnyis nyer dga' dang
NK119(he)001:3698: lhan cig gtam byed pa na khyod nyen dgas kyang
NK119(he)001:3699: dge 'dun gyi gnas mal stob pa na /
NK119(he)001:3700: gyad bu nor bzhin kho bo cag la tho 'tshams
NK119(he)001:3701: par ma byed ces zer bas gzhan 'phya ba la
NK119(he)001:3703: bya ba byed pa'i dge slong la dngos sam zur gyis 'phya bar byed pa'o //
NK119(he)001:3706: ltung byung gleng la ma thos lan gzhan 'debs /
NK119(he)001:3708: 'dun pa la phan pa'i bsam pas ltung ba gleng pa na /
NK119(he)001:3709: 'dun pas khyod la kho bo ltung ba mi gleng
NK119(he)001:3710: khyod kho bo la ltung ba ma glengs khyed dang
NK119(he)001:3711: kho bo mi 'dra ste kho bo'i ston pas byang
NK119(he)001:3713: zer ba gzhan gyis 'phya ba la bcas so //
NK119(he)001:3715: phyir bcos la ltung ba glengs pa na /
NK119(he)001:3716: ltung ba khas mi len par ngas ni ma thos sogs spyod pa sna tshogs pas lan 'debs pa'o //
NK119(he)001:3719: zhes pa la gnyis dang po /
NK119(he)001:3720: dge slong mang po dge 'dun gyi gnas mal ma
NK119(he)001:3721: bsdus par bla gab med par bzhag pas chud zos
NK119(he)001:3724: rang gi longs spyod pa'i dge 'dun gyi khri dang
NK119(he)001:3725: khri'u bla gab med par bzhag pas nyi rlung gis
NK119(he)001:3728: gding ba ma bsdus steng song dang /
NK119(he)001:3730: dge slong 'gas gtsug lag khang du r+ts+wa dang lo
NK119(he)001:3731: ma mang du bting ste ma bsdus par song ba
NK119(he)001:3732: dang / de nyid srog chags kyi gang ba la bcas so //
NK119(he)001:3734: gtsug lag khang du r+ts+wa dang lo ma'i tshogs bting pa ma bsdus par 'jog par byed pa'o //
NK119(he)001:3736: dge slong bskrad dang tho 'tshams de la gnyis kyi dang po ni /
NK119(he)001:3737: dge slong 'char kas rang dang lhan cig gnas pa'i dge slong gtsug lag khang gi phyir bton pas /
NK119(he)001:3738: mtshan mo thog dag tu sdug bsngal ba las bcas so //
NK119(he)001:3739: gnyis pa gzhan la gnod sems kyis gnas khang nas phyir skrod pa'o //
NK119(he)001:3741: phyis gnon byas pa la dang po ni /
NK119(he)001:3742: 'char kas rang gi grogs gsar bu la gru mo dang pus mos bardzisa pa la bcas so //
NK119(he)001:3744: dge slong gzhan la rang lus kyis bardzisa shing gnon pa'o //
NK119(he)001:3749: nyer dga' dang bsod snyoms pa gcig ljongs rgyu ba
NK119(he)001:3750: na kho bo'i khur 'di khyod kyis khur byas pas
NK119(he)001:3751: kho bo la mi dgos byas pas /
NK119(he)001:3752: ri rags kyi gtsug lag khang na bsod snyoms pa
NK119(he)001:3753: sgo dam par bcad de gnas pa'i steng nas khri'u
NK119(he)001:3754: rkang pa rno bar byas te lus shugs phyung ste
NK119(he)001:3755: mnan pas bsod snyoms pa'i dpral ba gzhoms pa la
NK119(he)001:3757: gzhan la gnod sems kyis lus shugs kyi ljid kyis khri rkang gnon pa'o //
NK119(he)001:3759: srog chags ldan pa'i chu dang /
NK119(he)001:3762: 'dun pas srog chags dang ldan pa'i chu la r+ts+wa
NK119(he)001:3763: dang lo ma sogs 'debs te longs spyod pas srog
NK119(he)001:3764: chags mang du shi bas gzhan ma dad pa la
NK119(he)001:3766: srog chags dang bcas pa'i chu la shes bzhin longs spyod pa'o //
NK119(he)001:3768: gtsug lag pha gu rim gnyis brtsigs /
NK119(he)001:3769: shes bzhin gyis so de la'ang dang po ni /
NK119(he)001:3770: drug sdes nyin gcig la gtsug lag brtsigs pa de'i nub mo zhig la bcas so //
NK119(he)001:3772: char chu'i 'jigs pa yod pa shes bzhin du char
NK119(he)001:3773: chu skyabs pa'i g.yogs ma byas par nyi ma gcig
NK119(he)001:3774: la rim pa gsum las lhag par brtsigs pa'o //
NK119(he)001:3777: ma bskos chos ston 'di nas mar bcu dge slong ma las gyur pa yin te /
NK119(he)001:3778: de'i dang po la gnyis kyi gleng gzhi ni /
NK119(he)001:3779: ston pas dge slong ma rnams la dge slong gnas
NK119(he)001:3780: brtan pas chos ston par byos gsungs pa la drug
NK119(he)001:3781: sdes chos ston cing dge slong ma dang rtse zhing
NK119(he)001:3782: lus la reg pa sogs byas pas gzhan ma dad
NK119(he)001:3785: dge slong ma'i ston par ma bskos pas de la chos ston pa'o //
NK119(he)001:3789: bskos kyang dga' byed kyis dge slong ma ut+pala'i mdog
NK119(he)001:3790: can la nyi nub bar chos ston pas dge slong
NK119(he)001:3791: ma 'khor bcas mnyan yod du phyin pas sgo bcad
NK119(he)001:3792: nas phyi rol du gnas pa chom rkun gyis bcom
NK119(he)001:3793: par brtson pas dge slong mas dmag tshogs su sprul
NK119(he)001:3794: pas bcom ma nus kyang chos ston pa po la
NK119(he)001:3795: gzhan gyis 'phya ba la bcas so //
NK119(he)001:3797: 'jigs bcas sar dge slong ma la nyi nub rjes su chos ston pa'o //
NK119(he)001:3799: kha zas phyir ston pa'i dang po ni /
NK119(he)001:3800: 'phags pa dga' byed dge slong ma la chos ston pa na /
NK119(he)001:3801: dge slong mas kha zas cung zad phul ba nyer
NK119(he)001:3802: dgas ma bzod nas dga' byed ni kha zas kho
NK119(he)001:3803: na'i ched du chos ston to zer ba la bcas
NK119(he)001:3805: dge slong ma'i ston par bskos pa la phrag dog gis skur par btab pa'o //
NK119(he)001:3807: gos btsems pa'i ltung byed la gnyis las /
NK119(he)001:3809: 'char kas dge slong ma sbed ma'i snam sbyar la
NK119(he)001:3810: sogs gos mang du btsems pas gzhan gyis 'phya ba
NK119(he)001:3811: las bcas so // gnyis pa ni /
NK119(he)001:3812: nye du ma yin pa'i dge slong ma'i gos btsems pa'o //
NK119(he)001:3814: chos gos byin pa'i dang po ni /
NK119(he)001:3815: tshong dpon las rab tu byung ba'i dge slong gis
NK119(he)001:3816: rang gi chung ma rnying pa yin pa'i dge slong
NK119(he)001:3817: ma la snam sbyar byin pas bcom ldan 'das 'khor
NK119(he)001:3819: dge slong de la chos gos med pa gzhan gyis 'phya ba la bcas so //
NK119(he)001:3820: gnyis pa ni nye du min pa'i dge slong ma la chos gos sbyin pa'o //
NK119(he)001:3822: don mthun lam 'grogs la gnyis las dang po ni /
NK119(he)001:3823: drug sdes gzhon nu bcu gnyis sde dang lhan cig
NK119(he)001:3824: lam ring po'i bar du song bas gzhan gyis 'phya
NK119(he)001:3827: yul dge slong ma dang lhan cig lam rgyang grags las lhag par 'grogs pa'o //
NK119(he)001:3830: zhes pa'i gleng gzhi dang ngo bo gnyis /
NK119(he)001:3831: gru dang lam barje ba ma gtogs sngar bzhin no //
NK119(he)001:3832: nyer brgyad pa dben par lhan gcig 'dug pa dang zhes pa la gnyis te /
NK119(he)001:3834: 'char kas khyim bdag gi chung ma dad pa can sbed ma dang lhan cig 'dug ste /
NK119(he)001:3835: kho bo cag gis sngon 'di dang 'di 'dra byas
NK119(he)001:3836: pa dran nam byas pa bsod snyoms pa gcig gis
NK119(he)001:3837: thos te 'phya ba la bcas so //
NK119(he)001:3839: dben pa skyabs yod du bud med dang lhan cig 'dug pa'o //
NK119(he)001:3841: 'greng ba dang de'i dang po gnyis pa lus 'greng
NK119(he)001:3842: ba dang 'dug pa'i khyad par ma gtogs snga ma
NK119(he)001:3844: sbyor bcug zas za rnams ni spang bar bya /
NK119(he)001:3846: drug sdes ljongs su rgyu ba bcu gnyis sdes mthong
NK119(he)001:3847: nas ming po dag khye'u bsos gsol zhing byas pas
NK119(he)001:3848: / sring mo dag des mi 'tsho bas khyim bdag
NK119(he)001:3849: la bsod snyoms sbyor chug byas pas bcu gnyis sdes
NK119(he)001:3850: khyim bdag la yang dag min pa'i yon tan brjod
NK119(he)001:3851: de 'tsho ba sbyor bcug pas gzhan ma dad pa
NK119(he)001:3852: / las bcas so // gnyis pa ni /
NK119(he)001:3853: dge slong mas nye du min pa'i khyim bdag gzhan la zas sbyor bcug pa'o //
NK119(he)001:3855: yang yang zas za ba'i ltung byed la gnyis las /
NK119(he)001:3857: ston pa 'khor bcas drag shul can gyis gdugs tshod drangs pa'i tshe /
NK119(he)001:3858: drug sdes gzhan sa nas a smri'i 'khur ba sogs bslangs nas zos /
NK119(he)001:3859: slar yang drag shul can sa nas bsod snyoms longs spyod pas gzhan ma dad pa las bcas so //
NK119(he)001:3861: nyin gcig la khyim pa nye du min par kha
NK119(he)001:3862: zas gnyis dang gsum sogs blangs te longs spyod pa'o
NK119(he)001:3865: zhag gcig lhag bsdad za dang /
NK119(he)001:3867: ri rags shig gi khyim du mu stegs pa'i rab
NK119(he)001:3868: byung gnas pa drug sdes der song nas dang po
NK119(he)001:3869: gzhan spyod kyis khyim pa dad par byas /
NK119(he)001:3870: phyis rang spyod kyis ma dad par byas pa dang /
NK119(he)001:3871: gcer bu pa drug cus dbyug pa'i rigs pas pham
NK119(he)001:3872: par byas te gzhan dag 'phya ba la bcas so
NK119(he)001:3874: mu stegs pa'i rab byung yod sar zhag gcig lhag par gnas te kha zas spyod pa'o //
NK119(he)001:3877: za dang zhes pa'i dang po ni /
NK119(he)001:3878: drug sdes mnyan yod du khyim bdag gi bu mo
NK119(he)001:3879: bag la bardzonga rgyus 'khur ba rnams nan gyis blangs
NK119(he)001:3880: bas bag mar 'gro ba'i thabs chag pa gzhan ma
NK119(he)001:3883: khyim pa nye du min pa las dus gcig la
NK119(he)001:3884: lhung bzed gsum las lhag pa'i kha zas slangs te
NK119(he)001:3885: za ba'o // so bzhi pa za rjes bza' bca' za ba dang /
NK119(he)001:3886: zhes spangs pa za ba'i gleng gzhi ni /
NK119(he)001:3887: ston pas zas spangs pa za bar mi bya'o //
NK119(he)001:3888: gsungs kyang 'gal bar byed pa na gzhan dag 'phya ba la bcas so //
NK119(he)001:3890: dang por zas la byin len byas pa na bsam
NK119(he)001:3891: sbyor gyis zas de nyid spangs te slar yang lhag
NK119(he)001:3892: por ma byas par zas de nyid la longs spyod
NK119(he)001:3894: spangs zas ltung 'byung ched du rdzun gyis stobs /
NK119(he)001:3896: dge slong rgan zhugs zhig la ltung ba yang yang
NK119(he)001:3897: byung ba slob dpon gyi drung du phyir bcos byas
NK119(he)001:3898: pa la rgan zhugs kyis slob dpon 'di yang bdag
NK119(he)001:3899: gi drung du ltung ba bshags dgos pa cig thabs
NK119(he)001:3900: bya'o snyam nas slob dpon gyis spangs ba'i kha zas
NK119(he)001:3901: lhag por ma byas bzhin byas so zer te slob
NK119(he)001:3902: dpon la byin pa gsol zin pa dang rgan zhugs
NK119(he)001:3903: kyis spang ba'i kha zas phyir 'chos shig zer bas
NK119(he)001:3904: / slob dpon gyis 'di ni kho bo la ltung
NK119(he)001:3905: bar mi 'gyur khyod la 'gyur ro zer ba la
NK119(he)001:3906: gzhan ma dad pa las bcas so //
NK119(he)001:3908: spang ba'i zas lhag por ma byas bzhin byas so zer nas dge slong gzhan la stob pa'o //
NK119(he)001:3910: gnang min mtshams nang logs su 'dus nas za /
NK119(he)001:3912: ston pa rgyal po'i khab na bzhugs tshe /
NK119(he)001:3913: lhas sbyin 'khor bcas kyis dge 'dun 'byed pa'i phyir
NK119(he)001:3914: lhan cig 'dus nas za ba la gzhan ma dad
NK119(he)001:3917: mtshams nang du bsam pa mi mthun pas dge 'dun
NK119(he)001:3918: spyi las logs su 'dus nas kha zas la longs
NK119(he)001:3920: dus min phyed yol za dang /
NK119(he)001:3923: bsod snyoms snga dro ma rnyed phyi dro cung zad
NK119(he)001:3924: rnyed pa zos pa na gzhan dag 'phya ba la
NK119(he)001:3926: rang gling gi nyi ma phyed yol nas skya rengs ma shar bar dus rung gi zas bza' ba'o //
NK119(he)001:3928: bsog 'jog za ba'i gleng gzhi ni /
NK119(he)001:3929: dge slong nag po pas 'bras chan mang po bsog 'jog byas pa la bcas so //
NK119(he)001:3931: sman gsum gang rung ba bsog 'jog byas te longs spyod pa'o //
NK119(he)001:3933: byin len ma byas sman bzhi khar mid pa /
NK119(he)001:3935: nag po pas dur khrod kyi zas gos rang gar blangs pa la bcas so //
NK119(he)001:3937: sman bzhi gang rung byin len ma byas par spyod pa'o //
NK119(he)001:3939: bsod pa zhim po'i zas blangs pa la gnyis las dang po ni /
NK119(he)001:3940: khyim bdag dad ldan gyis ston pa 'khor bcas spyan
NK119(he)001:3941: drangs nas gdugs tshod gsol zin nas drug sdes phyis
NK119(he)001:3942: lhag pa lhag ma byin pas ma mgu ste gzhan
NK119(he)001:3943: las bzang po slong ba na gzhan ma dad pa
NK119(he)001:3944: la bcas so // gnyis pa ni /
NK119(he)001:3945: khyim pa nye du min pa la zas bslangs nas
NK119(he)001:3946: slar yang gzhan la kha zas bsod pa zhes bzang
NK119(he)001:3949: srog chags bcas chur spyod pa'i gleng gzhi ni /
NK119(he)001:3950: sngar r+ts+war 'debs pa'i skabs bzhin la /
NK119(he)001:3951: ngo bo srog chags dang bcas pa'i chu la btung ba dang khrus byed pa la sogs pa'o //
NK119(he)001:3953: nyal po byed pa'i shul du nyal ba la dang po ni /
NK119(he)001:3954: 'char kas spos 'tshong gi khye'u rang gi chung ma
NK119(he)001:3955: dang lhan cig nyal po byed pa'i bar chad byas
NK119(he)001:3956: pa gzhan ma mos pa la bcas so //
NK119(he)001:3957: ngo bo ni khyim nang na 'dug ste khyim pa
NK119(he)001:3958: pho mo nyal po byed pa la bar chad byas
NK119(he)001:3961: zhes pa la gnyis kyi 'greng ba dang 'dug pa ma gtogs snga ma ltar ro //
NK119(he)001:3963: gcer bur byin pa'i dang po ni /
NK119(he)001:3964: kun dga' bo la gcer bu ma rgan gzhon gnyis
NK119(he)001:3965: kyis zas slangs pas rgan pa la 'khur ba gcig
NK119(he)001:3966: gzhon pa la gnyis byin pas rgan mos 'di na
NK119(he)001:3967: khyod la dga' ba zhig go zer nas skur ba
NK119(he)001:3970: phyi rol par gtogs pa'i bud med la zas gos
NK119(he)001:3971: kyi dgos pa khyad par can med bzhin byin pa'o
NK119(he)001:3973: dmag blta ba'i dang po ni /
NK119(he)001:3974: rgyal po gsal rgyal gyis dmag ri rags su 'dren
NK119(he)001:3975: tshe drug sdes dmag la bkren can khyod kyis ri
NK119(he)001:3976: rags rgyal po mi thub ste khyed cag dman la
NK119(he)001:3977: gcig shos mchog yin no zer bas rgyal po 'khor
NK119(he)001:3978: bcas ma dad pa la bcas so //
NK119(he)001:3980: rang gi khyim las 'das te dmag la blta zhing smod pa'o //
NK119(he)001:3982: dmag sar zhag gnyis lhag par nyal ba la gnyis te dang po ni /
NK119(he)001:3983: gsal rgyal gyi dmag ri rags su ma phebs pa
NK119(he)001:3984: na blon po rnams kyis mgon med zas sbyin bsod
NK119(he)001:3985: nams che bas des bos na phebs par 'gyur ro
NK119(he)001:3986: zer nas khyim bdag nang du phyin pa dge slong
NK119(he)001:3987: dang 'phrad 'dod nas bos pas gzhan ma 'ong drug
NK119(he)001:3988: sde 'ongs nas dmag 'phyas pa la bcas so //
NK119(he)001:3990: dmag sar zhag gcig lhag pa zhag gnyis yan 'dug pa'o //
NK119(he)001:3992: dmag gi ru bkod byed dang de'i gleng gzhi ni /
NK119(he)001:3993: dmag de'i nang du drug sde gnas tshe dpung tshogs
NK119(he)001:3994: dang go cha'i tshogs rgyal po 'khor bcas kyis bshams
NK119(he)001:3995: pa byed tshe logs su dkrugs shing ru bkod byas
NK119(he)001:3996: pas gzhan dag 'phya ba la bcas so //
NK119(he)001:3998: dmag nang du gnas te dgos pa khyad par can med bzhin tu ru bkod sogs byed pa'o //
NK119(he)001:4000: dge slong brdeg pa la dang po ni /
NK119(he)001:4001: 'char kas gzhon nu bcu bdun sde la phan tshun
NK119(he)001:4002: brdeg tu bcug pas phan tshun ngus zhing 'gyel ba
NK119(he)001:4003: la bcas so // gnyis pa ni /
NK119(he)001:4004: dge slong la brdeg gam brdeg tu gzhug pa'o //
NK119(he)001:4006: brdeg gzas pa'i dang po dang gnyis pa brdeg pa
NK119(he)001:4007: dang byed pa'i khyad par ma gtogs sngar bzhin no
NK119(he)001:4009: gnas ngan len gyis ltung ba 'chab pa'i dang po ni /
NK119(he)001:4010: nyer dgas rgyal byed tshal du bu mo zhig la
NK119(he)001:4011: lus kyis reg pa sna tshogs byas pa dge slong
NK119(he)001:4012: chos kyis mthong nas nyer dgas su la'ang ma smra
NK119(he)001:4013: zhes gsang bcug pa la bcas so //
NK119(he)001:4015: ltung ba rang la byung bzhin 'chab par byed pa'o //
NK119(he)001:4017: dge slong zan gcod pa'i ltung byed la /
NK119(he)001:4019: dge slong chos kyis nyer dag'i gnas ngan len brjod
NK119(he)001:4020: pa na nyer dgas chos la gnod par brtsams te
NK119(he)001:4021: dang po nyer dgas zas zos nas dge slong chos
NK119(he)001:4022: la snga dro'i dus gdugs tshod la ma bab zer
NK119(he)001:4023: te zas bkag grib tshad gzhal te bsod snyoms la
NK119(he)001:4024: 'gro bar brtsams pas nyer dgas khyod dus min du
NK119(he)001:4025: za'am rang gnyis lhan cig 'dug pas bde ba ma
NK119(he)001:4026: yin gyi gzhan du song zer bas /
NK119(he)001:4027: chos kyi zan bkag par rig nas gtsug lag khang
NK119(he)001:4028: du song ste da lus mdangs ma nyams bar dge
NK119(he)001:4029: sbyor byas ma nus pa na blo phab ste nyal
NK119(he)001:4030: ba gzhan gyis 'phya ba la bcas so //
NK119(he)001:4032: gnod sems kyis rang gi grogs la dus rung gi zas gcod par byed pa'o //
NK119(he)001:4034: me la reg tu bcug pa'i dang po ni /
NK119(he)001:4035: drug sdes me zor du 'phangs pa dang me mgal
NK119(he)001:4036: bskor ba la mu stegs 'phya ba la bcas so
NK119(he)001:4038: rgod bag gi bsam pas me la reg cing rtse ba'o //
NK119(he)001:4040: dge 'dun las la 'dun phul phyir ldog smra /
NK119(he)001:4043: 'dun pa koo sh+aam+b+hira thugs dam dal bar 'dug /
NK119(he)001:4045: dga' bo nyer dga' gnyis dge 'dun gyi nang du
NK119(he)001:4046: gnas tshe bcu bdun sdes sngon brnyas pa dran te
NK119(he)001:4047: nyer dga' gnas nas 'don pa'i ched du dga' bo
NK119(he)001:4048: la chos dri ma can dkru bar bya zer nas
NK119(he)001:4049: 'gyur byed kyi chur spangs pa na /
NK119(he)001:4050: gan+di brdung ste dga' bo la dge 'dun 'dus shig
NK119(he)001:4051: smras pas kho 'di 'dra bar gyur pas 'dun pa
NK119(he)001:4053: de nas bcu bdun sdes nyer dga' la bcu bdun
NK119(he)001:4054: sdes lto ba phral te rgyu mas rgyal byed tshal
NK119(he)001:4055: bskor ro zer ba la sogs dran nam zer nas
NK119(he)001:4056: gnas phyung bas nyer dgas dga' bo la kho bo
NK119(he)001:4057: gnas nas dbyung ngo zhes smre sngags byas pas /
NK119(he)001:4058: dga' bos gnas nas 'byin pa la 'dun pa mi
NK119(he)001:4059: gtong bas 'dun pa phyir 'byin zhig smras pa la
NK119(he)001:4060: gzhan gyis 'phya ba la bcas so //
NK119(he)001:4062: dge 'dun las la 'dun pa phul rjes slar yang 'dun pa phyir zlog par byed pa'o //
NK119(he)001:4064: bsnyen ma rdzogs dang nub gnyis lhag par nyal ba'i dang po ni /
NK119(he)001:4065: ston pas bsnyen par ma rdzogs pa dang lhan cig
NK119(he)001:4066: nub gnyis lhag par mi nyal bar bcas pa nyer
NK119(he)001:4067: dgas rang gi dge tshul dang nub gnyis lhag par
NK119(he)001:4068: nyal ba gzhan gyis de ltar mi rung bar ston
NK119(he)001:4069: pas ma gsung ngam zer bas /
NK119(he)001:4070: nub gnyis rung na gsum pa cis mi rung gsum
NK119(he)001:4071: par chang 'thung ngam kun dong zos sam zer ba
NK119(he)001:4072: la gzhan ma dad pa las bcas so //
NK119(he)001:4074: na ba la sogs min par bsnyen par ma rdzogs pa dang nub gnyis lhag par nyal ba'o //
NK119(he)001:4076: sdig lta'i chos lugs mi gtong ba la dang po ni /
NK119(he)001:4077: dge slong 'chi ltas kyis ston pas gsungs pa'i las
NK119(he)001:4078: 'bras la yid mi ches pa'i sdig lta byung ba
NK119(he)001:4079: sus bzlog kyang mi gtong ba la bcas so //
NK119(he)001:4081: ston pas gsung pa'i las 'bras la yid mi ches te bzlog kyang mi gtong pa'o //
NK119(he)001:4086: 'chi ltas de gnas phyung pa nyer dgas lhan cig
NK119(he)001:4087: gnas nas phebs par smras te mthun par byed pa
NK119(he)001:4088: na gzhan 'phya ba la bcas so //
NK119(he)001:4090: gnas nas phyung ba'i dge slong dang lhan cig gam mthun par byed pa'o //
NK119(he)001:4092: dge tshul sdig lta mi gtong lhan cig nyal ba'i gleng gzhi ni /
NK119(he)001:4093: nyer dag'i dge tshul tshe ma ta dang tshe ma ta chen po gnyis kyis /
NK119(he)001:4094: 'phyar g.yeng gi spyod pa byas pas gnas phyung pa
NK119(he)001:4095: nyer dag'i sar song nas smre sngags byas pas nyer
NK119(he)001:4096: dgas lhan cig nyal te spyod lam mthun par byas
NK119(he)001:4097: bas gzhan ma dad pa las bcas so //
NK119(he)001:4099: gnas phyung ba'i dge tshul dang lhan cig spyod lam mthun par 'dug pa'o //
NK119(he)001:4101: rung ba'i tshon min kha dog can min gyon pa'i dang po ni /
NK119(he)001:4102: drug sdes gar mkhan gyi cha lugs byas nas spyod
NK119(he)001:4103: lam sna tshogs byas pas gzhan ma dad pa la
NK119(he)001:4105: rung ba'i tshos gsum ma yin pa'i gos khru gang
NK119(he)001:4106: yan chad du longs pa gos gzhan gyis g.yogs med
NK119(he)001:4107: par gyon pa'o // de yang phyi rol du ngur
NK119(he)001:4108: smrig yod na nang du dkar po gon yang nyes
NK119(he)001:4109: pa med la phyi gos tshon chen kyis kha bsgyur
NK119(he)001:4112: rin chen dmag chas rol mo'i chas la reg pa'i gleng gzhi ni /
NK119(he)001:4113: drug sdes bsod snyoms sar rol mo'i cha byad blangs
NK119(he)001:4114: te bro brdungs pa na skye bo dag ma dad
NK119(he)001:4117: dgos pa med bzhin nor bu la sogs rin po
NK119(he)001:4118: che dang mda' mdung rol cha la rgod bag gis
NK119(he)001:4120: tsha dus rang gar khrus byed pa'i dang po ni /
NK119(he)001:4121: rgyal po gzugs can snying pos ston pa 'khor bcas
NK119(he)001:4122: la khrus kyi rdzing bu phul nas dge slong rnams
NK119(he)001:4123: khrus byed par zhus tshe drug sdes yun ring khrus
NK119(he)001:4124: byas pas rgyal po'i khrus kyi bar chad du gyur
NK119(he)001:4125: pas tsha dus zla gsum ma gtogs pa zla ba
NK119(he)001:4126: phyed phyed 'das dus su khrus byed par bcas pa
NK119(he)001:4130: gro bzhin te tsha dus kyi zla ba gsum dang /
NK119(he)001:4131: na ba la sogs pa'i dus min par zla phyed kyi snga rol du khrus byed pa'o //
NK119(he)001:4133: dud 'gro gsod pa'i ltung byed la dang po ni /
NK119(he)001:4134: 'char kas mda' lnga 'phangs te nam mkha' la bya
NK119(he)001:4135: rog rgyu ba gsod pas gzhan ma dad pa la
NK119(he)001:4137: gsod 'dod kyis dud 'gro'i rigs gsod pa'o //
NK119(he)001:4139: dge slong las la 'gyod pa bskyed pa'i dang po ni /
NK119(he)001:4140: bcu bdun sdes dge sbyor la brtson pa la 'char
NK119(he)001:4141: kas ci de ltar brtson pas ci bya mang du
NK119(he)001:4142: thos pa dang dgra bcom par ni nam yang mi
NK119(he)001:4143: 'gyur ci'i phyir lo nyi shu ma lon pa la
NK119(he)001:4144: bsnyen rdzogs byas na bsnyen par yang mi rdzogs la
NK119(he)001:4145: mkhan po yang smad pa yin no zer bas gzhon
NK119(he)001:4146: nu de dag sems khong du chud pa las bcas
NK119(he)001:4148: dge slong la bsnyen rdzogs kyis yon tan smod pa'i sgo nas yid dbyung pa'o //
NK119(he)001:4150: gag tshil sgog pa'i dang po ni /
NK119(he)001:4151: bcu bdun sdes rang gis grogs de'i thugs dang 'gal bar byas pa bshags pa na /
NK119(he)001:4152: cang mi smra bas gzhon nu zhig gis gag tshil
NK119(he)001:4153: byas pas rgod par rtsom pa na thams cad kyis
NK119(he)001:4154: de ltar byas pas rlung gyen du 'tshubs te shi
NK119(he)001:4157: dge slong la skyi g.ya' bar 'dod pas mchan khung la sogs 'bru nas g.ya' sgog pa'o //
NK119(he)001:4159: chur rtse ba'i dang po ni /
NK119(he)001:4160: bcu bdun sde chur zhugs te rtse sna mang po
NK119(he)001:4161: rtse ba la rgyal po gsal rgyal 'khor bcas ma
NK119(he)001:4164: rgod bag gi bsam pas chu la rtse ba'o //
NK119(he)001:4165: re lnga pa bud med gnas gcig nyal ba dang de'i gleng gzhi ni /
NK119(he)001:4166: ma 'gags pas ri rags su khye'u spyi rdol gyi
NK119(he)001:4167: ma bden mthong la 'god phyir de dang lhan cig
NK119(he)001:4169: bden mthong la bkod kyang gzhan ma dad pa la bcas so //
NK119(he)001:4171: mtshams nang gcig tu nub gcig bud med dang mnyam por nyal ba'o //
NK119(he)001:4173: dge slong sngangs byed ces pa'i dang po ni /
NK119(he)001:4174: 'char kas mtshan mo bcu bdun sde yod sar lwa
NK119(he)001:4175: ba phyir log gyon khar me bzung te 'byung po
NK119(he)001:4176: 'byung po smras pas gzhon nu dag skrag pa la
NK119(he)001:4178: dge slong la tho 'tsham pa'i bsam pas 'jigs pa sna tshogs ston pa'o //
NK119(he)001:4180: de'i spyod sbed pa'i dang po ni /
NK119(he)001:4181: drug sdes bcu bdun sde la khyed rnams nga la
NK119(he)001:4182: rgyun du 'gran pa yin na chu nang du yun
NK119(he)001:4183: ring bar 'dug gang nus 'gran zer nas thams cad
NK119(he)001:4184: chur nub pa dang nyer dga' chu nang nas langs
NK119(he)001:4185: te gzhon nu rnams kyi gos sbas /
NK119(he)001:4186: drug sdes gos gyon nas gzhan du song /
NK119(he)001:4187: bcu bdun sdes drug sde dang gos ma rnyed nas
NK119(he)001:4188: tho btsams par shes nas thang cig tu bsdad sh+aa
NK119(he)001:4189: ri'i bu byon nas gos gtad ci nyes dris pas
NK119(he)001:4190: lo rgyus bsnyad pa na gzhan dag 'phya ba la
NK119(he)001:4192: tho 'tsham pa'i sems kyis dge slong gi yo byad bskung pa'o //
NK119(he)001:4194: sngar byin gdeng med slar blang spyod pa dang /
NK119(he)001:4196: nyer dga' rgas shing 'khogs pa'i tshe gos dri ma
NK119(he)001:4197: can bkru ma nus pas thabs shig bya snyam ste
NK119(he)001:4198: / nye gnas la gos byin pas des bkrus shing kha bsgyur nas nyer dga' la bcol ba'i tshe /
NK119(he)001:4199: nyer dgas gdeng med bzhin rang gi longs spyod pa na gzhan dag 'phya ba la bcas so //
NK119(he)001:4201: rang gi min pa'i dge slong gis gos sbyin pa
NK119(he)001:4202: la sogs kyi gdeng med bzhin du longs spyod pa'o
NK119(he)001:4204: gzhi med bskur btab kyi dang po ni /
NK119(he)001:4205: mdza' bo dang sa la skyes gnyis kyis gyad bu
NK119(he)001:4206: nor la lhag mas skur pa btab pa la bcas
NK119(he)001:4208: dge slong mthong thos dog gsum gyi gzhi med bzhin du bskur ba btab pa'o //
NK119(he)001:4213: tha ga pa spyi ther bas rang gi chung ma
NK119(he)001:4214: la brdungs 'tshog byas pas bsod snyoms pa gcig dang
NK119(he)001:4215: 'grogs te mnyan yod du phyin pa na /
NK119(he)001:4216: tha ga pas grogs lnga brgya tsam sbran nas bu
NK119(he)001:4217: mo dang dge slong gnyis brdungs lhung bzed bcag chos
NK119(he)001:4218: gos ral ba la bcas so //
NK119(he)001:4220: bud med dang lhan cig skyes pa med par lam rgyang grags las 'das par lhan cig 'gro ba'o //
NK119(he)001:4224: dge slong 'ga' dpya khral ma byin pa'i tshong pa
NK119(he)001:4225: dang lhan cig lam gol ba la phyin pa sho
NK119(he)001:4226: gam pas tshor te tshong pa dang dge slong rnams
NK119(he)001:4229: rkun po lta bu dang lhan cig rgyang grags las lhag par 'da' ba'o //
NK119(he)001:4231: nyi shu ma lon pa la bsnyen rdzogs phog /
NK119(he)001:4233: mo'u 'gal gyi bus bcu bdun sde la bsnyen rdzogs mdzad pas /
NK119(he)001:4234: de dag gis tho rangs dus bkres pas smre sngags bton pa la bcas so //
NK119(he)001:4236: bsgrub bya lo nyi shu ma lon par shes bzhin bsnyen par rdzogs par byed pa'o //
NK119(he)001:4237: don gsum pa sa rko ba'i ltung byed la /
NK119(he)001:4239: drug sdes dgos med du sa rkos yur ba 'dren
NK119(he)001:4240: pa la mu stegs can la sogs ma dad pa
NK119(he)001:4241: la bcas so // gnyis pa ni /
NK119(he)001:4242: sra 'thas pa'i sa dgos pa med bzhin du rko ba'o //
NK119(he)001:4244: mgron pos zla bzhi lhag par zos /
NK119(he)001:4246: sh+aakya ming chen gyis ston pa 'khor bcas zla ba
NK119(he)001:4247: bzhi mgron du bos te zas bsod pa brims pa
NK119(he)001:4248: / drug sdes zas thob pa'i thabs shig bya snyam ste /
NK119(he)001:4249: dga' bo nyer dga' gnyis na rdzu byas nas sman
NK119(he)001:4250: pa la bstan pa des brdzun du rig nas snum
NK119(he)001:4251: bag rgya chen po gsol zer bas drug sde dga'
NK119(he)001:4252: nas sman pa khyod ni mkhas pa'o zer nas /
NK119(he)001:4254: bzhi nad g.yog byas nas zla ba bzhi las lhag
NK119(he)001:4255: par zos pa na gzhan dag 'phya ba la bcas
NK119(he)001:4257: sbyin bdag gis mgron du gnyer ba las lhag par gnas te longs spyod pa'o //
NK119(he)001:4259: mi shes brjod dang zhes pa'i dang po ni /
NK119(he)001:4260: bslab pa'i gzhi bca' ba mdzad tshe der ma 'dus pa la sgrogs par byed pa yin zhing /
NK119(he)001:4261: kun dga' bos lam pa la mgron du gnyer ba
NK119(he)001:4262: las ring du 'dug na ltung byed do zhes bcas
NK119(he)001:4263: pas dge slong rgyus med pa rnams la sgrogs shig
NK119(he)001:4264: smras pas / lam pas dge slong ma'i dbyar khang
NK119(he)001:4265: du song nas bcu gnyis sde dang drug sde la
NK119(he)001:4266: smras pas / / de dag gis bcas pa ma thos sam snyam nas /
NK119(he)001:4267: bslab pa 'di ltar bcas pa la slob par bya'o //
NK119(he)001:4269: mi mkhas pa khyed cag gis tshig tsam la slob
NK119(he)001:4270: par mi byed do zer ba na gzhan dag 'phya
NK119(he)001:4273: ston pas bcas pa'i bslab bya la slob pa'i thabs
NK119(he)001:4274: brjod pa khyad du bsad cing spong bar byed pa'o
NK119(he)001:4276: 'thab pa'i nyan rna byed pa'i dang po ni /
NK119(he)001:4277: bcu bdun sde sde snod 'dzin par gyur nas nyer
NK119(he)001:4278: dgas tho 'tshams pa 'di tsam sus kyang ma byas
NK119(he)001:4279: nga gnas nas dbyung bar bya'o zhes gros byed pa
NK119(he)001:4280: nyer dga' nyan rna byas pas thos te phan tshun
NK119(he)001:4281: mi mthun bar gyur pa las bcas so //
NK119(he)001:4282: ngo bo ni phan tshun zhe 'khon pas phag nyan byed pa'o //
NK119(he)001:4284: nyes med mi smra 'gro dang zhes pas bcu bdun
NK119(he)001:4285: sdes drug sdes nyam chung ngus gnas nas dbyung par
NK119(he)001:4286: brtsam pa dga' bos bzlog par brtsam pas gang phyir
NK119(he)001:4287: zlog pa de yang gnas phyung ngo zer bas dga'
NK119(he)001:4288: bo skrag nas cang mi smra bar song ba dang
NK119(he)001:4289: nyer dga' gnas phyung ba dga' bo'i drung du phyin
NK119(he)001:4290: nas ngus pas dga' bos nu bo gnas 'byin pa
NK119(he)001:4291: de khams gsum nas phyungs shig zer ba la gzhan
NK119(he)001:4294: las gral du dang por 'dus nas 'dun pa ma phul bar gzhan du 'gro ba'o //
NK119(he)001:4296: ma gus 'gal ba'i dang po ni /
NK119(he)001:4297: dge slong mang pos rtsod pa zhi bar byed pa na /
NK119(he)001:4298: dge slong glang chen bya bas dge slong mang po
NK119(he)001:4299: dang mi mthun par byas pa gzhan ma dad pa
NK119(he)001:4300: la bcas so // gnyis pa ni /
NK119(he)001:4301: dge 'dun gyis bcas pa'i chos ldan gyi bya ba la mi gus pas 'da' bar byed pa'o //
NK119(he)001:4303: chang btung ba'i dang po ni /
NK119(he)001:4304: dge slong legs 'ongs kyis khyim bdag gis chang phul
NK119(he)001:4305: ba btung bas sa la 'gyel ba ston pas gzigs
NK119(he)001:4306: nas / dge bsnyen yan chad kyis chang mi btung bar bcas so //
NK119(he)001:4308: myos shing 'gyel ba'i chang btung ba'i spang ba'o //
NK119(he)001:4310: dus min phyi dro grong la rgyu ba'i dang po ni /
NK119(he)001:4311: 'char kas sh+aa ris bu la gdams ngag zhus de bsgom pas dgra bcom thob tshe /
NK119(he)001:4312: ston pas khyim pa 'dul bar lung bstan pas drin
NK119(he)001:4313: lan bsab phyir grong du phyin nas skye bo mang
NK119(he)001:4315: mthar khyim bdag gi chung ma ma rungs mo zhig
NK119(he)001:4316: chom rkun pa dang 'dod log spyod pa la de'i
NK119(he)001:4317: nyes pa bshad pas bud med des chom rkun pa
NK119(he)001:4318: la 'di sod cig zer nas des ral gris dbu
NK119(he)001:4319: bcad de bkrongs pa la bcas so //
NK119(he)001:4321: nye min khyim par nyin phyed nas skya rengs ma shar bar gnas pa'o //
NK119(he)001:4323: zas bcas phyi dro rgyu dang khyim gsum 'das /
NK119(he)001:4325: sbyin bdag gis nyer dga' sbran nas ston pa 'khor bcas gdugs tshod la spyan drangs pa na /
NK119(he)001:4326: nyer dgas nga ma 'ong bar la gdugs tshod ma
NK119(he)001:4327: drong bsgos nas grong gzhan gyi khyim gsum tsam 'das
NK119(he)001:4328: te yun ring du 'gor ba ston pas gdugs tshod
NK119(he)001:4329: drongs gsungs kyang nyer dga' ma byung zer bas ston
NK119(he)001:4330: pas gzhan dbang thams cad sdug bsngal yin /
NK119(he)001:4331: rang dbang thams cad bde ba yin /
NK119(he)001:4332: gsungs nas bcas pa mdzad do //
NK119(he)001:4334: snga dro la grong gzhan du song bas sbyin bdag
NK119(he)001:4335: gis gdugs tshod drangs ba la gnod par byed pa'o
NK119(he)001:4337: rgyal po btsun mor brtse ba'i khab tu nyal ba'i dang po ni /
NK119(he)001:4338: rgyal po gsal rgyal gyi chung ma phreng ldan ma
NK119(he)001:4339: dang dbyar tshul ma'i slob dpon du sh+aa ra'i bu
NK119(he)001:4340: dang 'char ka gnyis gyur te pho brang du chos
NK119(he)001:4341: ston pa na sh+aa ri'i bu 'jug pa la mkhas
NK119(he)001:4342: pas dus su 'jug la 'char ka mtshan mo'i dus
NK119(he)001:4343: btsun mo 'khor bcas la chos bstan bsod snyoms blangs
NK119(he)001:4344: te skya rengs ma shar gong du phyir phyung pa
NK119(he)001:4345: la gzhan ma dad pa la bcas so //
NK119(he)001:4347: mtshan mo btsun mo dang bcas te rgyal po'i pho brang du 'jug pa'o //
NK119(he)001:4349: mdo sogs 'don la da gzod shes zer dang /
NK119(he)001:4351: so thar gyi mdo 'don pa na /
NK119(he)001:4352: drug sdes gus par mi nyan zhing 'di na ltung
NK119(he)001:4353: ba phra mo 'di 'dra yod pa da gzod shes
NK119(he)001:4354: zer nas bslab pa khyad du bsad pas gzhan ma
NK119(he)001:4357: gso sbyong gi dus su 'dul ba'i bslab bya shes bzhin khyad du gsod pa'o //
NK119(he)001:4359: rin chen khab ral zhes pa'i gleng gzhi ni /
NK119(he)001:4360: ba so mkhan chos shes bya ba bsod snyoms pa
NK119(he)001:4361: cig dad par byas nas dge slong mang pos ba
NK119(he)001:4362: so'i khab ral byed bcug ste slangs pas de'i 'tsho
NK119(he)001:4363: ba chad pa na gzhan ma dad pa la bcas
NK119(he)001:4365: nye min la ba so dang rus pa la sogs
NK119(he)001:4366: rin po che las khab ral byed bcug nas slang
NK119(he)001:4368: khri rkang tshad lhag bzos pa'i dang po ni /
NK119(he)001:4369: dge slong zhig khri rkang dma' bar gnyid log pas
NK119(he)001:4370: drug sbrul gyis dpral ba nas bzung ste shi bas
NK119(he)001:4371: / ston pas khri dma' bar mi nyal gsungs pas
NK119(he)001:4372: drug sdes khri rkang khru bcu gnyis pa na byed
NK119(he)001:4373: pa gzhan kha zer ba bcas so //
NK119(he)001:4375: khri rkang khru gang las lhag par byed pa'o //
NK119(he)001:4377: ngan sems shing bal khri steng gdab te 'gos /
NK119(he)001:4379: nyer dgas khri gzhan gyis 'phrog dogs nas bdag 'dug snyam ste /
NK119(he)001:4380: khri'i khar shing bal dkram pa la dge slong zhig
NK119(he)001:4381: ma brtags par nyal bas gos thams cad skya bor
NK119(he)001:4382: gyur pas gzhan dag kha lab pa la bcas so
NK119(he)001:4384: dge 'dun gyi khri la ngan sems kyis shing bal gyis g.yogs pa'o //
NK119(he)001:4386: gding ba tshad lhag byed pa'i ltung byed la dang po ni /
NK119(he)001:4387: dge slong mang bos gding ba shin tu rgya khyon
NK119(he)001:4388: che bar byas pa la gzhan ma dad pa la
NK119(he)001:4390: srid du khru gsum zheng du khru do dang sor drug las lhag pa'i gding ba 'chang ba'o //
NK119(he)001:4392: gnyan pa dgab pa tshad lhag gi gleng gzhi snga ma ltar las /
NK119(he)001:4395: zheng du khru gsum las lhag par byed pa'o //
NK119(he)001:4398: ras chen tshad lhag gi dang po sngar ltar la /
NK119(he)001:4401: zhing du khru gsum dang sor bco brgyad las lhag par byed pa'o //
NK119(he)001:4405: nyer dgas ston pa'i chos gos kyi tshad dang mnyam
NK119(he)001:4406: pa'i chos gos byas te gyon pas lus kyi ma
NK119(he)001:4407: rdzogs pas gzhan dag 'phya ba la bcas so //
NK119(he)001:4409: bde bar gshegs pa'i lus tshad dang mi ldan bzhin
NK119(he)001:4410: du bde bar gshegs pa'i chos gos kyi tshad byas
NK119(he)001:4411: te gyon pa'i kha na ma tho ba'o //
NK119(he)001:4412: de dag gis ltung byed 'ba' zhig pa dgu bcu gleng gzhi dang bcas pa bshad zin to //
NK119(he)001:4413: de yang bshags pa 'ba' zhig gis dag nus pas ltung byed 'ba' zhig pa zhes bya'o //
NK119(he)001:4415: so sor bshags bya'i sde ni bzhi yin te /
NK119(he)001:4417: dge slong ma las grong du zas bslangs zos /
NK119(he)001:4418: de la gnyis kyi dang po gleng gzhi ni /
NK119(he)001:4419: grong khyer rdo 'jog tu phyug po zhig la bu
NK119(he)001:4420: mo 'dzes ma gcig yod de ming yang ut+pala'i mdog
NK119(he)001:4422: der cher gyur te khyim na gnas pa mo'u 'gal gyis brtul te rgyun zhugs la bkod /
NK119(he)001:4423: de skye dgu'i bdag mos rab tu byung ste bsnyen par rdzogs nas dgra bcom thob /
NK119(he)001:4424: de dus rgyun du bsod snyoms thog mar blangs nas dge 'dun la phul /
NK119(he)001:4425: phyis cung zad re rang gi 'tsho bar byed pa la /
NK119(he)001:4426: nam zhig rang 'tsho ba'i bsod snyoms bslang nas 'ong
NK119(he)001:4427: pa dge slong bsod snyoms ma rnyed pa cig la
NK119(he)001:4428: phul / de'i nang par rang 'tsho ba'i bsod snyoms
NK119(he)001:4429: cung zad bslang pa nyer dgas bdag la byin zer
NK119(he)001:4430: nas blangs pas nyi ma gnyis su kha zas chad
NK119(he)001:4431: pas dge slong ma de 'gyel ba na gzhan ma
NK119(he)001:4434: yul dge slong ma la des rang nyid 'tsho ba'i bsod snyoms bslang nas spyod pa'o //
NK119(he)001:4435: gnyis pa khyim du dge slong ma bsgos mi zlog zos /
NK119(he)001:4437: mu ge cher byung dus drug sdes bcu gnyis sde
NK119(he)001:4438: la gang du dge 'dun spyan 'dren drangs pa der
NK119(he)001:4439: khyod cag gis zhal ta gyis la nged cag la
NK119(he)001:4440: zas mang du 'grim du chug cig ces bgos pas
NK119(he)001:4442: de ltar rung na bagyi'o zer nas kha zas gral rim du mi 'grim par /
NK119(he)001:4443: sbyin bdag la 'di ni 'phags pa dga' bo yin
NK119(he)001:4444: te sde snod gsum la mkhas shing rig pa dang
NK119(he)001:4445: grol ba'i spobs pa can yin pas zas phun sum
NK119(he)001:4447: de bzhin du nyer dga' sogs la smras pas /
NK119(he)001:4448: drug sdes de dag ma bzlog par zos pas gzhan dag 'phya ba la bcas so //
NK119(he)001:4450: sbyin bdag gi khyim du dge slong mar bsgos nas zas cher blangs pa za ba'o //
NK119(he)001:4452: bslab sdom spyi las rung min blangs te zos pa'i dang po ni /
NK119(he)001:4453: dmag dpon seng ge bya ba mu stegs pa la
NK119(he)001:4454: dad pa gcig ston pas bden mthong la bkod pas
NK119(he)001:4455: longs spyod thams cad dge 'dun la btang nas zad
NK119(he)001:4456: pa na / mu stegs dag nged la dad pa'i
NK119(he)001:4457: dus su longs spyod yod la da lta nor med
NK119(he)001:4458: do zer ba la brten nas de'i khyim du sh+aa
NK119(he)001:4459: ri'i bu dang mo'u 'gal gyi bu gnyis las gzhan
NK119(he)001:4460: pas zas mi blangs par bcas pas /
NK119(he)001:4461: drug sdes yang yang zas blangs pas khyim bdag 'khor bcas 'tsho bar ma nus pa la bcas so //
NK119(he)001:4462: gnyis pa ni khyim gyi bslab pa'i sdom pa byin
NK119(he)001:4463: pa'i sbyin bdag las zas blangs te longs spyod pa'o
NK119(he)001:4465: nags ma nyul bar dgon par zas bslangs bzhi'o //
NK119(he)001:4467: dgag dbye'i dus su sh+aakya'i bu mo dag gis zas
NK119(he)001:4468: khyer te 'ongs pa drug sdes de dag bsur phyin
NK119(he)001:4469: nas nags nang na chom rkun yod med ma nyul
NK119(he)001:4470: bar lam ka zhig tu 'dug pa chom rkun pas
NK119(he)001:4473: 'jigs bcas kyi sar chom rkun yod med ma nyul bar zas la longs spyod pa'o //
NK119(he)001:4474: 'di dag smre sngags kyi sgo nas so sor bshags
NK119(he)001:4475: dgos pas na sor bshags zhes bya ste bzhi po
NK119(he)001:4476: bshad zin to // lnga pa nyes byas brgya dang
NK119(he)001:4477: bcu gnyis zhes grags pa la sde tshan brgyad de
NK119(he)001:4478: bshad zin to // / gos bgo ba'i sde /
NK119(he)001:4483: lhung bzed la longs spyod pa'i sde /
NK119(he)001:4485: sgrub pa'i tshul las gyur pa'i sde'o //
NK119(he)001:4489: dang po sham thabs la bslab par bya ba bdun ni /
NK119(he)001:4490: sham thabs zlum min brtsengs 'jol glang sna 'dra //
NK119(he)001:4491: steb dang phub ma gdengs ka lta bu bdun te
NK119(he)001:4492: sham thabs kyi yar mtha' dang mar mtha' mdun rgyab
NK119(he)001:4493: gnyis mtho dman med par snyom pa zlum por bgo
NK119(he)001:4494: ba dang / pus mo yan chad du brtsengs pa min pa dang /
NK119(he)001:4495: long bu man chad du ha cang 'jol ba ma yin pa dang /
NK119(he)001:4496: mdun du gra glang po che'i sna ltar 'phyangs pa ma yin pa dang /
NK119(he)001:4497: ska rags kyi gong du t+aa li'i lo ma ltar
NK119(he)001:4498: steb pa ma yin pa dang ska rags kyis bar
NK119(he)001:4499: nas 'bru'i phub ma ltar phyir 'bur ba ma yin
NK119(he)001:4500: pa dang / ska rags kyi steng du sbrul mgo'i
NK119(he)001:4501: gdengs ka ltar mtho dman du 'dug pa ma yin
NK119(he)001:4502: pa dang / pa'o // stod g.yog rgyab gsum ste /
NK119(he)001:4503: zlum min ring thung stod gsum gos kyi bcu'o //
NK119(he)001:4504: de yang chos gos mdun rgyab gnyis mnyam par zlum por bgo ba /
NK119(he)001:4505: ha cang pus mo las yar brtsengs pa ma yin pa /
NK119(he)001:4506: ha cang pus mo las mar 'jol ba ma yin
NK119(he)001:4507: pa gsum ste bsdom pas gos kyi sde la bcu'o
NK119(he)001:4508: // gnyis pa spyod yul du 'gro ba'i nyi shu ni /
NK119(he)001:4509: lus ngag ma bsdam pa dang stod g.yogs sogs legs par bgo ba ma yin pa dang /
NK119(he)001:4510: ca co'i sgra dang bcas pa dang /
NK119(he)001:4511: mig g.yas g.yon du g.yengs pa dang /
NK119(he)001:4512: mig gnya' shing gang las ring du lta ba dang
NK119(he)001:4513: mgo bo gos kyi bstum pa gos sham thabs sogs
NK119(he)001:4515: stod g.yogs phrag pa g.yon pa la gzar ba dang /
NK119(he)001:4516: lag pa gnyis mdun nas gnya' gong du bsnol ba dang /
NK119(he)001:4517: lag gnyis rgyab nas ltag par bsnol ba dang /
NK119(he)001:4519: 'dug pa na rkang pa rkyang pa dang /
NK119(he)001:4520: rkang pa'i rting pa btegs te brang pas 'gro ba dang /
NK119(he)001:4521: rkang rting btsugs te tsog pus 'gro ba dang /
NK119(he)001:4522: lag pa'i gru brkyangs te dkur brten nas 'gro ba dang /
NK119(he)001:4523: lus gcus shing bsgyur ba dang /
NK119(he)001:4524: lag pa shar shar g.yug pa dang /
NK119(he)001:4526: gzhan dang phrag pa sprad de 'gro ba dang /
NK119(he)001:4527: gzhan dang lag pa sbrel te 'gro ba rnams /
NK119(he)001:4528: mi byed pa'i las te khyim du 'gro ba'i spyod yul nyi shu'o //
NK119(he)001:4529: gsum pa stan la 'dug pa'i sde la dgu yod de /
NK119(he)001:4530: stan 'di la sdod ces ma bsgos par 'dug pa dang /
NK119(he)001:4532: lus kyi ljid phab 'phong brdeb ste 'dug pa dang /
NK119(he)001:4533: rkang pa brkyangs nas bsnol ba dang /
NK119(he)001:4534: barla bsnol nas rkyang ba dang /
NK119(he)001:4535: long bu'i steng du long bu brtsegs te 'dug pa dang /
NK119(he)001:4536: khri 'og tu rkang pa bkug pa dang /
NK119(he)001:4537: rkang pa phan tshun gdang ste 'dug pa dang /
NK119(he)001:4538: 'doms mthong bar 'dug pa rnams spang ba 'dug tshul dgu yin no //
NK119(he)001:4539: bzhi pa zas slong ba'i sde la brgyad de /
NK119(he)001:4540: zas legs par lhung bzed kyi kha las mtho bar
NK119(he)001:4541: mi len 'bras chan dang tshod ma sogs mu dang
NK119(he)001:4542: kha da chad len pa dang /
NK119(he)001:4543: bzang ngan mnyam par mi len pa dang /
NK119(he)001:4544: mthar chags su mi len par thod rgal du len
NK119(he)001:4545: pa lhung bzed zur mig bltas te len pa dang
NK119(he)001:4546: / lhung bzed zas ma byung bar bzed sngas pa dang /
NK119(he)001:4547: sngar zas byung ba sbas nas slar bzed pa dang /
NK119(he)001:4548: snod gzhan bza' ba dang bca' ba'i steng du lhung bzed zed pa ste /
NK119(he)001:4549: de dag spangs pa rnams ni zas blang gi brgyad do //
NK119(he)001:4550: lnga pa zas za ba'i sde la nyer gcig yod de /
NK119(he)001:4551: dus dang 'gal bar za ba dang /
NK119(he)001:4552: ha cang kham che bar za ba dang /
NK119(he)001:4553: ha cang chung bar za ba dang /
NK119(he)001:4554: ran par za ba'ang min pa dang /
NK119(he)001:4555: zas za bar rtsom pa bzhin du kha gdangs pa dang /
NK119(he)001:4556: kha bkang ste smra ba dang /
NK119(he)001:4557: zas za tshe tsug tsug dang cag cag dang /
NK119(he)001:4558: hu hu dang phu phu bya ba dang /
NK119(he)001:4559: lce phyi rol tu phyung ste za ba dang /
NK119(he)001:4560: 'bru re re nas tha dad gud du phye ba dang /
NK119(he)001:4561: zas la skyon bltas te 'phya ba dang /
NK119(he)001:4562: zas kham gcig la mkhur ba phan tshun spo ba dang /
NK119(he)001:4565: lag pa la zas chags pa ldag pa dang /
NK119(he)001:4566: mdzub mos lhung bzed 'byog pa dang /
NK119(he)001:4568: lhung bzed skyom skyom byed pa dang /
NK119(he)001:4569: zas la mchod rten 'dra bar byed pa ste nyer gcig za ba'i tshe spang bar bya'o //
NK119(he)001:4570: drug pa lhung bzed la longs spyod pa'i sde la bcu bzhi ste /
NK119(he)001:4571: gzhan gyi lhung bzed la 'phyas mi 'dogs /
NK119(he)001:4572: phyir lta zhing lag pa ni /
NK119(he)001:4573: zas kyi sbags pas chu snod la mi reg /
NK119(he)001:4574: gzhan la sbags pa can gyi chu mi gtor /
NK119(he)001:4575: khyim pa 'dug pa la ma dris par zas kyis sbags pa'i chu mi 'bo ba dang /
NK119(he)001:4576: lhung bzed nang du zas kyi lhag ma bzhag ste mi dor /
NK119(he)001:4577: lhung bzed 'og gzhi med par sa rjen dang /
NK119(he)001:4580: sa cha bang rim can dang bzhir mi bzhag pa dang /
NK119(he)001:4581: gad kha dang g.yang sa dang rkan gzar du lhung bzed mi 'khru /
NK119(he)001:4583: 'bab chu drag po'i rgyun las ldog te mi 'khru ba ste bcu bzhi'o //
NK119(he)001:4584: bdun pa chos ston pa'i sde ni nyer drug ste /
NK119(he)001:4585: mi na bar 'dug pa la 'grogs te chos mi bshad /
NK119(he)001:4586: mi na bar nyal ba la 'dug ste chos mi bshad /
NK119(he)001:4587: mi na bar stan mthon po la 'dug ste rang dma' bar 'dug pa la chos mi bshad /
NK119(he)001:4588: mi na bar 'dug nas 'gro ba la phyi nas chos mi bshad /
NK119(he)001:4589: mi na bar lam po che'i 'gram nas 'gro ba
NK119(he)001:4590: la lam gyis 'gram nas 'gro zhing chos mi bshad
NK119(he)001:4591: / mi na bar mgo g.yogs pa dang /
NK119(he)001:4594: lag pa gnya' gong du bsnol ba dang /
NK119(he)001:4595: rgyab nas ltag par bsnol ba dang /
NK119(he)001:4596: do ker can te spyi gtsug tu skra bsdus te thor tshugs byas pa dang /
NK119(he)001:4598: mgo la cod pan btags pa /
NK119(he)001:4599: mgo la me tog gi phreng ba btags pa dang /
NK119(he)001:4600: mgo lwa thod dkris pa la chos mi 'chad /
NK119(he)001:4601: glang po che la zhon pa /
NK119(he)001:4603: khyogs kyi steng na 'dug pa dang /
NK119(he)001:4604: shing rta'i steng du 'dug pa dang /
NK119(he)001:4606: mi na bar lag na mkhar ba thogs pa /
NK119(he)001:4611: go cha gyon pa la chos mi bshad de nyer drug go //
NK119(he)001:4612: brgyad pa bsgrub tshul gsum ni /
NK119(he)001:4613: mi na bar 'greng ste bshang gci mi 'dor /
NK119(he)001:4614: chu'i nang dang r+ts+wa'i khrod la bshang gci dang snabs mi 'dor /
NK119(he)001:4615: gnod pa byung na ma gtogs par shing la mi gang las mthor 'dzeg pa na rgyu gcig go //
NK119(he)001:4616: 'di dag nyes pa phra mo'i rang bzhin yin pas nyes byas zhes bya'o //
NK119(he)001:4617: de dag gis dge slong gi khrims gnyis brgya dang
NK119(he)001:4618: lnga bcu rtsa gsum legs par gtan la phab zin
NK119(he)001:4619: to // bdun pa dge slong ma'i khrims la /
NK119(he)001:4622: spanga ltung sum cu so gsuma /
NK119(he)001:4623: ltung byed 'ba' zhig pa brgya brgyad cu /
NK119(he)001:4624: so sor bashagas pa bcu gnyis /
NK119(he)001:4625: nyes byas brgya dang bcu gnyis te bsdom pas sum brgya dang drug cu rtsa bzhi ste /
NK119(he)001:4627: rgyas par dge slong ma'i so thar las rtogs par bya'o //
NK119(he)001:4629: bsgrub pa'i bslab bya yongs su sbyongs ba'i tshul /
NK119(he)001:4630: gso sbyong dbyar gnas dgag dbye gos kyi gzhi /
NK119(he)001:4631: ko lpags gnas mal sman sogs gzhan du shes /
NK119(he)001:4632: zhes smos te thob pa mi nyams par bsrung ba
NK119(he)001:4633: bsgrub pa'i bslab bya mdo tsam bstan pa la gsum
NK119(he)001:4634: ste / bslab pa yongs sbyong gi gzhi gsum /
NK119(he)001:4635: bde bar gnas pa'i gzhi la gsum ste nang tshan du lnga /
NK119(he)001:4636: kun la thun mong du mkho ba las kyi gazhi'o //
NK119(he)001:4642: gnyen po bslab pa gso zhing /
NK119(he)001:4643: spang bya sdig pa rnams sbyong bas na gso sbyong zhes bya ste /
NK119(he)001:4645: dge ba mtha' dag yang dag gso byed cing //
NK119(he)001:4646: sdig pa mtha' dag yang dag 'dir sbyong ba //
NK119(he)001:4647: dge gso phyir dang sdig pa rnams sbyong phyir //
NK119(he)001:4648: de bzhin gshegs pas gso sbyong zhes gsungs so //
NK119(he)001:4649: de la dbye na bdun te /
NK119(he)001:4656: bkra shis pa'i gso sbyong ngo //
NK119(he)001:4657: de yang rigs su bsdu na /
NK119(he)001:4658: zhi gnas dang mthun pa'i gso sbyong gnyis su 'dus te /
NK119(he)001:4659: phyi ma lnga mthun pa'i gso sbyong gi nang tshan yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK119(he)001:4660: dang po zhi gnas kyi gso sbyong ni /
NK119(he)001:4661: tshul khrims kyis gzhi bzung ste sde snod la thos
NK119(he)001:4662: bsam byas nas de'i don bsgom pa'i nyams len te
NK119(he)001:4664: tshul gnas thos dang bsam gtan pas //
NK119(he)001:4665: sgom pa la ni rab tu sbyor //
NK119(he)001:4666: zhes pa'i tshul gyis zhi gnas kyis /
NK119(he)001:4667: 'dod chags kyi gnyen por mi sdug pa /
NK119(he)001:4668: zhe sdang gi gnyen por byams snying rje /
NK119(he)001:4669: gti mug gi gnyen por rten 'brel gyi gnas tshul /
NK119(he)001:4670: nga rgyal gyi gnyen po khams kyi rab dbye /
NK119(he)001:4671: phrag dog gi gnyen por dbugs dbyung rngub dran pa bsgom ste /
NK119(he)001:4673: keng rus chags bcas thams cad la //
NK119(he)001:4675: lhag mthong gis dran pa nyer bzhag bzhi sogs byang chub kyi chos rnams mngon du bya'o //
NK119(he)001:4676: gnyis pa mthun pa'i gso sbyong ni /
NK119(he)001:4677: gang du gnas mi mthun pa med pa /
NK119(he)001:4678: khyon chung tshad gding ba bzhi bcu shong ba che
NK119(he)001:4679: tshad dbus nas g.yas g.yon du dpag tshad phyed gsum
NK119(he)001:4680: re yod pa mtshams bzhir shing dang pha bong la
NK119(he)001:4682: gang zag rab tu byung ba sde lnga kas ltung
NK119(he)001:4683: ba la bshags bsdom tshul bzhin byas te bslab pa
NK119(he)001:4684: gong 'phel du byed dgos te 'dun pa 'bul ba
NK119(he)001:4686: cho ga rang la thog mar dge 'dun bsdu ba'i
NK119(he)001:4687: brda sprod pa'i g+han+di rung ba'i shing bcu drug las
NK119(he)001:4688: bya ba ste / g+han+di'i mdo las /
NK119(he)001:4689: tsan+dana bil ba pa la sha /
NK119(he)001:4690: a shwa ta dang tsan+dana dmar //
NK119(he)001:4691: rgya star ta la ke shu ka /
NK119(he)001:4692: shing sha pa dang ta ma la //
NK119(he)001:4693: a smra star bu skyu ru ra //
NK119(he)001:4694: tin ti pa ra a swa kam //
NK119(he)001:4695: 'di dag thams cad med na yang //
NK119(he)001:4698: g+han+di srid du sor brgyad cu rtsa bzhi zheng du
NK119(he)001:4699: sor drug dpangs su sor gnyis zur bzhir brgyad gzhog
NK119(he)001:4700: sor gnyis dang ldan pa rtse mo sbal pa'i mgo
NK119(he)001:4701: 'dra ba'o // gana g.yog kyang shing de nyid las
NK119(he)001:4702: bcad pa gan+di la 'phog pa'i tshad sor bcu gnyis
NK119(he)001:4703: lag pas bzung bar bya ba'i 'chang zung yang tshad
NK119(he)001:4704: de dang ldan pa rtse mo gnyis ne'u le'i mgo
NK119(he)001:4705: 'dra ba'o // bzhin yod pa'o // de nyid dge
NK119(he)001:4706: 'dun bsdus pa'i dus gtsug lag khang gi steng la
NK119(he)001:4708: de yang lo gcig la gso sbyong 'byung ba'i dus nyi shu rtsa bzhi yod de /
NK119(he)001:4709: zla ba bcu gnyis la yar ngo dang mar ngo'i gso sbyong gnyis re 'byung ste /
NK119(he)001:4710: de la gso sbyong gi basngagasa tshig lan gsum 'don cing /
NK119(he)001:4711: so sor thar pa'i mdo blo la yod pas klag
NK119(he)001:4712: cing rjes bsngo ba dang bkra shis la sogs pa
NK119(he)001:4713: byed pa'o // gnyis pa dbyar gnas ni /
NK119(he)001:4715: gnas khang ral ba dang grum pa bcos pa gzhan
NK119(he)001:4716: dag dad par bya ba'i phyir dbyar zla gsum du
NK119(he)001:4717: gnas par khas blangs dgos te /
NK119(he)001:4719: dbyar gnas pa khas blang ngo //
NK119(he)001:4722: gnas der yod pa rnams kyi mthar tshul shing dri
NK119(he)001:4723: bzang gis bgos pa gzeb kyi sprog mar ras dkar
NK119(he)001:4724: po bting pas dkris pa grangs las mi nyung ba
NK119(he)001:4725: rgan pa'i mtha' logs su bzhag nas /
NK119(he)001:4726: 'di na gnas pas khrims 'di dang 'di yod de /
NK119(he)001:4727: khrims 'di la gnas par spro bas tshul shing long zhig bgos nas 'brim pas /
NK119(he)001:4729: dang por ston pa sangs rgyas kyi tshul shing len /
NK119(he)001:4730: de nas rang rang gi len /
NK119(he)001:4731: rjes su dge tshul rnams kyi tshul shing rang rang gi mkhan slob rnams kyis len /
NK119(he)001:4732: mjug tu gzhi bdag gnyug mar gnas pa'i tshul shing gnas brtan gyis len /
NK119(he)001:4734: dge slong 'di snyed cig gis tshul shing blangs so //
NK119(he)001:4736: thos bsam b+hee ba la brtson cig 'khrug long la
NK119(he)001:4737: sogs spangs te byin gyis ma brlab par mtshams kyi
NK119(he)001:4738: phyi rol du zhag gcig kyang gnas mi rung la
NK119(he)001:4740: zhag bdun gyis brlab tu rung bar gsungs so //
NK119(he)001:4742: dbyar gnas kyi mthar der tshogs pa rnams dang rab
NK119(he)001:4743: byung gzhan glo bur du lhags pa rnams kyis kyang
NK119(he)001:4744: bya dgos te / rkyen ngan lta bus gzhan du
NK119(he)001:4745: 'gro dgos na dbyar gnas pa'i zla gcig gam phyed
NK119(he)001:4747: dgag dbye'i nyin par dbyar gnas pa'i rab byung rnams
NK119(he)001:4748: kyi mthong thos dogs gsum gyi sgo nas ltung ba
NK119(he)001:4749: glengs te ltung ba gtan la phab nas /
NK119(he)001:4750: ltung ba yod pa rnams bshags sdom byed dgos te /
NK119(he)001:4751: dgag dbyer bgos pa'i dge slong gis gral rim bzhin
NK119(he)001:4752: r+ts+wa zor pa 'brims te re re'i mdun du 'dug
NK119(he)001:4753: ste dgag dbye'i tshig brjod pa'o //
NK119(he)001:4754: gnyis pa bde bar gnas pa'i gzhi la gos sman
NK119(he)001:4755: gnas mal gsum la dbye bas lnga yod pa'i dang
NK119(he)001:4756: po gos mtha' gnyis su ma lhung bar bde bar
NK119(he)001:4757: gnas pa gos kyi gzhi la gsum te /
NK119(he)001:4758: bag yangs dang 'brel pa sra brkyang gi sde 'tsho ba'i yo byad dang 'brel pa gos kyi gzhi /
NK119(he)001:4759: dmigs gsal dang 'brel pa ko lpags kyi gazhi'o //
NK119(he)001:4761: sra brkyang zhes chos gos la dras drub byed pa'i shing gi stan sa yin te /
NK119(he)001:4762: de'i steng du chos gos du ma dras drub 'ding
NK119(he)001:4763: ba rkyang ba la sogs pas chos gos su byin
NK119(he)001:4765: de ni smin drug zla ba'i tshes bcu drug nas
NK119(he)001:4766: dbo zla'i bcu bzhi bar zla ba lnga la longs
NK119(he)001:4767: spyod rung ste / de'i rgyu dang kha dog kyang /
NK119(he)001:4768: spu che ba bshad rdab byas pa min pa /
NK119(he)001:4772: rung ba'i kha dog can la /
NK119(he)001:4774: mthud ma dang lhan rings dang /
NK119(he)001:4778: rnga mo'i bal las byas pa la sogs min par /
NK119(he)001:4779: tshad ni dras drubs zin pa'i srid du khru lnga /
NK119(he)001:4780: dpangs su khru gsum mam de las lhag kyang rung ngo //
NK119(he)001:4781: gnyis pa 'tsho ba'i yo byad dang 'brel bar gos kyi gzhi ni /
NK119(he)001:4782: de yang chos gos kyi rgyu mi rung ba ni /
NK119(he)001:4783: kha tshar dang phan tshar ma bcad pa dang /
NK119(he)001:4784: dpag bsam gyi shing las byung ba rnga mo'i bal las byung ba /
NK119(he)001:4785: khyim pa dang mu stegs kyi gos kyi dbyibs dang kha dog khra bo'o //
NK119(he)001:4788: bal gos sha na nyi 'og dang //
NK119(he)001:4789: ras gos dang ni zar ma dang //
NK119(he)001:4790: ko tam pa dang du gu la //
NK119(he)001:4791: chos gos rgyu ni rnam pa bdun //
NK119(he)001:4793: de yang kha dog mi rung ba dang rung ba gnyis las /
NK119(he)001:4796: rgya skyongs lo brgan rtsi dang gtsod //
NK119(he)001:4797: sman shing rtsi dang mthing shun mtshal //
NK119(he)001:4798: sin+d+hu ra dang gur gum ste //
NK119(he)001:4803: sngon po btsag dang dur smrig rtsi //
NK119(he)001:4804: 'di dag rung ba'i tshon gsum ste //
NK119(he)001:4806: de la snam sbyar ni nges par dras drubs dgos la /
NK119(he)001:4807: bla gos mthang gos dge slong ma'i shing dang dpung bcad dang rngul gzan la /
NK119(he)001:4810: tha ma thang thang por byas pa yin no //
NK119(he)001:4811: gding ba la glegs bur phyed gnyis las /
NK119(he)001:4812: gos gzhan la snam phran dang glegs bu'i bshad pa med de /
NK119(he)001:4814: snam sbyar nges par dras te bcad //
NK119(he)001:4815: gzhan dag ma nges gang gi phyir //
NK119(he)001:4817: de la gos bcu gsum yod de /
NK119(he)001:4825: rngul gzan gyi gzan gyi gzan dang /
NK119(he)001:4831: dbyar gyi gos ras chen bcang pa bya'o //
NK119(he)001:4834: rab kyi rab 'bring tha gsum ni /
NK119(he)001:4846: nyer lnga las lhag pa mi rung ste tshem bu'i rang bzhin no //
NK119(he)001:4847: de ni grong khyer du bsod snyoms dang /
NK119(he)001:4849: chos nyan bshad tshe gyon par bya zhing /
NK119(he)001:4850: sha rjen mchan khung gi drod kyis mi gnod pa'i
NK119(he)001:4851: phyir rdul gzan zheng du mtho gang dang srid du
NK119(he)001:4852: khru phyed do yod pa'i lhan pa mchan zhabs su
NK119(he)001:4855: glegs bu phyed dang gsum gsum gyi bdag nyid can snam phran bdun ma yin la /
NK119(he)001:4856: rab 'bring tha ma gsum gyis tshad snam sbyar bzhin no //
NK119(he)001:4857: mthang gos ni dpangs su khru do //
NK119(he)001:4859: tha ma lte ba man chad /
NK119(he)001:4860: pus mo yan chad de 'khor gsum khebs pa'i tshad do //
NK119(he)001:4861: khru'i don ni rang gi spyi gtsug nas rkang mthil bar cha bdun byas pa'i cha gnyis so //
NK119(he)001:4863: nyin mo mthang gos kyi 'og tu gyon par bya ba sham thabs kyi gzan ni /
NK119(he)001:4864: mtshan mo mthang gos kyi 'og tu gyon par bya ba ste tshad mthang gos bzhin no //
NK119(he)001:4865: rdul gzan dang po de'i gzan ni nyin mo dang
NK119(he)001:4866: mtshan mo bla gos kyi 'og tu gyon par bya
NK119(he)001:4867: ba tshad bla gos bzhin no //
NK119(he)001:4871: dge slong rnag nad can gyi sha la sbyar ba ste tshad ji tsam dgos pa'o //
NK119(he)001:4872: g.yan dgab pa ni g.yan pa'i nad can gyis sha
NK119(he)001:4873: la sbyar ba ste tshad ni srid du khru drug
NK119(he)001:4876: skra breg tshe chos gos srung phyir stod du gyon pa ste /
NK119(he)001:4880: srid du khru gsum zheng du khru do sor drug ste gnas mal skyabs pa'i phyir gding ba'o //
NK119(he)001:4882: dbyar char chu skyabs phyir du bgo ba /
NK119(he)001:4884: zheng du khru gsum dang sor bco brgyad do //
NK119(he)001:4885: de dag thams cad rung ba'i tshon gyis kha bsgyur ba'o //
NK119(he)001:4886: gos 'di dag byin gyis brlabs tshul gzhung tshig gis
NK119(he)001:4887: gsal la snam sbyar grangs mang po yod na gcig
NK119(he)001:4889: gzhan rnams mkho ba dang lhag pa'i yo byad du byin gyis brlabs par bshad do //
NK119(he)001:4890: gsum pa dmigs bsal dang 'brel pa ko lpags kyi gzhi ni /
NK119(he)001:4891: gong du bstan pa'i yul dbus rnams su lham sogs ma gnang la mtha' 'khob tu gnang ste /
NK119(he)001:4893: mtha' 'khob tu mchil lham dag bcang bar bya'o //
NK119(he)001:4894: zhes pas lham yu med pa khra bo min pa lug ru lta bu min pa /
NK119(he)001:4895: a shwa ta dang ka ra bi ra'i 'dab ma ltar min pa /
NK119(he)001:4896: gser dngul can min pa bcang rung zhing /
NK119(he)001:4897: khyim gzhan du gzhan med na ko lpags la 'dug
NK119(he)001:4898: rung zhing nyal bar mi bya zhes mdor rtsar gsungs
NK119(he)001:4899: so // gnyis pa zas mtha' gnyis su ma ltung
NK119(he)001:4900: ba'i sgo nas bde bar gnas pa sman gyi gzhi
NK119(he)001:4905: thun tshod du rung ba dang /
NK119(he)001:4907: 'tsho ba'i bar du bcang pa nyid do //
NK119(he)001:4908: zhes pas bzhi las dang po dus rung gi sman ni /
NK119(he)001:4909: bkres pa sel ba'i sman du gnang ba'i bza' ba lnga dang /
NK119(he)001:4913: sna tshogs 'bras chan zan dang sha /
NK119(he)001:4914: phye dang 'khur ba bza' ba lnga //
NK119(he)001:4917: 'jig rten kha zas su grags pa'i //
NK119(he)001:4918: rtsa ba sdong bu me tog 'bras //
NK119(he)001:4919: lo ma yang ni bca' ba lnga //
NK119(he)001:4921: gsum pa thun tshod du rung ba ni /
NK119(he)001:4922: nyin mtshan cha drug gi tha ma la skom pas gdung na /
NK119(he)001:4923: tshags su btsags pa'i rtsam thang sla ba dang bu ram gyi khu ba sla ba dang /
NK119(he)001:4924: skyu ru ra'i khu ba btung bar gnang ba'o //
NK119(he)001:4925: gsum pa zhag bdun pa'i sman ni /
NK119(he)001:4926: 'dus pa'i nad sel bar gnang ba'i sman /
NK119(he)001:4927: zhun mar 'bru mar sbrang rtsi bu ram bskol zhing brtsigs pa'i hwags zhag bdun gnang ba'o //
NK119(he)001:4928: bzhi pa 'tsho bcang gi sman ni /
NK119(he)001:4929: 'dus pa'i nad sel ba'i sman rtsa ba sdong po
NK119(he)001:4930: 'dab ma me tog 'bras bu lnga byin gyis brlabs
NK119(he)001:4931: pa ji srid 'tsho bar gnang ba'o //
NK119(he)001:4932: gzhan yang sro khang bsten pa /
NK119(he)001:4933: khrus bsten pa mig la phan pa'i dom lpags kyang bsten par gsungs so //
NK119(he)001:4934: zas de dag kyang lus la rgyags pa dang dregs
NK119(he)001:4935: pa skye ba'i gnyen po chos sgrub rten lus gnas
NK119(he)001:4936: pa'i 'du shes dang lus kyi srin bu gso ba'i
NK119(he)001:4937: 'du shes dang ldan pas longs spyod de /
NK119(he)001:4939: rgyags phyir ma lags snyems pa'i phyir ma lags //
NK119(he)001:4940: chags phyir ma lags lus gnas 'ba' zhig phyir //
NK119(he)001:4943: dkon mchog rjes dran mdo kha phud lhag ma dang bcas te longs spyod de /
NK119(he)001:4945: dang por lha la bshos gtsang 'bul //
NK119(he)001:4946: de rjes chos skyong bsrung ma la //
NK119(he)001:4947: gtor ma shin tu rgya chen bya //
NK119(he)001:4948: rang gis zos shing btung pa yi //
NK119(he)001:4949: lhag ma 'byung po rnams la byin //
NK119(he)001:4951: gsum pa gnas mal mtha' gnyis su ma lhung ba gnas mal gyi gzhi ni /
NK119(he)001:4952: gang du longs spyod par bya ba'i gnas mal gyi sgo khang du srid pa'i 'khor lo bri ste /
NK119(he)001:4953: mdo rtsa bar sgo khang du 'khor ba'i 'khor lo bri'o //
NK119(he)001:4955: steng du lha dang mi rnams so //
NK119(he)001:4957: de yang srin po'i gzugs kyi lto ba yangs pa bzlum por bskor ba'i dbus su /
NK119(he)001:4958: sbrul dug gsum ste kun 'byung mtshon /
NK119(he)001:4959: dang phug ron gyi mjug ma phag gis bzung pa bris /
NK119(he)001:4960: de rgyab steng du sum cha dang 'og tu gsum
NK119(he)001:4961: gnyis byas pa'i steng gi dum bu gnyis byas la
NK119(he)001:4962: gcig la lha dang lha min gcig la mi bri
NK119(he)001:4963: 'og ma cha gsum byas pa'i dbus ma dmyal ba
NK119(he)001:4964: / g.yas g.yon du yi dwags dang dud 'gro bri /
NK119(he)001:4965: de'i rgyab cha bcu gsum la ma rig pa sdug bsngal bden pa mtshon /
NK119(he)001:4966: rgan mo long ma lta bu /
NK119(he)001:4968: rnam par shes pa spre'u lta bu /
NK119(he)001:4969: ming gzugs grur brag phug stong pa'i ri bong lta bu zhes dga' ldan pa rnams gsungs so //
NK119(he)001:4970: zhugs pa lta bu skye mched drug grong stong lta bu /
NK119(he)001:4971: reg pa skyes bu phan tshun reg pa lta bu /
NK119(he)001:4972: tshor ba mig la mda' zug pa lta bu /
NK119(he)001:4973: sred pa chang 'thung ba lta bu /
NK119(he)001:4974: len pa spre'usa shing thog len pa lta bu /
NK119(he)001:4975: srid pa bya sgo nga la gab pa lta bu /
NK119(he)001:4976: skye ba skye bzhin pa lta bu /
NK119(he)001:4977: rgas pa 'khar ba la brten pa lta bu /
NK119(he)001:4978: shi ba ni shi ba'i ro lta bu bri'o //
NK119(he)001:4979: de ltar srid pa'i 'khor lo cha lnga pa'i steng nas /
NK119(he)001:4982: sangs rgyas bstan la 'jug par bya //
NK119(he)001:4983: 'dam bu'i khyim la glang chen bzhin //
NK119(he)001:4984: 'chi bdag sde ni gzhom par bya //
NK119(he)001:4987: 'khor lo dkar po sangs rgyas 'gog pa'i bden pa mtshon /
NK119(he)001:4988: bzheng thabs can bris 'dug kyi phyag gis nye bar ston pa bri'o //
NK119(he)001:4989: srid pa'i 'khor lo la rab gnas mi dgos par mkhas pa rnams bzhed do //
NK119(he)001:4990: gsum pa kun la thun mong du mkho ba las kyi gzhi la'ang /
NK119(he)001:4991: dge 'dun dang 'brel pa'i las dngos dang /
