NK119(he)001:4992: zhar byung gang zag dang 'brel pa'i las kyi rnam bzhag mang na'ang /
NK119(he)001:4993: 'dir dge slong gis bya ba'i las rigs la brgya rtsa gcig yod de /
NK119(he)001:4994: gsol ba 'ba' zhig pa'i las nyer bzhi /
NK119(he)001:4995: gsol ba dang gnyis kyi las zhe bdun /
NK119(he)001:4996: gsol ba dang bzhi'i las sum cu'o //
NK119(he)001:4999: gsang dang nang du dri phyir dang //
NK119(he)001:5000: gso sbyong de la ltung bcas dang //
NK119(he)001:5001: de la dge 'dun yid gnyis dang //
NK119(he)001:5002: rtsod dang nges nyid ma yin dang //
NK119(he)001:5003: de yi don du lnga po dag /
NK119(he)001:5004: thams cad dgag dbyer gtogs pa yin //
NK119(he)001:5005: dbyar gnas khas blangs nyid dang ni //
NK119(he)001:5006: shi ba'i rdzas dang nor 'dra dang //
NK119(he)001:5007: chos gos sra brkyang gtad pa dang //
NK119(he)001:5008: chos gos sbyin par bya ba dang //
NK119(he)001:5009: gnas ngan len ni brjod pa dang //
NK119(he)001:5010: grangs su bzhugs pa bzhi zhal ta ba la bshes ngor 'phya ba /
NK119(he)001:5012: bsgo ba'i tshig gis gzhan rna la gzon pa /
NK119(he)001:5013: ci yang mi smra bas gzhan rna la gzon pa ste /
NK119(he)001:5014: ngan pa'i grangs su bzhugs pa'i las bzhi'o //
NK119(he)001:5016: khyim gyi sdom dang de gzhi dang //
NK119(he)001:5017: lhung bzed kha sbub bya ba dang //
NK119(he)001:5018: de nyid bzlog par bya ba dang //
NK119(he)001:5019: gsol ba 'ba' zhig las yin no //
NK119(he)001:5022: gnas dang mtshams ni gnyis po dang //
NK119(he)001:5023: mi 'bral myos dang dmag dbye dang //
NK119(he)001:5024: gnas mal stob par byed pa dang //
NK119(he)001:5025: rung ba'i sa gzhi rko ba dang //
NK119(he)001:5026: sra rkyang dang ni de 'ding dang //
NK119(he)001:5027: spang dang lag gi bla dang ni //
NK119(he)001:5028: gnas khang bsko la sogs pa dang //
NK119(he)001:5029: gzu dang gsal dang sbed pa dang //
NK119(he)001:5030: tshul shing 'brim par byed pa dang //
NK119(he)001:5031: khang pa khang chen bstan pa dang //
NK119(he)001:5033: stan dang lhung bzed 'brim pa dang //
NK119(he)001:5034: ma dad go bar bya ba dang //
NK119(he)001:5035: ston pa dang ni nags nyul dang //
NK119(he)001:5036: phyag mi bya dang mang phyir dang //
NK119(he)001:5037: mkhar ba dra ba'i phyir dang ni //
NK119(he)001:5038: rnyed pa gcig tu bya phyir dang //
NK119(he)001:5039: bslab pa sbyin dang nye gnas dang //
NK119(he)001:5040: bu dang nye du phyir 'gro ba //
NK119(he)001:5041: gsol dang gnyis kyi las yin no //
NK119(he)001:5044: bsnyen par rdzogs par bya ba dang //
NK119(he)001:5045: mu stegs gnas dang mtshams grol dang //
NK119(he)001:5046: mthun pa'i gso sbyong sbyin la sogs gso sbyong bdun po dang //
NK119(he)001:5049: spo ba dpyad nas rang bzhin gyi gnas su dbyung ba /
NK119(he)001:5050: sra rkyang dbyung ba ste brgyad do //
NK119(he)001:5051: dang dran dang ma myos dang //
NK119(he)001:5052: de nyid tshol du bzhugs bsko bar bya ba mi
NK119(he)001:5053: mthun pa'i las bcu gcig ste dge 'dun dbyen dang
NK119(he)001:5062: sdig ldan dge tshul bsnyil mi'i las so //
NK119(he)001:5064: bsgo bar bya ba rnams dang ni //
NK119(he)001:5065: nyams pa sbyin par bya ba ste //
NK119(he)001:5066: gsol dang bzhi'i las yin no //
NK119(he)001:5068: sgrub pa'i bslab bya 'di dag phra zhing rgya che
NK119(he)001:5069: bas 'dir ni sa bon tsam du bsdus te rgyas
NK119(he)001:5070: par gzhan nas khums par byos shig /
NK119(he)001:5071: gnyis pa gnang bkag gi don mdor bstan pa ni /
NK119(he)001:5072: mdor na ye nas gnang dang bkag pa med //
NK119(he)001:5073: byar rung dang nye mi rung ldog byed na //
NK119(he)001:5074: de dag spyod cing mi rung dang nye zhing //
NK119(he)001:5075: rung ba ldog na kun tu spangs zhes gsungs //
NK119(he)001:5076: de la rje 'bri gung pa la sogs kha cig /
NK119(he)001:5077: gnang ba thams cad ye nas gnang ba dang /
NK119(he)001:5078: bkag pa thams cad ye nas bkag pa yin zhes gsungs kyang /
NK119(he)001:5080: rje sa pan gyis sdom gsum rab dbyer /
NK119(he)001:5081: ye bkag ye gnang zhes bya ba //
NK119(he)001:5082: sangs rgyas bstan dang mthun pa min //
NK119(he)001:5083: nyan thos dang ni theg chen gyi //
NK119(he)001:5084: gnang bkag thams cad gcig tu med //
NK119(he)001:5085: des na la la'i gnang ba ni //
NK119(he)001:5086: la la'i bkag pa nyid du 'gyur //
NK119(he)001:5088: nyan thos rtsa ba'i sde bzhi gyes pa bco brgyad
NK119(he)001:5089: 'di dag gi gnang bkag mi 'dra ba re re
NK119(he)001:5090: yod de / ye nas bkag pa dang gnang ba
NK119(he)001:5091: yin na gcig gi sdom pa gcig gi ltung bar
NK119(he)001:5092: yod de / 'gyur te / dper na yod smras mdo legs sbyar nas 'don pa la /
NK119(he)001:5093: gnas brtan pas legs sbyar du 'don na ltung bar 'gyur la /
NK119(he)001:5094: yod smras smin spu bzhar na ltung bar gsungs la /
NK119(he)001:5095: sde pa gzhan 'ga' ma bzhar na ltung bar gsungs pas /
NK119(he)001:5097: bu ram phyi dro'i kha zas ye gnang yin na sde pa gzhan ltung bar 'gyur la /
NK119(he)001:5098: ye bkag yin na yod smra'i dge slong ltung ba can du 'gyur bar gsungs pas /
NK119(he)001:5099: des na gang du dgos pa chen po'i don la
NK119(he)001:5100: sogs par spyod du rung ba dang phyogs nye zhing
NK119(he)001:5101: mi rung ba de las ldog par 'dug na spyod
NK119(he)001:5102: cing / mi rung ba dang nye rung ba las
NK119(he)001:5103: ldog par snang na rtsam pa thams cad du spang
NK119(he)001:5104: cing / bar rigs te / mdo rtsa las /
NK119(he)001:5105: mi rung ba dang mthun la rung ba dang 'gal ba ni rung ba ma yin par bsdu'o //
NK119(he)001:5106: phyi ma dang mthun la snga ma dang 'gal ba ni rung bar ro //
NK119(he)001:5108: gsum pa zhar la sdom pa'i rten bshad pa /
NK119(he)001:5109: skye ba'i rten ni mu stegs mtshams med byas //
NK119(he)001:5110: sgra mi snyan dang za ma'i ched du len //
NK119(he)001:5111: ma ning rigs lnga mtshan gsum 'gyur ba dang //
NK119(he)001:5112: sprul pa ma gtogs gling gsum skyes pa yii //
NK119(he)001:5113: skyes pa bud med sdom pa'i rten du 'dod //
NK119(he)001:5114: de dag ni sngar bshad zin cing /
NK119(he)001:5115: mtshams med lnga dang nye ba lnga ni ma bsad
NK119(he)001:5116: pa de dang nye ba dge slong ma sun phyung
NK119(he)001:5118: de dang nye ba byang chub sems dpa' gsod pa /
NK119(he)001:5120: de dang nye ba slob pa rgyun zhugs gsod pa /
NK119(he)001:5122: de dang nye ba dge 'dun gyi sgo 'phrog pa /
NK119(he)001:5123: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku la ngan sems kyi khrag phyung pa /
NK119(he)001:5124: de dang nye ba mchod rten bshig pa'o //
NK119(he)001:5125: gzhan ni go bar sla ba nyid do //
NK119(he)001:5126: spyi don bzhi pa tha ma nyams na gso ba'i tshul bshad pa la gsum /
NK119(he)001:5130: dang po la spyi dang bye brag go //
NK119(he)001:5132: gtong ba bslab pa phul dang shi 'phos dang //
NK119(he)001:5133: mtshan gnyis gcig char byung dang lan gsum 'gyur //
NK119(he)001:5134: rgyu 'bras med ltas rtsa ba chad rnams lci //
NK119(he)001:5135: so thar gyi sdom pa de /
NK119(he)001:5136: bslab pa phul bas gtong ste /
NK119(he)001:5137: sdom pa'i mi mthun phyogs khas blangs pa'i phyir /
NK119(he)001:5138: shi 'phos pas gtong ste khas blangs las dus 'das pa'i phyir /
NK119(he)001:5139: mtshan gnyis gcig char byung ba dang /
NK119(he)001:5142: rgyu 'bras med par lta ba'i log lta byung na gtong ste /
NK119(he)001:5143: sdom rten gyi rtsa ba chad pa'i phyir te /
NK119(he)001:5147: gnyis pa bye brag gi gtong mtshams ni /
NK119(he)001:5148: nyi shu ma lon bsnyen rdzogs rjes su shes //
NK119(he)001:5149: dge slong sdom gtong brten phyir khas blangs 'das //
NK119(he)001:5150: dge slob ma'o mtshan 'das bsnyen gnas kyi //
NK119(he)001:5151: sdom pa gtong rnams so so'i thun mong min //
NK119(he)001:5152: bsnyen rdzogs byed pa la bsgrub bya lo nyi shu
NK119(he)001:5153: lon pa'am lon pa'i 'du shes yod dgos pa la
NK119(he)001:5154: / kha cig gis lo nyi shu lon pa'i 'du shes kyi sgo nas bsnyen rdzogs blangs /
NK119(he)001:5155: phyis nyi shu ma lon par shes tshe /
NK119(he)001:5156: mngal gyi zla ba dang shol zlas kha bskang bas nyi shu tshang na bsnyen rdzogs mi gtong la /
NK119(he)001:5157: ma tshang na dge tshul du 'gyur te /
NK119(he)001:5158: 'dul ba tshig le'ura byas pa las /
NK119(he)001:5159: gang de nyi shu ma lon pa'i //
NK119(he)001:5160: lo yis bsnyen pa rdzogs gyur na //
NK119(he)001:5161: zla shol mngal gyi zla rnams kyis //
NK119(he)001:5162: mkhas pa yis ni dgang bar bya //
NK119(he)001:5163: gal te de ltar na yang 'di //
NK119(he)001:5164: lo ni nyi shu ma lon na //
NK119(he)001:5165: dge tshul nyid du gnas 'gyur gyi //
NK119(he)001:5166: de ni bsnyen par rdzogs min nyid //
NK119(he)001:5168: khas blangs las 'das pas dge slob ma'i sdom pa gtong la /
NK119(he)001:5169: mtshan mo'i skad cig ma 'das pas bsnyen gnas gtong ste /
NK119(he)001:5170: nyin mtshan gyi mtha' can yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK119(he)001:5172: rtsa ltung byung dang dam chos nub na'ang gtong //
NK119(he)001:5173: kha che'i yul gyi bye brag smra ba rnams //
NK119(he)001:5174: sdom ldan rtsa ltung byung ba gnyis ldan na //
NK119(he)001:5175: nor ldan bu lon can bzhin 'dod pa dang //
NK119(he)001:5176: de la mdo sde pa na re /
NK119(he)001:5177: rtsa ltung 'chab bcas byung na gtong ste /
NK119(he)001:5178: de ngo tsha dang khrel med kyis gsang ba'i phyir /
NK119(he)001:5179: gos dmar ba'i sde pa na re /
NK119(he)001:5180: lung gi chos nub pas gtong ste /
NK119(he)001:5181: de tshe bslab pa'i mtshams rnam par bzhag pa med pa'i phyir /
NK119(he)001:5183: lung gi chos nub pa tsam gyis sdom pa sngar yod mi gtong ste /
NK119(he)001:5184: lung gi chos med kyang rtogs pa'i chos ma nus pa'i phyir /
NK119(he)001:5185: 'on kyang de tshe sdom pa sngar med gsar du mi skye ste /
NK119(he)001:5186: sdom pa 'bog pa'i cho ga'i rnam bzhag med pa'i phyir /
NK119(he)001:5188: kha che bye brag tu smra ba na re /
NK119(he)001:5189: rtsa ltung 'chab bcas byung ba'i dge slong de tshul
NK119(he)001:5190: khrims dang ldan pa dang 'chab pa gang yang yin
NK119(he)001:5191: te / sdom pa'i rdzas rang rgyud la tshang bar yod pa dang /
NK119(he)001:5192: sems rgyud la rtsa ltung 'chab bcas kyi gso ba'i phyir /
NK119(he)001:5194: mi zhig la nor yang yod /
NK119(he)001:5195: bu lon yang yod pa bzhin no //
NK119(he)001:5198: kha cig ltung bar 'gyur las smad //
NK119(he)001:5199: gzhan dag dam chos nub pa las //
NK119(he)001:5200: kha che rnams ni byung ba la //
NK119(he)001:5201: bu lon nor bzhin gnyis su 'dod //
NK119(he)001:5203: gzhan yang kha cig rtsa bzhi gcig spyod kun nyams zer /
NK119(he)001:5204: dang po'i las can sems 'khrug 'tshor bas gzir /
NK119(he)001:5205: bsgrub par ma nus pa nyes pa med /
NK119(he)001:5207: rtsa ba bzhi po gang rung gcig spyad na kun shor ba yin zhe'o //
NK119(he)001:5209: phyogs gcig blangs pas thams cad blangs par mi 'gyur la /
NK119(he)001:5210: phyogs gcig btang bas thams cad btang bar mi 'gyur ro //
NK119(he)001:5212: gzhan yang las dang po pa gnang bkag gi mtshams
NK119(he)001:5213: ma phyed cing sems 'khrug pas bsgrub par ma nus
NK119(he)001:5214: pa la nyes pa med ces bshad do //
NK119(he)001:5215: 'chab pa zhes grags gsang ste mi brjod pa //
NK119(he)001:5216: pham pa 'chab bcas tshe 'dir gsor mi rung //
NK119(he)001:5217: rtsa ba pham pa gsod rku rdzun dang mi tshangs
NK119(he)001:5218: spyod bzhi 'chab pa byung na gsor mi rung ste
NK119(he)001:5219: / rgyud ngo tsha khrel med kyis gang ba'i phyir /
NK119(he)001:5221: des de byas ma thag tu dge slong du mi rung //
NK119(he)001:5222: dge sbyong du mi rung ngo //
NK119(he)001:5223: sh+aakya'i sras ni mi rung ngo //
NK119(he)001:5224: dge slong gi dngos po las nyams pa /
NK119(he)001:5228: de'i dge slong gi tshul phyis blang du med par 'gyur ro //
NK119(he)001:5229: dper na shing ta la'i mgo bcad na sngon por rgyas par mi 'gyur ba bzhin no //
NK119(he)001:5231: gnyis pa bshags shing gso ba'i tshul la'ang /
NK119(he)001:5232: bshags tshul spyir bstan pa dang /
NK119(he)001:5233: bye brag stobs bzhi'i bshags tshul gnyis las /
NK119(he)001:5235: ltung ba gang zhig 'chab pa med na dngos po brjod pa yis //
NK119(he)001:5236: dge 'dun la bshags mthong sdom bar gyis 'dag /
NK119(he)001:5237: sdom pa slar nod lhag ma bcu gsum sogs //
NK119(he)001:5238: lci yang la ltos bshags te rim par ldang //
NK119(he)001:5240: gal te sems ni gcig gis kyang //
NK119(he)001:5242: tha ma byung bar gyur na yang //
NK119(he)001:5243: de ni phal par mi 'gyur ro //
NK119(he)001:5245: dge 'dun la ltung ba gang yin gyi dngos po brjod de mi 'chab bo 'chag go byas nas /
NK119(he)001:5246: dge 'dun gyis khyod kyis de ltung bar mthong ngam slan chad sdom mam brjod de /
NK119(he)001:5248: sdom mo lan gsum byas te /
NK119(he)001:5249: pham pa bzhi la sdom pa slar nod /
NK119(he)001:5251: de las sor bshags kyi yang /
NK119(he)001:5252: de las nyes byas ni bshags bya tsam dang /
NK119(he)001:5253: yid kyis sdom bya tsam ste /
NK119(he)001:5254: lci yang gi rim pa ltar bshags pas 'dag go //
NK119(he)001:5255: gnyis pa stobs bzhi'i bshags tshul bye brag tu bstan pa ni /
NK119(he)001:5256: chos bzhi bstan pa'i mdo las /
NK119(he)001:5258: byang chub sems dpa' chos bzhi dang ldan na sdig
NK119(he)001:5259: pa byas shing bsags pa thams cad zil gyis gnon
NK119(he)001:5260: par 'gyur ro // bzhi gang zhe na 'di lta te /
NK119(he)001:5262: gnyen po kun tu spyod pa dang /
NK119(he)001:5265: de la dang pos ni mi dge ba'i las spyod na'ang de la 'gyod pa mang ba yin no //
NK119(he)001:5266: gnyis pa ni mi dge ba'i las byas kyang dge ba'i las la shin tu brtson pa yin no //
NK119(he)001:5267: gsum pa ni sdom pa yang dag par blang nas
NK119(he)001:5268: sdig pa mi byed pa'i sdom pa thob pa yin
NK119(he)001:5269: no // bzhi pa ni sangs rgyas dang /
NK119(he)001:5271: dge 'dun la skyabs su song ba dang byang chub kyi sems mi gtong ba yin no //
NK119(he)001:5273: mdor na stobs bzhir ma 'dus bshags pa med //
NK119(he)001:5274: sngar byas 'gyod bshags dug 'thung skyug pa ltar //
NK119(he)001:5275: 'gyod pa snying nas rnam par sun phyung stobs //
NK119(he)001:5276: de yang sngar byas kyi sdig pa la dug khong
NK119(he)001:5277: du song ba ltar 'gyod pa drag po snying nas
NK119(he)001:5278: bskyed de bshags pa gal che ste /
NK119(he)001:5279: sngon sor phreng can gyis mi stong du gcig ma
NK119(he)001:5280: tshang ba gsod pa sun 'byin gyi stobs nyams su
NK119(he)001:5281: blangs pas dgra bcom thob pa lta bu'o //
NK119(he)001:5282: dug la sman bzhin 'jug pa drag po yis //
NK119(he)001:5283: nyes phyir dge ba'i gnyen po kun spyod stobs //
NK119(he)001:5284: de yang nyes pa dug dang 'dra ba la dge ba sman ltar du bsten pas dag ste /
NK119(he)001:5286: gang gis sdig pa'i las byas pa //
NK119(he)001:5287: dge ba yis ni mthar byed de //
NK119(he)001:5288: nyi zla sprin las phyung ba bzhin //
NK119(he)001:5291: sngon khye'u bde byed bya ba ma bsad pa gcig
NK119(he)001:5292: gis gnyen po'i stobs bsten pas lhar skyes nas rgyun
NK119(he)001:5294: dug mi 'thung ltar phyi nas nyes sdom pa //
NK119(he)001:5295: nges shes drag po rnam par sor chud stobs //
NK119(he)001:5296: de yang phyis nas srog la bab kyang sdig pa
NK119(he)001:5297: mi byed pa dug mi 'thung ba ltar sdom ste
NK119(he)001:5300: 'dren pa rnams kyis bdag gi sdig /
NK119(he)001:5301: nongs pa legs par bzung du gsol //
NK119(he)001:5302: 'di ni bzang po ma lags pas //
NK119(he)001:5303: phyin chad bdag gis yongs mi bgyid //
NK119(he)001:5305: sngon gcung dga' bo zhes bud med la shin tu
NK119(he)001:5306: chags pa zhig yin kyang rnam par sor chud pa'i
NK119(he)001:5307: stobs nyams su blangs pas dgra bcom thob pa lta
NK119(he)001:5308: bu'o // sman pa bsten ltar skyabs sems ltung bshags sogs //
NK119(he)001:5309: dad pa drag po rten gyi stobs bzhi spyad //
NK119(he)001:5310: de yang dug la sman bsten pa ltar sdig pa'i
NK119(he)001:5311: gnyen por skyabs 'gro sems bskyed dad pa drag po
NK119(he)001:5312: bskyed dgos te / phag mo'i rtogs brjod las /
NK119(he)001:5313: gang dag sangs rgyas skyabs song ba //
NK119(he)001:5317: sdig pa stobs chen shin tu mi bzad pa //
NK119(he)001:5318: de ni rdzogs pa'i byang chub sems min pa //
NK119(he)001:5319: dge gzhan gang gis zil gyis gnon mi 'gyur //
NK119(he)001:5322: srid 'gro nyam ngar byis pa'i blo yis ni //
NK119(he)001:5323: shin tu mi bzad sdig pa gang bgyis pa //
NK119(he)001:5324: stobs bcu mnga' ba'i spyan sngar bdag mchis te //
NK119(he)001:5325: sdig pa de kun so sor bshags par bgyi //
NK119(he)001:5327: sngon rgyal bu mthong ldan bya ba pha gsod pa
NK119(he)001:5328: zhig gis rten gyi stobs nyams su blangs pas byang
NK119(he)001:5329: chub sems dpar gyur bar bshad do //
NK119(he)001:5332: gang zhig sngon chad bag med gyur pa las //
NK119(he)001:5333: phyis nas bag dang ldan par gyur te yang //
NK119(he)001:5334: zla ba sprin bral lta bur rnam mdzes te //
NK119(he)001:5335: dga' bo sor phreng mthong ldan bde byed bzhin //
NK119(he)001:5337: 'on kyang sdig ltung stobs ldan res spyod na //
NK119(he)001:5338: sa thob yun du 'gor bas mig ltar bsrung //
NK119(he)001:5339: de yang bcas pa'i kha na ma tho ba sdom pa'i zhig ral dang /
NK119(he)001:5340: rang bzhin gyi kha na ma tho ba mi dge
NK119(he)001:5341: bcu la spyad pas de dag gi las 'bras dang
NK119(he)001:5342: 'khor bar 'khor ba'i nyes dmigs sde snod rnams las
NK119(he)001:5343: rgya cher 'byung bas 'dir 'chad mi dgos la de
NK119(he)001:5344: phyir thar pa'i sa lam la sgrib par 'gyur bas
NK119(he)001:5345: mig ltar du bsrung ba gal che ste /
NK119(he)001:5347: de ltar ltung ba stobs ldan dang //
NK119(he)001:5348: byang chub sems stobs ldan pa dag /'khor ba res kyis 'gro byed na //
NK119(he)001:5349: sa thob pa la yun ring thogs //
NK119(he)001:5351: gnyis pa sdom pa'i phan yon la gnyis te /
NK119(he)001:5355: phan yon nad dang rgyal po'i chad phyir blangs //
NK119(he)001:5356: rkyen 'ga' sel yang 'jigs skyob tshul khrims yin //
NK119(he)001:5357: sdom pa blang pa la yang tshe 'di'i lto gos kyis phongs pa sel ba'i phyir dang /
NK119(he)001:5358: rgyal po'i chad pas 'jigs pa las sel phyir blangs kyang 'jigs skyobs kyi tshul khrims las /
NK119(he)001:5359: phyi ma'i ched blangs legs smon tshul khrims zhes //
NK119(he)001:5360: lha mi'i bde 'bras thob kyang thar pa min //
NK119(he)001:5361: rang nyid phyi ma lha mi'i bde 'bras thob par 'dod pas blangs na'ang /
NK119(he)001:5362: legs smon gyi tshul khrims tsam du 'gyur gyi thar
NK119(he)001:5363: pa thams cad mkhyen pa thob pa ma yin te
NK119(he)001:5365: kun dga' bos bram ze'i bu mo la mtho ris
NK119(he)001:5366: kyi yon tan skyabs su 'gro ba las byung ba'i
NK119(he)001:5367: tshul bshad pa / bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
NK119(he)001:5368: kun dga' bo de ni ma lags te srid pa'i
NK119(he)001:5369: bde ba gnyer ba de ni skyes bu ma rabs
NK119(he)001:5370: zhes bya'o // de bas na thar pa'i yon tan yang dag par sgrogs shig ces gsungs so //
NK119(he)001:5371: 'o na ci ltar yin zhe na /
NK119(he)001:5372: nges par 'byung ba'i tshul khrims sdom ldan na //
NK119(he)001:5373: dgra bcom thob pa dga' bo'i rnam thar bzhin //
NK119(he)001:5374: de yang 'khor ba'i nyes dmigs mthong nas spangs 'dod /
NK119(he)001:5375: thar pa'i phan yon mthong nas bsgrub 'dod kyi bsam
NK119(he)001:5376: pa dang ldan pa'i sgo nas byang chub don gnyer
NK119(he)001:5377: gyi nges 'byung bsam pas zin pa'i sdom pa dang
NK119(he)001:5378: ldan na / sngon gcung dga' bo rang gi chung
NK119(he)001:5379: ma la chags pa'i dbang gis gang ltar yang nges
NK119(he)001:5380: 'byung ba'i blos rab tu ma byung ba la bcom
NK119(he)001:5381: ldan 'das kyis rdzu 'phrul mngon par 'du mdzad de
NK119(he)001:5382: rigs drug gi bde sdug mngon du bstan pas 'khor
NK119(he)001:5383: ba las nges par 'byung ste rab tu byung ba
NK119(he)001:5384: la dgra bcom thob pa lta bu'o //
NK119(he)001:5385: gnyis pa khyad par gyi yon tan ni /
NK119(he)001:5387: skyabs gsum 'dzin sogs yon tan phyi ma mchog /
NK119(he)001:5388: snga ma phyi ma'i thun mong lam yin zhes //
NK119(he)001:5389: sems bskyed sngags kyi 'dul bya de dang mtshungs //
NK119(he)001:5390: de phyir yon tan kun gyi gzhi rten yin //
NK119(he)001:5391: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa'i gzhi mar gyur ba ni dam pa'i chos 'dul ba 'di yin zhing /
NK119(he)001:5392: de la'ang so sor thar pa rigs bdun po de'ang
NK119(he)001:5393: snga ma'i sdom pa de dag phyi ma'i sdom pa'i
NK119(he)001:5394: rten yin te / bsnyen par rdzogs pa'ang /
NK119(he)001:5395: thog mar skyabs gsum 'dzin pa'i dge bsnyen rim gyis 'jug dgos te /
NK119(he)001:5399: dge slong nyid dag gis snga ma ma byas pa la phyi ma mi bya'o //
NK119(he)001:5401: byang chub tu sems bskyed par 'dod pa des kyang
NK119(he)001:5402: dang po so sor thar gyi sdom pa thob dgos
NK119(he)001:5404: so sor thar pa rigs bdun gyi //
NK119(he)001:5405: rtag tu sdom brtson ldan pa la //
NK119(he)001:5406: byang chub sems dpa'i sems bskyed kyi //
NK119(he)001:5407: skal ba yod kyi gzhan du min //
NK119(he)001:5409: yang sngags kyi lam la zhugs par 'dod pa des
NK119(he)001:5410: kyang thog mar 'dul ba las rab tu byung dgos
NK119(he)001:5411: te / kri ya dpung bzang gi rgyud las /
NK119(he)001:5412: rgyal ba ngas gsungs so sor thar pa yi //
NK119(he)001:5413: tshul khrims rnam dag 'dul ba ma lus las //
NK119(he)001:5414: sngags pa khyim pas rtags dang cho ga spangs //
NK119(he)001:5415: lhag ma rnams ni nyams su blang bar bya //
NK119(he)001:5417: de'i steng du byang sems kyi bslab bya dang yang ldan pa dgos te /
NK119(he)001:5419: gang dag byang chub sems ni ma bskyed dang //
NK119(he)001:5420: gang dag rigs dang dbang bskur cho ga med //
NK119(he)001:5421: gang dag dkyil 'khor du ni ma zhugs pas //
NK119(he)001:5422: nga yi gsang sngags bzlas na phung bar 'gyur //
NK119(he)001:5424: gsang sngags nang rgyud la zhugs pa des kyang nges par dgos te /
NK119(he)001:5425: dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa'i skabs su so sor thar pa dang /
NK119(he)001:5426: byang sems kyi sdom pa bzung dgos pa'i phyir theg
NK119(he)001:5427: pa'i mthar thug rdzogs pa chen por zhugs pa des
NK119(he)001:5429: chos thams cad der ma 'dus pa'am /
NK119(he)001:5432: ma rdzogs pa med pas rdzogs pa chen po zhes bya ba dang /
NK119(he)001:5433: lam gyi cha lag yin pa'i phyir des na bstan
NK119(he)001:5434: pa'i gzhi ma ni 'dul ba'i tshul khrims yin pas
NK119(he)001:5435: / mgon po klu sgrub snying po'i zhal snga nas /
NK119(he)001:5436: khrims ni rgyu dang mi rgyu'i sa bzhin du //
NK119(he)001:5437: yon tan kun gyi gzhi rten thub pas gsungs //
NK119(he)001:5439: de la deng sang kha cig gsang sngags bla med
NK119(he)001:5440: tu khas blangs te theg pa chung ngu'i chos so
NK119(he)001:5441: // zhes 'dul ba la rtog dpyod tsam yang mi
NK119(he)001:5442: gtong bar ce re long du song pa ni blo
NK119(he)001:5444: slob dpon chen po pad ma 'byung gnas kyang kun
NK119(he)001:5445: dga' bo las rab tu byung ba nas mthar grub
NK119(he)001:5446: thob rnal 'byor gyi dbang du gyur pa sogs /
NK119(he)001:5448: bod kyi snga dar phyi dar gyi gsar rnying thams
NK119(he)001:5449: cad kyis 'dul ba la gces spras mi mdzad pa
NK119(he)001:5450: med cing / dam chos 'dul ba med na sangs rgyas bstan pa med //
NK119(he)001:5452: bstan pa'i gzhi ma yin pas 'dul ba slob //
NK119(he)001:5454: gzhan gnod gzhi bcas rab spangs skabs gsum lam //
NK119(he)001:5455: rigs bdun so thar chu 'dzin lhun 'thug pa //
NK119(he)001:5456: spangs dang sgrub pa'i chu bsil 'phro ba yis //
NK119(he)001:5457: skye dgu'i nyon mongs me tshogs gzhil bar shog /
NK119(he)001:5458: sangs rgyas bstan pa'i gser gzhi las byung zhing //
NK119(he)001:5459: mngon mtho nges legs rgya mtsho'i dbus na brjid //
NK119(he)001:5460: ldan dang grol ba'i nyi zla'i ska rags can //
NK119(he)001:5461: tshul khrims rin chen lhun po thob par shog /
NK119(he)001:5462: nyes tshogs rdul gyi mig sman rab dben zhing //
NK119(he)001:5463: spangs rtogs phun tshogs 'od stong mthar khyab pas //
NK119(he)001:5464: rgyal bstan sbrang rtsi'i khang bzang rab rgyas nas //
NK119(he)001:5465: gling bzhi'i 'gro kun gsal ba'i dpal 'bar shog /
NK119(he)001:5466: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i lam gyi cha lag
NK119(he)001:5467: sdom pa gsum rnam par nges pa'i 'grel pa rnam
NK119(he)001:5469: 'dul ba so thar gyi rnam par dbye ba ste /
NK119(he)001:5470: rim par phye ba gnyis pa gtan la dbab zin to //
NK119(he)001:5471: da ni rim par phye ba gsum pa byang chub
NK119(he)001:5472: sems dpa'i sems bskyed kyi bslab pa rnam par dbye
NK119(he)001:5474: byang sems kyi bslab pa'i gleng gzhi /
NK119(he)001:5475: thog mar sdom pa thob tshul /
NK119(he)001:5477: tha ma nyams na gso tshul lo //
NK119(he)001:5479: ston pa byon cing chos gsungs tshul /
NK119(he)001:5480: de'i bstan pa shing rta'i srol gnyis kyi rnam bzhag /
NK119(he)001:5482: de'i dbye ba dang bzhi las /
NK119(he)001:5484: byang sems kyi bslab pa'i gleng gzhi /
NK119(he)001:5485: skal bzang 'gro ba'i 'dren pa thub chen des //
NK119(he)001:5486: bya rgod phung sogs theg chen rigs rnams la //
NK119(he)001:5487: shin tu rgyas pa'i sde snod dpag yas gsungs //
NK119(he)001:5488: de la theg chen thun mong pa ltar na /
NK119(he)001:5489: bdag cag gi ston pa 'dis bskal pa grangs med
NK119(he)001:5490: gsum gyi gong du de bzhin gshegs pa thub pa
NK119(he)001:5491: chen po las sems bskyed nas grangs med gsum du
NK119(he)001:5492: tshogs bsags nas mthar 'og min du sangs rgyas te
NK119(he)001:5493: sprul pas mdzad pa bcu gnyis bstan nas don mdzad
NK119(he)001:5494: par 'dod de / chos dang longs spyod mngon par sangs rgyas pa'i mdo las /
NK119(he)001:5495: rin chen sna tshogs mdzes pa yis //
NK119(he)001:5496: 'og min gnas ni nyams dga' bar //
NK119(he)001:5497: gtsang ma'i gnas kyi steng bzhugs te //
NK119(he)001:5498: yang dag sangs rgyas der sangs rgyas //
NK119(he)001:5499: sprul pa po zhig 'dir sangs rgyas //
NK119(he)001:5501: theg chen thun mong ma yin pa ltar na /
NK119(he)001:5502: bskal pa grangs med bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i gong rol du sangs rgyas nas /
NK119(he)001:5503: slar yang gdul bya'i don du sems bskyed tshogs bsags
NK119(he)001:5504: mdzad pa bcu gnyis kyi tshul ston par mdzad pa
NK119(he)001:5505: ni / yab sras mjal ba'i mdo las /
NK119(he)001:5506: sngon 'das pa'i dus bskal pa dpag tu med pa'i
NK119(he)001:5507: gong rol du 'jig rten gyi khams gang g+aa'i klung
NK119(he)001:5508: gi bye ma snyed kyi zhing gcig tu gyur pa
NK119(he)001:5509: der / de bzhin gshegs pa dbang po'i tog ces bya bar sangs rgyas nas don mdzad de /
NK119(he)001:5511: dpa' bo chen po thabs mkhas che //
NK119(he)001:5512: sems can yongs su smin mdzad phyir //
NK119(he)001:5513: bye ba phrag brgyar rgyal ba nyid //
NK119(he)001:5514: sangs rgyas nyid du bstan gyur kyang //
NK119(he)001:5515: da dung du yang 'dren pa khyod //
NK119(he)001:5516: sangs rgyas mang po bstan par mdzad //
NK119(he)001:5520: nga ni bskal ba bye ba phrag khrig brgya phrag
NK119(he)001:5521: mang po'i gong rol du mngon par rdzogs par sangs
NK119(he)001:5523: bskal pa bye stong bsam gyis mi khyab pa //
NK119(he)001:5524: de yi tshad ni nam yang med pas na //
NK119(he)001:5525: byang chub mchog rab 'di ni ngas thob ste //
NK119(he)001:5526: ngas ni rtag tu chos kyang rab 'chad do //
NK119(he)001:5529: 'pho dang lhums zhugs bltams pa dang //
NK119(he)001:5530: bzo dang rol rtsed nges 'byung dang //
NK119(he)001:5531: bka' spyod drung gshegs bdud sde bcom //
NK119(he)001:5534: de la chos kyi 'khor lo ji ltar bskor zhe na /
NK119(he)001:5535: gnas phun sum tshogs pa bya rgod phung po'i ri bo la sogs par /
NK119(he)001:5536: ston pa phun sum tshogs pa sh+aakya thub pas /
NK119(he)001:5537: 'khor phun sum tshogs pa thun mong gi 'khor rnam pa bzhi la /
NK119(he)001:5538: sh+aa ri'i bu dang mo'u 'gal gyi bu la sogs par dgra bcom lnga stong tsam dang /
NK119(he)001:5539: skye dgu'i bdag mo la sogs dge slong ma lnga brgya tsam dang /
NK119(he)001:5540: khyim bdag mgon med zas sbyin dang /
NK119(he)001:5541: dge bsnyen ma sa ga bzang mo la sogs dge bsnyen pho mo dang /
NK119(he)001:5542: lha klu dri za la sogs rab tu mang po dang /
NK119(he)001:5543: thun mong min pa'i 'khor sa thob pa'i byang chub sems dpa' bzang skyong dang /
NK119(he)001:5545: dra bas byin la sogs pa la /
NK119(he)001:5546: chos phun sum tshogs pa bka' bar pa mtshan nyid
NK119(he)001:5547: med pa'i chos kyi rnam grangs yum sras bcu bdun
NK119(he)001:5548: la sogs pa / dus phun sum tshogs pa dgung
NK119(he)001:5549: lo bzhi bcu zhe gsum nas bdun cu rtsa gnyis
NK119(he)001:5551: de'ang mdo sde'i sde snod gtso bor sems kyi bslab pa ston pa las /
NK119(he)001:5552: mdo sde'i 'dul ba byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pa'i tshogs rnam par bzhag pa dang /
NK119(he)001:5553: mdo sde'i mdo sde ting nge 'dzin zab cing rgya che ba dang /
NK119(he)001:5554: mdo sde'i mngon pa sa lam gzungs dang ting nge 'dzin gyi rab dbye ji snyed pa rnams so //
NK119(he)001:5558: stong phrag nyi shu lnga pa /
NK119(he)001:5559: khri brgyad stong pa ste rgyas pa skor gsum /
NK119(he)001:5562: sdud pa ste bsdus pa skor gsum mo //
NK119(he)001:5569: rab stsal rnam gnon gyis zhus pa /
NK119(he)001:5575: yang mdo sde che gsum zhes /
NK119(he)001:5580: de yang byang sems kyi skabs su don dam pa'i sems /
NK119(he)001:5581: sems bskyed kyi rtsa bar gyur pa stong nyid snying
NK119(he)001:5582: rje'i rang bzhin rigs sam khams bde bar gshegs pa'i
NK119(he)001:5583: snying po mngon du gsal ba ni bka' tha ma
NK119(he)001:5584: don dam rnam par nges pa'i chos yin te /
NK119(he)001:5585: de yang 'phags pa gzungs kyi dbang phyug rgyal pos zhus pa'i mdo dang /
NK119(he)001:5586: dpal phreng seng ge'i nga ro sgras zhus pa'i mdo dang /
NK119(he)001:5587: bu mo rin chen gyis zhus pa'i mdo dang /
NK119(he)001:5588: lha mo dri ma med pas zhus pa'i mdo dang /
NK119(he)001:5589: mi'u thung sor phreng can gyi mdo dang /
NK119(he)001:5590: mya ngan las 'das pa'i mdo dang /
NK119(he)001:5591: byams pas zhus pa'i mdo dang /
NK119(he)001:5592: de bzhin gshegs pa'i snying po'i mdo la sogs pa ste /
NK119(he)001:5593: 'di dag gi rnam grangs rgyas par bka' 'gyur gyi dkar chag las rtogs par bya'o //
NK119(he)001:5595: de'i bstan pa shing rta'i srol gnyis kyi rnam bzhag bstan pa ni /
NK119(he)001:5596: de ltar ston pa 'das nas byang chub sems dpa'i sde snod de dag ji ltar bsdus na /
NK119(he)001:5597: kha cig rgya gar gyi lho phyogs b+hi ma sam+b+ha
NK119(he)001:5598: zhes bya ba'i ri la byams pa dang 'jam dbyangs
NK119(he)001:5599: la sogs pa dbang thob pa'i sems dpa' du ma
NK119(he)001:5601: rigs sngags 'chang ba ji snyed pa 'dus nas theg
NK119(he)001:5602: pa chen po sngags dang pha rol du phyin pa
NK119(he)001:5603: gnyis ka bsdu bar bshad pa yang yod la /
NK119(he)001:5604: 'di ni bsdu ba rnam pa gsum gyi dus 'jam dbyangs kyis bsdus pa dbu ma dang /
NK119(he)001:5605: byams pas bsdus pa sems tsam ste srol gnyis las /
NK119(he)001:5607: ston pas gsungs pa'i byang chub sems dpa'i sde snod
NK119(he)001:5608: de dag /'jam dbyangs bka' bsdus klu sgrub sogs kyis
NK119(he)001:5609: bkral // zhi ba lhas spel zab mo lta ba'i lugs //
NK119(he)001:5610: de yang sangs rgyas 'das nas lo bzhi brgya na rgya gar lho phyogs /
NK119(he)001:5611: bee ta'i yul du slob dpon klu sgrub snying po
NK119(he)001:5612: byon te bka' dang po'i 'grel pa gtam gyi tshogs
NK119(he)001:5613: dang / bar ba'i 'grel pa rigs pa'i tshogs dang /
NK119(he)001:5614: tha ma'i 'grel pa bstod pa'i tshogs dang /
NK119(he)001:5615: gzhan yang bshes spring dang mdo kun las btus pa la sogs pa du ma mdzad do //
NK119(he)001:5616: de'i rjes su slob dpon zhi ba lha byon nas
NK119(he)001:5617: byang chub sems dpa'i spyod pa la 'jug pa dang
NK119(he)001:5618: / bslab btus la sogs pa du ma mdzad nas
NK119(he)001:5619: zab mo lta ba'i lugs kyi shing rta'i srol chen
NK119(he)001:5624: klu'i rgyal po rgya mtshos zhus pa'i mdo dang /
NK119(he)001:5626: sangs rgyas kyis yang dag par sdud pa dang /
NK119(he)001:5627: ye shes snang ba rgyan gyi mdo dang /
NK119(he)001:5628: bden pa gnyis la 'jug pa dang /
NK119(he)001:5629: dkon mchog za ma tog dang /
NK119(he)001:5630: yum sras bcu bdun la sogs bar pa mtshan nyid med pa'i chos kyi rnam grangs rnams yin no //
NK119(he)001:5631: zhes mkhas grub ye shes rgyal mtshan pas gsang snying 'grel par bshad do //
NK119(he)001:5632: de yang dbu ma'i lugs zab mo lta ba'i rgyud pa rang la ji ltar brgyud zhe na /
NK119(he)001:5644: byang sems zla ba rgyal mtshan /
NK119(he)001:5645: gro lung pa chen po blo gros byang chub /
NK119(he)001:5646: spyi bo lhas pa byang chub 'od /
NK119(he)001:5649: mkhan po smon lam tshul khrims /
NK119(he)001:5651: slob dpon gzhon nu rdo rje /
NK119(he)001:5659: sprul sku sna tshogs rang grol /
NK119(he)001:5661: rgyal sras pad ma phrin las /
NK119(he)001:5662: kun mkhyen tshul khrims rdo rje /
NK119(he)001:5663: des rab 'byams pa pad ma blo gros la'o //
NK119(he)001:5664: gnyis pa rgya chen spyod pa'i srol ni /
NK119(he)001:5666: byams pas bka' bsdus thogs med sku mched bkral //
NK119(he)001:5667: jo bo rjes spel rgya chen spyod pa'i srol //
NK119(he)001:5668: sangs rgyas kyi bka' de dag byams pas bsdus te
NK119(he)001:5669: gnas pa na sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa la phyi
NK119(he)001:5670: pa'i dgra lan gsum byung nas shin tu nyams smas
NK119(he)001:5671: pa na / 'das lo dgu brgya lhag stong du nye ba na /
NK119(he)001:5672: dge slong ma gsal ba'i tshul khrims bya ba des /
NK119(he)001:5673: rang ni rten bud med du song bas sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa gso bar mi nus te /
NK119(he)001:5675: rgyal rigs gcig dang bsdongs pas slob dpon thogs med dang /
NK119(he)001:5676: bram ze zhig dang bshos pas dbyig gnyen 'khrungs te /
NK119(he)001:5677: thogs med kyis lo bcu gnyis su mgon po byams
NK119(he)001:5678: pa bsgrubs nas grub te dga' ldan gyi gnas su
NK119(he)001:5679: lha'i dro skad cig mi'i lo lnga bcur bzhugs nas
NK119(he)001:5681: 'byed gnyis theg pa chen po'i rgyud bla ma dang lnga /
NK119(he)001:5682: sdom pa rnam pa gnyis la sogs byams pa dang 'brel ba'i chos nyi shu dang /
NK119(he)001:5684: mngon pa kun btus la sogs mdzad do //
NK119(he)001:5685: dbyig gnyen gyis de dag gi 'grel tika du ma dang /
NK119(he)001:5688: rnam bshad rig pa la sogs mdzad do //
NK119(he)001:5689: phyis na jo bo rje dpal a ti sha zhes sam di pam ka ra byung nas /
NK119(he)001:5691: des byang chub lam rim dang spyod bsdus sgron ma la sogs pa dang /
NK119(he)001:5692: mdo kun btus zer ba zhig kyang mdzad de sems
NK119(he)001:5693: tsam gyi gzhung rgya chen spyod pa'i srol rgyas par
NK119(he)001:5699: rgyan stug po bkod pa la sogs pa bka' tha
NK119(he)001:5700: ma don dam nges pa ste chos mngon pa'i gsung
NK119(he)001:5701: rab rnams yin no zhes ye shes rgyal mtshan gsung
NK119(he)001:5702: ngo // de'i sdom rgyun gang zhe na /
NK119(he)001:5725: chu mig pa seng ge dpal /
NK119(he)001:5727: btsan dgon pa dang dben dge ba gnyis /
NK119(he)001:5728: de gnyis la bla brang ba chos dpal rgyal mtshan /
NK119(he)001:5729: kun mkhyen klong chen rab 'byams man gong bzhin no //
NK119(he)001:5731: gsang sngags gter ma la sogs pa nas sems bskyed
NK119(he)001:5732: blangs pa 'di dag srol gnyis gang gi lugs su
NK119(he)001:5733: 'du zhe na / bdag cag gi ston pa rig 'dzin chen po /
NK119(he)001:5734: pad ma'i ring lugs n+aa ga rdzu nar mthun /
NK119(he)001:5736: zab mo lta brgyud dang mthun te brgyud pa ni
NK119(he)001:5737: gter chos rang rang gi mtshams nas brgyud par shes
NK119(he)001:5738: so // 'di ni theg pa thun mong pa kun dang go bstun te 'chad pas shes par bya'o //
NK119(he)001:5739: gsum pa byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pa'i ngo bo byams dang snying rjes rgyud brlan zhing /
NK119(he)001:5740: gzhan gyi don du byang chub thob 'dod pas /
NK119(he)001:5741: sgo gsum nyes pa spang ba'i sems dapa'o //
NK119(he)001:5742: de yang sems bskyed kyi ngo bo byams dang snying rjes rgyun brlan pa ste /
NK119(he)001:5744: 'di ni snying rje'i ljon shing snying po can //
NK119(he)001:5745: 'gro ba'i khur chen legs par khyer ba ni //
NK119(he)001:5748: sems bskyed pa ni gzhan don phyir //
NK119(he)001:5749: yang dag rdzogs pa'i byang chub 'dod //
NK119(he)001:5752: bdag gi lus dang ngag gi las //
NK119(he)001:5753: thams cad du ni dag par bya //
NK119(he)001:5754: yid kyis las kyang dag bya ste //
NK119(he)001:5755: mi dge'i las rnams mi bya'o //
NK119(he)001:5758: blo che ba dang gtong ba che dang sems dpa' che //
NK119(he)001:5759: go cha chen po bgos shing bdud kyi rgyu 'dul ba //
NK119(he)001:5760: rgyu des de ni byang chub sems dpa' zhes brjod do //
NK119(he)001:5762: bzhi pa dbye ba la'ang gnyis te /
NK119(he)001:5766: dbye ba klu sgrub thogs med srol gnyis grags //
NK119(he)001:5767: re re'ang gcig nas drug par gnyis gnyis te //
NK119(he)001:5768: zab mo lta ba'i rgyan gyur klu sgrub yab sras
NK119(he)001:5769: kyi rjes su 'brang ba dbu ma lugs kyi sems
NK119(he)001:5770: bskyed dang / rgya chen spyod pa'i rgyan gyur thogs
NK119(he)001:5771: med sku mched kyi rjes su 'brang nas sems tsam
NK119(he)001:5772: lugs kyi sems bskyed gnyis ka la'ang dbye ba 'di
NK119(he)001:5774: de yang gcig nas drug gi bar dang sa mtshams dpes dbye ba dang bdun du gnas pa las /
NK119(he)001:5775: dang po sems bskyed pa'i rten rigs kyi rang bzhin dang mtshungs par /
NK119(he)001:5776: dang po stong nyid snying rje'i snying po can /
NK119(he)001:5777: de yang sdong po bkod pa las /
NK119(he)001:5778: kye rgyal ba'i sras dag byang chub sems dpa'i rigs zhes bya ba de ni /
NK119(he)001:5779: chos kyi dbyings lhur len pa /
NK119(he)001:5780: nam mkha' ltar yangs pa rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal ba ste /
NK119(he)001:5781: de la gnas pa'i byang chub sems dpa' rnams ni
NK119(he)001:5782: 'das pa dang ma 'ongs pa dang da ltar byung
NK119(he)001:5783: ba'i sangs rgyas rnams kyi rigs su skyes pa yin
NK119(he)001:5786: stong nyid snying rje'i snying po can //
NK119(he)001:5787: byang chub bsgrub pa kha gcig la'o //
NK119(he)001:5789: de yang rigs sam khams bde bar gshegs pa'i snying
NK119(he)001:5790: po de kun la yod kyang re zhig rigs sad
NK119(he)001:5793: sbyor ba'i sngon du snying rje dang //
NK119(he)001:5794: mos pa dang ni bzod pa dang //
NK119(he)001:5795: dge la yang dag sbyor ba ni //
NK119(he)001:5796: rigs kyi rtags su shes par bya //
NK119(he)001:5798: 'di dag gi rnam gzhag rgyas par shing rta chen po la sogs su rtogs par bya ste /
NK119(he)001:5799: don dam sems bskyed de yang ngo bo 'di las gzhan pa zhig med do //
NK119(he)001:5801: tshogs gnyis bslabs pa kun rdzob don dam gnyis /
NK119(he)001:5802: zhes gnyis tshan gyi dbye na /
NK119(he)001:5803: kun rdzob don dam gnyis te /
NK119(he)001:5805: kun rdzob don dam dbye ba yis //
NK119(he)001:5806: byang chub sems de rnam pa gnyis //
NK119(he)001:5808: de'ang bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs gnyis la
NK119(he)001:5809: slob pa so skye dang mi slob pa 'phags pa'i
NK119(he)001:5811: phyi rol sems can la dmigs pa dang /
NK119(he)001:5812: nang sems nyid la dmigs pa gnyis kyis kun rdzob don dam gyi sems bskyed gnyis su bzhag go //
NK119(he)001:5814: tshul khrims ting 'dzin shes rab bslab pa gsum /
NK119(he)001:5817: dag par byed pa tshul khrims kyi bslab pa /
NK119(he)001:5818: gnas par byed pa sems kyi bslab pa /
NK119(he)001:5819: grol bar byed pa shes rab kyi bslab pa'i sems gsum gyi rnam pa gsum mo //
NK119(he)001:5821: yang tshul khrims gsum gyi dbang du mdzad nas /
NK119(he)001:5823: gang kha na ma tho ba sdom pa'i sems dang /
NK119(he)001:5824: dge ba'i chos sdud pa'i sems dang /
NK119(he)001:5825: sems can smin par byed pa'i sems te /
NK119(he)001:5826: sems bskyed pa 'di gsum la nan tan du bya'o //
NK119(he)001:5829: tshogs sbyor mos pas bskyed pa'i sems bskyed dang //
NK119(he)001:5830: ma dag sa bdun lhag bsam dag pa dang //
NK119(he)001:5831: dag pa sa gsum rnam par smin pa dang //
NK119(he)001:5832: thugs rje chen po'i sgrib kun spangs pa ni //
NK119(he)001:5833: sangs rgyas sa yi sems bskyed dag dang bzhi //
NK119(he)001:5836: sems bskyed de ni sa rnams la //
NK119(he)001:5837: mos dang lhag bsam dag pa dang //
NK119(he)001:5838: rnam par smin pa gzhan du 'dod //
NK119(he)001:5839: de bzhin sgrib pa spangs pa'o //
NK119(he)001:5842: de yang rab dga' dri med 'od byed pa //
NK119(he)001:5843: 'od 'phro sbyong dka' mngon 'gyur ring du song //
NK119(he)001:5846: mi g.yo legs pa'i blo gros chos kyi sprin //
NK119(he)001:5849: drug pa lnga ni lam lnga /
NK119(he)001:5852: tshogs sbyor mthong sgom mi slob pa'i lam lnga'i sems bskyed do //
NK119(he)001:5854: las dang po pa'i sems bskyed pa dang /
NK119(he)001:5855: yongs su sbyongs ba byas pa'i sems bskyed pa dang /
NK119(he)001:5856: chos mthong ba'i sems bskyed pa dang /
NK119(he)001:5857: rnam par grol ba'i sems bskyed pa dang /
NK119(he)001:5858: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i sems bskyed pa ste /
NK119(he)001:5859: rab 'byor 'di la ma zhugs pa gzhug par bya'o //
NK119(he)001:5860: zhugs pa yongs su sbyong bar bya'o //
NK119(he)001:5862: 'phags pa'i lam bden bsgom par bya'o //
NK119(he)001:5863: sangs rgyas kyi spyan sgrib pa med par thob par bya'o //
NK119(he)001:5867: pha rol phyin drug dang ldan pa'i sems bskyed pa drug dang ldan pas zhes so //
NK119(he)001:5868: phar phyin bcu la ltos nas bcur bshad pa yang yod de /
NK119(he)001:5870: byang chub kyi sems rnam pa bcu bsgom nas /
NK119(he)001:5872: bdun pa sa mtshams kyi dbye na /
NK119(he)001:5873: dpe sa gser zla ba me sogs nyer gnyis ni /
NK119(he)001:5874: sa mtshams kyis dbye sa bcu'i bar du'o //
NK119(he)001:5875: nyi shu rtsa gnyis kyi dpes bstan pa nyid /
NK119(he)001:5876: blo gros rgyal mtshos zhus pa'i mdo las gsungs pa ltar /
NK119(he)001:5878: de yang sa gser zla ba me //
NK119(he)001:5879: gter dang rin chen 'byung gnas mtsho //
NK119(he)001:5880: rdo rje ri sman bshes gnyen dang //
NK119(he)001:5881: yid bzhin nor bu nyi ma glu //
NK119(he)001:5882: rgyal po mdzod dang lam po che //
NK119(he)001:5883: gzhon pa bkod ma'i chu dang ni //
NK119(he)001:5884: sgra snyan chu bo sprin rnams kyis //
NK119(he)001:5885: rnam pa nyi shu rtsa gnyis so //
NK119(he)001:5887: dpe de dag gi don ni rim pa ltar /
NK119(he)001:5892: zhes sogs gsungs pa 'dir dpe don sbyar nas ston pa ni /
NK119(he)001:5895: bsam pa gser lta bu dang /
NK119(he)001:5896: lhag pa'i bsam pa zla ba tshes pa lta bu
NK119(he)001:5897: gsum ni rim pa ltar tshogs lam chung 'bring che
NK119(he)001:5898: gsum gyi sems bskyed la de skad ces btags so
NK119(he)001:5899: // sbyor ba me lta bu ni sbyor lam bzhi'i sems bskyed do //
NK119(he)001:5900: sbyin pa gser lta bu dang /
NK119(he)001:5901: tshul khrims rin po che'i 'byung gnas lta bu dang /
NK119(he)001:5902: bzod pa mtsho lta bu dang /
NK119(he)001:5903: brtson 'grus rdo rje lta bu dang /
NK119(he)001:5904: bsam gtan ri lta bu dang /
NK119(he)001:5905: shes rab sman lta bu dang /
NK119(he)001:5906: thabs la mkhas pa bshes gnyen lta bu dang /
NK119(he)001:5907: smon lam yid bzhin gyi nor bu lta bu dang /
NK119(he)001:5908: stobs nyi ma lta bu dang /
NK119(he)001:5909: ye shes kyi pha rol tu phyin pa glu dbyangs
NK119(he)001:5910: snyan pa lta bu ni sa dang po nas bcu
NK119(he)001:5911: pa'i bar la rim pa bzhin no //
NK119(he)001:5912: mngon shes rgyal po lta bu dang /
NK119(he)001:5913: tshogs gnyis mdzod khang lta bu dang /
NK119(he)001:5914: byang chub kyi phyogs dang mthun pa'i chos lam po che lta bu dang /
NK119(he)001:5915: snying rje lhag mthong gnyis bzhon pa bzang po lta bu dang /
NK119(he)001:5916: gzungs spobs gnyis bkod ma'i chu mig lta bu lnga ni sa brgyad pa /
NK119(he)001:5917: dgu pa bcu pa gsum ka la khyab par yod do //
NK119(he)001:5918: chos kyi dga' ston sgra snyan lta bu dang /
NK119(he)001:5919: bgrod pa gcig pa'i lam chu bo lta bu dang /
NK119(he)001:5920: chos kyi sku dang mtshungs par ldan pa sprin lta bu gsum ni /
NK119(he)001:5921: sa bcu pa la yod de ye shes dang phrin
NK119(he)001:5922: las chen po sems can gyi don byed pa'i phyir
NK119(he)001:5924: 'di dag slob dpon che ba'i sde la sogs pas
NK119(he)001:5925: 'jig rten pa'i lam thams cad smon pa bden mthong
NK119(he)001:5927: a b+h+ya ka ra la sogs kha cig tshogs lam man chad smon pa /
NK119(he)001:5928: sbyor lam yan chad 'jug par 'dod la /
NK119(he)001:5929: rgya mtsho'i sprin la sogs pa byang chub thob 'dod kyi blos ma bskyed pa smon pa /
NK119(he)001:5930: bskyed pa 'jug par 'dod pa la sogs mang yang /
NK119(he)001:5931: kun mkhyen klong chen pa'i bzhed pas grub mtha' mdzod las /
NK119(he)001:5932: 'dir gzhan don du byang chub 'dod la smon pa dang /
NK119(he)001:5933: sbyor bas khyab na zhugs pa ni 'jug pa ste /
NK119(he)001:5934: ngo bo gcig la ldog pa tha dad du 'dod pa yin no //
NK119(he)001:5936: gnyis pa mdor bstan pa ni /
NK119(he)001:5937: kun kyang bsdu na smon 'jug rnam pa gnyis //
NK119(he)001:5938: de yang bsam pas smon dang sbyor bas khyab //
NK119(he)001:5939: 'gro bar 'dod dang 'gro ba nyid bzhin no //
NK119(he)001:5940: de yang sngar bshad pa'i sems bskyed kyi rnam dbye
NK119(he)001:5941: ji snyed pa de dag kyang smon 'jug gnyis su
NK119(he)001:5942: 'dus te / smon pa ni byang chub thob par
NK119(he)001:5943: 'dun pa bsam pas smon pa 'gro bar 'dod pa
NK119(he)001:5946: de'i chos la sbyor ba 'gro bzhin pa lta bu ste /
NK119(he)001:5948: byang chub sems de mdor bsdus na //
NK119(he)001:5949: rnam pa gnyis su shes bya ste //
NK119(he)001:5950: byang chub smon pa'i sems dang ni //
NK119(he)001:5951: byang chub 'jug pa nyid yin no //
NK119(he)001:5953: bye brag ji ltar shes pa ltar //
NK119(he)001:5954: de bzhin mkhas pas 'di gnyis kyi //
NK119(he)001:5955: bye brag rim bzhin shes par bya //
NK119(he)001:5957: spyi don gnyis pa thog mar sdom pa thob pa'i tshul la'ang gnyis te /
NK119(he)001:5964: dang po sdom pa ma thob thob tshul ni /
NK119(he)001:5965: len tshul sdom gnas dge ba'i bshes gnyen la //
NK119(he)001:5966: theg chen snod gyur dad ldan slob ma yis //
NK119(he)001:5967: yan lag bdun mthar smon 'jug stabs gcig tu //
NK119(he)001:5968: len zhing rang gzhan dga' ba bsgom pa rnams //
NK119(he)001:5969: klu sgrub lugs yin thogs med bzhed pa ni //
NK119(he)001:5971: byang sems kyi sdom pa 'bog par byed pa'i dge ba'i bshes gnyen ni /
NK119(he)001:5972: sdom pa nyi shu pa las /
NK119(he)001:5973: bla ma sdom la gnas shing mkhas //
NK119(he)001:5974: nus dang ldan las blang bar bya //
NK119(he)001:5977: rtag par dge ba'i bshes gnyen ni //
NK119(he)001:5978: theg chen don la mkhas pa dang //
NK119(he)001:5979: byang chub sems dpa'i brtul zhugs mchog /
NK119(he)001:5980: srog gi phyir yang mi gtong ngo //
NK119(he)001:5983: bla ma bzang las sdom pa blang //
NK119(he)001:5984: sdom pa'i cho ga la mkhas dang //
NK119(he)001:5985: bdag nyid gang zhig sdom pa gnas //
NK119(he)001:5986: sdom pa 'bogs bzod snying rjer ldan //
NK119(he)001:5987: bla ma bzang por shes par bya //
NK119(he)001:5991: bskal bzang slob ma dad dang shes rab che //
NK119(he)001:5992: brtson 'grus bag yod dran dang shes bzhin ldan //
NK119(he)001:5993: bka' las mi 'da' sdom dang dam tshigabasrunga //
NK119(he)001:5994: sgo gsum dul zhing snying rje phan sems che //
NK119(he)001:5995: khong yangs spro ring gtong phod dag snang che //
NK119(he)001:5996: bsten zhing mos gus che ba de dag gis //
NK119(he)001:5997: zhes pa'i tshul de gnyis srol gnyis ka la 'dra'o //
NK119(he)001:5998: de lta bu'i slob ma la dbu ma lugs ltar na /
NK119(he)001:5999: phyogs gang du gnas gtsang mchod pas mdzes shing nyams dga' bar /
NK119(he)001:6000: rgyal ba'i sku gzugs la sogs sta gon bya //
NK119(he)001:6001: zhes ngal gsor bshad pa ltar bstan pa des mtshon
NK119(he)001:6002: nas tshogs zhing sprul zhing spyan 'dren pa sogs bya'o
NK119(he)001:6005: gang zhig rgyal ba yid byed pa //
NK119(he)001:6006: de yi mdun na de bzhugs te //
NK119(he)001:6007: rtag par byin gyis barloba par byed //
NK119(he)001:6008: nyes pa kun las rnam par grol //
NK119(he)001:6010: de nas yan lag bdun pa bya ba ni /
NK119(he)001:6012: phyag 'tshal ba dang mchod cing bshags pa dang //
NK119(he)001:6013: rjes su yi rangs bskul zhing gsol ba yi //
NK119(he)001:6014: dge ba cung zad bdag gis ci bsags pa //
NK119(he)001:6015: thams cad rdzogs pa'i byang chub chen por bsngo //
NK119(he)001:6016: zhes 'phags pa bzang po spyod pa nas byung ba
NK119(he)001:6017: ltar ram bdun rnam dag gang yang rung ba dang
NK119(he)001:6018: / yang de'i steng du skyabs su 'gro ba dang /
NK119(he)001:6019: sems bskyed pa'i yan lag gnyis bsnan pas yan lag bcu pa zhes bya'o //
NK119(he)001:6020: gzhan yang yan lag bcu'i nang nas chos kyi 'khor lo bskor bar bskul ba dang /
NK119(he)001:6021: mya ngan las mi 'da' bar gsol gnyis phri bas yan lag bdun te /
NK119(he)001:6022: de yang ston pa gzugs kyi sku la yan lag de gnyis dgos kyi /
NK119(he)001:6024: khyad par longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku la mi dgos te /
NK119(he)001:6025: chos nges pa theg pa chen po'i chos kyi 'khor
NK119(he)001:6026: lo dus nges par rtag pa rgyun gyi 'khor lor
NK119(he)001:6027: bskor ba la sogs pa nges pa lnga ldan du
NK119(he)001:6029: rgya gar gyi slob dpon ngag dbang grags pas /
NK119(he)001:6030: gzugs kyi sku ni mya ngan las //
NK119(he)001:6031: 'da' bar byed kyi gcig shos min //
NK119(he)001:6033: de ltar yan lag bdun pa phul ba'i phan yon ni /
NK119(he)001:6034: dpal sbas gyis zhus pa'i mdo las //
NK119(he)001:6035: gang zhig phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas la //
NK119(he)001:6036: dmigs nas thal mo sbyar byas te //
NK119(he)001:6037: phyag 'tshal de ni mchod phyir ram //
NK119(he)001:6038: bsod nams dag la yi rangs zhing //
NK119(he)001:6039: sdig pa dag kyang 'chags par bgyid //
NK119(he)001:6040: bskul dang gsol ba 'debs gyur pa //
NK119(he)001:6041: de yi bsod nams phung po ni /
NK119(he)001:6042: nam mkha' gang bar rtag tu 'byung //
NK119(he)001:6044: de ltar legs par grub pa'i rjes su /
NK119(he)001:6045: 'og nas 'byung ba'i cho ga'i tshig brjod de smon 'jug gi sems bskyed gnyis ka blang ngo //
NK119(he)001:6046: de'i rjes su rang dga' ba bsgom pas /
NK119(he)001:6048: ming don barje ba gsum las /
NK119(he)001:6051: sems ni 'di ltar gzengs bstod de //
NK119(he)001:6052: deng dus bdag tshe 'bras bu yod //
NK119(he)001:6053: mi yi srid pa legs par thob //
NK119(he)001:6054: de ring sangs rgyas rigs su skyes //
NK119(he)001:6055: sangs rgyas sras su da gyur to //
NK119(he)001:6056: da ni bdag gis ci nas kyang //
NK119(he)001:6057: rigs dang mthun pa'i las brtsams ste //
NK119(he)001:6058: skyon med btsun pa'i rigs 'di la //
NK119(he)001:6059: rnyog par mi 'gyur de ltar bya //
NK119(he)001:6060: long bas phyag dar phung po las //
NK119(he)001:6061: ji ltar rin chen rnyed pa ltar //
NK119(he)001:6062: de bzhin ji zhig ltar stes nas //
NK119(he)001:6063: byang chub sems ni bdag la skyes //
NK119(he)001:6067: bdag gis de ring skyob pa thams cad kyi //
NK119(he)001:6068: spyan sngar 'gro ba bde gshegs nyid dang ni //
NK119(he)001:6069: bar du bde la mgron du bos zin gyi //
NK119(he)001:6070: lha dang lha min la sogs dga' bar byos //
NK119(he)001:6072: gsum pa sems bskyed thob ma thag tu so skye'am
NK119(he)001:6073: nyan thos rang rgyal zhes pa'i ming dang mi ldan
NK119(he)001:6075: de yang ming gi rnam grangs bcu drug yod de /
NK119(he)001:6077: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' che //
NK119(he)001:6078: blo ldan nyid dang gsal ba'i mchog /
NK119(he)001:6079: rgyal sras rgyal ba'i gzhi dang ni //
NK119(he)001:6080: rgyal byed rgyal ba'i myu gu dang //
NK119(he)001:6081: rtsal ldan dang ni 'phags mchog dang //
NK119(he)001:6082: ded dpon dang ni grags mchog dang //
NK119(he)001:6083: snying rje che dang bsod nams che //
NK119(he)001:6084: dbang phyug de bzhin chos dang ldan //
NK119(he)001:6086: ming du ma zad don kyang 'pho ste /
NK119(he)001:6088: byang chub sems bskyed gyur pa'i skad cig la //
NK119(he)001:6089: 'khor ba'i btson rar bsdom pa'i nyams thag rnams //
NK119(he)001:6090: bde gshegs rnams kyi sras zhes rab brjod cing //
NK119(he)001:6091: 'jig rten lha mir bcas pas phyag byar 'gyur //
NK119(he)001:6093: gnyis pa slob dpon thogs med kyi lugs la /
NK119(he)001:6094: smon sems len la so thar mi dgos kyang //
NK119(he)001:6095: yang dag blang ba rigs bdun sngon song nas //
NK119(he)001:6096: bar chad dri dang bslab pa khas len pa sogs //
NK119(he)001:6097: smon 'jug cho ga so so'i sgo nas len //
NK119(he)001:6098: 'di ltar smon pa sems bskyed rkyang pa len pa la so thar mi dgos kyang /
NK119(he)001:6099: smon 'jug gnyis ka yang dag par len pa'i rten de /
NK119(he)001:6100: so thar rigs bdun gyi sdom pa dang ldan pa zhig nges par dgos te /
NK119(he)001:6101: jo bo rjes byang chub lam sgron las /
NK119(he)001:6102: so so thar pa rigs bdun gyi //
NK119(he)001:6103: rtag tu sdom gzhan ldan pa la //
NK119(he)001:6104: byang chub sems dpa'i sems bskyed kyi //
NK119(he)001:6105: skal ba yod kyi gzhan du min //
NK119(he)001:6107: de lta bu'i gang zag de la nyes pa dang
NK119(he)001:6108: mthun par bar chad dri ba dang bslab pa la
NK119(he)001:6109: slob par khas len pa sogs byas nas /
NK119(he)001:6110: dngos ni smon sems sngon la blang //
NK119(he)001:6111: de rjes 'jug pa blang ste cho ga ltar bya'o //
NK119(he)001:6112: de ltar blang ba'i yul dge ba'i bshes gnyen med na /
NK119(he)001:6113: rgyal ba'i rten la rung bar srol gnyis mthun //
NK119(he)001:6114: thob mtshams brjod pa gsum gyi tha la'o //
NK119(he)001:6115: de yang zab pa dang rgya che ba'i lugs gang la'ang /
NK119(he)001:6116: rang stobs kyi nus pa yod na mdun gyi nam
NK119(he)001:6117: mkhar sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs bsam
NK119(he)001:6119: 'jam dpal zhing gi yon tan bkod pa'i mdo las gsungs pa ltar byang chub lam sgron las /
NK119(he)001:6120: gal te bla ma ma rnyed na //
NK119(he)001:6121: de la gzhan sdom nod pa yi //
NK119(he)001:6122: cho ga yang dag bshad par bya //
NK119(he)001:6124: mgon po rnams kyi spyan sngar ni //
NK119(he)001:6125: rdzogs pa'i byang chub sems bskyed cing //
NK119(he)001:6126: zhes sogs cho ga ltar gsungs so //
NK119(he)001:6128: spyod 'jug la sogs nas gsungs pa'ang yod la /
NK119(he)001:6129: 'dir ni kun mkhyen chen pos 'grel chen shing rta chen por gsungs pa ltar 'don te /
NK119(he)001:6130: de yang yul dge ba'i bshes gnyen nam /
NK119(he)001:6131: rgyal ba'i rten gang yang rung ba'i mdun du bdag nyid pus btsugs thal mo sbyar te /
NK119(he)001:6133: dus 'di nas bzung ste ji srid byang chub snying
NK119(he)001:6134: po la mchis kyi bar du rkang gnyis rnams kyi
NK119(he)001:6135: mchog / sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK119(he)001:6136: 'dod chags dang bral ba rnams kyi mchog /
NK119(he)001:6137: dam pa'i chos rnams la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK119(he)001:6138: tshogs rnams kyi mchog /'phags pa phyir mi ldog pa'i dge 'dun rnams la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK119(he)001:6140: phyogs bcu na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das thams cad bdag la dgongs su gsol /
NK119(he)001:6141: sa bcu la gnas pa'i byang chub sems dpa' rnams bdag la dgongs su gsol /
NK119(he)001:6142: bla ma rdo rje 'dzin pa chen po rnams bdag la dgongs su gsol /
NK119(he)001:6143: ji ltar sngon gyi sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams dang /
NK119(he)001:6144: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po rnams kyis
NK119(he)001:6145: byang chub chen por thugs bskyed pa de bzhin du
NK119(he)001:6146: / bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi bas kyang /
NK119(he)001:6147: sems can ma bsgral ba rnams bdag gis bsgral ba dang /
NK119(he)001:6148: ma grol ba rnams grol ba dang /
NK119(he)001:6149: dbugs ma dbyung ba rnams dbugs dbyung ba dang /
NK119(he)001:6150: yongs su mya ngan las ma 'das pa rnams yongs su mya ngan las 'da' ba'i phyir /
NK119(he)001:6152: byang chub snying po la mchis kyi bar du byang chub chen por sems bskyed par bagyi'o //
NK119(he)001:6154: gsum pa brjod dgos pa'i rgyu mtshan /
NK119(he)001:6156: brjod pa dang pos smon pa sems bskyed la //
NK119(he)001:6157: gnyis pas 'jug pa sems bskyed gsum pa yis //
NK119(he)001:6158: gnyis ka brtan zhing dag pa thob par 'gyur //
NK119(he)001:6161: brjod pa dang gnyis pa gsum pa dag gis smon
NK119(he)001:6162: pa dang 'jug pa gnyis ka chos brtan pa'i mchog
NK119(he)001:6165: de yang smon 'jug ngo bo tha dad pa med
NK119(he)001:6166: de brjod pa gsum las ldog pa tha dad par
NK119(he)001:6167: ston kyang ngo bo gcig yin te /
NK119(he)001:6169: smon pa dang 'jug pa 'di gnyis ni /
NK119(he)001:6170: ngo bo dbyer med pas gzhan gyi don du byed pa gcig pa nyid dang /
NK119(he)001:6171: tha mi dad pa'i rang bzhin du shes par bya ba nyid do //
NK119(he)001:6173: gnyis pa don dam sems bskyed ni /
NK119(he)001:6174: don dam sems bskyed cho gas blang thob pa //
NK119(he)001:6175: gsang sngags lugs yin mdo las bshad srid na //
NK119(he)001:6176: dam bca' nyid yin bsgom pa'i stobs las skyes //
NK119(he)001:6177: de yang don dam sems bskyed kyi ngo bo gshis kyi rang bzhin te /
NK119(he)001:6178: de gsang sngags las rkyen kun rdzob sems bskyed cho
NK119(he)001:6179: gas blang nas rgyu don dam sems bskyed mngon du
NK119(he)001:6180: byed pa dang / dbang gnyis pa dang gsum par
NK119(he)001:6181: kun rdzob dang don dam byang chub kyi sems mngon
NK119(he)001:6182: du byed pa ste rgyas par slad nas 'chad par
NK119(he)001:6184: sems bskyed chen po'i mdo las kyang //
NK119(he)001:6185: byang chub tu sems ji ltar bskyed ce na thams
NK119(he)001:6186: cad nam mkha' ltar mtshan nyid med cing ye nas
NK119(he)001:6187: 'od gsal ba rnam par dag pa de la ni
NK119(he)001:6189: de dang mthun pa'i sems sngon ma skyes pa'i sems
NK119(he)001:6190: rin po che skyes pa la ni byang chub tu
NK119(he)001:6193: mdo las don dam sems bskyed sgom pa las skye yang cho gas skye bar bshad pa med de /
NK119(he)001:6194: klu sgrub kyis byang chub kyi sems rnam par bshad pa las /
NK119(he)001:6195: de ltar byang chub kyi sems bskyed pa ni smon lam gyi rang bzhin kun rdzob kyi rnam pa'o //
NK119(he)001:6196: byang chub sems dpa'i gsang sngags kyi sgo'i spyad pa spyod par 'dod pa rnams kyis /
NK119(he)001:6197: ma bsgrib yang don dam yang bsgom pa'i stobs kyis bskyed par bya'o //
NK119(he)001:6200: sangs rgyas brgya las mi nyung ba'i zhal mthong nas lung gi chos thos pas /
NK119(he)001:6201: yongs su 'dzin pa dam pa dang /
NK119(he)001:6202: bskal pa brgya las mi nyung bar tshogs gnyis bsags
NK119(he)001:6203: pas bsgrub pa'i chos 'dzin pas sgrub pa dam pa
NK119(he)001:6204: dang / mnyam gzhag nas rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes skyes pas rtogs pa'i chos 'dzin pas /
NK119(he)001:6206: dam pa gsum gyis zin pa ni don dam sems bskyed do //
NK119(he)001:6209: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rab mnyes bya //
NK119(he)001:6210: bsod nams ye shes tshogs rab bsags //
NK119(he)001:6211: chos la mi rtog ye shes ni //
NK119(he)001:6212: skye phyir de ni don dam 'dod //
NK119(he)001:6214: sa dang po'i yon tan skyes pa ni don dam sems bskyed kyi thog ma yin la /
NK119(he)001:6215: so so'i skye bo'i gnas skabs na don dam sems
NK119(he)001:6216: bskyed mtshan nyid pa med par sa pan la sogs
NK119(he)001:6217: blo gros mnga' ba kun bzhed do //
NK119(he)001:6218: rnal 'byor r+aa ga a s+ya ni kun rdzob byang
NK119(he)001:6219: chub kyi sems bsgom pa na rnam par mi rtog
NK119(he)001:6220: pa'i ye shes la mnyam par bzhag pas don dam
NK119(he)001:6221: sems bskyed kyang des grub bo gsungs pa'ang 'gal ba
NK119(he)001:6223: spyi don gsum pa bar du thob pa mi nyams par bsrung ba'i thabs la'ang gnyis te /
NK119(he)001:6225: de skye ba'i rten bshad pa'o //
NK119(he)001:6227: dbye ba rgyas par bshad pa dang /
NK119(he)001:6228: gces pa'i sdom pas 'gags bsdu ba'o //
NK119(he)001:6234: bar du mi nyams bsrung ba'i thabs bshad pa //
NK119(he)001:6235: byang chub sems dpa'i tshul khrims gsum yin te /
NK119(he)001:6236: nyes spyod sdom dang dge ba chos sdud dang //
NK119(he)001:6237: sems can don byed gsum las dang po ni /
NK119(he)001:6238: zhes smos pas dang po nyes spyod sdom pa'i tshul khrims la'ang gnyis te /
NK119(he)001:6243: yan lag gi nyes byas so //
NK119(he)001:6244: dang po la gsum rgyal po la nges pa lnga /
NK119(he)001:6248: dkon mchog dkor 'phrog dang ni chos spangs las //
NK119(he)001:6249: tshul ldan tshul 'chal khrims gcod bslab 'bebs sogs //
NK119(he)001:6250: mtshams med las byed log lta lnga rgyal po //
NK119(he)001:6251: de ltar rgyal po la 'byung du nye ba ste /
NK119(he)001:6252: 'di dag nam mkha'i snying po'i mdo las /
NK119(he)001:6253: gsungs pa ltar bslab btus su tshigs su bcad de //
NK119(he)001:6254: dkon mchog gsum gyi dkor 'phrog pa //
NK119(he)001:6255: phas pham pa yi ltung bar 'dod //
NK119(he)001:6256: dam pa'i chos ni spong byed pa //
NK119(he)001:6257: gnyis pa thub pas gsungs pa yin //
NK119(he)001:6258: tshul khrims 'chal ba'i dge slong la //
NK119(he)001:6259: ngur smrig 'phrog dang brdeg pa dang //
NK119(he)001:6260: btson rar 'jug par byed pa dang //
NK119(he)001:6261: rab tu byung ba 'bebs pa dang //
NK119(he)001:6262: srog dang bral byed gsum pa yin //
NK119(he)001:6263: mtshams med lnga po byed pa dang //
NK119(he)001:6264: log par lta ba 'dzin pa dang //
NK119(he)001:6267: grong ljongs grong khyer grong rdal yul 'khor rnams //
NK119(he)001:6268: 'joms par byed pa'ang blon por nges pa lnga //
NK119(he)001:6270: grong la sogs pa 'joms pa yang //
NK119(he)001:6271: rtsa ba'i ltung bar rgyal bas gsungs //
NK119(he)001:6276: ljongs ni yul gru tha dad pa /
NK119(he)001:6277: yul 'khor ni cher grangs su langs pa yin par grags so //
NK119(he)001:6279: ma sbyangs stong nyid brjod sngas nyan thos smon //
NK119(he)001:6280: rdzogs byang phyir ldog theg dman sems bskyed dang //
NK119(he)001:6281: so thar spangs nas theg chen slob pa dang //
NK119(he)001:6282: nyan thos theg pas chags sogs mi ldog pas //
NK119(he)001:6283: de ldog de yi 'bras bu med par byas //
NK119(he)001:6284: phrag dog dbang gis bdag bstod gzhan smod dang //
NK119(he)001:6285: dge slong chad pas gcod bcug sug 'bul dang //
NK119(he)001:6286: spangs ba'i longs spyod kha ton pa la byin //
NK119(he)001:6287: zhi gnas 'dor bcug phal la ltung nges brgyad //
NK119(he)001:6288: de skad du snga ma las /
NK119(he)001:6289: blo sbyongs ma byas sems can la //
NK119(he)001:6290: stong pa nyid ni ston pa dang //
NK119(he)001:6291: sangs rgyas nyid la zhugs pa dag /
NK119(he)001:6292: rdzogs pa'i byang chub bzlog pa dang //
NK119(he)001:6293: so sor thar pa yongs spangs te //
NK119(he)001:6294: theg pa che la sbyor ba dang //
NK119(he)001:6295: slob pa'i theg pas chags la sogs //
NK119(he)001:6296: spangs bar 'gyur ba min zhes brjod //
NK119(he)001:6298: rang gi yon tan brjod pa dang //
NK119(he)001:6299: rnyed pa dang ni bkur sti dang //
NK119(he)001:6300: tshigs bcad rgyu yis gzhan smod dang //
NK119(he)001:6301: bdag ni zab mo bzod pa'o zhes //
NK119(he)001:6302: log pa nyid ni smra ba dang //
NK119(he)001:6303: dge sbyong chad pas gcod 'jug dang //
NK119(he)001:6304: dkon mchog gsum gyi sbyin byed dang //
NK119(he)001:6305: sbyin pa len par byed pa dang //
NK119(he)001:6306: zhi gnas 'dor bar byed pa dang //
NK119(he)001:6307: yang dag 'jog gi longs spyod rnams //
NK119(he)001:6308: kha ton byed la sbyin pa rnams //
NK119(he)001:6309: de dag rtsa ba'i ltung ba ste //
NK119(he)001:6310: sems can dmyal ba chen po'i rgyu //
NK119(he)001:6311: rmi lam 'phags pa nam snying po'i //
NK119(he)001:6312: mdun du 'dug ste bshags par bya //
NK119(he)001:6314: de yang rgyal po la sogs /
NK119(he)001:6315: de der 'byung nyes bzhag gi kun la kun //
NK119(he)001:6316: ming du bco brgyad rdzas su bcu bzhi ste //
NK119(he)001:6317: smon 'jug sems gtong de rnams rtsa ltung yin //
NK119(he)001:6318: 'di dag byang chub sems dpa' rgyal po'i tshul dang /
NK119(he)001:6320: phal pa'i tshul can de dag la 'byung du nye
NK119(he)001:6321: ba'i cha nas rgyal po la nges pa lnga la
NK119(he)001:6323: don la gang zag gcig gi rgyud la'ang de dag thams cad bsrung dgos so //
NK119(he)001:6324: 'di dag ming gi sgo nas bco brgyad yod kyang /
NK119(he)001:6326: rgyal po'i dang po'i bzhi dang blon po'i lnga po gcig pas lnga /
NK119(he)001:6327: phal pa'i brgyad dang bcu bzhi ru 'adu'o //
NK119(he)001:6328: thun mong pa smon sems btang ba dang bcu dgu /
NK119(he)001:6329: de'i steng du dkon mchog brtsegs pa las /
NK119(he)001:6331: dge ba la mi sbyor ba dang nyi shu'o //
NK119(he)001:6332: zla ba snying po'i mdo dang /
NK119(he)001:6333: nam mkha'i snying po'i mdo las kyang 'jug sems spong ba nyid ltung byed du gsal lo //
NK119(he)001:6334: gnyis pa yan lag gi nyes byas ni /
NK119(he)001:6335: yan lag nyes byas brgyad cu la sogs pa //
NK119(he)001:6336: phra phyir 'dir ni ma bshad bslab btus blta //
NK119(he)001:6337: de yang nyes byas brgyad cu zhes pa /
NK119(he)001:6338: slob dpon zhi ba lhas mdzad pa'i bslab btus su gsungs na'ang 'dir smras pa /
NK119(he)001:6339: dbang gi 'bras rgyu'i mtha' 'kho ba lhor gzhan phug /'chos skyob gang gi bdun gyi bdun pas dben //
NK119(he)001:6340: blo rtog dus kyi myu gus yid byed kyang //
NK119(he)001:6341: dbyig ldan shed bu swo'u can phongs bzhin //
NK119(he)001:6343: gnyis pa sems tsam pa'i lugs la'ang gnyis te /
NK119(he)001:6348: rgyas par bshad pa gnyis las /
NK119(he)001:6350: thogs med lugs ni smon pa'i bslab bya la //
NK119(he)001:6351: sems can blos mi gtong dang phan yon dran //
NK119(he)001:6352: tshogs bsags byang sems sbyangs la brtson pa dang //
NK119(he)001:6353: dkar nag chos brgyad blang dor smon pa'i yin //
NK119(he)001:6354: de yang sems can blos mi gtong ba ni /
NK119(he)001:6356: pha rol sems can gcig gi phyir yang ni //
NK119(he)001:6357: bskal pa bye ba brgyar yang mi skyo ba //
NK119(he)001:6359: phan yon dran par bya ste /
NK119(he)001:6361: byang chub sems kyi bsod nams gang //
NK119(he)001:6362: gal te de la gzugs mchis na //
NK119(he)001:6363: nam mkha'i khams ni kun bkang yang //
NK119(he)001:6364: de ni de las lhag par 'gyur //
NK119(he)001:6366: tshogs gnyis bsags dgos par yang /
NK119(he)001:6368: tshogs gnyis lam la ma brten par //
NK119(he)001:6369: mthar phyin 'bras bu thob ma yin //
NK119(he)001:6371: byang chub kyi sems sbyangs dgos te zhi ba lhas /
NK119(he)001:6372: sems ni bskyed par ma byas na //
NK119(he)001:6373: sangs ni rgya bar mi 'gyur ro //
NK119(he)001:6374: zhes pa'i tshul gyis dkar nag chos brgyad blang dor du bya'o //
NK119(he)001:6375: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa ni /
NK119(he)001:6376: mchod 'os bslu dang 'gyod med 'gyod pa bskyed //
NK119(he)001:6377: dam par skur 'debs 'gro la g.yo sgyus spyod //
NK119(he)001:6378: nag po'i chos bzhi spangs zhing bzlog pa ni //
NK119(he)001:6379: dkar po'i chos bzhi yin pas kun tu spyod //
NK119(he)001:6380: spangs bar bya ba nag po'i chos bzhi ni /
NK119(he)001:6382: 'od srung chos bzhi dang ldan na byang chub kyi sems brjed par 'gyur te /
NK119(he)001:6384: bla ma dang mchod par 'os pa bslus pa dang /
NK119(he)001:6385: gzhan 'gyod pa'i gnas ma yin pa la 'gyod pa bskyed pa dang /
NK119(he)001:6386: sems bskyed pa'i byang chub sems dpa' la sdang sems kyis skyon brjod pa dang /
NK119(he)001:6387: sems can la g.yo dang sgyus spyod pa'o //
NK119(he)001:6389: blang bya dkar po'i chos bzhi yang de nyid las /
NK119(he)001:6390: 'od srung byang chub sems dpa' chos bzhi dang ldan
NK119(he)001:6391: na skye ba thams cad du skyes ma thag tu
NK119(he)001:6392: byang chub kyi sems mngon du 'gyur zhing /
NK119(he)001:6393: byang chub kyi snying po la 'dug gi bar du bar ma dor brjed par mi 'gyur ro //
NK119(he)001:6396: tha na bzhad gang kyi phyir yang rdzun du mi smra ba dang /
NK119(he)001:6397: g.yo sgyu med par sems can thams cad kyi mdun na gnas pa dang /
NK119(he)001:6398: byang chub sems dpa' la ston pa'i 'du shes kyis basngagasa pas phyogs bcur brjod pa dang /
NK119(he)001:6399: sems can thams cad theg pa chen po la 'god cing 'dzin du 'jug pa ste /
NK119(he)001:6402: mdo ting nge 'dzin rgyal po las /
NK119(he)001:6403: gzhon nu 'du shes bzhi dang ldan na byang chub kyi sems brtan por 'gyur te /
NK119(he)001:6404: bzhi gang zhe na yang dag pa'i dge ba'i bshes gnyen la sangs rgyas kyi 'du shes dang /
NK119(he)001:6405: des bstan pa'i chos la lam gyi 'du shes dang /
NK119(he)001:6406: de bsgrub pa rnams la lam grogs kyi 'du shes dang /
NK119(he)001:6407: sems can thams cad la bu gcig pa'i 'du shes so //
NK119(he)001:6409: gnyis pa 'jug pa'i bslab bya la gnyis /
NK119(he)001:6411: yan lag gi nyes byas so //
NK119(he)001:6413: rnyed bskur lhag zhen bdag bstod gzhan smod dang //
NK119(he)001:6414: ser snas zang zing chos nor mi ster dang //
NK119(he)001:6415: khro bas gzhan 'tshe bshags sbyong gis mi ldog /
NK119(he)001:6416: g.yom las chos ltar bcos mos ston pa bzhi //
NK119(he)001:6417: rtsa ltung bzhi ste 'jug pa'i bslab bya'o //
NK119(he)001:6419: sdom pa nyi shu pa las /
NK119(he)001:6420: rnyed dang bkur sti chags pa yis //
NK119(he)001:6421: bdag bstod gzhan la smod pa dang //
NK119(he)001:6422: sdug bsngal mgon med gyur pa la //
NK119(he)001:6423: ser snas chos nor mi ster dang //
NK119(he)001:6424: gzhan gyi bshags kyang mi nyan par //
NK119(he)001:6425: khros pas gzhan la 'tshog pa dang //
NK119(he)001:6426: theg pa chen po spangs byed cing //
NK119(he)001:6428: zhes rtsa ba'i ltung ba pham 'dra bzhi zhes bya'o //
NK119(he)001:6429: gnyis pa yan lag gi nyes byas bzhi bcu zhe drug ni /
NK119(he)001:6430: nyes byas phra ba zhe drug gzhan du shes //
NK119(he)001:6432: sdom pa nyi shu pa de nyid las /
NK119(he)001:6433: sems can don byed 'gal ba so bzhi ni //
NK119(he)001:6434: dang po sbyin pa dang 'gal ba bdun ni /
NK119(he)001:6435: dkon mchog gsum la gsum mi mchod //
NK119(he)001:6437: rgan pa rnams la gus mi byed //
NK119(he)001:6438: dris pa la ni lan mi 'debs //
NK119(he)001:6439: mgron pos bdag gir mi byed dang //
NK119(he)001:6440: gser la sogs pa len mi byed //
NK119(he)001:6441: chos 'dod rnams la sbyin mi byed //
NK119(he)001:6442: tshul khrims dang 'gal ba dgu ni /
NK119(he)001:6444: pha rol dad phyir slob mi byed //
NK119(he)001:6445: sems can don la bya ba chung //
NK119(he)001:6446: snying rjer bcas na mi dge med //
NK119(he)001:6447: 'tsho ba log pa dang du len //
NK119(he)001:6448: 'phyar nas rab tu rgod la sogs //
NK119(he)001:6449: 'khor ba gcig tu bgrod par bsam //
NK119(he)001:6450: grags pa ma yin mi spongs ba //
NK119(he)001:6451: nyon mongs bcas kyang 'chos mi bya //
NK119(he)001:6452: bzod pa dang 'gal ba bzhi ni /
NK119(he)001:6453: gshe la lan du gshe la sogs //
NK119(he)001:6454: khros pa rnams ni yal bar dor //
NK119(he)001:6455: pha rol shad kyis chags pa spyad //
NK119(he)001:6456: khros pa'i sems kyis rjes su 'jug /
NK119(he)001:6459: le lo la sogs sel mi byed //
NK119(he)001:6460: chags pa bre mo'i gtam la brten //
NK119(he)001:6461: bsam gtan dang 'gal ba gsum ni /
NK119(he)001:6463: bsam gtan sgrib pa spangs mi byed //
NK119(he)001:6464: bsam gtan ro la yon tan lta //
NK119(he)001:6465: shes rab dang 'gal ba brgyad ni /
NK119(he)001:6466: nyan thos theg pa ldang bar byed //
NK119(he)001:6467: rang tshul yod bzhin de la brtson //
NK119(he)001:6468: brtson min phyi rol bstan bcos brtson //
NK119(he)001:6469: brtson pa byas kyang de la dga' //
NK119(he)001:6470: theg pa chen po spangs bar byed //
NK119(he)001:6471: bdag la bstod cing gzhan la smod //
NK119(he)001:6472: chos kyi don du 'gro mi byed //
NK119(he)001:6473: don la smod cing yi ge ston //
NK119(he)001:6474: sems can don byed dang 'gal ba bcu gnyis ni /
NK119(he)001:6475: dgos pa'i grogs su 'gro mi byed //
NK119(he)001:6476: nad pa'i rim 'gro bya ba spangs //
NK119(he)001:6477: sdug bsngal sel bar mi byed dang //
NK119(he)001:6478: bag med rnams la rig mi ston //
NK119(he)001:6479: byas la lan du phan mi 'dogs //
NK119(he)001:6480: gzhan gyi mya ngan sel mi byed //
NK119(he)001:6481: nor 'dod pa la sbyin mi byed //
NK119(he)001:6482: 'khor rnams kyi ni don mi byed //
NK119(he)001:6483: gzhan gyi blo dang mthun mi 'jug /
NK119(he)001:6484: yon tan basngagasa pa smra mi byed //
NK119(he)001:6485: rkyen du 'tshams pa tshar mi gcod //
NK119(he)001:6486: rdzu 'phrul la sogs sdig mi byed //
NK119(he)001:6488: gnyis pa dge ba chos sdud kyi tshul khrims la'ang /
NK119(he)001:6489: spyi don mdor bstan pa dang /
NK119(he)001:6490: so so'i don rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK119(he)001:6492: dge ba chos sdud phar phyin drug bslab ste /
NK119(he)001:6493: de yang pha rol tu phyin pa drug po 'di
NK119(he)001:6494: ni rgyal sras rnams kyi thar lam chen po yin
NK119(he)001:6495: pas bsgrub par bya dgos pa ni /
NK119(he)001:6497: rgyal sras rnams kyis kun la bslab bya ste //
NK119(he)001:6498: gtso bo pha rol phyin pa drug la bslab //
NK119(he)001:6501: sbyin dang tshul khrims bzod brtson bsam gtan dang //
NK119(he)001:6502: de bzhin shes rab gzhal med pha rol phyin //
NK119(he)001:6503: 'di dag rgyas mdzad srid pa'i rgya mtsho yi //
NK119(he)001:6504: pha rol phyin pa rgyal ba'i dbang po mdzod //
NK119(he)001:6506: pha rol du phyin pa drug gi ngo bo ni /
NK119(he)001:6508: 'khor gsum du mi rtog pas rang gi bdog pa
NK119(he)001:6509: gzhan la gtong sems dge ba sa bon dang bcas
NK119(he)001:6510: pa ni sbyin pa'i pha rol du phyin pa'o //
NK119(he)001:6511: de'i byed las gzhan gyi dbul ba sel ba'o //
NK119(he)001:6512: 'khor gsum mi rtog pas srid zhi'i skyon spangs ba'i
NK119(he)001:6513: sems pa sa bon dang bcas pa'i tshul khrims so
NK119(he)001:6514: // byed las 'tshe ba las log pa'o //
NK119(he)001:6515: 'khor gsum mi rtog pas gnod pa dang skyo ngal
NK119(he)001:6516: bzod cing chos nyid la mi skrag pa ni bzod
NK119(he)001:6517: pa'o // de'i byed las khro ba med pa'o //
NK119(he)001:6518: 'khor gsum mi rtog pas dge ba las spro ba brtson 'grus so //
NK119(he)001:6520: 'khor gsum mi rtog pas sems rtse gcig bsam gtan no //
NK119(he)001:6521: byed las nyon mongs pa zhi ba'o //
NK119(he)001:6522: 'khor gsum mi rtog pas chos nyid rang bzhin rtogs pa ni shes rab bo //
NK119(he)001:6523: byed las shes bya rtogs shing 'khor ba las sgrol ba'o //
NK119(he)001:6525: pha rol tu phyin pa de dag gi yon tan ni bzhi ste /
NK119(he)001:6526: gzhan don byang chub la dmigs pas rgya che ba dang /
NK119(he)001:6527: mngon mtho nges legs 'grub pas don che ba dang /
NK119(he)001:6528: 'jig rten las 'das pas zang zing med pa dang /
NK119(he)001:6529: dge ba gong du 'phel bas mi zad pa ste /
NK119(he)001:6530: mdo sde'i rgyan las rgya che ba dang zang zing med /
NK119(he)001:6531: don che ba dang mi zad pa /
NK119(he)001:6532: sbyin pa la sogs thams cad kyi //
NK119(he)001:6533: yon tan bzhi ni shes par bya //
NK119(he)001:6535: grangs nges pa la gsum las /
NK119(he)001:6536: dang po mngon mtho 'grub pa dang nyon mongs pa spangs pa la ltos nas /
NK119(he)001:6539: longs spyod dang lus phun sum tshogs pa dang //
NK119(he)001:6540: 'khor rtsom phun sum tshogs pas mngon mtho dang //
NK119(he)001:6541: rtag tu nyon mongs dbang nyid mi 'gro dang //
NK119(he)001:6542: bya ba rnams la phyin ci ma log pa'o //
NK119(he)001:6544: gnyis pa gzhan don byas pas rang don 'grub pa la ltos te drug tu nges par /
NK119(he)001:6546: mi phongs pa dang rnam par mi 'tshe dang //
NK119(he)001:6547: rnam 'tshe bzod dang bya bas mi skyo dang //
NK119(he)001:6548: dga' byed legs par brjod pa de yi phyir //
NK119(he)001:6549: gzhan gyi don ni rang gi don yin no //
NK119(he)001:6551: gsum pa bslab pa gsum gyi dbang du byas nas /
NK119(he)001:6553: bslab gsum dbang du mdzad nas ni //
NK119(he)001:6554: rgyal bas pha rol phyin pa drug /
NK119(he)001:6555: yang dag bshad de dang po gsum //
NK119(he)001:6556: tha ma gnyis kyis rnam pa gnyis //
NK119(he)001:6557: gcig ni gsum char la yang gtogs //
NK119(he)001:6561: shes rab ni shes rab kyi bslab pa /
NK119(he)001:6562: brtson 'grus ni gsum ka'i grogs su bsdus pa'o //
NK119(he)001:6565: snga ma la brten phyi ma skye //
NK119(he)001:6566: dman dang mchog tu gnas phyir dang //
NK119(he)001:6567: rags pa dang ni phra ba'i phyir //
NK119(he)001:6568: de dag go rim bstan pa yin //
NK119(he)001:6570: snga ma snga ma las phyi ma phyi ma skye bas rgyu dang 'bras bu rim pa dang /
NK119(he)001:6571: sbyin pa las tshul khrims bzang bas mchog dman dang /
NK119(he)001:6572: snga ma snga zhing rtogs sla la phyi ma dka'
NK119(he)001:6573: bas phra rags kyi rim pa ste gsum la ltos
NK119(he)001:6577: re ba med pa'i sbyin pa dang //
NK119(he)001:6578: yang srid mi 'dod tshul khrims dang //
NK119(he)001:6579: thams cad pa la gzod par dang //
NK119(he)001:6580: yon tan kun sdud brtson 'grus dang //
NK119(he)001:6581: de bzhin bsam gtan gzugs med min //
NK119(he)001:6582: shes rab thabs dang ldan pa yi //
NK119(he)001:6583: pha rol phyin pa drug po la //
NK119(he)001:6584: brten pa rnams kyi yang dag sbyor //
NK119(he)001:6588: dbul ba sel bar byed pa dang //
NK119(he)001:6589: bsil ba thob dang khro bzod dang //
NK119(he)001:6590: mchog la sbyor dang yid 'dzin dang //
NK119(he)001:6591: don dam shes pa'i phyir bshad do //
NK119(he)001:6593: gnyis pa so so'i rang bzhin rgyas par bshad pa la'ang drug las /
NK119(he)001:6594: dang po sbyin pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa ni /
NK119(he)001:6596: dbul ba sel phyir chos nor mi 'jigs sbyin //
NK119(he)001:6597: de la chos kyi sbyin pa /
NK119(he)001:6598: zang zing nor gyis sbyin pa /
NK119(he)001:6599: mi 'jigs pa skyabs kyi sbyin pa gsum ste /
NK119(he)001:6600: 'phags pa 'jig rten 'dzin gyis dri bas lung bstan pa'i mdo las /
NK119(he)001:6601: de la chos kyi sbyin pa gang zhe na /
NK119(he)001:6604: glegs bam sbyin pa ni chung ngu'o //
NK119(he)001:6605: skal pa ji lta ba bzhin du /
NK119(he)001:6608: bla na med pa'i chos ston pa ni chen po'o //
NK119(he)001:6609: bla na med pa'i byang chub 'dzin du 'jug cing /
NK119(he)001:6610: nam mkha' ltar bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i chos ston pa ni shin tu chen po'o //
NK119(he)001:6611: de la zang zing gi sbyin pa gang zhe na /
NK119(he)001:6615: de la gtong ba zhes pa ni /
NK119(he)001:6619: dge slong gzhan la sbyin pa'o //
NK119(he)001:6620: gtong chen po zhes bya ba ni /
NK119(he)001:6624: shin tu gtong ba zhes bya ba ni /
NK119(he)001:6628: rkang pa la sogs gtong ba bya dka' ba'o //
NK119(he)001:6632: mthu dang ldan pas ri rgya klung rgya sdom pa la sogs pa ste /
NK119(he)001:6639: chu la sogs pa'i 'jigs pa las yongs su skyabs pa yin par rigs par bya'o //
NK119(he)001:6642: spangs pa'i sems kyis tshul khrims rnam gsum spyad //
NK119(he)001:6645: 'od srung de la byang chub sems dpa'i tshul khrims ni rnam pa gsum ste /
NK119(he)001:6647: dge ba'i chos rnams sdud pa'i tshul khrims dang /
NK119(he)001:6648: sems can gyi don byed pa'i tshul khrims so //
NK119(he)001:6649: de la sdom pa'i tshul khrims kyis ni mi dge ba las sems bsrung ba yin no //
NK119(he)001:6650: dge ba chos sdud kyi ni /
NK119(he)001:6651: dge ba'i rtsa ba mngon par bsgrub pa yin no //
NK119(he)001:6652: sems can don byed kyis ni gzhan la phan pa lhur len pa yin no //
NK119(he)001:6654: dang po ni nyes spyod sdom pa'i tshul khrims ni /
NK119(he)001:6655: khyim pa dang rab tu byung ba'i phyogs gnyis kyi so sor thar pa rigs bdun gyi sdom pa'o //
NK119(he)001:6657: rab tu byung ba'i bslab par brjod pa de dag
NK119(he)001:6658: gi steng du smon 'jug gi sems bskyed thob la
NK119(he)001:6659: ma nyams par yod pa ni byang chub sems dpa'
NK119(he)001:6660: rab tu byung ba yin par gsungs la /
NK119(he)001:6662: byang chub sems dpa'i khyim pa dang /
NK119(he)001:6664: khye'u dang bu mo'i gzugs su 'dug pa bye ba
NK119(he)001:6665: khri rab tu mang po dag dang thabs cig tu
NK119(he)001:6667: dge ba chos sdud ni pha rol tu phyin pa
NK119(he)001:6668: drug gis bsdus pa'i yon tan ma skyes pa bskyed
NK119(he)001:6670: sems can don byed ni thabs la mkhas pas dngos sam brgyud nam sems can la phan 'dogs shing /
NK119(he)001:6671: bsdu dngos bzhis gdul bya rnams mngon mtho dang nges legs la bkod pa'o //
NK119(he)001:6673: khong khro zab mo sdug bsngal bzod pa bya /
NK119(he)001:6676: mi bajeda ji mi snyam shes dang //
NK119(he)001:6677: snying rjes chos la brten pa'i phyir //
NK119(he)001:6680: 'di ltar pha rol gyis gnod pa'i 'tshe ba sogs
NK119(he)001:6681: pa byas pa la khong khro mi bskyed pa ni
NK119(he)001:6683: thar ba dang rang gzhan gyi don bsgrub pa'i dka'
NK119(he)001:6684: spyad bzod pa ni sdug bsngal dang len ji mi
NK119(he)001:6686: snying rjes gzhan gyi don la skyo ngal med pa
NK119(he)001:6687: dang stong nyid zab mo la mi skrag pa ni
NK119(he)001:6688: chos nyid dmigs pa med pa'i bzod pa'o //
NK119(he)001:6691: go cha dge sdud gzhan phan brtson 'grus brtsoms //
NK119(he)001:6692: de yang dge ba bsgrub cing bdud bzhi 'joms pa'i rgyu go cha'i brtson 'grus dang /
NK119(he)001:6693: lam lnga sa bcu la sogs pa'i dge ba'i chos sdud pa'i brtson 'grus dang /
NK119(he)001:6694: rang dang gzhan gyi don gyi phyir gzhan phan gyi brtson 'grus gsum ste /
NK119(he)001:6696: rgyal ba'i sras rnams go cha sbyor ba'i bdag nyid brtson 'grus dpe med byas //
NK119(he)001:6697: rang dang gzhan gyi nyon mongs tshogs gzhom byang chub dam pa thob par byed //
NK119(he)001:6700: 'jig rten 'jig rten 'das pa'i bsam gtan bsgom //
NK119(he)001:6701: 'jig rten pa dang 'jig rten las 'das pa gnyis
