NK119(he)001:9920: 'gyod pa drag pos bshags pas so //
NK119(he)001:9921: dam las 'das nas lo dag gis //
NK119(he)001:9922: bar du ma chod bshags pas so //
NK119(he)001:9923: lo ni gcig dang gsum dag las //
NK119(he)001:9924: dam tshig ral ba zhes bya ba //
NK119(he)001:9925: mchog tu drag na gso ru rungs //
NK119(he)001:9926: lo gsum dag las 'das pa ni //
NK119(he)001:9927: de nas gso rung mi rung ste //
NK119(he)001:9928: gal te blang na gnyis ka 'tshig /
NK119(he)001:9929: nges par sa spyod sdug bsngal la //
NK119(he)001:9930: rgyun du spyod pa kho na'o //
NK119(he)001:9934: dbang bdun thob la lha grangs re re la //
NK119(he)001:9935: bzlas pa sum khri drug stong byas pas spyod //
NK119(he)001:9936: de yang dbang gang yin pa'i lha re re la
NK119(he)001:9937: bsnyen pa khri phrag gsum dang stong phrag drug bzlas
NK119(he)001:9939: bum gsang thob nyams sngon du chad las spyad //
NK119(he)001:9940: de rjes dal du zhugs la dbang bzhi len //
NK119(he)001:9941: dbang gong ma gnyis po thob nas nyams na thog mar rdo rje sems dpa'i bsgom bzlas dang /
NK119(he)001:9942: sbyin bsreg tshogs 'khor la sogs pas nyams pa bshags shing snod rung du byas nas /
NK119(he)001:9943: slar dkyil 'khor du zhugs nas bla ma las dbang dang dam tshig blang bar bya ste /
NK119(he)001:9944: dam pa dang po'i rgyud las /
NK119(he)001:9945: rtsa ba'i ltung ba byung gyur na //
NK119(he)001:9947: dag pa rgyu ru 'jug par bya //
NK119(he)001:9948: slar yang gnang ba thob pa ni //
NK119(he)001:9949: tshogs kyi nang du 'gro ba na //
NK119(he)001:9950: rgan pa'i ming ni gzhon pa zhes //
NK119(he)001:9951: zhes dang rtsa ltung bcu bzhi par //
NK119(he)001:9952: gsum la skyabs 'gro nas brtsam ste /
NK119(he)001:9953: byang chub sems sogs sdom pa ni //
NK119(he)001:9954: gal te bdag la phan 'dod na //
NK119(he)001:9955: sngags pas 'bad de bzung bar bya //
NK119(he)001:9958: sher dbang tshig dbang thob nyams bskyed rim dang //
NK119(he)001:9959: 'pho med tshul khrims rdzogs pa'i rim pa dag /
NK119(he)001:9960: rang rgyud byin rlabs ma gtogs gzhan mi 'dag /
NK119(he)001:9962: rang gi sems rgyud byin gyis brlab pa'i rim pas te /
NK119(he)001:9964: dam tshig dam tshig ces bya ba //
NK119(he)001:9965: gud na yod pa ma yin te //
NK119(he)001:9966: rang gi sems nyid dam tshig yin //
NK119(he)001:9967: ji snyed snang ba'i chos rnams kun //
NK119(he)001:9968: rang rig kun bral nyid snang bas //
NK119(he)001:9969: ci snang ji srid rang rig nyid //
NK119(he)001:9970: 'dre ldog spyi tshugs gar song yang //
NK119(he)001:9971: snying po'i don las 'das mi srid //
NK119(he)001:9972: rang bzhin dam tshig chen po'o //
NK119(he)001:9973: zhes pa'i tshul gyis sbyang ngo //
NK119(he)001:9975: 'gal na tshogs 'khor nyams na bdog pas bskang //
NK119(he)001:9976: 'das na bu dang chung ma nor sogs dang //
NK119(he)001:9977: ral na rang gi srog gis gso bar bshad //
NK119(he)001:9978: de yang dam tshig bkod pa'i rgyud las //
NK119(he)001:9980: nyams na rang gi bdog pas bkang //
NK119(he)001:9981: 'das pa bu dang chung ma dang //
NK119(he)001:9982: nye 'khor lus dang ngag dag dang //
NK119(he)001:9983: yid dang bdog par bcas pas bskang //
NK119(he)001:9984: ral na rang gi srog gis bskang //
NK119(he)001:9987: snying po rgyan las gso ba'i cho ga ni //
NK119(he)001:9988: tshogs zhing la bshags dral ba'i sngags rgya dang //
NK119(he)001:9989: bkru ba'i rim pas gtum mo'i mer bsreg dang //
NK119(he)001:9990: mi dmigs sgom dang dbang bzhi blang ba lnga //
NK119(he)001:9991: tshogs su zhugs dang rten la sme ba dang //
NK119(he)001:9992: man+dala 'bul dang mchod rten bya ba dang //
NK119(he)001:9993: me la sbyong dang gtor ma gtong ba dang //
NK119(he)001:9994: gsang sngags bzla dang zab mo'i bsam gtan dang //
NK119(he)001:9995: srog skyab bka' klog bla ma bsten pa dang //
NK119(he)001:9996: bdag 'jug rgyal ba'i yig brgya dus bzang bzlas //
NK119(he)001:9997: phung po gsum pa rdor sems bla ma dang //
NK119(he)001:9998: thig le phra mo'i rnal 'byor sgom pas gso //
NK119(he)001:9999: de ltar rdo rje snying po'i rgyan gyi rgyud las /
NK119(he)001:10000: gso thabs nyer lnga gsungs pa'i /
NK119(he)001:10001: thog mar tshogs gnyis bsags pa'i zhing dkon mchog gsum gyi spyan sngar bshags pas 'dag ste /
NK119(he)001:10003: srid 'gro nyams ngar byis pa'i blo yis ni //
NK119(he)001:10004: shin tu mi bzad sdig pa gang bgyis pa //
NK119(he)001:10005: stobs bcu mnga' ba'i spyan sngar bdag mchis te //
NK119(he)001:10006: sdig pa de kun so sor bshags par bgyi //
NK119(he)001:10008: sdig pa dral ba'i sngags dang phyag rgyas sbyong ste /
NK119(he)001:10009: sngags ni mu tig khad ka la sogs sbyong rgyud ltar la phyag rgya ni /
NK119(he)001:10011: rdo rje bsdam pa dam byas te //
NK119(he)001:10012: gung mo gnyis ni ngos sbyar nas //
NK119(he)001:10013: tha ma bzhi yi rtse sprad pa //
NK119(he)001:10014: skad cig tu ni sdig bral lo //
NK119(he)001:10017: nyams sgrib dag pa'i khrus sam /
NK119(he)001:10018: yo ga'i rdo rje rtse mo las //
NK119(he)001:10019: sdom pa la gnas pa ni nang gi khrus //
NK119(he)001:10020: yan lag bdun pas rgyud sbyong gsang ba'i khrus //
NK119(he)001:10021: phyag rgya bcings bkrol rnal 'byor khrus zhes bya //
NK119(he)001:10024: yum lnga'i rang bzhin kha dog lnga'i me sbar bas
NK119(he)001:10025: 'khor lo lnga'i dug lnga'i rnam pa 'gro ba lnga'i
NK119(he)001:10026: bag chags bsregs nas zhing khams lnga mngon du byed
NK119(he)001:10027: pa'o // mi dmigs bsgom pas gso sbyong bya ste /
NK119(he)001:10029: ji bzhin pa yi sems yid la //
NK119(he)001:10030: ma bcos pa yi blo bzhag ste //
NK119(he)001:10031: de la g.yo ba med gyur na //
NK119(he)001:10032: dam tshig thams cad bskang pa yin //
NK119(he)001:10033: nyams pa'i chad pa byung na yang //
NK119(he)001:10034: mgon skyabs de las che ba med //
NK119(he)001:10036: dbang bzhi blang bas sgrib gnyis dag pa dang /
NK119(he)001:10037: rnal 'byor gyi tshogs 'dus par tshogs kyi 'khor lo
NK119(he)001:10038: bskor te nyams pa 'di zhes gleng ste mthong sdom
NK119(he)001:10039: bya ba dang / rten gyi drung du smre sngags kyis bshags te /
NK119(he)001:10040: dung dung gdung ba'i smre sngags 'di 'don zhing //
NK119(he)001:10041: nyam thag phongs pa'i nga ngo 'don lags na //
NK119(he)001:10043: man+dala 'bul bas sdig pas 'dag par man+dala gyi cho gar gsungs pa dang /
NK119(he)001:10044: mchod rten byas pas byang bar de bzhin gshegs pa'i mchod rten gyi le'u las bshad cing /
NK119(he)001:10045: til la sdig sgrib bstim nas mer sreg par sbyong rgyud las gsungs /
NK119(he)001:10046: 'byung po dang yi dwags la gtor ma btang ba dang /
NK119(he)001:10047: gsang sngags bzlas pas sbyong bar dpung bzang las bshad do //
NK119(he)001:10048: bsam gtan b+hee pas 'dag pa de bzhin gshegs pa'i mdo las bshad cing /
NK119(he)001:10049: gzhan gyi srog skyabs pas byang ste nye'u 'don zhes bya la /
NK119(he)001:10052: slob ma 'jug pa'i tshul gyis ni //
NK119(he)001:10053: thog mar slob dpon 'jug par bya //
NK119(he)001:10054: zhes pas bdag 'jug blang ba dang /
NK119(he)001:10056: dus kyi lha la phyag 'tshal zhing sngags bzlas pa dang /
NK119(he)001:10057: phung po gsum pa'i mdo 'don pa dang /
NK119(he)001:10058: bla ma rdor sems sgom bzlas phra mo'i rnal 'byor dang bcas pas skong bar bya ste /
NK119(he)001:10059: dgongs tshig gsum pa'i rgyud las /
NK119(he)001:10060: rdo rje sems dpa' b+hee nas ni //
NK119(he)001:10061: sngags kyang rab tu zlos byed pa //
NK119(he)001:10062: de yi sdig kun byang nas ni //
NK119(he)001:10065: 'di dag gsang sngags spyi'i gso thabs su gnas la /
NK119(he)001:10067: glang chen rab 'bog rgyud las gsungs pa yi //
NK119(he)001:10068: rnal 'byor spyi khrus 'gyod tshangs dong sprugs kyis //
NK119(he)001:10069: bshags pas mi 'dag med phyir nyams su blang //
NK119(he)001:10070: 'di ni gzhi dam tshig gis bzung ba'i rim pa
NK119(he)001:10071: dbang gi las kyi glang chen rab 'bog gi gsung
NK119(he)001:10072: gi nges pa rtsa ba'i rgyud gsum gyi bar ba
NK119(he)001:10074: rgyud kun 'dus rig pa'i le'u brgyad pa dang /
NK119(he)001:10075: a nu lung gi ma mo'i le'u bzhi pa dang
NK119(he)001:10076: bshags pa'i rgyud dri med rgyal po'i le'u bzhi pa
NK119(he)001:10077: nas 'byung zhing / ye shes sku mchog rang bzhin dkyil 'khor ni //
NK119(he)001:10078: zhes sogs ngag 'don dang de'i dgongs pa gsal ba'i
NK119(he)001:10079: 'grel tika la sogs pa ni gzhan du 'dug pa
NK119(he)001:10081: de yang nges tshig sa ma y+aa'i sgra las dam tshig ces bya ste /
NK119(he)001:10082: thun mong ltar na dam bca' ba'i tshul gyis 'jug ste /
NK119(he)001:10084: rgyal ba'i gsang chen rmad pa'i chos //
NK119(he)001:10085: ma nyams dam du 'dzin pa'i phyir //
NK119(he)001:10086: bla mas ji skad bstan pa bzhin //
NK119(he)001:10087: dam bca' tshig na bstan pa 'jig /
NK119(he)001:10088: dam tshig ces su bstan pa yin //
NK119(he)001:10090: khyad par ma bsrung na nyes dmigs thob pas dam tshig ces bya ste /
NK119(he)001:10092: dam pa rnams kyi bka' bcag cing //
NK119(he)001:10094: rdo rje can yang tshig par 'gyur //
NK119(he)001:10096: ma bshags tshe 'dir yid mi 'ong bas mnar //
NK119(he)001:10097: phyi ma rdo rje'i dmyal ba zhes bya ba //
NK119(he)001:10098: mnar med do zla med ba'i gnas su skye //
NK119(he)001:10101: dam tshig la ni 'da' gyur na //
NK119(he)001:10102: 'di phyi'i bde legs nyams pa dang //
NK119(he)001:10103: yid du mi 'ong sna tshogs myong //
NK119(he)001:10104: sa spyod me yi sdug bsngal la //
NK119(he)001:10105: bskal ba bye ba grangs med gnas //
NK119(he)001:10107: lnga pa phan yon bstan pa ni /
NK119(he)001:10108: ma nyams par bsrung bas phan yon thob pas dam tshig ces bya ste /
NK119(he)001:10110: dam pa rnams kyi dgongs pa la //
NK119(he)001:10111: dbang dang byin rlabs thob pa yi //
NK119(he)001:10112: dam pa'i tshul bzhin nges spyad na //
NK119(he)001:10113: mi mthun phyogs rnams tshig par 'gyur //
NK119(he)001:10114: zhes gsungs pas gong du bshad pa'i dam tshig de dag las /
NK119(he)001:10115: ma nyams ring mtha' skye ba bcu drug gam //
NK119(he)001:10116: myur na 'adi'am 'chi kha bar do ru //
NK119(he)001:10117: thun mong grub pa brgyad dang dbang phyug brgyad //
NK119(he)001:10118: mchog gi dngos grub kha sbyor bdun ldan thob //
NK119(he)001:10119: de phyir rang gzhan don gnyis lhun gyis grub //
NK119(he)001:10120: de yang gsang sngags kyi sgor zhugs nas dam tshig ma nyams na /
NK119(he)001:10121: dbang po tha ma'i tha ma yang ring mtha' skye ba bcu drug nas grol te /
NK119(he)001:10123: gal te rnal 'byor de brtson nas //
NK119(he)001:10125: yang na mthong ba tsam gyis ni //
NK119(he)001:10126: skye ba bcu drug mya ngan 'das //
NK119(he)001:10127: so so skye bo sangs rgyas nyid //
NK119(he)001:10130: dbang po dang brtson pa rab tu gyur bas tshe 'di la sangs rgyas thob ste /
NK119(he)001:10132: bskal pa skye ba du ma ru //
NK119(he)001:10133: sangs rgyas sku dngos mi mthong ba //
NK119(he)001:10134: gsang sngags che 'di'i cho ga yis //
NK119(he)001:10137: dam tshig dang ldan zhing brtson pa 'bring yang 'chi kha'i bar do la grol te /
NK119(he)001:10139: gzugs can phung po rang lus 'di //
NK119(he)001:10141: yid ni rdo rje'i skur 'gyur na //
NK119(he)001:10145: yang na lus 'di spangs ma thag /
NK119(he)001:10146: bla na med pa'i ye shes sku //
NK119(he)001:10147: brtson pa mi ldan pas kyang 'grub //
NK119(he)001:10148: brtson 'grus ldan pas smros ci dgos //
NK119(he)001:10149: zhes dus nye bar bstan nas /
NK119(he)001:10150: grub par bya ba dngos grub mchog thun gnyis las /
NK119(he)001:10151: thun mong dngos grub grub pa brgyad dang dbang phyug brgyad thob ste /
NK119(he)001:10154: mig sman dang ni rkang mgyogs dang //
NK119(he)001:10156: ril bu dang ni mkha' spyod nyid //
NK119(he)001:10157: mi snang ba dang bcud kyi len //
NK119(he)001:10158: gang phyir de ni rdo rje 'dzin //
NK119(he)001:10159: mnyes par byas pas myur du thob //
NK119(he)001:10162: mig la rdzas sogs byug pas sa 'og gi gter la sogs pa mthong ba'o //
NK119(he)001:10163: rkang mgyogs ni mchil lham 'grub ste gon pas rgya mtsho'i mtha' 'khor ba'o //
NK119(he)001:10164: ral gri ni des pha rol gyi dgra 'joms pa'o //
NK119(he)001:10166: ril bu ni des gnod sbyin la sogs las la 'khor te gang bsam 'grub pa'o //
NK119(he)001:10167: mkha' spyod ni mkha' la 'gro ba'o //
NK119(he)001:10168: mi snang ba ni lus mi mngon pa'o //
NK119(he)001:10169: bcud kyis len pas tshe nyi zla dang mnyam /
NK119(he)001:10170: stobs glang po che dang mnyam /
NK119(he)001:10172: ldang ba shing bal las yang pa'o //
NK119(he)001:10175: sku yi dbang phyug gsung gi dbang phyug dang //
NK119(he)001:10176: thugs kyi dbang phyug yon tan phrin las dang //
NK119(he)001:10177: rdzu 'phrul kun tu 'gro ba'i dbang phyug dang //
NK119(he)001:10178: gang 'dod gnas dang dbang phyug don brgyad do //
NK119(he)001:10180: de yang gang 'dul gyi skur sprul ba sku'i dbang phyug /
NK119(he)001:10181: chos 'khor rgyun chad med pa gsung gi dbang phyug /
NK119(he)001:10182: rtog med thugs rje mnga' ba thugs kyi dbang phyug /
NK119(he)001:10183: rdzu 'phrul thogs pa med pa rdzu 'phrul gyi dbang phyug /
NK119(he)001:10184: dus gsum ro gcig par byang chub pa kun 'gro'i dbang phyug /
NK119(he)001:10185: ri rab so gnyis kyi rdul snyed kyi lha mos
NK119(he)001:10186: mchod kyang 'dod pas gos pa med pa 'dod pa'i
NK119(he)001:10187: dbang phyug / nor bu ltar 'gro ba'i re 'dod
NK119(he)001:10188: bskang bas gang 'dod bskyed pa'i dbang phyug /'og min
NK119(he)001:10189: gyi gnas na khams gsum chos kyi rgyal po rtag
NK119(he)001:10190: tu bzhugs pa ni gnas kyi dbang phyug ste brgyad
NK119(he)001:10191: dbang phyug / do // mchog gi dngos grub kha sbyor bdun ldan thob ste /
NK119(he)001:10193: longs spyod rdzogs dang kha sbyor bde chen rang bzhin med //
NK119(he)001:10194: snying rjes yongs gang rgyun mi 'chad dang 'gog pa med //
NK119(he)001:10195: yan lag 'dun dang ldan pa'i bsgrub bya 'di //
NK119(he)001:10197: de'ang 'og min du sems dpa' chen po rnams la
NK119(he)001:10198: zab rgyas gsang sngags kyi chos 'khor la rgyun du
NK119(he)001:10199: longs spyod pas longs spyod kyi yan lag /
NK119(he)001:10200: mtshan dpe rdzogs pa'i ye shes kyi sku nyid rang
NK119(he)001:10201: 'od yum dang sbyor bas kha sbyor gyi yan lag
NK119(he)001:10202: dang / rgyun chad med pa zag med bde ba
NK119(he)001:10203: chen po'i yan lag gsum ni longs sku'i khyad chos
NK119(he)001:10204: yin la dmigs med kyi thugs rje mkha' ltar khyab
NK119(he)001:10205: dang / pa ni / snying rjes yongs su gang
NK119(he)001:10206: ba'i yan lag /'phrin las rgya chen pos 'gro ba'i
NK119(he)001:10207: don rtag tu mdzad pa ni rgyun mi chad pa'i
NK119(he)001:10208: dang / pa ni / yan lag dang / myang
NK119(he)001:10209: 'das zhi ba'i mtha' la mi gnas pa 'gog pa'i
NK119(he)001:10210: yan lag gsum ni sprul sku'i khyad chos yin la
NK119(he)001:10211: dang / pa ni / yan lag dang / /
NK119(he)001:10212: stong nyid snying rje zung du 'jug pa spros pa
NK119(he)001:10213: thams cad dang bral ba'i rang bzhin med pa'i yan
NK119(he)001:10214: lag ste chos sku'i khyad chos su gnas pa'o //
NK119(he)001:10215: de ltar rang don chos kyi sku las ma g.yos bzhin du /
NK119(he)001:10216: gzhan don gzugs sku'i rnam par 'phrul pas 'khor ba ji srid bar don mdzad pa ste /
NK119(he)001:10218: zhi sku dpag bsam shing ltar rnam dag cing //
NK119(he)001:10219: yid bzhin nor bu lta bur rnam mi rtog /'gro
NK119(he)001:10220: grol bar du 'jig rten 'byor slad rtag /'di ni
NK119(he)001:10221: spros dang bral la snang ba yin //
NK119(he)001:10223: de ltar na chos thams cad kyi mthar thug pa gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa yin te /
NK119(he)001:10224: bstan pa'i snying po yin pas gsang sngags slob //
NK119(he)001:10225: ces 'byung ba yin pas 'o skol rnams sems rab tu dang bas /
NK119(he)001:10226: bla med rdo rje theg pa la yi dam bya bar rigs so //
NK119(he)001:10227: theg mchog snying po'i chu 'dzin 'thug po las //
NK119(he)001:10228: bla med dbang bzhi'i sprin zeg 'thul ba dang //
NK119(he)001:10229: mnyam du rim gnyis sgra brgya cher sgrog pas //
NK119(he)001:10230: mchog mthun dngos grub lo thog rgyas par shog /
NK119(he)001:10231: dal 'byor gru chen rdo rje gsum gyis bcings //
NK119(he)001:10232: dpal ldan bla ma'i mnyan pas legs bzung bar //
NK119(he)001:10233: snang grags srid zhi'i mgron tshogs kyis gang bas //
NK119(he)001:10234: 'khor ba'i gzhol 'gro skad cig sgrol byed shog /
NK119(he)001:10235: rta bdun dbang po shar ri'i rtser son bzhin //
NK119(he)001:10236: sgra gcan lam bsal 'byung po'i bya rnams yibs //
NK119(he)001:10237: legs bshad snang ba blo rgyud 'char ba'i mod //
NK119(he)001:10238: thar lam mngon byed ngan 'gro rnams chad shog /
NK119(he)001:10239: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i lam gyi cha lag
NK119(he)001:10240: sdom pa gsum rnam par nges pa'i 'grel ba rnam
NK119(he)001:10242: gsang sngags rig 'dzin gyi sdom pa'i rnam par dbye ba ste /
NK119(he)001:10243: rim par phye ba bzhi pa gtan la dbab zin to //
NK119(he)001:10244: de ltar sdom pa gsum gyi rnam dbye bstan nas /
NK119(he)001:10245: da ni rim par phye ba lnga pa sdom gsum
NK119(he)001:10246: gang zag gcig gis ji ltar nyams su blang ba'i
NK119(he)001:10248: rnam dbye spyir bstan pa dang /
NK119(he)001:10250: 'bras bu nges pas 'gag bsdam pa gsum las /
NK119(he)001:10255: de ltar sdom gsum gang zag rgyud gcig la /
NK119(he)001:10256: rang ldog ma 'dres dgag dgos yongs su rdzogs //
NK119(he)001:10257: ngo bo gnas 'gyur yon tan yar ldan pas //
NK119(he)001:10258: gnad kyis mi 'gal dus skabs gang gtsor spyad //
NK119(he)001:10259: ces pa ni bsdus don sa bcad kyi bsdoms su gnas pa ste /
NK119(he)001:10269: de yang blang yul bsam pa cho ga rnams //
NK119(he)001:10270: so sor nges phyir rang ldog ma 'dres yin //
NK119(he)001:10271: 'di ltar gong du bshad pa ltar sdom pa gsum po re re bzhin /
NK119(he)001:10275: len pa'i tshul cho ga bsrung thabs dang bcas pa
NK119(he)001:10276: so sor ma 'dres pa yod pas na rang ldog
NK119(he)001:10278: gnyis pa dgag dgos yongs rdzogs ni /
NK119(he)001:10279: dgag bya nyon mongs dgos pa mi 'ching bar //
NK119(he)001:10280: rang rang lam gyi ngos nas yongs su rdzogs //
NK119(he)001:10281: spang bsgyur lam du khyer ba so so yang //
NK119(he)001:10282: nyon mongs rang mtshan spang bar mkhas rnams mthun //
NK119(he)001:10283: de la rnam pa thams cad du dgag par bya ba ni /
NK119(he)001:10284: thabs dang mi ldan pa'i nyon mongs pa rang kha ma nyid yin la /
NK119(he)001:10285: dgos pa gang gis nyon mongs pas mi 'ching zhing
NK119(he)001:10286: ye shes bskyed par 'gyur ba ni yang dag pa'i
NK119(he)001:10287: lam ste / dgag dgos yongs rdzogs zhes /
NK119(he)001:10288: dper na thams cad 'dus la mkhar brtsig zer ba bzhin /
NK119(he)001:10289: sdom pa gsum kas rgyud gcig pu de'i mi dge ba sdam pa gcig ste /
NK119(he)001:10291: chos gang zhig dngos dang rgyud nas kun tu 'dod chags pa'i rgyur 'gyur la /
NK119(he)001:10292: kun tu 'dod chags dang bral bar mi 'gyur ba 'di ni chos ma yin /
NK119(he)001:10294: ston pa'i bstan pa ma yin par shes par byos shig /
NK119(he)001:10295: chos gang zhig dngos dang brgyud nas kun tu 'dod
NK119(he)001:10296: chags dang bral ba'i rgyur 'gyur gyi kun tu 'dod
NK119(he)001:10297: chags pa'i rgyur mi 'gyur ba 'di ni chos yin
NK119(he)001:10299: ston pa'i bstan pa yin par shes par byos shig /
NK119(he)001:10300: de bzhin du zhe sdang la sogs pa'i bar mang du gsungs so //
NK119(he)001:10303: zhen pa med cing rmongs pa med //
NK119(he)001:10304: gang zag de ni nyon mongs rnams //
NK119(he)001:10305: legs par nyid du rtogs par 'gyur //
NK119(he)001:10307: 'o na gsang sngags las nyon mongs lnga mi spangs bar bshad pas /
NK119(he)001:10308: de ma spang na yon tan mi skye zhing sangs rgyas mi thob bo //
NK119(he)001:10310: lam dang 'bras bu'i yon tan ni nyon mongs pa'i rgyu kho na las thob ste /
NK119(he)001:10311: ye shes yin zhing de goms par bya ba'i phyir te /
NK119(he)001:10313: dper na lud bcas tshan dang bcas pa la //
NK119(he)001:10314: sa bon skye yi tsha sgos gdung la min //
NK119(he)001:10315: de bzhin nyon mongs la sogs skyes pa la //
NK119(he)001:10316: rgyal sras rnams kyi rgyal ba'i chos rnams skye //
NK119(he)001:10318: ci ngan 'gro log par brgyud cing 'ching ba ma yin nam /
NK119(he)001:10320: nyon mongs pa'i rang bzhin shes nas goms pa des
NK119(he)001:10321: nyes pas mi gos shing bde 'gro'i lus dang 'bras
NK119(he)001:10324: sangs rgyas lam ni thams cad kun //
NK119(he)001:10325: nyon mongs las ni brtsam par bya //
NK119(he)001:10327: de yang rtsa ba pham pa bzhi lta bu la mtshon na /
NK119(he)001:10328: 'dul ba nas srog gcod pa la yul bsam sbyor
NK119(he)001:10329: ba mthar thug bzhi nyon mongs pa rang mtshan pa
NK119(he)001:10330: dgos la / byang sems las thabs la mkhas pa ma yin na /
NK119(he)001:10332: gsang sngags su don dam par rtag chad kyi mtha' dang bral zhing /
NK119(he)001:10333: kun rdzob tu bdag nyid sgyu ma dang /
NK119(he)001:10334: sems can mig yor lta bu'i sgrol ba ltar snang yang /
NK119(he)001:10335: snang dus nas sems can rang mtshan du ma grub pas srog bcad du med de /
NK119(he)001:10336: rmi lam sgyu ma bzhin no //
NK119(he)001:10337: srog gcad bya dang gcod byed du snang ba sems
NK119(he)001:10338: 'khrul pa'i log rtog tsam las don la gnyis su
NK119(he)001:10341: sgyu ma mig yor lta bu'i tshul //
NK119(he)001:10342: srog med srog kyang bcad du med //
NK119(he)001:10343: srog kyang skyes bu'i log rtog tsam //
NK119(he)001:10344: bden pa gnyis ka dbyer med cing //
NK119(he)001:10346: yul 'khor skyong gis zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK119(he)001:10347: bdag dang gzhan dang srog kyang skyes bu rnams //
NK119(he)001:10348: med par snang la rang bzhin gnyis med pa //
NK119(he)001:10349: phyin ci log tsam nyid las gzhan med de //
NK119(he)001:10350: yang dag kun brtags sgyu ma'i tshul //
NK119(he)001:10353: ji ltar sgyu ma mkhan gyis 'jig rten na //
NK119(he)001:10354: sems can brgya phrag mang po sprul byas te //
NK119(he)001:10355: sprul pa de dag thams cad bsad gyur kyang //
NK119(he)001:10356: sgyu ma de dag bsad pa yod min ltar //
NK119(he)001:10357: 'gro ba 'di dag sgyu ma'i rang bzhin te //
NK119(he)001:10358: 'di la mtha' ni nam yang dmigs su med //
NK119(he)001:10359: gang dag de ltar mtha' yas mos byed pa //
NK119(he)001:10360: de dag 'jig rten na ni tshor ba med //
NK119(he)001:10361: gang dag rang bzhin med chos 'di zhes pa //
NK119(he)001:10362: dpa' ba de dag 'jig rten mya ngan 'da' //
NK119(he)001:10363: 'dod pa'i yon tan spyod kyang chags med cing //
NK119(he)001:10364: chags pa rnams spang sems can 'dul bar byed //
NK119(he)001:10365: mi dbang rnams ni sems can phan par mdzad //
NK119(he)001:10367: ma byin par len pa la'ang /
NK119(he)001:10368: gsang sngags kyi lam 'dir chos thams cad bden gnyis
NK119(he)001:10369: dbyer med don la rang bzhin ma grub cing tha
NK119(he)001:10370: snyad du'ang grub pa med de /
NK119(he)001:10371: sgyu ma mkhan rang gi sprul pa'i nor rang gis longs spyod pa ltar /
NK119(he)001:10372: gzhan gyi rdzas dang nor len pa po tha dad med par rang bzhin gcig tu shes na /
NK119(he)001:10373: rang snang gi rdzas la rang snang gi len pa'i
NK119(he)001:10374: tshul gyis ma byin par blangs kyang blang bya blang
NK119(he)001:10375: byed blang rgyu'i mtshan ma'i 'khor gsum gyi chos thams
NK119(he)001:10376: cad ye nas rnam par dag pa nam mkha' lta
NK119(he)001:10379: ji ltar sgyu mas sgyu ma'i nor blang ste //
NK119(he)001:10380: rmi lam nang bzhin dgos pa de spyad kyang //
NK119(he)001:10381: de la las med rnam par smin pa med //
NK119(he)001:10382: de bzhin chags sems ye shes 'dir bslab te //
NK119(he)001:10383: mya ngan 'das pa dam pa'i mchog zhir 'gro //
NK119(he)001:10386: gzhan don du gyur pa'i dgos pa khyad par can yod na /
NK119(he)001:10387: ji ltar phan pa de ltar smras na nyes pa med de /
NK119(he)001:10388: 'di ltar 'khor 'das kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad
NK119(he)001:10389: rmi lam sgyu ma lta bu'i rang bzhin yin la
NK119(he)001:10390: / de dag so so'i ming dang tshig tu btags
NK119(he)001:10391: pa de yang so so'i rtog pas glo bur du
NK119(he)001:10393: de ltar rtogs na rdzun gyi tshig gtang yul gtong
NK119(he)001:10394: byed gtang rgyu dang bcas pa chos su grub pa
NK119(he)001:10395: ming tsam btags pa tsam du'ang yod pa ma yin
NK119(he)001:10396: te sgra de nyid kyang phyi nang gang du'ang med
NK119(he)001:10397: pas grags stong skye med yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK119(he)001:10398: nye bar 'khor gyi zhus pa'i mdzod las /
NK119(he)001:10399: ji ltar changs pas bcangs te byis pa la //
NK119(he)001:10400: ston cing ngag tu yod ces brjod byas nas //
NK119(he)001:10401: de yi changs pa stong par mthong nas ni //
NK119(he)001:10402: byis pa de ni cho nges ngu ba ltar //
NK119(he)001:10403: de bzhin sangs rgyas bsam gyis mi khyab par //
NK119(he)001:10404: sems can tshul la mkhas shing mkhyen pa rnams //
NK119(he)001:10405: chos rnams 'di kun gsog gsob mkhyen gyur nas //
NK119(he)001:10406: 'jig rten dag la yod dang med ces ston //
NK119(he)001:10409: nyon mongs pa 'dod chags rang kha ma'i rtog pa
NK119(he)001:10410: log nas bde stong zag pa med pa'i ye shes
NK119(he)001:10411: rgyud la bskyed pa'i thabs lam la nyes pa med
NK119(he)001:10412: de / 'di ni chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin
NK119(he)001:10413: gang du'ang ma chags pa dngos po dang mtshan ma
NK119(he)001:10414: gang du'ang ma grub pa'i gnas lugs stong pa nyid
NK119(he)001:10415: rtogs pa ni chags pa ste shes rab mtha' gnyis
NK119(he)001:10416: la mi gnas pa'i ngang nas /
NK119(he)001:10417: yab yum snyoms par 'jug pa'i ye shes la chags
NK119(he)001:10418: pa nyid la tha mal gyi 'dod chags med pa
NK119(he)001:10419: ni thabs snying rje chen po'i rang bzhin te /
NK119(he)001:10420: tha mal gyi 'dod chags las mchog tu gyur pa
NK119(he)001:10421: bde stong gnyis med kyi ye shes la rol pa
NK119(he)001:10422: ste / tshangs par spyod pa rnam par dag pa'i chags pa chen po ste /
NK119(he)001:10424: ji ltar rmi lam sgyu ma'i rang bzhin du //
NK119(he)001:10425: skyes bu 'dod bstan de yang de 'dra zhes //
NK119(he)001:10426: ngo bo nyid kyis stong gsal dngos po med //
NK119(he)001:10427: las med rnam par smin pa de yod min //
NK119(he)001:10429: des na 'dod chags sangs rgyas lam //
NK119(he)001:10430: rang bzhin dbyer med yin par ni //
NK119(he)001:10431: rab tu rtogs par gyur pas na //
NK119(he)001:10432: 'dod chags las ni zhen pa med //
NK119(he)001:10434: de bzhin 'dod chags gang mchod pa //
NK119(he)001:10435: de ni sangs rgyas mchod pa yin //
NK119(he)001:10438: 'dod chags dang ni stong pa nyid //
NK119(he)001:10439: de gnyis gnyis su yod ma yin //
NK119(he)001:10441: dus 'khor gyi rgyud don dam bsnyen pa las /
NK119(he)001:10442: 'dod chags gang zhig gis ni sems can gdul gyur pa //
NK119(he)001:10443: de nyid kyis ni rnal 'byor srid pa'i pha rol bsgrod //
NK119(he)001:10444: dug gang gis ni sems can 'ching bar 'gyur ba yis //
NK119(he)001:10445: dug sngags shes pa de nyid kyis ni nad 'phrog byed //
NK119(he)001:10448: ji ltar tshad pas tshig pa yang //
NK119(he)001:10449: me nyid la ni gdung bar bya //
NK119(he)001:10450: de bzhin 'dod chags mes tshig pa //
NK119(he)001:10452: skye bo mi bzad pa yi las //
NK119(he)001:10453: gang dang gang gis 'ching gyur pa //
NK119(he)001:10454: thabs dang ldan na de nyid kyis //
NK119(he)001:10458: bzlog pa'i bsgom pa 'di nyid ni //
NK119(he)001:10459: sangs rgyas mu stegs kyis mi shes //
NK119(he)001:10461: des na tshangs spyod la gnas pa dang dbang gsum
NK119(he)001:10462: pa'i rnal 'byor pa gnyis gnad gcig ste nyon mongs
NK119(he)001:10463: pa rang mtshan pas ma gos pa'i phyir ro //
NK119(he)001:10464: rnam pa thams cad du mi spyod pa nyid gtso na /
NK119(he)001:10465: bu chung dang ma ning la sdom pa lhag par skye ba rigs so //
NK119(he)001:10467: dbang gsum po dngos 'gal du gnas pa yin na /
NK119(he)001:10468: sngags kyi rten khyim pa kho na 'ong bar rigs pa las /
NK119(he)001:10469: rten ni gsum las dge slong mchog /
NK119(he)001:10472: yon tan thams cad kyi gzhi ma dam pa'i chos 'dul ba las rab tu byung ba /
NK119(he)001:10473: so sor thar pa'i sdom pa la gnas pa /
NK119(he)001:10474: gsum la skyabs su 'gro ba'i yid kyis sngar brten tam /
NK119(he)001:10477: gsang sngags las mi spang bar bshad pa'ang /
NK119(he)001:10478: nyon mongs pa rnams kun rdzob tu smig rgyu dang
NK119(he)001:10479: 'dra ste skad cig gis mi rtag pas rang gi
NK119(he)001:10480: rang spangs shing / don dam par gang gis dngos
NK119(he)001:10481: por yang ma grub pas kun tu btsal na yang
NK119(he)001:10482: mi rnyed pa'i phyir spang du med de /
NK119(he)001:10483: phyir mi ldog pa 'khor lo'i mdo las /
NK119(he)001:10484: ma rig nam mkha' ji bzhin te //
NK119(he)001:10485: chos rnams thams cad mtshan nyid med //
NK119(he)001:10486: 'dod chags med cing zhe sdang med //
NK119(he)001:10487: nga rgyal dang ni phrag dog kun //
NK119(he)001:10488: sgyu 'dra ngo bo nyid med de //
NK119(he)001:10489: yod med mi dmigs rten dang bral //
NK119(he)001:10492: nyon mong rnams ni yul na mi gnas dbang sogs la min bar na'ang min //
NK119(he)001:10493: de las gzhan na'ang min na 'di dag gar gnas 'gro ba kun gnod de //
NK119(he)001:10494: 'di ni sgyu 'dra de phyir snying la 'jigs spang shes phyir brtson pa bsten //
NK119(he)001:10496: ye nas stong pa'i dngos 'di la //
NK119(he)001:10497: thob pa ci yod shor ci yod //
NK119(he)001:10498: mi dgar ci yod dgar ci yod //
NK119(he)001:10499: thams cad nam mkha' 'dra bar ni //
NK119(he)001:10500: bdag 'dras yongs su bzung bar bgyi //
NK119(he)001:10502: thabs kyi zin na lam gyi grogs yin te /
NK119(he)001:10504: nyon mongs lam ni dag pa che //
NK119(he)001:10505: thabs kyi 'dod yon rgyan gyi mchog /
NK119(he)001:10506: thams cad thams cad rol pa las //
NK119(he)001:10507: myur du he ru ka dpal 'gyur //
NK119(he)001:10510: ji ltar grong khyer rnams kyi mi gtsang lud //
NK119(he)001:10511: de ni bu ram shing pa'i zhing la phan //
NK119(he)001:10512: de bzhin byang chub sems dpa'i mi gtsang lud //
NK119(he)001:10513: de ni rgyal ba'i zhing gi chos la phan //
NK119(he)001:10515: de yang nyon mongs pa lam du khyer tshul yang /
NK119(he)001:10516: rje gong bu ba skyo ston sh+aakya ye shes kyis zhal nas /
NK119(he)001:10517: skad cig ma dang po la nyon mongs pa gcig thol gyis skyes pa la /
NK119(he)001:10518: skad cig ma gnyis pa la chos nyid du shes pas lam du byed par gsungs kyang /
NK119(he)001:10519: de ltar na nyon mongs pa lam du byed pa min te /
NK119(he)001:10520: de'i rjes thog gi shes pa lam byed yin pa'i phyir /
NK119(he)001:10521: rje gsang bdag sgro phug pa ni /
NK119(he)001:10522: nyon mongs pa kam gyis skyes pa la lam du byed de /
NK119(he)001:10523: de yang rtogs pa lta bu'i rtsis zin pa /
NK119(he)001:10524: rang rgyud du ma shor ba /
NK119(he)001:10525: nyon mongs pa rang gi mtha' la ma zhen pa
NK119(he)001:10526: ste chos gsum ldan zhig lam du byed gsungs pa
NK119(he)001:10528: kun mkhyen klong chen rab 'byams kyi bzhed pa /
NK119(he)001:10529: nyon mongs pa zhe sdang lta bu gcig sal gyis skyes tshe /
NK119(he)001:10530: gti mug gi sgrib pas lung ma bstan du ma
NK119(he)001:10531: song bar gsal le hrig ge 'char ba de ka
NK119(he)001:10533: de las gzhan rjes shes kyi gnyen po bsten pa
NK119(he)001:10534: lta bu ni rtog pa'i 'phro mthud pa sems kyi
NK119(he)001:10535: cha la / de dus kyi gsal le ba rang ni gnas pa'i cha yin pas bzhag la /
NK119(he)001:10536: gting gsal gyi ye shes rig pa skad gcig ma
NK119(he)001:10537: rjen ce re ba de ka skyong bar gsungs shing
NK119(he)001:10538: / de yang zhe sdang gi gsal ngar des lung
NK119(he)001:10539: ma bstan gyi rten nam stengs so med par ches
NK119(he)001:10540: dngos su gsal ba'i phyir nyon mongs ye shes skye
NK119(he)001:10541: ba'i rgyur bshad de rmad byung rgyal po las /
NK119(he)001:10542: stong pa bsgom pas ye shes skye mi 'gyur //
NK119(he)001:10543: snang ba 'di la zhen pa drag byas na //
NK119(he)001:10544: nyon mongs shas che'i sa nas ye shes 'char //
NK119(he)001:10545: dper na chu bo chen po bug pa bzhin //
NK119(he)001:10548: dge dang mi dge'i las rnams kun //
NK119(he)001:10549: de nyid shes pas grol bar 'gyur //
NK119(he)001:10550: nyon mongs ye shes chen po ste //
NK119(he)001:10551: nags la me bzhin rnal 'byor grogs //
NK119(he)001:10554: thabs chen rnams dang ldan pa la //
NK119(he)001:10555: nyon mongs byang chub yan lag 'gyur //
NK119(he)001:10558: de ltar na nyon mongs pa lam du byas pa
NK119(he)001:10559: ma yin te thabs lam du byas pa'i phyir ro
NK119(he)001:10561: nas las zan du byed par 'dod dam phye las zan du byed /
NK119(he)001:10562: rngo btag byas na phye'i zan du 'gyur gyi nas kyi zan du mi 'a grub bo //
NK119(he)001:10563: rgyu nas la rkyen rngo btag byas pas zan du 'grub bo //
NK119(he)001:10565: 'dir yang rgyu nyon mongs pa las rkyen thabs kyis lam du byed pa kho na te /
NK119(he)001:10566: de yang man ngag rin po che'i mdzod las /
NK119(he)001:10567: gnyen pos rkyen ngan thub pa'i chos drug ni //
NK119(he)001:10568: nyan thos bzhin du dgra ltar spang ba dang //
NK119(he)001:10569: pha rol phyin ltar yongs su sbyangs ba dang //
NK119(he)001:10570: sngags ltar thabs kyi lam du bsgyur ba dang //
NK119(he)001:10571: yang zab gnad kyis rang sar grol ba dang //
NK119(he)001:10572: mtha' bral ngang du rang zhir btang ba dang //
NK119(he)001:10573: bya brtsal med par yang la la bzla ste //
NK119(he)001:10574: blo rig bstun nas gang ltar sgom byed kyang //
NK119(he)001:10575: 'gag la nyon mongs rang gar ma song gces //
NK119(he)001:10577: de ltar nyon mongs pa'i dngos po gcig la spang
NK119(he)001:10578: bsgyur lam khyer gang byas kyang nyon mongs pa rang
NK119(he)001:10579: mtshan pa spang bar don mthun te /
NK119(he)001:10580: gser las byas pa'i rang bzhin gcig la /
NK119(he)001:10581: chol zang du byas pa'i tshe rtsog pa dang /
NK119(he)001:10582: gzhong bar byas pa'i tshe gtsang ba dang /
NK119(he)001:10583: gdu bur byas pa'i tshe rgyan dang /
NK119(he)001:10584: lha'i sku gzugs su byas pa'i tshe mchod pa'i rten
NK119(he)001:10585: du byed bzhin du rkyen gyis theg pa rang rang
NK119(he)001:10587: ye nas dag pa'i ye shes yin pas /
NK119(he)001:10588: gzhi lam 'bras bu'i chos su nyon mongs pa de
NK119(he)001:10589: nyid 'gyur ba'i spang bya ma yin pa'i rgyu mtshan
NK119(he)001:10591: gsum pa ngo bo gnas 'gyur ni /
NK119(he)001:10592: sdom pa gsum po de yang /
NK119(he)001:10593: so thar kun bslangs sems bskyed kyis zin na //
NK119(he)001:10594: nyes spyod sdom pa zhes bya'i tshul khrims yin //
NK119(he)001:10595: dbang thob rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sdom par 'gyur //
NK119(he)001:10596: de phyir ngo bo gnas 'gyur yin no zhes //
NK119(he)001:10597: 'bum phrag lnga pa'i lung gis gsal bar grub //
NK119(he)001:10598: de yang byang chub tu sems bskyed pa'i rtsis zin
NK119(he)001:10599: pa na nyan thos so thar thams cad byang sems
NK119(he)001:10601: dbang thob pa na gnyis ka rig 'dzin sngags kyi sdom pa'i ngo bor gnas 'gyur ba yin no //
NK119(he)001:10603: rgyud 'bum phrag lnga pa'i lung de kho na nyid
NK119(he)001:10604: kyi ye shes grub pa zhes bya ba las byung
NK119(he)001:10605: ba / rdo yi rigs kyi bye brag bzhus //
NK119(he)001:10606: lcags dang zangs dang dngul du 'byung //
NK119(he)001:10607: gser 'gyur rtsi yi dngos po yis //
NK119(he)001:10608: kun kyang gser du bsgyur bar byed //
NK119(he)001:10609: de bzhin sems kyi bre brag gis //
NK119(he)001:10610: rigs can gsum gyi sdom pa yang //
NK119(he)001:10614: 'di sngar yang drangs pas zlos skyon du sems par mi bya ste /
NK119(he)001:10615: kun byed kyi lung khungs gcig klong chen pas gnas
NK119(he)001:10616: lugs mdzod 'grel du lan gsum drangs pa bzhin no
NK119(he)001:10618: rig pa 'dzin pa dang byang chub sems pa'i sdom pa gnyis ni nang mi 'gal mod /
NK119(he)001:10619: so sor thar pa 'di ni byang sdom gyi rten du mi rung ste /
NK119(he)001:10620: so so thar pa ni gling gsum gyi skyes pa bud me las gzhan la mi skye la /
NK119(he)001:10621: byang sems ni 'gro ba kun la skye ba'i phyir dang /
NK119(he)001:10622: gnas pa'i rten yang so thar ni shi 'phos la sogs pas gtong la /
NK119(he)001:10623: byang sems ni byang chub bar mi gtong ba'i phyir zhe na /
NK119(he)001:10624: nyan thos dang thun mong pa'i so sor thar pa ni de ltar kho bo yang 'dod la /
NK119(he)001:10625: theg chen so sor thar pa ni ji srid 'tsho ba'i bar khas blangs kyi /
NK119(he)001:10626: sngags thob dus gtong rgyu ma bshad pa'i phyir dang /
NK119(he)001:10627: byang sems byang chub bar khas blangs kyi sngags thob dus gtong rgyur ma bshad pa'i phyir ro //
NK119(he)001:10628: 'o na gsum ldan gyi tha snyad med de sngags sdom gcig pu thal zhe na /
NK119(he)001:10629: des na ngo bo sngags su gcig pas gzhan gnyis gnas 'gyur yin la /
NK119(he)001:10630: ldog cha so sor ma 'dres te khas blangs pa'i
NK119(he)001:10631: cha las nyams rkyen ma byung bar so sor gnas
NK119(he)001:10632: pa'i phyir ro // zhes shing rta rnam dag nas gsungs so //
NK119(he)001:10633: gzhan nas thun mong so thar khas blangs pa'i dge
NK119(he)001:10634: slong des sems bskyed nas dkyil 'khor du zhugs pa
NK119(he)001:10635: na gsum ldan du ci ltar 'gyur zhe na /
NK119(he)001:10636: dge slong des sems bskyed pa na so thar thams
NK119(he)001:10637: cad byang chub sems dpa' nyes spyod sdom pa'i tshul
NK119(he)001:10639: dkyil 'khor du zhugs pas sdom pa thams cad rig pa 'dzin pa'i sdom par 'gyur te /
NK119(he)001:10641: dper na rdo las zangs su 'gyur //
NK119(he)001:10642: zangs las gser gyi rnam pa ste //
NK119(he)001:10643: zangs kyi dus na rdo med cing //
NK119(he)001:10644: gser du gyur pas zangs mi snang //
NK119(he)001:10645: rig 'dzin nang gi dge slong la //
NK119(he)001:10646: so sor thar dang byang chub sems //
NK119(he)001:10647: gnyis po gnas pa nyid du ni //
NK119(he)001:10648: sangs rgyas kyis kyang ma gsungs so //
NK119(he)001:10650: rig 'dzin sngags kyi rang dus na so sor thar
NK119(he)001:10651: dang byang sems rdzas gzhan tha dad pa med do
NK119(he)001:10652: // sngags kyi sdom pa rdzas su ngo bo gnas 'gyur du yod pa'i phyir la /
NK119(he)001:10653: ldog pa ma 'dres par yod de /
NK119(he)001:10654: slob dpon sgeg pa'i rdo rjes /
NK119(he)001:10655: theg chen dam tshig la gnas na //
NK119(he)001:10656: dge slong byang chub sems dpa' dang //
NK119(he)001:10659: bzhi pa yon tan yar ldan ni //
NK119(he)001:10660: 'jig rten rnal 'byor rnal 'byor blo khyad kyis //
NK119(he)001:10661: gong ma gong mas gnod phyir 'og ma yi //
NK119(he)001:10662: yon tan yar ldan 'og ma zil gyis gnon //
NK119(he)001:10664: yongs rdzogs gsang ba'i rgyud las /
NK119(he)001:10665: rgyal dgongs theg pa mtha' yas pa //
NK119(he)001:10666: rnal 'byor pa yang blo khyad kyis //
NK119(he)001:10667: gong ma gong ma'i lta ba yis //
NK119(he)001:10669: de phyir gong mas khyad par 'phags //
NK119(he)001:10671: gong du rim par phye ba dang por bshad pa
NK119(he)001:10672: ltar nyan thos nas a ti'i bar gcig nas gcig
NK119(he)001:10673: tu khyad par du 'phags pa kho na yin zhing
NK119(he)001:10674: / 'di ltar so sor thar pa'i sdom par ni byang sems dang sngags sdom med la /
NK119(he)001:10675: byang sems so thar 'dus kyang sngags sdom med pa dang /
NK119(he)001:10676: sngags sdom du sdom pa 'og ma gnyis ka 'dus te /
NK119(he)001:10677: bre gsum gyi nang du bre do 'du ba ltar
NK119(he)001:10678: yon tan yar ldan du 'dus pas 'og ma zil
NK119(he)001:10679: gyis gnon te / nye ba 'khor gyis zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK119(he)001:10680: nye ba 'khor nyan thos kyi theg pa pa rnams kyi sbyor ba yang gzhan /
NK119(he)001:10681: lhag pa'i bsam pa yang gzhan /
NK119(he)001:10682: theg pa chen po la yang dag par zhugs pa
NK119(he)001:10683: rnams kyis sbyor ba yang gzhan lhag pa'i bsam pa
NK119(he)001:10685: nye bar 'khor de la nya thos kyi theg pa
NK119(he)001:10686: pa'i tshul khrims yongs su dag pa gang yin pa
NK119(he)001:10687: de ni byang chub sems dpa'i tshul khrims yongs su
NK119(he)001:10689: byang chub sems dpa'i tshul khrims yongs su dag pa ni /
NK119(he)001:10690: nyan thos kyi theg pa pa'i tshul khrims yongs su dag pa nyid yin no //
NK119(he)001:10692: nyan thos kyi theg pa ni skad gcig tsam srid
NK119(he)001:10693: par skye bar len par spro na'ang nyes pa yin
NK119(he)001:10694: la / byang chub sems dpa' ni sems can gyi
NK119(he)001:10695: don la bskal pa dpag tu med par 'khor bar
NK119(he)001:10696: gnas pa la mi skyo ba yin no //
NK119(he)001:10698: sgyu 'phrul dra ba chen po las /
NK119(he)001:10699: bla med mchog gi sdom pa ru //
NK119(he)001:10700: 'dul ba'i dbang gis tshul khrims dang //
NK119(he)001:10701: ma lus kun 'dus rnam par dang //
NK119(he)001:10704: dbang gsum bgrod pa'i rnal 'byor pa //
NK119(he)001:10705: de ni dge slong chen por gsungs //
NK119(he)001:10706: de yis thams cad bya ba nyid //
NK119(he)001:10708: pad ma nying gung brtsegs pa'i rgyud las /
NK119(he)001:10709: mi dge spangs shing bag yod brten la sogs //
NK119(he)001:10710: brtan khrims rab 'bring tha ma'i sdom pa yang /
NK119(he)001:10711: stong nyid snying rje ldan na bsrung mi dgos //
NK119(he)001:10712: ma bsrungs sdom pa chen po de la gnas //
NK119(he)001:10713: snying rje byang chub sems dang ldan pa yi //
NK119(he)001:10714: rang las gzhan gces don du srog yang bcad //
NK119(he)001:10715: stong nyid dam tshig chen po'i rnal 'byor pa //
NK119(he)001:10716: ci ltar spyad kyang bde ba chen po nyid //
NK119(he)001:10718: des na nyan thos kyi so thar yang 'dir 'dus te /
NK119(he)001:10719: gtso bo rang don sgrub pa'i sdom pa de'ang rnal
NK119(he)001:10720: 'byor pas rang nyid sdug bsngal las thar pa'i phyir
NK119(he)001:10722: srog gcod dus nyid na sems kyi zhe sdang la
NK119(he)001:10723: sogs pa'i mi dge ba med pas rang gi zag
NK119(he)001:10724: pa rang min pa bsdom pa'i phyir /
NK119(he)001:10725: srog gcod spangs pa'i sdom par 'dus te /
NK119(he)001:10727: chos kun ye nas dag pa'i phyir //
NK119(he)001:10728: log rtog ye nas rnam par dag /
NK119(he)001:10729: dam tshig 'di ni rmad po che //
NK119(he)001:10731: de ltar gzhan kun la'ang sbyar ro //
NK119(he)001:10732: byang sems kyi bslab bya yang yar ldan du 'dus te /
NK119(he)001:10733: spyod pa gang zhig nyon mongs pa rang kha ma bsdams sas sdom pa'i tshul khrims /
NK119(he)001:10734: de la brten nas yon tan gong 'phel du ston pas dge ba chos sdud /
NK119(he)001:10735: thabs des gzhan don 'ba' zhig byed pas sems can don byed kyi tshul khrims 'dus te /
NK119(he)001:10736: thabs chen rnams dang ldan pa la //
NK119(he)001:10737: nyon mongs byang chub yan lag 'gyur //
NK119(he)001:10739: lnga pa gnad kyi mi 'gal ba ni /
NK119(he)001:10740: rtsa ba bzhi la sogs pa pham ltung thams cad la'ang /
NK119(he)001:10741: lha dang sngags dang chos kyi 'du shes gsum gyis 'khrig na rnal 'byor de //
NK119(he)001:10742: yul bsam sbyor ba mthar thug ma tshang bas //
NK119(he)001:10743: rmi lam ji bzhin gnad kyis 'gal mi srid //
NK119(he)001:10744: de yang mi tshangs bar spyod pa lta bu la mtshon na /
NK119(he)001:10745: so sor thar pa las ni /
NK119(he)001:10746: bdag nyid dge slong yin pa /
NK119(he)001:10747: yul khams drug ldan gyi mi'i bud med dgos pa la /
NK119(he)001:10748: 'dir bdag dang phyag rgyar lhar bskyed pas lus ngag lha'i 'du shes /
NK119(he)001:10749: bsam pa 'dod chags rang kha mas bslangs te ngo tsha med par ma 'khrul ba dgos pa las /
NK119(he)001:10750: 'dir dkyil 'khor gsum du shes pa'i ngang nas rig
NK119(he)001:10751: pa skad cig mar ngos 'dzin par 'dod pa dang
NK119(he)001:10752: / sbyor ba'ang zag byed du nor bu bcug nas pags rim las 'das pa dgos pa las /
NK119(he)001:10753: rdo rje dang pad mar gsal bas de gnyis rang
NK119(he)001:10754: mtshan pa med pas byin rlabs chos kyi 'du shes
NK119(he)001:10755: / mthar thug bde ba bdag gir ba myong dgos pa las /
NK119(he)001:10756: bde stong zung 'jug gi ye shes dga' ba bzhi'i
NK119(he)001:10757: rim pas rnam byang gi chos thams cad rgyud la
NK119(he)001:10758: mngon du byed pa ni 'dod pa chos kyi 'du
NK119(he)001:10759: shes dang gsum gyis zin pas /
NK119(he)001:10760: yul bsam sbyor ba mthar thug bzhi ma tshang bas rmi lam dang 'dra ste /
NK119(he)001:10761: rmi lam ni bkag byar med de /
NK119(he)001:10763: rmi lam ni med pa dang 'dra'o //
NK119(he)001:10765: byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pa dang 'gal ba med de /
NK119(he)001:10766: gzhan la phan 'dod kyi thabs khyad par can gyis zin pa'i phyir /
NK119(he)001:10767: stong nyid snying rje gnyis dang ldan pa ni gnang ba ste /
NK119(he)001:10769: gang dag sems can don 'gyur ba'o //
NK119(he)001:10770: thabs de rgyal sras bslab pa'i mchog /
NK119(he)001:10771: sprin las char chen 'bab pa yis //
NK119(he)001:10772: lo thog phun tshogs byed pa bzhin //
NK119(he)001:10773: zhes pa kun la sbyar ro //
NK119(he)001:10776: mda' mkhan mo la phyag rgyar mdzad nas /
NK119(he)001:10777: khar sang phan chad dge slong min //
NK119(he)001:10778: khar sang phan chad bram ze yin //
NK119(he)001:10779: de ring tshun chad dge slong yin //
NK119(he)001:10780: he ru ka dpal dge slong mchog /
NK119(he)001:10781: ces gsungs nas de'i rjes la klu sgrub kyi mkhan po mdzad do //
NK119(he)001:10785: bsam pa zhe sdang gis gsod sems sbyor ba mtshon sogs /
NK119(he)001:10786: mthar thug yi rangs dgos pa las /
NK119(he)001:10789: bdud rtsi lnga 'am zag rdzas la /
NK119(he)001:10790: gzugs dang ming rus bcas pa la //
NK119(he)001:10791: zhes pas mi dang mi las gzhan pa'i dud 'gro la sogs ma yin la /
NK119(he)001:10792: rnam shes h'u du gsal ba /
NK119(he)001:10793: sdug bsngal bral 'dod kyi bsam pas chos dbyings su spar te /
NK119(he)001:10794: sangs rgyas kyi sar bkod pa ni mthar thug ste 'gal ba med de /
NK119(he)001:10796: dper na sgyu ma mkhan gyis bzhi mdor sprul byas te //
NK119(he)001:10797: skye bo phal cher mgo mang bye ba gcod byed pa //
NK119(he)001:10798: bsad bya de dag ci 'dra de 'dra byang chub sems //
NK119(he)001:10799: 'gro kun sprul 'drar rab shes de la 'jigs pa med //
NK119(he)001:10801: ma byin par len pa la'ang /
NK119(he)001:10802: yul mis bdag tu bzung ba'i longs spyod bsam pa rku sems /
NK119(he)001:10803: sbyor ba rin thang tshang ba /
NK119(he)001:10804: mthar thug thob blo dgos pa las /
NK119(he)001:10805: 'dir bdag gzhan gnyis su med par rtogs pas rang
NK119(he)001:10806: snang gi rdzas rmi lam lta bu len pa dang
NK119(he)001:10807: / rang snang la longs spyod pa las rku sems med la /
NK119(he)001:10808: sbyor ba rmi lam rgyu ma ltar rtogs pas /
NK119(he)001:10809: mthar thug thob bya thob byed med pas 'gal ba med de /
NK119(he)001:10811: ji ltar sgyu mas sgyu ma'i nor blangs te //
NK119(he)001:10812: rmi lam nang bzhin dgos pa de spyad kyang //
NK119(he)001:10813: de la las med rnam par smin pa med //
NK119(he)001:10815: lung 'dir sngar yang drangs pas zlos so zhe na /
NK119(he)001:10817: dus 'khor gyi 'brel chen pad ma dkar por mtshan brjod tshar gsum drangs pa dang /
NK119(he)001:10818: tshig gsal du ting 'dzin rgyal po'i mdo lung re re'ang du ma drangs pa lta bu'o //
NK119(he)001:10819: rdzun du smra ba yang yul mi'i 'gro ba la
NK119(he)001:10820: 'du shes bsgyur phyir lha la sogs pa ma mthong
NK119(he)001:10822: zhes pa la sogs dgos pa la /
NK119(he)001:10823: chos thams cad rdzun mnyam du shes nas phan pa'i
NK119(he)001:10824: yan lag tu smra ba'i phyir na 'gal ba med
NK119(he)001:10826: dngos po med la dngos por ston //
NK119(he)001:10827: dngos por snang la med smra ba //
NK119(he)001:10828: rgyal ba kun gyi bka' yin te //
NK119(he)001:10829: bslu ba'i dam tshig chen po yin //
NK119(he)001:10832: dper na sngags kyi kun tu spyod pa'i skabs su chang 'thung pa la /
NK119(he)001:10833: nyan thos pas ni ltung ba dang /
NK119(he)001:10834: byang sems pas phyogs mthun gyi nyes par bshad kyang nyes par mi 'gyur te /
NK119(he)001:10835: de'i tshe bdag nyid dge slong ngam /
NK119(he)001:10836: byang chub sems dpa' yin dgos pa la /
NK119(he)001:10837: lhar bskyed pas gzhi gzhan du 'gyur /
NK119(he)001:10838: dngos po myos byed chang yin dgos pa la /
NK119(he)001:10839: sngags dang phyag rgya ting nge 'dzin gyis bdud rtsir
NK119(he)001:10840: byin gyis brlabs te longs spyod par gsungs pa dang
NK119(he)001:10841: / bsam pa dang 'du shes gzhan du ma 'gyur ba dgos pa la /
NK119(he)001:10842: lha dkyil 'khor bdud rtsir 'du shes gnas 'gyur pas
NK119(he)001:10843: nyes pa med pa'i steng du lha mnyes pa dang
NK119(he)001:10844: / lta ba ting 'dzin bsgom pa'i grogs su 'char
NK119(he)001:10845: bas yon tan yar ldan du yod pa bzhin no
NK119(he)001:10846: / // de bzhin du bslab pa'i cha shas kun la sbyar bar bya'o //
NK119(he)001:10847: mdor na nyes pa bskyed na sdom pa gsum kar bkag la /
NK119(he)001:10848: yon tan bskyed na gang nas kyang bkag pa med
NK119(he)001:10849: pas bslab pa rnams kyi che 'bring dang gnang bkag
NK119(he)001:10850: shes shing spyir btang ba dang dmigs kyis bsal ba
NK119(he)001:10852: zhes kun mkhyen rin po ches nges don shing rta chen por gsungs so //
NK119(he)001:10854: dam pa rin po che la kun dgas zhus pa /
NK119(he)001:10855: nyan thos kyi tshul khrims sna gcig la brten 'tshal lam zhus pas /
NK119(he)001:10856: brten na yang bzang ste thar pa'i skas yin /
NK119(he)001:10857: lar mang po mang po nyung ngu nyung ngu'i nang du 'du ba yin /
NK119(he)001:10858: gsang sngags kyi dam tshig gtsang mar bsrung na /
NK119(he)001:10859: 'og ma'i bslab pa ma bsrungs kyang der 'du ba yin /
NK119(he)001:10860: sdom pa gsum la rdzas tha dad pa med /
NK119(he)001:10861: tha dad du bsrung ba yang yod de yar ldan yin gsungs so //
NK119(he)001:10862: des na sdom pa gsum gyi spang blang gang zhig /
NK119(he)001:10863: thabs snying rje chen po dang shes rab stong pa
NK119(he)001:10864: nyid kyis zin pa'i tshe 'gal 'du'i rnam par mi
NK119(he)001:10865: 'gyur te / ting 'dzin rgyal po'i mdo las /
NK119(he)001:10866: lus kyi sdom pa dag ni dben zhing stong //
NK119(he)001:10867: de dag mtshan nyid med par bar snang bzhin //
NK119(he)001:10868: sdom pa'i mtshan nyid 'di 'dra sus shes pa //
NK119(he)001:10869: de la sdom pa nam yang med mi 'gyur //
NK119(he)001:10870: ngag gi sdom pa gang gis bslab ldan pa //
NK119(he)001:10871: tshig dang sgra rnams brag cha 'dra bar shes //
NK119(he)001:10872: mi lam lta bur 'jigs pa med par 'jug /
NK119(he)001:10873: de ni ngag gi sdom pa dben zhes bya //
NK119(he)001:10874: yid kyi sdom pa nam yang mi dmigs shing //
NK119(he)001:10875: rtog pa med la rloms sems mi byed de //
NK119(he)001:10876: de yang mi lta mngon par mi byed de //
NK119(he)001:10877: de ni yid kyi sdom pa mchog tu brjod //
NK119(he)001:10878: zag med sdom pa gang zhig sus shes pa //
NK119(he)001:10879: de la skye ba nam yang yod mi 'gyur //
NK119(he)001:10881: des na chos gang la'ang thabs dang shes rab /
NK119(he)001:10882: stong nyid snying rje zung du 'jug pa dgos te /
NK119(he)001:10883: srid pa zhi ba'i mtha' gnyis la mi gnas pa'i mya ngan las 'das pa yin pa'i phyir /
NK119(he)001:10885: snying rje dang bral stong pa nyid zhugs gang //
NK119(he)001:10886: des kyang lam mchog rnyed pa ma yin no //
NK119(he)001:10887: 'on te snying rje 'ba' zhig bsgom na yang //
NK119(he)001:10888: 'khor ba 'dir gnas thar pa thob mi 'gyur //
NK119(he)001:10889: gang dag gnyis po sbyor bar nus pa de //
NK119(he)001:10890: 'khor ba mi gnas mya ngan 'das mi gnas //
NK119(he)001:10892: sems nyid ngal gso'i le'u brgyad par /
NK119(he)001:10893: shes rab ldan pa thabs kyis grol 'gyur te /
NK119(he)001:10894: ji ltar dug la sngags kyis btab pa bzhin /
NK119(he)001:10895: shes rab med na thabs kyis 'ching 'gyur te /
NK119(he)001:10896: de phyir gnas lugs rtogs pa'i shes rab bskyed //
NK119(he)001:10900: shes rab dang ldan pa rnams ni thabs kyi rnam par grol lo //
NK119(he)001:10901: shes rab dang mi ldan pa rnams ni thabs kyis yongs su 'ching ngo //
NK119(he)001:10905: mkhas rnams de yis myur du grol //
NK119(he)001:10907: de yang sdom pa gsum gyi spang blang gi spyod pa rnams la thabs zhes bya ste /
NK119(he)001:10908: snying rje chen pos zin pa la /
NK119(he)001:10909: spyod dus kyi shes pa spang blang re dog gi
NK119(he)001:10910: 'ching bas ma bcings par rang byung gi ye shes
NK119(he)001:10911: gzung ba chos kyi bdag dang 'dzin pa gang zag
NK119(he)001:10912: gi bdag gi mtha' dang bral bar rgyu 'bras bya
NK119(he)001:10913: rtsol las 'das pa'i rig pa ka dag gi ye
NK119(he)001:10914: shes rjen hu re ba 'di ka shes rab stong
NK119(he)001:10916: de ltar stong nyid snying rje zung 'jug gi ngang
NK119(he)001:10917: nas gang ltar spyod kyang rang bzhin med par sgyu
NK119(he)001:10918: ma'i dpe brgyad kyi rnam par rang grol ba nyid
NK119(he)001:10920: mthong dang thos dang reg dang dran pa dang //
NK119(he)001:10921: zas skom 'khyam dang 'gro dang 'dug pa dang //
NK119(he)001:10922: cal col gtam dang lan smras gyur pa la //
NK119(he)001:10923: sems su shes na gcig gi rnam pa las mi spyod //
NK119(he)001:10925: des na rig pa stong gsal bar med yul bral 'di nyid kyi ngo na /
NK119(he)001:10926: dgag sgrub spang blang du snang ba'i spyod pa kun kyang med bzhin du snang ba /
NK119(he)001:10933: ye grol klong yangs par brdal ba ni /
NK119(he)001:10938: ngo mtshar ba'i dgod po 'chor te /
NK119(he)001:10940: ji srid dbang po yul gyi grong la lhung ba na //
NK119(he)001:10941: de srid rang nyid las med rab tu rgyas //
NK119(he)001:10942: khyed cag da lta ci byed gar 'gro sems dang kyee //
NK119(he)001:10943: de ni shin tu dka' ba'i dgongs pas 'jug /
NK119(he)001:10945: gzung 'dzin med pa'i spyod pa la 'gal byar mi rung ste /
NK119(he)001:10947: rlung gis shing bcag lta bu na //
NK119(he)001:10948: srog bcad pa yang mi 'gal lo //
NK119(he)001:10949: chu yis sa khyer lta bu na //
NK119(he)001:10950: ma byin len yang mi 'gal lo //
NK119(he)001:10951: chu mig rlung khug lta bu na //
NK119(he)001:10952: mi tshangs spyod kyang mi 'gal lo //
NK119(he)001:10953: brag gi brag cha lta bu na //
NK119(he)001:10954: rdzun du smras kyang mi 'gal lo //
NK119(he)001:10956: drug pa dus skabs gang gtso'i dbang du bsrung ba ni /
NK119(he)001:10957: spyi dang bye brag gnyis las /
NK119(he)001:10959: sdig to mi dge'i phyogs dang tshogs pa'i gseb /
NK119(he)001:10960: 'og ma gtsor byed 'dod pas 'ben pa dang //
NK119(he)001:10961: spyod pa'i dus dang dben par gsang sngags spyad //
NK119(he)001:10962: nang ma 'dom na ma 'dres yongs rdzogs bsrung //
NK119(he)001:10963: 'dom na dgag dgos rtsi zhes mkhas rnams bzhed //
NK119(he)001:10964: de yang sdig to mi dge ba dang 'dod pas dben pa'i phyogs gnyis las /
NK119(he)001:10967: skye bo phal pa gang zag sdig to can gyi khrod dang /
NK119(he)001:10968: mang du 'dus pa'i tshogs gseb la sogs par so thar dang byang sems gtsor bsrung dgos te /
NK119(he)001:10969: gsang sngags kyi spyod pa rngam po che la gzhan
NK119(he)001:10970: mi dad cing sgro skur gyi gzhir 'gro ba dang
NK119(he)001:10971: / blo chung rnams skrag ste chos spang gi las sogs pa dang /
NK119(he)001:10972: sngags kyi gsang sgo 'chol bar 'gyur te /
NK119(he)001:10974: gang gis sems can ma dad gyur //
NK119(he)001:10975: de ni sgrim te rnam spang zhes dang /
NK119(he)001:10977: gsang ba sgrogs pa bdun pa yin //
NK119(he)001:10979: gnyis pa 'dod pas dben pa'i ltung ba rnams ni spyod pa la zhugs pa'i dus dang /
NK119(he)001:10980: dben pa'i gsang sngags kyi spyod pas skyongs te /
NK119(he)001:10982: dben par spyod la rab tu brtsom //
NK119(he)001:10984: 'jig rten ma dad pa'i phyogs gnyis kar bkag pa rnams thams cad du 'bad de bsrung bar bya'o //
NK119(he)001:10985: ltung ba nang ma 'dom par sdom ldan gyi gang zag rang bzhin du gnas pa na /
NK119(he)001:10986: gang du bshad pa'i ma 'dres yongs rdzogs su bsrung /
NK119(he)001:10987: nang 'dom na dgag dgos yongs rdzogs kyi bsrung tshul bshad pa nyid shes par bya'o //
NK119(he)001:10989: las dang po dang rnal 'byor grub thob dang //
NK119(he)001:10990: thams cad mkhyen pa'i spyod pa gang yin pa //
NK119(he)001:10991: dus tshod 'brel pa dgos zhes dus 'khor bshad //
NK119(he)001:10992: de la las dang po pa dang /
NK119(he)001:10995: thams cad mkhyen pa'i spyod pa bzhi las /
NK119(he)001:10996: dang po ni thun mtshams kyi bya ba gtso bor byed pa ste /
NK119(he)001:11006: rjes bsngo bas zin par spyod pa'o //
NK119(he)001:11009: yi ge 'bri mchod sbyin pa dang //
NK119(he)001:11010: nyan dang klog dang 'dzin pa dang //
NK119(he)001:11011: 'chad dang kha ton byed pa dang //
NK119(he)001:11012: de sems pa dang bsgom pa ste //
NK119(he)001:11013: chos spyod bcu yi bdag nyid 'di'i //
NK119(he)001:11014: bsod nams phung po dpag tu med //
NK119(he)001:11016: spyan ras gzigs kyi zhal nas /
NK119(he)001:11017: rten gsum bzhengs dang srog 'don zam pa 'dzug /
NK119(he)001:11018: mchod sbyin khrus dang bskor ba tshul khrims rnams //
NK119(he)001:11019: 'gro ba'i don la brtson pa nga yi sras //
NK119(he)001:11020: lus de bor nas bde ba can du 'gro //
NK119(he)001:11022: yang mi dge bcu spang ba dang /
NK119(he)001:11023: phar phyin bcu la 'jug par 'dod pa'ang yod do //
NK119(he)001:11024: sdom pa 'og ma gtsor byed de kun tu bzang po'i spyod pa zhes bya'o //
NK119(he)001:11025: gnyis pa nyams myong cung zad skyes pas spyod pa phyi nang gnyis su phye la /
NK119(he)001:11026: gsang spyod kyi dus su dbang /
NK119(he)001:11029: rang gzhan byin gyis rlabs pa'i dus bzhir sngags kyi
NK119(he)001:11030: sdom pa gtso bor blang pas 'og ma gnyis kyi
NK119(he)001:11031: yon tan yar ldan du 'gro ste /
NK119(he)001:11034: gsum pa brtan pa cung zad thob pas /
NK119(he)001:11035: rig pa brtul zhugs kyi spyod pa sbyor sgrol tshogs
NK119(he)001:11036: dang glu gar dngos dang yid kyi phyag rgya bcas
NK119(he)001:11037: te spros bcas spros med kyi spyod pa tshad bzung
NK119(he)001:11040: re 'ga' dur khrod zhugs nas sgron ma dag la spyad //
NK119(he)001:11041: nyam nga med pa'i sems kyis yi dwags gnas su nyal //
NK119(he)001:11042: gdol pa rnams dang 'grogs te ro yi 'khor lo drangs //
NK119(he)001:11043: 'dir bya 'di byed med pa'i spyod pa tshad du bzung mi bya //
NK119(he)001:11044: glu gar gling bu rtsed 'jo rol mo'i tshogs su 'jug /
NK119(he)001:11045: he ru ka yi gar dang drug las skyes tshogs glus //
NK119(he)001:11046: sems ni gzengs bstod cung zad skyo bar mi bya'o //
NK119(he)001:11047: rgyab tu la ba bgos shing yan lag zangs mas spras /
NK119(he)001:11048: 'khor lo ldan pa'i thor tshugs spyi bo dag tu bzung //
NK119(he)001:11049: rus pa'i dum bus yan lag thams cad brgyad byas nas //
NK119(he)001:11050: glang chen stag gi lpags pas stod dang smad dkris te //
NK119(he)001:11051: kha t+wam dril bu ldan pa lag tu thogs par byed //
NK119(he)001:11052: gsang chen smyon pa'i spyod pa lhag par byas nas ni //
NK119(he)001:11053: byi min mi bya min pa spyod pa rang shugs kyis //
NK119(he)001:11054: glang chen mtsho ru 'jug 'dra rtag tu smyon sems kyis //
NK119(he)001:11055: smad pa'i chos rnams spyad na grol bar 'da' bsnun smra //
NK119(he)001:11057: 'di la mgon po kun tu spyod pa zhes bya'o //
NK119(he)001:11060: dug las bdud rtsir bsgyur ba dang //
NK119(he)001:11061: bsad pa gso bar nus pa ste //
NK119(he)001:11062: phyogs las rnam par rgyal ba'i spyod pa zhes bya'o //
NK119(he)001:11064: dka' thub sdom pa mi bzad pa //
NK119(he)001:11066: 'dod pa'i yon tan thams cad la //
NK119(he)001:11069: gnyis pa ngo bo mdor bstan pa ni //
NK119(he)001:11070: yon tan gzhi rten so thar gang nus te //
NK119(he)001:11071: byang chub sems bskyed sngags kyi yan lag yin //
NK119(he)001:11072: smin byed dbang thob sdom gsum mig ltar bsrung //
NK119(he)001:11073: gdan gsum lha ru shes pa'i bskyed rim dang //
NK119(he)001:11074: mtshan bcas mtshan ma med pa'i rdzogs rim bsgom //
NK119(he)001:11075: de yang byang chub tu sems bskyed pas so thar
NK119(he)001:11076: gyi sdom pa ci rigs pa bsrung ba'i steng du
NK119(he)001:11077: gsang sngags kyi dam tshig ma nyams par sdom pa
NK119(he)001:11078: gsum ldan du gong du bshad pa'i tshul gyis dpral
NK119(he)001:11079: ba'i mig bzhin du bsrung bar bya ste /
NK119(he)001:11080: man ngag rin po che'i mdzod las /
NK119(he)001:11081: bsrung sdom ngo lkog med pa'i chos drug ni //
NK119(he)001:11082: bstan pa'i rtsa ba tshul khrims shes pa dang //
NK119(he)001:11083: ngan song sna khrid sdig par shes pa dang //
NK119(he)001:11084: srung sdom med na chos rtsa rul ba dang //
NK119(he)001:11085: yon tan kun gyi rten du shes pa dang //
NK119(he)001:11086: mtho ris 'dzegs pa'i skas su shes pa dang //
NK119(he)001:11087: thar bar bsgrod pa'i bzhon par shes pa yis //
NK119(he)001:11088: khrims gtsang srung la nan tan gces spras bya //
NK119(he)001:11091: rang gi go yul tsam gyis lta ba la kha g.yar /
NK119(he)001:11092: gsang sngags las 'di ltar bshad do zhes snyad tshol te /
NK119(he)001:11093: spyod pa bag med tho co rtsing pos snyad mu
NK119(he)001:11094: ge la bkal nas snam bu bor tshang byed pa
NK119(he)001:11095: lta bu ni / rnam pa thams cad du mi bya ste /
NK119(he)001:11096: bde bar gshegs pa'i bka' mdo rgyud bstan bcos thams
NK119(he)001:11097: cad nas lta ba mtho dgos spyod pa zhib dgos
NK119(he)001:11099: lta ba dma' spyod pa rtsing dgos par bshad pa gcig kyang med de /
NK119(he)001:11100: slob dpon pad+mas gcod 'grel 'phrul gyi bang mdzod du /
NK119(he)001:11101: lta ba mtho ru mi bgyi ru //
NK119(he)001:11102: chos kyi dbyings la yangs dog med //
NK119(he)001:11103: sgom pa srang la mi 'jur rgyu //
NK119(he)001:11104: dbang po tshogs drug rtog 'dod che //
NK119(he)001:11105: spyod pa zhib tu mi len rgyu //
NK119(he)001:11106: khams gsum 'khor ba g.yang sa che //
NK119(he)001:11108: spyod pa blang dor bral ba'i don rtogs kyang //
NK119(he)001:11109: 'bras bu rgyud la mngon du ma gyur bar //
NK119(he)001:11110: mdzad spyod 'di ltar bgyis na legs //
NK119(he)001:11111: thugs dgongs sangs rgyas 'drar gyur kyang //
NK119(he)001:11112: mdzad spyod mi dang mthun par mdzod //
NK119(he)001:11113: ces sogs rgya cher gsungs pa dang /
NK119(he)001:11114: dgongs 'dus lha sras zhal gdams las //
NK119(he)001:11115: lta ba rgya mtsho yangs pa'i don rtogs kyang //
NK119(he)001:11116: spyod pa kun rdzob las 'bras zhib tu gzob //
NK119(he)001:11117: sems nyid yangs pa rnal ma'i don rtogs kyang //
NK119(he)001:11118: dam tshig bsrung sdom 'dul khrims ma nyams srungs //
NK119(he)001:11120: lta ba 'phang mtho spyod pa rtsing gyur na //
NK119(he)001:11121: mu stegs rgyang 'phen lta bar mchis nyen yod //
NK119(he)001:11122: kha lta mtho la chos spyod khyad du gsod //
NK119(he)001:11123: gtan sdug dmyal ba'i gnas su gol bar mchi //
NK119(he)001:11125: rnal 'byor pa bya ba don chos nyid la blo 'byor ba la zer ba yin /
NK119(he)001:11126: tho co'i smyon spyod gang rung rung byed pa rnams rnal 'byor pa'i ming med /
NK119(he)001:11127: sngags pa bya ba thabs dang shes rab zung du
NK119(he)001:11128: 'brel pa'i lam gyis myur du sangs rgya ba la
NK119(he)001:11129: zer ba yin / brnag sems can kha chos bon gyer byed pa sngags pa'i gral khyur mi tshud /
NK119(he)001:11130: ces o rgyan chen pos gsungs so //
NK119(he)001:11131: 'o na lta ba'i bogs spyod pas 'don pa ma yin nam zhe na /
NK119(he)001:11133: spyod pa dus tshod dang 'brel pa gtso che la /
NK119(he)001:11134: gzhan du spyod pa sngas pas dngos grub la ring bar 'gyur te /
NK119(he)001:11135: rgya gar gyi grub chen dz+aa len+d+ha ri'i slob ma
NK119(he)001:11136: tsar+ya pa rus pa'i rgyan drug bgos te spyod pa
NK119(he)001:11137: la zhugs pa / slob dpon gyis da rung ma
NK119(he)001:11138: ran gsungs kyang ma nyan par song bas ri bo
NK119(he)001:11139: zhig tu skom pas nyen pa na /
NK119(he)001:11140: mi zhig thod pa khyer glang po che gnyis ded byung ba la chu slangs pas /
NK119(he)001:11141: glang 'di stag la za ma shor nga chu len du 'gro zer te song ba na /
NK119(he)001:11142: stag byung ste ma thub par glang zos /
NK119(he)001:11143: mi de byung ba na slob dpon du gyur te
NK119(he)001:11144: spyod pa ma ran pa de ltar yin gsungs nas
NK119(he)001:11145: yal / yang byon pa na bkres pas mi ro
NK119(he)001:11146: gcig 'dug pa za bsam nas mi zhig la gri
NK119(he)001:11147: yal / g.yar bas / spyod pa byed na 'di
NK119(he)001:11148: ltar gyis zhes mi de bya rog tu byas nas
NK119(he)001:11149: zos pa dang slob dpon du gyur te yal /
NK119(he)001:11150: yang chu bo chen po gcig gi 'gram du mdze
NK119(he)001:11151: mo nyam thag gcig gis spyod pa ba nga khur
NK119(he)001:11153: sdom bu pa gcig gis khur bas chu'i dbus su phyin pa na /
NK119(he)001:11155: khur ba po grub thob tsa phu ba yin /
NK119(he)001:11156: dur khrod du tshogs 'khor byed pa na /
NK119(he)001:11157: mi nag po gcig gis ngas tshogs dpon byed zer ba la ma bcol bas /
NK119(he)001:11158: tshogs grol khar bde mchog tu gyur nas /
NK119(he)001:11159: bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gros ma gnang bar spyod pa mi 'grub /
NK119(he)001:11160: skye ba 'dir mchog mi 'grub bar dor grol gsungs nas mi snang bar bshad pa bzhin no //
NK119(he)001:11161: seng ges mchong sar wa mchong pas g.yang du lhung bar grags so //
NK119(he)001:11162: de ltar sdom pa gsum gyi spyir btang ba dang dmigs kyis bsal ba shes pa des /
NK119(he)001:11163: lam bskyed pa dang rdzogs pa'i rim pa gnyis bsgom par bya ste /
NK119(he)001:11165: bskyed pa yi ni rim pa dang //
NK119(he)001:11166: rdzogs pa'i rim pa rnam pa gnyis //
NK119(he)001:11167: thabs 'di rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyis //
NK119(he)001:11168: skas kyi rim pa lta bur gsungs //
NK119(he)001:11169: zhes rim gnyis tha dad par snga ma phyi ma'i lam du 'dod pa dang /
NK119(he)001:11171: bskyed ba yi ni rim pa dang //
NK119(he)001:11172: de bzhin rdzogs pa'i rim pa ste //
NK119(he)001:11173: rim gnyis mnyam par bzhag nas ni //
NK119(he)001:11174: rdo rje can gyi chos 'chad do //
NK119(he)001:11175: zhes bskyed rdzogs zung 'jug tu bsgom par gsungs pa ste /
NK119(he)001:11178: gnyis pa ni brtan thob la dgongs pa'o //
NK119(he)001:11180: rgyu sde'i dgongs pas tha dad pa mang na'ang /
NK119(he)001:11181: gsang sngags bla med nang rgyud kyis bsgom tshul la'ang /
NK119(he)001:11182: sngags gsar ma ltar na ting nge 'dzin gsum gyis bsgom par 'dod pa yod de /
NK119(he)001:11184: sbyor ba yi ni snyoms 'jug bya //
NK119(he)001:11185: de nas dkyil 'khor rgyal po mchog /
NK119(he)001:11186: de nas yang ni las rgyal mchog /
NK119(he)001:11187: de ltar sam b+hu tir yang bshad de /
NK119(he)001:11188: gzhal yas khang nas gtso bo bskyed pa'i bar sbyor ba /
NK119(he)001:11189: 'khor spro ba nas mchod bstod bar dkyil 'khor rgyal
NK119(he)001:11190: mchog /'khor gyi bsnyen pa'i man ngag sogs las rgyal
NK119(he)001:11192: rnal 'byor yan lag drug gis bskyed pa'ang yod de /
NK119(he)001:11194: sangs rgyas gnas ni rdzogs pa dang //
NK119(he)001:11195: kun tu bzang po'i rang bzhin dang //
NK119(he)001:11196: rang gi lhag ba'i lhar bsgrub dang //
NK119(he)001:11197: mchod bstod 'dud rtsi myong la sogs //
NK119(he)001:11199: ces gzhal yas khang dang gdan bskyed par rnam snang
NK119(he)001:11200: gi yan lag lha bskyed nas spyan 'dren rjes su
NK119(he)001:11201: chags pa rdo rje sems dpa'i yan lag dbang bskur
NK119(he)001:11202: rgyas gdab pa mi bskyod pa'i yan lag bdud rtsi
NK119(he)001:11203: la longs spyod pa don 'grub kyi yan lag /
NK119(he)001:11204: bdud rtsi myong ba thig pa myong ba 'od dpag med kyi yan lag /
NK119(he)001:11205: yon tan bstod pa rin 'byung gi yan lag zhes bya'o //
NK119(he)001:11208: gong bu chu dang gzugs su gnas //
NK119(he)001:11209: gzugs la 'das bzhis rtogs par bya //
NK119(he)001:11210: zhes pas lha'i sa bon gong bur gnas pa /
NK119(he)001:11211: des don gnyis byas 'od kyi thig ler snang ba chur gnas pa /
NK119(he)001:11212: lha bskyed nas rgyas gdab par gzugs su gnas pa /
NK119(he)001:11213: des na ting nge 'dzin gsal ba rdzogs rim du bsdu ba gzugs las 'das pa ste /
NK119(he)001:11214: gnas pa bzhi'i chings 'di 'brog mi lcog rjes 'brangs dang bcas pas rtsis cher mdzad do //
NK119(he)001:11215: yang rnal 'byor gyi rgyud rnams su mngon byang lngas bskyed par gsungs te /
NK119(he)001:11216: thog mar gdan pad ma las mngon par byang chub pa /
NK119(he)001:11217: gdan gyi steng du lha'i phyag mtshan 'god pa thugs phyag mtshan las mngon par byang chub pa /
NK119(he)001:11218: de la sa bon gyis mtshan pas gsung yig 'bru las mngon par byang chub pa /
NK119(he)001:11219: de las lha bskyed pa sku yongs su rdzogs pa las mngon par byang chub pa /
NK119(he)001:11220: de la ye shes pa bstims te lha ye shes
NK119(he)001:11221: sems dpa' las mngon par byang chub pa ste phun
NK119(he)001:11222: sum tshogs pa lnga'i bkod pa rdzogs par byed pa'o
NK119(he)001:11223: // yang rnal 'byor chen po'i gzhung 'ga' zhig las /
NK119(he)001:11224: rim lnga'i man ngag gis bskyed rdzogs b+hee bar gsungs te /
NK119(he)001:11226: rlung 'byin 'jug ni bdag byin gyis brlabs pa'i rim pa /
NK119(he)001:11227: 'khor lo lngar rigs lnga'i phyag mtshan las 'od zer spro bsdu ni sna tshogs rdo rje'i rim pa /
NK119(he)001:11228: 'khor lo bzhir bde ba rgyas pas dga' bzhi'i ye
NK119(he)001:11229: shes bskyed pa ni nor bu 'gengs pa'i rim pa
NK119(he)001:11230: / phyag mtshan lnga rigs lnga yab yum du gyur
NK119(he)001:11231: te sbyor mtshams nas bdud rtsis lus khengs par bsam
NK119(he)001:11232: ste gtum mo bsgom pa ni dz+aa len+d+ha ri'i rim
NK119(he)001:11233: / pa / sku dang sa bon bsdus te mi
NK119(he)001:11234: dmigs pa'i ngang la bzhag pa ni bsam gyis mi
NK119(he)001:11235: khyab pa'i rim pa zhes bya'o //
NK119(he)001:11236: gsang sngags rnying ma ltar na'ang bskyed pa ma h+aa yo ga la /
NK119(he)001:11237: phyi snod gzhal yas khang du gsal //
NK119(he)001:11238: nang bcud lha dang lha mor gsal //
NK119(he)001:11239: zhes phyi snod 'jig rten 'byung ba rim brtsegs dang bcas te rten gzhal yas khang dang /
NK119(he)001:11240: nang bcud kyi sems can snang grags thams cad brten pa lhar gsal ba dang /
NK119(he)001:11241: lung a nu yo ga ltar na /
NK119(he)001:11243: gdal khyab lpags pas rab g.yogs keng rus mkhar //
NK119(he)001:11244: sha khrag phung po 'dus ba'i gzhal yas khang //
NK119(he)001:11245: zhes lus gzhal yas khang dang /
NK119(he)001:11246: snang ba'i ngo bo pad+ma badz+ra rtsal //
NK119(he)001:11247: stong pa'i bdag nyid lha lcam gsang ba'i yum //
NK119(he)001:11248: zhes sems dang sems byung lhar gsal ba dang //
NK119(he)001:11249: rdzogs pa chen po a ti yo ga ltar na //
NK119(he)001:11250: rgyud bcu bdun la sogs par //
NK119(he)001:11251: rig pa ye shes dkyil yin te //
NK119(he)001:11252: sems byung rtog tshogs 'khor du gsal //
NK119(he)001:11253: zhes rig pa skad cig ma lha dang /
NK119(he)001:11254: sems byung rnams 'khor dang gzhal yas khang du gsal ba'o //
NK119(he)001:11256: sngon du de bzhin nyid dang /
NK119(he)001:11258: rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin gsum gyis khog phub te mngon
NK119(he)001:11259: byang lngas rten dang brten pa'i dkyil 'khor 'khor lo
NK119(he)001:11260: gsal btab nas spyan 'dren mchod bstod la sogs cho
NK119(he)001:11268: dngos kyi rnam pa gsal ba rnam dag dran pa ste /
NK119(he)001:11270: rten dang brten pa gsal la ma 'dres par bskyed pa la /
NK119(he)001:11271: brda dang don gyi rnam dag dran pas a 'thas dang 'khrul 'dzin las grol ba /
NK119(he)001:11275: dran rtog thugs kyi khyer so gsum dang ma bral
NK119(he)001:11276: ba'i bskyed rdzogs zung 'jug tu nyams su len pa'o
NK119(he)001:11277: // de yang bsnyen bsgrub yan lag bzhis bskyed tshul gsar rnying mtshungs te /
NK119(he)001:11279: bsnyen pa'i dam tshig rab sbyor ba //
NK119(he)001:11280: byang chub mchog ni bsgom par bya //
NK119(he)001:11281: nye bar bsgrub pa sgrub mchog la //
NK119(he)001:11282: rdo rje'i skye mched rnam par dpyad //
NK119(he)001:11283: sngags kyi bdag po bsgom pa yis //
NK119(he)001:11284: bsgrub pa'i tshe na bskul bar bya //
NK119(he)001:11285: sgrub pa chen po byed pa'i tshe //
NK119(he)001:11286: dbu rgyan la ni rigs bdag bsam //
NK119(he)001:11287: rdo rje rnam bzhi 'di dag gis //
NK119(he)001:11288: tha mal pa yi bsnyen pa bya //
NK119(he)001:11291: mnga' ris pa pad+ma dbang rgyal 'di nyid kyi zhal nas /
NK119(he)001:11292: bdag nyid lha ru gsal ba ni /
NK119(he)001:11293: bsnyen pa'i yan lag dang po yin //
NK119(he)001:11294: skye mched mkha' gsang byin brlabs pa //
NK119(he)001:11295: nye bar bsnyen cing bsgrub pa yin //
NK119(he)001:11296: de la ye shes spyan drangs pa //
NK119(he)001:11297: de nyid dbang bskur rigs rgyas gdab //
NK119(he)001:11298: sgrub pa chen po bshad pa yin //
NK119(he)001:11300: de yang gdan gsum tshang ba'i lha ni nang rgyud gsum la yod de /
NK119(he)001:11301: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa las /
NK119(he)001:11302: rdo rje phung po'i yan lag ni /
NK119(he)001:11303: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas lnga ru grags //
NK119(he)001:11304: zhes phung po lnga rigs lngar gsal ba de bzhin gshegs pa'i gdan /
NK119(he)001:11305: sa chu spyan dang m+aa ma ki /
NK119(he)001:11306: me rlung gos dkar dam tshig sgrol //
NK119(he)001:11307: nam mkha' dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma //
NK119(he)001:11308: zhes 'byung ba lnga yum lngar 'du shes pa rig ma'i gdan /
NK119(he)001:11309: skye mched khams rnams mang po kun //
NK119(he)001:11310: lha dang lha mo'i ngo bo nyid //
NK119(he)001:11311: ces mig sogs skye mched rnams sa snying la sogs
NK119(he)001:11312: par gsal byang chub sems dpa'i gdan te gzhan la'ang
NK119(he)001:11313: de bzhin du shes par bya ste 'di ni dpal
NK119(he)001:11314: sa skya ba rjes 'brang dang bcas pa'i chos skad
NK119(he)001:11315: yang dag pa'o // de yang lha longs spyod rdzogs
NK119(he)001:11316: sku gdan gsum tshang ba'i sgo nas smin byed rnams
NK119(he)001:11317: la dbang dang ma tshang ba'i sgo nas rjes gnang
NK119(he)001:11318: yin zhes mkhas grub ye shes rgyal mtshan gsungs so
NK119(he)001:11319: yang dag pa'o // // rdzogs rim la'ang mtshan ma dang bcas pa zhi gnas kyi bsam gtan dang /
NK119(he)001:11320: mtshan ma med pa lhag mthong gi shes rab gnyis
NK119(he)001:11321: zung 'jug tu nyams su len par bya ste spyod
NK119(he)001:11322: 'jug las / zhi gnas rab tu brtan pa'i lhag mthong gis //
NK119(he)001:11323: nyon mongs rnam par rtog pa gzhil byed de //
NK119(he)001:11324: thog mar zhi gnas btsal bya de yang ni //
NK119(he)001:11325: 'jig rten zhen pa med la mngon dgas 'grub //
NK119(he)001:11327: zhi gnas ni snga phyi'i rtogs pa 'gag pa'i bar
NK119(he)001:11328: gyi rtog med kyi bsam gtan mar me rlung gis
NK119(he)001:11329: ma bskyod pa ltar gar gtad du sems yer gnas
NK119(he)001:11330: pa ni sems las su rung ba'i zhi gnas bde
NK119(he)001:11331: gsal mi rtog pa'i nyams dang bcas pa ste /
NK119(he)001:11332: de la'ang zhen pa dang chags pa med par gnas pa'o //
NK119(he)001:11333: lhag mthong ni de dus kyi rig pa dri ma
NK119(he)001:11334: med pa stong gsal nam mkha' ltar sgrib byed dang
NK119(he)001:11335: gral ba rjen ne hrig ge sal le ba 'di
NK119(he)001:11336: yin te / 'di'i gdangs sam rtsal las sems byung
NK119(he)001:11337: nyon mongs pa'i rtog tshogs ji ltar shar yang rjes
NK119(he)001:11338: yin te / su mi mthud / ched du mi
NK119(he)001:11339: dgag par rig pa dri ma med pa'i rang zhal
NK119(he)001:11341: rnam rtog rten med rang sang rang yal la sogs
NK119(he)001:11342: te rba rlabs rgya mtshor yal ba ltar 'gyur te
NK119(he)001:11343: / de ltar sal ler gnas pa'i cha ni bsam gtan yin te /
NK119(he)001:11344: khams gong mar skye ba'i rgyu las ma yin pas /
NK119(he)001:11345: gnas bdo pa'i rig pa ngo bo stong sang nge /
NK119(he)001:11347: gsal stong du rjen ne hu re ba rang gnas
NK119(he)001:11348: kyi bsam gtan dang ldan pa de nyid shes rab
NK119(he)001:11349: stong pa nyid ces bya ba ste de'i ngang la
NK119(he)001:11350: bzo bcos dang 'dzin zhen med par bzhag pas sku
NK119(he)001:11351: gsung thugs rang chas lhun grub kyi sa la gtan
NK119(he)001:11353: gsum pa 'bras bu nges pas 'gag bsdam pa ni /
NK119(he)001:11355: nye rgyu'i spyod pas rim bzhin mtshams spyor na //
NK119(he)001:11356: 'adi'am 'chi kha dang ni bar do dang //
NK119(he)001:11357: rang bzhin sprul sku'i zhing du rdzogs sangs rgyas //
NK119(he)001:11358: byang chub la nye rgyu'i spyod pa gang gis sgrub
NK119(he)001:11359: pa cho ga'i yan lag theg chen la mos shing
NK119(he)001:11360: blo gros dang brtson 'grus ldan pas /
NK119(he)001:11361: ji ltar sgrub pa thabs kyi yan lag zhi gnas dang lhag mthong /
NK119(he)001:11362: gnyis med sgrub pa ngo bo'i yan lag zhi lhag
NK119(he)001:11363: zung 'jug gi nyams len dbang po dang brtson 'grus
NK119(he)001:11365: yang rab tshe 'dir grol ba ste /
NK119(he)001:11366: gsang sngags thun mong ltar na dag pa mkha' spyod dang /
NK119(he)001:11367: rnying ma ltar na 'pho ba chen po'i sku 'grub pa'o //
NK119(he)001:11368: dbang po rab 'bring tha gsum 'chi kha dang /
NK119(he)001:11369: chos nyid srid pa'i bar do la ji ltar grol ba'i tshul bstan pa gsum las /
NK119(he)001:11371: skyes bu gang zhig 'byung ba'i thim rim rnams rdzogs
NK119(he)001:11372: nas khams dkar dmar dang srog rlung gsum snying khar
NK119(he)001:11373: 'dus pas nyon mongs pa rang bzhin gyi rtog pa
NK119(he)001:11374: brgyad cu 'gag ste bde gsal mi rtog pa'i ye
NK119(he)001:11375: shes rang rig rjen ce re ba rnam rtog thams
NK119(he)001:11376: cad bral ba 'char te ngos zin pas bar do
NK119(he)001:11377: med par chos kyi skur sangs rgya ba ste /
NK119(he)001:11379: lus can rnams ni 'chi ba'i tshe //
NK119(he)001:11380: bdud rtsi zla ba thur du 'gro //
NK119(he)001:11381: steng du nyi rdul sgra gcan dang //
NK119(he)001:11382: rnam shes srid pa'i mtshan nyid do //
NK119(he)001:11384: 'od gsal de la sems zin na //
NK119(he)001:11385: bar do med par mya ngan dang //
NK119(he)001:11386: sdug bsngal kun las nges par grol //
NK119(he)001:11389: bar do dang po ngos ma zin na /
NK119(he)001:11390: rig pa dbang po'i sgo las phyir don pa dang
NK119(he)001:11391: mnyam du gzhi snang lhun grub chos nyid bar do'i
NK119(he)001:11393: 'ja' 'od zer gsum gyi klong nas rgyal ba'i dkyil
NK119(he)001:11394: 'khor bsam gyis mi khyab pa 'char ba de dag
NK119(he)001:11395: rang snang du ngo shes pas skad cig la bar
NK119(he)001:11396: do dag pa longs spyod rdzogs pa'i skur sangs rgya
NK119(he)001:11398: de las ngos ma zin pa na /
NK119(he)001:11399: dag pa'i snang ba de dag 'ja' ltar du yal ba'i mod las /
NK119(he)001:11400: rang gar 'chi ba'i gnas khang yo byad nor rdzas la sogs pa da lta bzhin du mthong ste /
NK119(he)001:11401: shi bar shes nas sdug bsngal dpag tu med cing /
NK119(he)001:11402: ma nges pa'i rtags drug /'jigs pa'i dgra bzhi /
NK119(he)001:11403: ya nga ba'i g.yang sa gsum la sogs pas mnar ba na /
NK119(he)001:11404: dag pa'i zhing khams lnga dang mkha' spyod 'og min
NK119(he)001:11405: sprul sku'i zhing du 'dun pa gtad pas zhing der
NK119(he)001:11406: bardzusa te skyes nas sa lam rnams rim gyis bsgrod
NK119(he)001:11407: de sprul pa'i skur sangs rgya ba'o //
NK119(he)001:11408: 'di dag gi rnam bzhag rgyas par bla ma dam
NK119(he)001:11409: pas mdzad pa'i bar do'i dmar khrid las rtogs par
NK119(he)001:11410: bya'o // gzhan yang sangs rgyas kyi yon tan sku /
NK119(he)001:11411: brten pa ye shes kyi rnam bzhag la sogs pa'ang gzhan du shes par bya'o //
NK119(he)001:11412: de ltar legs bshad tshangs pa'i mdun du b+hi //
NK119(he)001:11413: 'gro khams rgya mtsho'i bar du sgrog pa yis //
NK119(he)001:11414: tshig don gnas la rmongs pas gnyid log pa //
NK119(he)001:11415: de dag rigs kyi yon tan sad par shog /
NK119(he)001:11416: tshul khrims phun tshogs chos 'dul khang bzang rtser //
NK119(he)001:11417: rgyal sras spyod pa'i rgyal mtshan nam mkhar snyegs //
NK119(he)001:11418: gsang sngags zab don yid bzhin tog gis spras //
NK119(he)001:11419: gang gi dpal la dgos 'dod char dbab shog /
NK119(he)001:11420: rnam grol sdom gsum yid 'ong push+ka ri //
NK119(he)001:11421: don gnyis sbrang rtsi'i lding khang kun nas bkram //
NK119(he)001:11422: mchog thun ma la ya'i bsung las dgengs pas //
NK119(he)001:11423: skal ldan b+h+ra ma ra kun tshim byed shog /
NK119(he)001:11424: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i lam gyi cha lag
NK119(he)001:11425: sdom pa gsum rnam par nges pa'i 'grel pa rnam
NK119(he)001:11427: sdom gsum spyir bshad pa'i rim par phye ba zhes /
NK119(he)001:11428: tha ma ste lnga pa gtan la dbab zin to //
NK119(he)001:11429: spyi don gsum pa da ni mthar phyin pa mjug gi don la gsum ste /
NK119(he)001:11430: gzhan lugs phal cher ma dag par bstan pa /
NK119(he)001:11431: rang lugs dag par bstan cing dge ba bsngo ba /
NK119(he)001:11432: mtshan bstan pas mtha' bsdu ba'o //
NK119(he)001:11434: snyigs ma lnga bdo ba'i dus /
NK119(he)001:11435: deng sang ma sbyangs mu cor smra ba brgyas //
NK119(he)001:11436: rang gi ye shes rdul tsam ma rtogs par //
NK119(he)001:11437: rang bzo'i cho gas rmongs rnams tshim pa'i dus //
NK119(he)001:11438: skyabs de bsam gyin snying nas mchi ma dku //
NK119(he)001:11439: de yang deng sang gi dus gangs can gyi ljongs
NK119(he)001:11440: 'dir mdo rgyud dang mi mthun pa'i rang bzo'i cho
NK119(he)001:11441: ga sdom gsum gyi gzhung dang mi mthun pa du
NK119(he)001:11442: ma 'dug ces / bdag nyid chen po sa skya pan+di tas sdom gsum rab dbyer gsungs pa yang /
