NK119(he)001:11444: lus sems gnyis ji srid 'tsho ba'i bar zhes dang /
NK119(he)001:11445: yod pa'i dge ba zhes dang /
NK119(he)001:11448: bcas pa dang rang bzhin gyi kha na ma tho ba gnyis gcig par 'dod pa dang /
NK119(he)001:11450: bsnyen gnas nyin par bsrungs ba sang nyin 'bul zhes pa dang /
NK119(he)001:11453: byams snying rje thabs mkhas la ma ltos par gshis
NK119(he)001:11454: kyi dge ba yin zhes pa dang mdo bskul ring
NK119(he)001:11455: mo dang / zhang g.yu brag pas rgyu la 'bras gnas dang /
NK119(he)001:11456: chos dbyings bsngo rgyur 'dod pa dang /
NK119(he)001:11457: rgod tshang bas gnas pa'i dge ba zhes dang /
NK119(he)001:11458: stag lung pas rang bzhin gyi dge ba zhes dang /
NK119(he)001:11459: zhang mtshal pa dang bkag phyag pa la gsung rab tshig gi na ya zhes dang /
NK119(he)001:11460: bal po'i 'dul 'dzin dang 'dul bstod lugs pa kha cig /
NK119(he)001:11461: bsngo ba byed tshe ril bas chu sbreng ba dang /
NK119(he)001:11462: dge bshes phyag sor ba la sogs pas rmi lam du sems bskyed blang zhes pa dang /
NK119(he)001:11463: 'bri khung bas bdag gzhan barje mi rung dang /
NK119(he)001:11464: don dam sems bskyed cho gas blang ba dang /
NK119(he)001:11465: bka' brgyud pa phag mo'i byin rlabs kyi chos sgo 'byed pa dang /
NK119(he)001:11466: ye gsang yin zhes pa la sogs te ma dag pa du ma dang /
NK119(he)001:11467: tha na tsa ri da dang /
NK119(he)001:11468: ri bo gangs can ti ser 'dod pa bkag pa la sogs pa mtha' yas pa gsungs pa ltar /
NK119(he)001:11469: ma dag pa du ma mthong bas yid skyo bas
NK119(he)001:11470: mchi ma 'khrug ste sangs rgyas 'ba' zhig la ra
NK119(he)001:11473: bdag ni 'jigs pas rnam skrags nas //
NK119(he)001:11474: kun tu bzang la bdag nyid 'bul //
NK119(he)001:11475: 'jam dpal dbyangs la'ang bdag nyid kyi //
NK119(he)001:11476: bdag gi lus ni 'bul bar bgyi //
NK119(he)001:11477: thugs rje'i spyod pa ma 'khrul ba //
NK119(he)001:11478: spyan ras gzigs dbang de la yang //
NK119(he)001:11481: sa pan gyis phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas la 'phrin yig mdzad pa lta bu'i rang bzhin no //
NK119(he)001:11482: 'o na thams cad mkhyen pa sa pan gyis mdzad pa'i sdom gsum rab dbye lta bus chog mod /
NK119(he)001:11483: 'di brtsams mi dgos so zhe na /
NK119(he)001:11484: bdag nyid chen po des ni rgyu mtshan nyid dang /
NK119(he)001:11485: 'bras bu gsang sngags kyi chos thams cad sdom pa gsum dang ma 'brel ba med pas /
NK119(he)001:11486: de'i skabs kyi ma dag pa thams cad sun phyung
NK119(he)001:11487: ba chos dang chos ma yin par rnam par 'byed
NK119(he)001:11488: pa'i spyi chings su mdzad pa las /
NK119(he)001:11490: sdom pa'i rnam grangs la sogs pa las chog dang /
NK119(he)001:11492: dbang bzhi'i gzhung la sogs nas rtogs dgos par mdzad pa'i phyir ro //
NK119(he)001:11493: 'on kyang sdom gsum gyi bka' dang bstan bcos ji snyed mchis na 'dis ci bya zhe na /
NK119(he)001:11494: de ltar lags kyang bde blag tu rtogs pa'i ched du tshig la don 'dus par bshad kyi /
NK119(he)001:11495: gzhan du bde bar gshegs pas sngar ma bstan pa'i gzhung gcig 'dir 'chad pa min te /
NK119(he)001:11496: de yin na nang pa sangs rgyas pa'i lugs las gzhan zhig lags par mi 'gyur ram /
NK119(he)001:11499: sngon chad ma grags pa'ang 'dir brjod min //
NK119(he)001:11500: sdeb sbyor mkhas pa'ang bdag la yod min te //
NK119(he)001:11501: de phyir gzhan don bdag gis 'dir ma byas //
NK119(he)001:11502: rang gi yid la b+hee phyir ngas 'di brtsam //
NK119(he)001:11504: des na rgyu mtshan gzhan yang /
NK119(he)001:11505: mdo sngags lam rnams mu med 'gro ba'i phyir //
NK119(he)001:11506: tshang la ma nor lam 'di rgyal bas gsungs //
NK119(he)001:11507: gangs can 'di na de dag phyogs rer 'dzin //
NK119(he)001:11508: gcig tu sems kyang sdom gsum ming tsam lus //
NK119(he)001:11509: mdo sngags mu med pa dag kyang gang zag gcig
NK119(he)001:11510: gi lam gyi chos su ma tshang ba med par
NK119(he)001:11511: 'dus pa las / la la zhig 'dul ba la zhugs kyang byang sems bsdus mi shes /
NK119(he)001:11512: de bzhin du byang chub sems dpa'i theg par zhugs
NK119(he)001:11513: kyang gsang sngags la sogs pa kun 'gal bar 'dzin
NK119(he)001:11514: nas gcig tu bsdus mi shes pa dag la phan
NK119(he)001:11515: pa'i phyir / gang zag gcig gis ji ltar nyams su blang tshul ston pa yin te /
NK119(he)001:11516: rdzogs pa chen po sems nyid ngal gso las /
NK119(he)001:11517: deng sang phal gyi blo mig ma dag pas //
NK119(he)001:11518: sngags dang pha rol phyin gzhung so so'i lam //
NK119(he)001:11519: 'gal bar 'dzin nas gcig tu sdud mi shes //
NK119(he)001:11520: de phyir de dag phyogs ris mig can yin //
NK119(he)001:11521: 'dir ni rgyu 'bras theg pa'i zab don mchog /
NK119(he)001:11522: gcig tu bsdus nas nyams su len pa'i thabs //
NK119(he)001:11525: bstan bcos 'di ni mkhas grub du ma'i legs bshad las /
NK119(he)001:11526: sgrim po'i blo yis phyogs gcig dag tu bkod //
NK119(he)001:11527: de phyir nongs pa'i dri ma med snyam rloms //
NK119(he)001:11528: dge des kun gzigs go 'phang myur thob shog /
NK119(he)001:11530: bstan bcos 'dir ni ma rtogs pa dang log par rtog pa 'ga' yang med de /
NK119(he)001:11531: bde bar gshegs pa'i bka' dang /
NK119(he)001:11532: mkhas shing grub pa brnyes pa'i bstan bcos du ma
NK119(he)001:11533: la thos bsam byas pa'i mthu las byung ba'i phyir
NK119(he)001:11534: / des na dge ba 'dis 'gro ba sems can
NK119(he)001:11535: thams cad kyis myur du rnam pa thams cad mkhyen
NK119(he)001:11536: pa sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang thob par gyur cig
NK119(he)001:11537: / ces pa ste / rgyud bla ma las /
NK119(he)001:11538: de ltar yid ches lung dang rig pa la //
NK119(he)001:11539: brten nas bdag nyid 'ba' zhig dag phyir dang //
NK119(he)001:11540: gang dag mos dge phun tshogs dang ldan blo //
NK119(he)001:11541: de dag rjes su bzung phyir 'di bshad do //
NK119(he)001:11545: sdom gsum rnam nges tshig gi rim par phye ba 'di yang /
NK119(he)001:11546: gangs ri'i phreng bas bskor ba'i yul ljongs /
NK119(he)001:11547: lho phyogs kyi rgyud du nges par 'byung ba'i bsam pa can /
NK119(he)001:11548: bod la'ang yul gling chen po gsum las /
NK119(he)001:11549: stod mnga' ris su byon pa'i gter ston /
NK119(he)001:11550: pad+ma dbang gi rgyal pos bkod pa yongs su rdzogs so //
NK119(he)001:11552: thog ma bar dang mthar dge ba zhes dge'o gsum gzhan du 'byung ba las /
NK119(he)001:11553: 'dir sdom gsum rnam nges la dge'o //
NK119(he)001:11555: sdeb sbyor rin chen 'byung gnas las //
NK119(he)001:11556: shin tu don dang ldan pa la //
NK119(he)001:11557: tshig gcig lan gnyis brjod par bya //
NK119(he)001:11559: rang don chos sku 'grub pas dge ba dang /
NK119(he)001:11560: gzhan don gzugs sku 'grub pas dge ba gnyis yin par dam chos pad+ma dkar po las gsungs so //
NK119(he)001:11561: de ltar rgyal ba'i gsung rab rab 'byams rgya mtsho'i skabs gsum lam yangs par /
NK119(he)001:11562: legs bshad sdom gsum rta bdun dbang po ma lus skye dgu'i 'dren byed mchog /
NK119(he)001:11563: rab gsal tshig don sgrib med rnam bkra'i snang ba phyogs kyi mthar khyab pas //
NK119(he)001:11564: skal bzang blo yi pad+mo ches cher rab bzhad thar gling snang byed yin //
NK119(he)001:11565: grangs med rgyal ba snga phyir gshegs pa'i shul //
NK119(he)001:11566: rgyu 'bras theg pa kun gyi nyams len gnad //
NK119(he)001:11567: rnam grol byang chub bsgrod pa'i lam bzang mchog /
NK119(he)001:11568: sdom gsum rnam nges rnam bshad 'di byas so //
NK119(he)001:11569: gang zhig rtsom pa po dag chos nyid bden mthong min yang rang ngo mthong lo tsam /
NK119(he)001:11570: yi dam gnang ba ma thob na'ang pad 'byung gnyis pa'i bka' yi gnang ba thob //
NK119(he)001:11571: rig gnas lnga mkhas min kyang gsung rab rgya mtsho'i gnas la blo kha 'dud pa skad //
NK119(he)001:11572: mkhas grub bshes gnyen mang po'i zhabs pad brten byas brgyud pa'i man ngag yod mchis grags //
NK119(he)001:11573: bdag blo'i rnam dpyod yid mkhar thos bsam chu yi shing rta rab tu 'khrigs //
NK119(he)001:11574: don zab dbyar gyi rnga gsang cher sgrog mos dge phun tshogs glog phreng can //
NK119(he)001:11575: legs bshad bdud rtsi'i zegs mas skal bzang blo gros myu gu rab rgyas nas //
NK119(he)001:11576: gang zhig chos kyi phongs pa'i bru tsha ba dag ming gi mthar byed yin //
NK119(he)001:11577: brtson pa rgya mtsho'i nor 'dzin las 'thon rnam dkar bsod nams rkang 'thung mchog /
NK119(he)001:11578: lhag bsam yal 'dab rab rgyas rang gzhan don gnyis grib bsil kun nas g.yo //
NK119(he)001:11579: zab don 'bras mang dang bcas kun nas dga' ba'i pad+mo 'dzum pa can //
NK119(he)001:11580: don gnyis 'dab bzang yongs kyis dga' bas bstan slad kho bos 'di skad do //
NK119(he)001:11581: dge ba de yis 'di nas chos bzod ma thob bar //
NK119(he)001:11582: bde gshegs gsung rab mdzod dang nam yang mi 'bral zhing //
NK119(he)001:11583: rgyal dang rgyal ba'i sras kyis rnam kun rjes bzung ste //
NK119(he)001:11584: skye dgu 'dren pa'i dpal dang mgon du bdag gyur cig /
NK119(he)001:11585: gang yang bcas dang rang bzhin kha na ma tho ba //
NK119(he)001:11586: sdom pa gsum dang 'gal ba'i las rnams kun byang nas //
NK119(he)001:11587: bslab gsum spang rtogs rab rgyas mchog mthun grub brnyes nas //
NK119(he)001:11588: tshe des byang chub mchog gi go 'phang thob par shog /
NK119(he)001:11589: slar yang 'gro khams ji srid bar //
NK119(he)001:11590: sprul dang yang sprul sgyu ma'i gar //
NK119(he)001:11591: 'gro re'i don du bdag mchis te //
NK119(he)001:11592: kun mkhyen sa la dkri bar shog /
NK119(he)001:11593: sangs rgyas bstan pa'i rdzing bu bstan 'dzin pad+mo'i tshogs kyis yongs gang zhing /
NK119(he)001:11594: skye dgu ngang mo'i tshogs rnams nyer 'tshe med par chos bzhin spyod pas rgyu /
NK119(he)001:11595: legs tshogs rten 'brel rnam dag dbang po'i gzhu sbreng rang gzhan rgyud la bkram /
NK119(he)001:11596: don gnyis lhun grub sbrang char sil mas 'gro kun dga' ba'i dpal bskyed shog //
NK119(he)001:11597: ces sdom pa gsum rnam par nges pa'i 'grel pa rnam grol lam bzang zhes bya ba 'di yang /
NK119(he)001:11598: rig 'dzin chen po pad ma sam b+ha wa dang dbyer ma mchis pa'i /
NK119(he)001:11599: dpa' bo dang d+aak+ki'i tshogs dpon grub pa'i dbang phyug rig 'dzin bdud 'dul rdo rje dang /
NK119(he)001:11600: mthu stobs dbang phyug klong gsal snying po dang /
NK119(he)001:11601: b+aee ro tsa na dang ngo nyid dbyer med pa pad ma gar dbang 'gyur med rdo rje dang /
NK119(he)001:11602: sprul pa'i sku mchog mi 'gyur rdo rje ste /
NK119(he)001:11603: gter ston bzhi'i zhabs kyi pad mo la spyi bos btud cing /
NK119(he)001:11604: smin grol gyi bdud rtsi thob pa /
NK119(he)001:11605: gzhan yang mkhas grub du ma'i gsung gi bdud rtsis legs par 'byor ba /
NK119(he)001:11606: kun mkhyen pad ma blo gros kyi rigs chos kyi brgyud pa 'dzin pa /
NK119(he)001:11607: shar phyogs mdo khams stag bu'i yul du skyes pa'i
NK119(he)001:11608: tshangs spyod kyi dge bsnyen sems dpa' chen po gsum
NK119(he)001:11611: rang gis brjed tho zin bris 'ga' zhig snga sor bris pa las /
NK119(he)001:11613: rtsa ba'i bla ma k+aa ma la bir+y+aa d+ha ras /
NK119(he)001:11614: gsung gis mthar thug par bris zhes yang yang bka' stsal pa spyi bor mnos te /
NK119(he)001:11615: bar khrod smin grol chos lding gi gtsug lag khang chen por sbyar ba dge'o //
NK119(he)001:11617: bstan bcos rtsa ba'i brgyud pa ni /
NK119(he)001:11618: mnga' ris pa pad ma dbang rgyal /
NK119(he)001:11619: gnubs dbon byams pa chos kyi rgyal mtshan /
NK119(he)001:11621: dge slong sangs rgyas rdo rje /
NK119(he)001:11622: stag bla pad ma rdo rje dang pad ma rig
